plink (ˈpilinki) v. plinked; plinking; plinks shanqarid yar, sida laba birood ama quraaradood is taabtay; dhihid ama dhalaw-dhalawlayn. e.g. We could hear the piano plinking away in our next next door. -plinker n.; -plink n.

proinsulin (ˌparaw’insalan) n. bilawga abuuranka hore ee dheecaanka insulin; waxaana sameeya ganaca (pancreas), la aanteedna cudurka macaanka (type 1 diabetes).  

recognition sequence n. ogaanshaha rugaha susunka  hidda-side (genetic sequences) meesha restriction enzymes cadadak DNA.

suicide gene n. hidda-side (gene) ku sababa in unuug isdilo ama ku dhinto habka apoptosis.

supercoil (ˈsupar,koyal) n. labada xirig (double helix) ee DNA oo sida qaabka xarafka 8 isku laba-qoolaaba. -supercoil v.

transgenic (taraanis’jenik) adj. la xariira noole hidda-sidihiisa lagu baddalay hidde-side isir kale: transgenic plants or animals. -transgenic n.

transposon (taraanis’pawzaan) n. jaan ama cad ka mid ah DNA oo u guura meel kale oo ka mid ah hidda-sidaha (genome).

ultraorthodox (ˌaltara’ortha,dhaakis) adj. aad xag-jir diineed u ah, siiba Yahuud: very orthodox.

homeobox (ˈhawmiya,baakis) n. koox hidda-sidayaal oo qaabeeya abuuranka noolayaal dhawr-unugyayaal ah (multicellular organisms) kalana duwan (morphogenesis).

homeotic (ˌhawmi’yaadhik) adj. la xariira hidda-sidayaal sare oo jiheeya koritaanka meelo jirka ka mid ah ama qaab-dhiskooda: homeotic genes.

homeosis (ˌhawmi’yawsis) n. also homoeosis qaabaysmadka dhirta ama qaab-dhismeed noolaha ama xibin jirka ka mid ah oo qaab kale yeelata: homeotic change.

X-ray crystallography n. hab taxliilineed (falanqayneed) oo lagu jajabsho (diffraction) nudo ilays (x-ray) si loo helo caddaymahood ama qaab-dhismeedkooda.

academic journal n. eeg scholarly journal.

alphanumeric (ˌaalfanu’merik) adj. also alphanumerical (ˌaalfanu’merikal) ka kooban xarfo, tirooyin, iyo badanaa summado: alphanumeric characters. -alphanumerically (ˌaalfanu’meriklii) adv.; -alphanumerics (ˌaalfanu’merikis) plural noun.

annotated (ˈaana,teydhidh) adj. faahfaahin ku dara; sharraxaad raaciya: annotated lists/edition.

bibliographic record n. diiwaangalin caddaysa xogo qoraallo tixraaceed (bibliographic information) aruuris ah; kana mid yihiin (call number, author, title, publication information, physical description, subject headings, etc.).

book drop n., pl. book drops meel lagu rido buugta lagu soo celiyo maktabad.

book truck n. gaariyoole (cart) buugta ku soo noqotay maktabad lugu geeyo meelahoodii (shelves).

Boolean operator n. waa “AND”, “OR” and “NOT” oo la adeegto markii xog laga baarayo maktabad si loo soo koobo. e.g. teen ‘OR’ youth ‘AND’ American ‘NOT’ Somalia.

Boolean searching n. eeg Boolean operator.

bound periodicals n. cadad jariirad ama joornaal (magazines and journals) soobaxyadoodii hore buug ahaan la iskugu dhajiyay, isku tiradii lagu raadinjiray (call number) ayana leeyihiin.

circulation desk n. miiska xoghaynta maktabad oo laga hubiyo buugta lala baxayo ama la soo celinayo, iyo haddii daahid ganaax jiro (check out and return books, pay fines).

classification system n. habab loo kooxeeyo loona habeeyo xog si loo barbardhigo xog kale.

proximity operators n. erayo cayiman oo ugu dhadhaw erayga laa raadiynayo oo xariir ka dhexeeyo; inta badan waxaa la adeegtaa ADJ, NEAR, WITH oo u taagan adjacent, near, iyo within. e.g. Use South ADJ America for the phrase South America.

reference library n. 1 buug aruuris ah oo inta badan isku ah maaddo gaar ah (particular subject). 2 maktabad oogolaata in buugta lagu isticmaalo gudaheeda, laakin aan lala bixikarin (not taken out).

bunker fuel n. or bunker oil n. noocyo shidaal culus oo kala duwan, loona isticmaalo maraakiibta.

bunker oil n. eeg bunker fuel.

centrifugal pump n. qalab (pump) ku butaaciya dareere wareeg xooggan. kale loogu yeeraa impeller.

casinghead gas n. neef dabiici ah oo ceel shidaal lagala soo saaro shidaalka ceeriin.

CF/D n. abbr. cubic feet per day; tirada dhaqsaha qulqulka ceel shidaal ama dhuun (pipeline).

million cubic feet per day n. abbr. MMcf/d halbeeg cabbir oo lagu muujiyo inta dareere (gas, water etc.) la isticmaalay, la soo saaray, ama lagu qulquliyay dhuumo maalintii.

phylogenetics noun plural but singular laan ka mid ah cilmiga oo gooni u eegta xiriirka ka dhexeeya abuuranka, kuna salaysan xariirka hidda-sidayaalkooda ay muujiyeen DNA iyo RNA.

phylogenetic tree n. jaantus muujiya hidda-sidaha iyo xariirka noolaha ka dhexeeya.

haplography (haa’palaagrafii) n. xaraf qoraal ahaan khalad looga booday, sida mispell ee misspell.

haplotype (ˈhaaplaw,taayp) n. kooxo astaamo hidda-sidayaal (alleles) oo israaca, watana hal hidda-side oo aad iskugu dhaw iskuguna xiran.

histocompatibility (ˈhis,tawkam,paadha’biladhii) n., pl. histocompatibilities xaalad nuduhu (tissues) is ogolaadaan si habboonna iskugu baxaan ama abuurmaan. Barbardhig major histocompatibility complex.

HLA (ˌeej,el,eey) n. eeg major histocompatibility complex.  

biallelic (ˈbaaya’liilik) adj. la xariira ama saameeya astaamaha (alleles) iyo hidda-sidaha.

haplogroup n. waxay sahashaa in qofka dumarka ah dib ugu abtirsado ayeeyooyinkii hore (hooyo, hooyadeed, ayeydeed, abootadeed, iwm.) ama ninku dib ugu abtirsado dhanka awoowayaalkii hore (aabbe, aabbihiis, awowgiis, abkawgiis, iwm.); taas oo muujisa sida bulshada aduunku isku dhexgashay.

compressor station n. haan isku cadaadisa mugga hawo.

condensate (ˈkaandan,seyt) n. neef (gas) ama uumi (vapor) dareere ahaan lagu helay ama qabtay.

conventional crude n. dareere shidaal (petroleum) oo si caadi ah lagu qodikaro ama lagu soo saarikaro.

crown land n. dhul boqortooyo ama dawlad leedahay.

crude oil n. shidaal ceeriin ama aan la sifayn.

cubic foot n. shidaal cufkiisa (one cubic foot).

cubic feet per day n. abbr. cf/d; tirada cubic feet (ft3) oo laga soo saaro ceel 24 saac.

cubic food n. halbeeg mug oo la mid ah hal cag oo jibbaaran ama dhinac walba ah (ft3 or cu ft).

cushion gas n. neef (gas) inteeda joogta ahaan loogu weeleeyo haan neef dabiici ah. 

daisy-chain (ˈdheyzii,jeyn) v. daisy-chained; daisy-chaining; daisy-chains wada-xariirin, siiba computers. -daisy chain n.

development well n. meel laga qodo shidaal ama neef (gas).

downstream sector n. soo saarka ugu danbeeya iyo iibgaynta badeecad dhammaystiran ee laga iibiyo macaamiil.

drilling fluid n. iskudaran dhoobo iyo dareerayaal kiimikooyin shidaal oo wata neefo (gaseous) kala duwan. kale loogu yeeraa drilling mud.

drilling mud n. eeg drilling fluid.

drill string n. madaxa dhuunta dhulka duleelisa oo biyo ku darmaya ku jajabisa dhagaxda adag.

drygas (ˈdaraay,gaas) n. neef (gas) aan lahayn uumi biyood.

enhanced oil recovery n. abbr. EOR hab lagu kordhiyo soo saarka shidaal ceeriin ee ku haray ceel shidaal.

enhanced recovery n. hab caadi dib loogu soo celiyo qof galay qalliin caafimaad.

exploratory well n. ceel shidaal oo loo qoday sahmin ahaan, laakin aan wali laga gaarin wax natiijo ah.

farm-in n. beer loo adeegto beerasho iyo xoolo dhaqasho.

form out v. farmed out; farming out; farms out 1 shaqo-u-xilsaarid qabashadeed. 2 ku wareejin ilmo qof kale hayntood. 3 tababar u dirid cayaartooy. 4 ku beeris dhul hal nooc-abuur.

feedstock (ˈfiidh,istaak) n. waxyaalo ceeriin (raw material) oo wax laga warshadeeyo. e.g. Crude oil is feedstock of gasoline production.

gas cap n. furka haan shidaal ee gaari.

naphtha (ˈnaaftha) n. 1 noocyo badan ee dareere noole ama iskudar dareere carfa hydrocarbon laga miiray petroleum ama dhuxul (coal tar) oo wax lagu milo. 2 petroleum. kale loogu yeeraa straight-run gasoline.

straight-run gasoline n. eeg naphtha.

gathering line n. dhuun shidaal ka qaadda ceel gaarsiisana dhuun-weynta.

heating oil n. waxay isku dhawyihiin shidaal naafato (diesel fuel), waxaana loo adeegtaa qandicinta biyaha.

heavy crude n. saliid ceeriin oo dhafaag ah, ceelkana aan sahal uga soo bixinkarin.

horizontal drilling n. marka ceel la shidaal gaaro ayaa dhuunta jiif laga dhigaa si ay balliga shidaal u dhex sabbayso.

independent producer n. hawlgal ka madax-bannaan habka caadiga ah oo shaqadooda xor u ah.

infill drilling n. ku daris qodista ceelal cusub kuwii hore u jiray.

injection well n. ceel lagu shubo neef, hawo, ama biyo si ceelasha u dhaw u soo maaxdaan.

jet fuel n. nooc shidaalka dayaaradaha ah. kale loogu yeeraa aviation turbine fuel.

aviation turbine fuel n. abbr. ATF (avtur) eeg jet fuel.

autosomal DNA Testing n. raad-raac dib loogu sameeyo firka qof ayada oo laga eego hidda-sidaha qof (autosomal chromosomes), kaas oo wax ka xambaarsan DNA qofka, waxna kala wadaaga mid kale oo ay qaraabo yihiin, xag hooyo ama aabbe, toos iyo dadabba (maternally and paternally, both directly and indirectly).

centimorgan (ˈsenta,moorgan) n. abbr. cM halbeeg hidda-side oo u dhigma 1/100 ama (1%) morgan.

morgan (ˈmorgan) n. 1 halbeeg tilmaama fogaan ahaan inta u dhexaysa laba hidda-sidayaal yaryar (genes) ee hiddaside-weynaha (chromosome), isku dhawaantooduna sheegto qaraabanimo. 2 centimorgan.  

DNA Code and Codons n. afgaradka (code) DNA, waana luuqad “afar xaraf” ka kooban iyo 64 saddex-xarafyo “erayo” loogu yeero codons; nolol oo dhanna 64 codons ayay ka koobantahay.

DNA Double Helix n. eray loo isticmaalo qaab-dhismeedka DNA oo u eg sallaan la maroojiyay (a twisted ladder).

DNA Function n. shaqada DNA oo ah aruurinta xogaha hidda-sidayaasha oo dhan oo noole u baahanyahay in ay ku abuuranto.

DNA markers n. susunka (sequence) DNA oo ah calaamadaha hidda-side oo ka muuqda meelaha ay uga jiraan hidda-sidaha (chromosome); kuwa aad iskugu dhawna waa la hidda-raacay.

gene variants n. isbaddal joogtooba oo ku dhaca susunka DNA (DNA sequence). kale loogu yeeraa gene mutation.

gender variance n. jinsiga qof oo aan nin ama naag toona aan ahayn (gender atypical): gender nonconformity. -gender-variant or -gender variant adj.

gender nonconforming

(ˈjendar,naankan,formin) adj. jinsi aan raacin nin ama naag wixii lagu yiqiin. -gender nonconformity n.  

gender expression n. jinsiyadda qof oo ka duwanaankarta midda lagu yaqaan, sida ninkii oo naag iska dhiga ama naagtii oo nin iska dhigta.

nonconformity (ˌnaanka’formadhii) n. aan waafaqin xeer, caado, ama sharci.

gene mutation n. hal ama ka badan hidda-side (gene) oo isbaddal ku dhaco, qaarkoodna keenaan cudur ama cillad hidda-side.

genetic testing n. baaris cilmiyeed lagu sameeyo DNA qof, si xogta hidda-sidayaasha wax looga ogaado.

genome-wide association study n. abbr. GWAS baaris cilimyeed lagu sameeyo dhammaan hidda-sidayaasha DNA oo dhan (the genome), si dad badan looga ogaado kala duwanaansho yar (small variations).

heritability (ˌheradha’biladhii) n. saamiga la hidda-raaco; saamiga firsasho.

mitochondrial DNA n. garangar hidda-side oo laga helo gudaha unugyarayaal wareegsan (cellular organelles) oo ku dhexjira unugyada (mitochondria), qofkuna ka hidda-raaco hooyada kali ah; meesha nuclear DNA laga hidda-raaco labada waalidba.

non-coding DNA n. qayb ka mid ah DNA oo aan saamayn ku lahayn samaynta hidda-sidayaasha, laakin ka caawisa xagga hawl-qabadka.

pedigree collapse n. sida taranka laba qof ee DNA u gaabato, taas oo keentay qaraabanimadooda, haddii ay ogyihiin ama aysan ogaynba.  

polymerase (pa’limareys) n. maalikiyuullo isku xirxiran oo kiimiko ahaan xariir u leh. Barbardhig DNA polymerase, RNA polymerase.

DNA polymerase n. dheecaanno (enzyme) caawiya isbadinta DNA.

RNA polymerase n. dheecaanno (enzyme) saamayn ku leh samaynta RNA.

base pair n., pl. base pairs labada liil (double helix) midkood ee qaabeeya sallaanka DNA.

denature (ˌdii’neyjar) v. denatured; denaturing 1 doorin; ka baddalid shay asalka uu ahaa. 2 baaddalid qaab-dhiska maalikiyuul, kululayn ama si kale. -denaturant (ˌdii’neyjaranti) n.; -denaturation (ˌdii,neyja’reyshan) n.

genetic locus n. meesha hidda-side gaar ah (gene) uga jiro hidda-sidayaasha (chromosome): physical location of a gene.

gene frequency n. saami yar oo ah astaan gaar ahaaneed (particular allele) oo bulshada qaarkeed laga helo: variant of a gene.

heterozygosity (ˌhedharaw,zaay’gaasadhii) n. laba astaamood (two alleles) oo isku rug (position) la ah hal hidda-side: being heterozygous.

oligonucleotide (a,liga’nukiya,taaydh) n. iskuxir gaaban ee nucleic acid  (sida DNA ama RNA), inta badan ka kooban ilaa 20 nucleotides.  

polymerase chain reaction n. hab shaybaareed lagu sameeyo cadad gaar ah nuqullo badan oo DNA, kana yimid muunad (sample) xambaarsan in yar oo DNA.

endonuclease (ˌendhaw’nukli,yeys) n. dheecaan (enzyme) laba ama ka badan si uu u sameeyo qiyaaso kala duwan. Barbardhig exonuclease.

exonuclease (ˌeksaw’nukli,yeys) n. dheecaan (enzyme) jajabiya nucleic acid asaga oo mid-mid uga saaraya nucleotides qaybta danbe ee iskuxiranka (chain). Barbardhig endonuclease.

sex chromosomes n. hidda-side oo kala doora ahaanshaha nin ama naag (xx oo naagta ah iyo xy oo ninka ah).

tandem repeat n. taxan isku eg oo DNA oo u teedan si isdabayaal ah.

adenovirus (ˌaadanaw’vaayras) n. nooc kasta oo ah bahda faayraska (Adenoviridae) oo ku dhaca marinnada neefta ee dadka: infection of respiratory system. -adenoviral (ˌaadanaw’vaayral) adj.

alkaptonuria (ˌaal,kaapta’nuriya) n. or alcaptonuria cudur kaadi-madawbaad.

alkaptonuria n. eeg alkaptonuria.

homogentisic acid (ˌhawmaw,jen’tizik) n. iskudhis kiimiko C8H8O4  oo laga helo dhiigga iyo kaadida qof uu asiibay cudurka alkaptonuria.

antennae (aan’tenadh) adj. dareeme ama dareemayaal leh (antennas ama an antenna), siiba cayayaan: having antennae.

cDNA (ˈsii,dhii,en’eey) n. abbr. copy DNA gacan-ku-samays DNA ah. kale loogu yeeraa complementary DNA.

complementary DNA n. eeg cDNA.

cell cycle n. hab unuggu maro marxalado uu u qaybqaybsamo.

transcriptase (taraan’iskirip,teys) n. eeg RNA polymerase.

central dogma n. aragti oranaysa in xogta hidda-sideed u qulqulsho hal jiho, ka bilaabmatana DNA aaddana RNA kana sii aaddo protein.

homologue (ˈhawma,loog) n. or  homolog  wax sida iskudhis kiimiko ama hidda-side oo kale ah: homologous.

homolog n. eeg homologue.

light crude n. dareere petroleum oo culaab fudud: API Gravity is greater than 10.

American Petroleum Institute n. or API Gravity cabbir lagu eego sida dareeraha petroleum u culusyahay ama u fududyahay marka la barbardhigo biyo: haddii API gravity ka weynyahay 10, waa fudayd, waana sabbeeyaa; haddii u ka yaryahayna 10, waa culsys, waana degaa (sinks).

API Gravity n. abbr. American Petroleum Institute.

viscosity (vi’skaasadhii) n., pl. viscosities 1 dhoojaan; dhagdhag: being viscous. 2 cabbir qulqulisdiidka dareere, taas oo lagu cabbiro isliska gudaha dhaqaaqa dareere: fluid's resistance to flow.

liquified natural gas n. abbr. LNG neef (gas) dabiiciyan ah oo la iskugu cufay dareere ahaan hab qaboojineed.

LNG n. abbr. liquified natural gas.

liquefied petroleum gas n. abbr. LPG mid kasta oo ka mid ah dhawr iskujiryo dareere guban’og ee hydrocarbons propene, propane, butene, and butane.

LPG n. abbr. liquefied petroleum gas.

asset-backed security n. dhaqaale rahamad ama curaar ahaan (financial assets) qof u kaba il-dhaqaale ka soo galo ahaan (income-generating assets).

account debtor n. daynqabe xoolo ku leedahay cid kale (creditor).

accreting swap n. koror fuula faa’iidada dulsaarka.

accrual basis n. lacag la kasbaday (earned) ama wax lagu baxshay (spent), laakiin wali aan la bixin.

accrual bond n. faa’iido inteed laga helay (debt), laakiin aan wali soo gacan-galin (not yet collected). kale loogu yeeraa accrued interest.

accrued interest n. eeg accrual bond.

accrued interest n. faa’iido aan la bixin oo la xariirta dayn la qaatay, maal-gashi, kaydin (credit cards, loans, investments, and savings).

accumulated benefit obligation n. abbr. ABO xisaabinta lacagta ka aruurtay qorshihii hawlgabku (pension plan) marka u joogsado.

ABO n. abbr. accumulated benefit obligation.

accumulated depreciation n. hoos-u-dhac muddo aruursamay oo ku dhaca qaymaha hanti.

automated clearing house n. abbr. ACH shabakad electronic oo bangiyada iyo xawaaladuhu ku kala waaridaan lacagaha.

acid test n. imtixaan daran ama adag: a severe test.

tranche (ˈtaraanash) n. qayb; cad; qaar, siiba loo adeegto maalgalin (investing): a section, portion, or slice.

adverse opinion n. qoraal soo jeedin oo uu sameeyo hanti-dhawre (auditor), kuna caddeeyo in shirkad dhaqaalaha ay sheeganayso in ay leedahay uusan sax ahayn.

affinity card n. kaadh (credit card) bangi bixiyo oo uu kula shirkoobo urur samafal, marka la isticmaalana xoogaa deeq ah u go’do.

affirmative pregnant n. nooc ballan ama heshiis laga rabo in ka qaygaluhu uusan jabin sharuudo gaar ahaaneed (certain terms).

affordable housing program n. abbr. AHP qorshe guriyayn la awoodikaro.

AHP n. abbr. affordable housing program.

allonge (aa’lawnji) n. xaanshi yar oo dheeraad ahaan ugu dhaggan qoraal (document): rider.

anticipatory hedge n. mawqif hore looga sii qaato wax la gadandoono ama la iibindoono.

arbitrage (ˈaarba,taraash) n. shay lagu soo gatay qayme jaban, kadibna lagu sii iibiyay qayme sare.   -v. arbitraged; arbitraging ku gadatin qayme jaban iyo ku sii iibin qame sare.

arbitrageur (ˌaarba,taraa’shar) n. or arbitrager (ˈaarba,taraashar) qof qayme jaban wax ku gata, kuna sii iibiya qayme sare: arbitrage.

 assumable (a’sumabal) adj. loo qaateen; loo maleeyo: being assumed. -assumability (a,suuma’biladhii) n.

assumed name n. magac beeneed: an alias.

asymmetric behavior n. dhaqaale muujiya dheellitir la’aan.

backtesting n. hab xog hore la adeegto si loo agaado saxnimadeeda.

bad delivery n. gaarsiin aan samayn sharuudihii looga baahnaa.

balloon loan n. dayn guri oo muddo gaaban ah, shan ilaa todoba sano, marka ay dhammaatana la bixiyo lacag badan oo daboosha baaqigii haray.

break-even point n. inta lacagta qof soo gasha ay le’egtahay inta uu kharaj u bixiyo. e.g. After several years, the company has finally reached the break-even point.

buydown n. lacag dheeraad ah oo hormaris ahaan loo bixiyo, si loo yareeyo lacagta billaha ah ee guri la qaatay laga bixiyo.

check truncation n. hab jeeggii xaanshida ahaa (physical paper) lagu baddalo qaab electronic si ka dhaqsiyo badan.

chose in action n. xaquuq qofku leeyahay in uu helo dayn ka maqan ama waxyeelo (damage) soo gaartay, kali ah ayada oo loo marayo dacwo sharciyeed.

coinsurance (ˌkawan’shuranis) n. boqolkii inta daboosha kharajka caafimaad ee qof bixinteeda mas’uul ka yahay, marka laga jaro wixii laga jari lahaa.

commitment letter n. waqrad ballanqaad qoraal oo dhexmarta daynshe iyo daynqaate (lender and a borrower).

compensating balance n. eeg compensation balance.

compensation balance n. lacagta ugu yar oo laga rabo in daynqabuhu ku soo rido koontadiisa bangiga (bank account).

consolidated statement n. iskudaris ama wadarayn (financial statement) ee shirkad laamaheeda kala duwan.

contra asset n. nooc koonto hantiyeed (asset account) oo waxa ku jira ay yihiin tabane (negative) ama eber.

institution bank n. bangi mu’asasah; bangi ka dhex adeega kuwa kale, siiba bangiyada maxalliga iyo kuwa caalamiga (domestic and international banks).

counterparty (ˈkaantar,paadhii) n. qolada kale oo ka qaybgalaysa iswaydaarsiga wax kala gadasho: those parties that are a part of a financial transaction.

covariance (ˌkaw’veriyanis) n. xariirka cabbir oo ka dhexeeya laba doorsoome oo xulasho la’ (two random variables).

covariant (ˌkaw’veriyanti) adj. wax kale ku kala duwan, inkasta oo isku xariir xisaabeed ka dhexeeyo.

contrariant (kan’tareriyanti) adj. lid ah; ka horyimaada, siiba xukun: opposed: antagonistic: contrary. e.g. Contrariant groups. -contrariantly adv.

contrarianism (kan’tareriya,nizam) n. mucaarad; ka horyimaada nadaam ama firad: practices of a contrarian.

contravalid adj. aan lahayn qayme; been ah: not based on truth.

self-contradictory (ˌselaf,kaantara’dhiktarii) adj. is burinaya; laba wax oo iska soo horjeeda ah.

contraversion n. dhinaca lidka u leexeda: antistrophe.

antistrophe (aan’tistara,fii) n. hooris, siiba qasiido ama hees. -antistrophic (ˌaanta’staraafik) adj.; -antistrophically (ˌaanta’staraafiklii) adv.

strophe (ˈistaraw,fii) n. hees ama gabay qaaybta hooris ahaan u soo noqnoqota.

epode (ˈe,pawdh) n. qasiido hooriskeeda gaaban oo gadaal ka raaca.

monovariant adj. eeg univariant.

univariant adj. hal doorasho kali ah leh, loona adeegto habka physical-chemical. Barbardhig bivariant, phase rule.

bivariant adj. laba doorsoome leh (two variables). Barbardhig phase rule.

phase rule n. xeer heer (phase); xeerku waxa uu qeexayaa, tirooyinka heerarka xornimo ee habka dheellitiranka, waxa uu la mid yahay tirada wax ka koobanyihiin oo laga jaray tiradada heerarka oo lagu daray 2 (F = C − P + 2).

intraovarian adj. ka dhaca ama ka jira gudaha minka (ovary).

data mining n. computer ka raadin xog waxtar leh.

payably adv. 1 in la bixiyo ay tahay, siiba dayn. 2 laga faa’iidikaro: profitably.

debenture (di’benjar) n. dayn dheer (long-term debt) oo aan lahayn wax curaar ah (collateral).

defeasance (di’fiizanis) n. 1 joojin lahaanshihii guri ayada oo la raacayo heshiiskii. 2 aan sharci ahayn hadda iyo wixii ka danbeeya: rendering null.

rendering null n. aan sharci ahayn hadda iyo wixii ka danbeeya.

leveraged (ˈlevarijti) adj. ka faa’iidaysad.

disintermediation (ˌdhis,intar,miidhi’yeyshan) n. jaris lacagta loogaysto khidmad ahaan marka lacag lala baxayo (transaction). -disintermediate (ˌdhis,intar’miidhi,yeyt) v.  

drawee (daro’ii) n. bangi sarrifa ama lacageeya jeeg (check) la soo qoray.

estop (e’staap) v. estopped; estopping xayirid; xannibid: impede.

Fannie Mae n. magac naanayseed Federal National Mortgage Association.

fictitious name n. magac aan ahayn kan runta ah oo ogolaansho dawlad looga helo: an artificial name deliberately adopted.

floriated (ˈfalori,yeydhidh) adj. qurxin ubax ama qaab ubax leh. -floriation (ˌfalori’yeyshan) n.

apportionable (a’porshanabal) adj. la qayb-qaybsankaro: being apportioned.

Freddie Mac n. magac naanayseed Federal Home Loan Mortgage Corporation.

fungible (ˈfanjabal) adj. la isku baddalankaro, qayme ahaan: substituted for something of equal value. e.g.  Commodities are fungible goods. -fungibility (ˌfanja’biladhii) n.

Ginnie Mae n. magac naanayseed Government National Mortgage Association.

histogram (ˈhista,graam) n. laydhi (rectangular) garaafeed oo xog tirooyin muujiya.

hypothecate (haay’paatha,keyt) v. hypothecated; hypothecating curaar ama rahamad ahaan u dhigid hanti (sida guri ama gaari) si lacag loogu dayn-qaato, ayada oo aan la wareejin mulkiyaddii. -hypothecation (haay,paatha’keyshan) n.; -hypothecator (haay,paatha,keydhar) n.

intercompany (ˌintar’kaampnii) adj. or inter-company ka dhexjira laba ama ka badan shirkadood: involving different companies.

kurtosis (ˌkar’tosas) n. cabbir qorshayneed lagu qeexo nooca xog-qoraaleed (dataset).

dataset (ˈdheydha,set) n. data set pl. datasets also data sets xog qoraaleed; xog-qoraaleed ururis ah oo ka timid hal xog-ileed.

peakedness (ˈpiiknis) n. 1 fiiq cayiman. 2 kurtosis.

cumulant (ˈkiyumilanti) adj. kordha inyar-inyar.

liquidity (li’kwidhadhii) n. lacagayn; shay aad loogu baahanyahay oo dhaqsa loo lacagaynkaro.

lockbox (ˈlaak,baakis) n. sanduuq qufulan, sida midka post-office box.

air float n. aad u faraxsan; hawada sabbaynaya farxad darteed.

megapolis (ma’gaapalas) n., pl. megapolises eeg megalopolis.

Tusaale: Af-Soomaaligu ma qabo xarfaha p, v, iyo z; xiriirka ka dhexeeya xarfaha shaqalka (vowel letters) iyo dhawaaqyada shaqalka (vowel sounds) waa isku mid, meesha English dhawr codayn (multiple sounds) uu leeyhay shaqal (vowel). -phonotactic (ˌfawna’taaktik) adj.

hyper- horgale (prefix) 1 sare; kore (super-): hypermarket. 2 aad: hypersensitive. 3 ka badan: hyperemia.

hypergraphia n. aad u jecel wax qoris mar kasta si caadiga ka baxsan: an intense desire to write.

hyperhidrosis (ˌhaayparhaay’darawsis) n. aad u dhidida, siiba si caadiga ka baxsan: excessive sweating.

hypermagnesemia (ˌhaayparaˌmaagni’siimiya) n. dhiigga oo ay aad ugu badantahay macdanta magnesium: an abnormally elevated level of magnesium in the blood serum.

hyperosmolarity (ˌhaaypawsma’laaritii) n. xaalad dhiigga aad ugu badantahay cusbo (sodium), sonkor (glucose), iyo walxo kale, taas oo biyaha ka saarta jirka xibnihiisa kale oo maskaxdu ku jirto. -hyperosmolar (ˌhaapa,raaz’mawlar) adj.

hyperphosphatemia (ˌhaayparˌfaas’tiimiya) n. dhiigga oo ay aad ugu badantahay macdanta phosphate.

hypo- horgale (prefix) or hyp- 1 hoos (under, beneath, down): hypodermic. 2 dhimman; caadiga ka yar (less than normal): hypotension. 3 heerka ugu hooseeya dareerin iskudhisyo (series of compounds): hypophosphite.

hypoalbuminemia (ˌhaaypaw-aal,biyuuma’niimiya) n. xaalad jirku uusan samaynkarin in ku filan albumin protein, taas oo mas’uul ka ah ku haynta dareeraha xididadda dhiigga: hypoproteinemia.

hypomnesia (ˌhaay,paam’niishiya) n. xasuusta oo aad u yaraata: deficiency of the memory.

hyponatremia (ˌhaaypawney’tiriimiya) n. dhiigga oo aad ugu yaraato (sodium), qofka caadiga ahna laga rabo 135 ilaa 145 milliequivalents per liter (mEq/L). –hyponatremic (ˌhaaypawney’triimik) adj.

macrolide (ˈmaakra,laaydh) n. koox daawooyin ah oo lagu daaweeyo caabuq bakteriya faayras (various bacterial infections), inta badan loo isticmaalo Azithromycin, clarithromycin, iyo erythromycin.

Othello syndrome n. masayr ama hinaaso qof maleeyo in qofka kale uusan daacad u ahayn. kale loogu yeeraa morbid jealousy.

morbid jealousy n. eeg Othello syndrome.

ototoxic (ˌawdha’taaksik) adj. la xariira; dhibaateeya dareemayaasha maqalka ama dheelitirka (balance); dhagta u keena ototoxicity: damage to the ear. e.g. There are several ototoxic medications. -ototoxicity (ˌawdhataak’sisatii) n.

ovarian teratoma n. buro minka ku abuurmata, inta badanna ma ahan kaankaro, laakiin aad bay u xanuun badantahay.

teratoma (ˌtera’tawma) n., pl. teratomas also teratomata (ˌtera’tawmadha) buro ka kooban nudo kala duwan oo isku murugsan (heterogeneous mixture of tissues).

over-the-counter n. abbr. OTC.

oxter (ˈaakistar) n. (chiefly Scotland and Ireland) kilil; shaqfal: armpit.

oxy (ˈaaksii) adj. wata ama xambaarsan oxygen (often used in combination): oxyhemoglobin.

oxymoron (ˌaaksi’mor,aan) n., pl. oxymorons also oxymora (ˌaaksi’mora) isku daris ama israacis laba eray oo lid isku ah: a combination of contradictory words. e.g. “old news,” “organized chaos.” “curyaan dhan.” -oxymoronic (ˌaaksima’raanik) adj.; -oxymoronically (ˌaaksima’raaniklii) adv.

oxycodone (ˌaaksii’kaw,dhawn) n. daawo maandooriye (opioid medicine) loo isticmaalo xanuun baabi’iye.

OxyContin (ˌaaksiiˈkaantin) trademark eeg oxycodone.

oxygen tent n. teendho lagu xiro qaarka hore ee bukaan sariir-jiif ah (bedridden) oo neef oxygen ku socoto.

oxytocin (ˌaaksi’tawsan) n. dheecaan (hormone) xoodiya docoshada muruqa minka (contraction of uterine muscle) waqtiga foosha, ka dibna samaynta caanaha (lactation after childbirth).

p arm of a chromosome n. hidda-side (chromosome) gacankiisa ugu gaaban, marka laga eego labada gacnood isku xirankooda dhexe (centromere); 'p' comes from the word 'petit', the French translation of 'small'.

p.c. n. abbr. cuntayn ka dib: after meals (from the Latin "post cibum", after meals).

p.o. n. abbr. po (per os), also PO or p.o. afka: by mouth (daawo afka laga qaato).

p.r.n. n. abbr. Latin term “pro re nata,” hadba sidii loogu baahdo: as needed.

PA n. physician assistant.

PA X-ray n. raajo laga qaado back-to-front; PA (posteroanterior). Barbardhig AP X-ray.

AP X-ray n. raajo laga qaado front-to-back; AP (anteroposterior).

pachy- comb. form dhumuc (thick): pachytene.

pachytene (ˈpaaki,tiin) heerka saddexaad oo hidda-side isku soo uruuro oo dhumuc yeesho, iskuna kala qaybsho labo lammaane (chromatids). -pachytene adj.

pachymeter (pa’kimadha) n. qalab lagu cabbiro dhumuc waraaq: thickness of paper.

pain management n. maarayn xanuun.

dolorimetry (ˌdawla’rimatarii) n., pl. dolorimetries hab loo cabbiro xanuun inta uu le’egyahay: the measurement of pain. -dolorimetric (ˌdawlara’metrik) adj.; -dolorimetrically (ˌdawlara’metriklii) adv.

dol. n. abbr. dolorimetry: halbeeg lagu cabbiro xanuun.

pain unit n. halbeega cabbira xanuun inta uu le’egyahay. eeg dol.

paleo- comb. form la xariira waxyaalihii hore: paleobotany.

paleobotany (ˌpeyliyaw’baadhnii) n. laan ka mid ah botany oo gooni u eegta xashka dhirta dhimatay (fossil plants). -paleobotanical (ˌpeyliyawba’taanikal) or -paleobotanic (ˌpeyliyawba’taanik) adj.; -paleobotanically (ˌpeyliyawba’taaniklii) adv.; -paleobotanist (ˌpaaliyaw’baadhnisti) n.

paleolithic (ˌpeyliiya’lithik) adj. la xariira waayadii hore ee dhagaxu hub iyo qalab ahaa (Stone Age).

paleolithic diet n. cunto cunis lagu saleeyaya tii waagii hore Stone Age (lean meats, fish, vegetables, fruit, nuts, and seeds).

globus pallidus (ˈgalawbas ˈpaaladhas) n. lakabka gudaha maskaxda oo xukuma dhaqdhaqaaqa. kale loogu yeeraa pallidum.

palliative treatment n. daawyn qaadda xanuun, siiba kaankaro (cancer) ama cudur kale oo daran.

palmitate (ˈpaalma,teyt) n. cusbo kasta or (ester) oo ah palmitic acid.

palmitic acid n. eeg long-chain fatty acid.

long-chain fatty acid n. abbr. LCFA dufan (saturated or unsaturated) oo xambaarsan 13–21 carbons.

pancolitis n. cudur ku dhaca malawad oo ku faafa dhammaantiis, keenana calool-xanuun, shuban, iyo daal.

panhypopituitarism (ˈpaan,haaypawpa’tuwata,rizam) n. xaalad dheecannada uu sii daayo qanjirka (pituitary gland) ay yaraato: hypopituitarism.

hypopituitarism (ˌhaaypawpa’tuwata,rizam) n. siddeed dheecaan (hormones) oo midkood ama ka badan yaraato (decrease) ee uu soo daayo qanjirka (pituitary gland). -hypopituitary (ˌhaaypawpa’tuwa,terii) adj.

panniculus (pa’nikilas) n. xulus; lakab baruur ah, siiba caloosha: an abdominal panniculus.

panniculus adiposus (pa’nikilas ˌaadha’pawsas) n. baruur kasta oo meel korka ka daboosha.

adiposus (ˌaadha’pawsas) n. eeg panniculus adiposus.

papilledema (ˌpaapala’diima) n. barar wareegga danbe ee isha guruxeeda (optic disc) oo uu keeno cadaadis gudaha ah. kale loogu yeeraa choked disk.

choked disk n. or choked disc eeg papilledema.

optic disc n. or optic disk pl. optic discs or optic disks wareegga danbe ee isha guruxeeda.

optic disk n. eeg optic disc.

para- horgale (prefix) or par- 1 dhinac: parenteral.

parenteral (pa’rentaral) adj. daawo qaadashadeed, ka baxsan afka ama marinnada dheefshiidka; ay tahayna in laga qaato xidid ama duris (intravenously or by injection). e.g. He was receiving parenteral nutrition. -parenterally (pa’rentarallii) adv.

paracentesis (ˌpaara,sen’tiisas) n. hab daaweyn oo irbad (trocar, aspirator) looga soo dhuuqo dareere gala meelaha u dhexeeya caloosh, mindhicirka, iyo beerka (peritoneal cavity).

trocar (ˈtaraw,kaar) n. or trochar irbad daba buuran oo jirka dareere looga soo dhuuqo: a drainage outlet.

paraskevidekatriaphobia n. ka cabsada Jimce bishu tahay 13naad.

triskaidekaphobia (ˌtiri,skaay,deka’fawbiya) n. ka cabsada tirada 13.

parentectomy n. ka goyn ama ka qaadis ilmo waalid ama labadaba (a parent or both parents).

parietal pericardium n. xuub dahaara wadnaha. Barbardhig epicardium.

Parkinsonism (ˈpaarkansa,nizam) n. eeg Parkinson’s disease.

paronychia (ˌpera’nikiya) n. cudur (infection) ku dhasha qobka (cuticle) ciddiyaha (finger or toe).

paroxysm (ˈperak,sizam) n. 1 asiibo; cudur soo booddo ah: convulsion. 2 ficil ama dareen soo booddo: outburst. -paroxysmal (ˌperak’sizmal) adj.

paroxysmal atrial tachycardia n. nooc garaac wadnaha oo aad ah.

partial seizure n. saamaysa maskaxda qaybteed kali ah, siiba temporal lobe.

parvovirus (ˈpaarvaw,vaayras) n. cadaanyo faayras (virus) oo la isqaadsiiyo, dhabannada caseeya ciyaalka. kale loogu yeeraa slapped-cheek disease.

slapped-cheek disease n. eeg parvovirus.

patient autonomy n. bukaan xaqa uu u leeyahay in uu gaaro go’aannada daaweyntiisa ayada oo aysan ku qalqaalin bixiyayasha xannaanada caafimaad (health care providers). 

pavlov pouch n. qayb ka mid calool eey oo gooni tijaabo caafimaad loogu sameeyo.

PCA n. abbr. patient-controlled analgesia.

penile (ˈpii,naayl) adj. la xariira ama saameeya gus.

prophylaxis (ˌparawfa’laaksis) n., pl. prophylaxes (ˌparawfa’laak,siiz) isku dayid ka hortag cudur.

percentile (par’sen,taayl) n. cabbir qorshayn (statistics); qaab lagu muujiyo heerka ay wax meel ka joogaan wax ay ka tirsanaayeen, tusaale: haddii natiijo arday ka yahay 10th percentile, taas macnaheedu waa 10 percent buu ka hooseeyaa natiijooyinka ardayda kale oo ah 90%: he scored in 10th percentile.

Cheyne-Stokes breathing n. eeg Cheyne-Stokes respiration.

-plegia n. comb. form naafo (paralysis); curyaan: diplegia.

pleiotropy (palaay’aatrapii) n. xaalad hal hidda-side (single gene) laga soo firsado waalidka (traits) laba iyo ka badan astaamood ama dabeecadood: the quality of being pleiotropic.

pleiotropic (ˌpalaaya’tarawpik) adj. abuura (sameeya) hal iyo ka badan: a pleiotropic gene.

pleiotropism (paay’aatra,pizam) n. xaalad uu keenay ama abuuray (a pleiotropic gene).

pleomorphic (ˌpiliya’morfik) adj. awood qaab baddalasho leh (polymorphic): pleomorphic bacteria. -pleomorphism (ˌpiliya’mor,fizam) n.

polymorphism (ˌpaalii’mor,fizam) n. awood qaab ama muuqaal (forms or shapes) kala duwan yeelankara. -polymorphic (ˌpaalii’morfik) adj.; -polymorphically (ˌpaalii’morfiklii) adv.

single nucleotide polymorphism n. inkasta oo dadku wadaago walxo hidda-side (genetic materials) 99.9 boqolkiiba, haddana hal xaraf oo DNA ayay ku kala duwanyihiin — loona yaqaan single nucleotide polymorphisms, ama SNPs ("snips").

Plummer-Vinson syndrome (ˈpalamar’vinsan ˈsin,darawm) n. abbr. PVS xaalad marinka gudaha dhuunta hunguriga cuntada (esophageal lumen) ay cariiryawdo, liqidduna (dysphagia) adkaato, dhiigyarina timaaddo (hypochromic anemia), loona sababeeyo birta oo dhiigga ku yaraatay (an iron deficiency). UK looga yaqaan Paterson-Brown-Kelly syndrome.

Paterson-Brown-Kelly syndrome n. eeg Plummer-Vinson syndrome.

PVS n. abbr. Plummer-Vinson syndrome.

pneumococcus (ˌnuma’kaakas) n., pl. pneumococci (ˌnuma’kaak,saay) bakteriya (Streptococcus pneumoniae) oo gasha sanbabbada keentana (pneumonia) iyo cudurro kale oo la isqaadsiiyo. -pneumococcal (ˌnuma’kaakal) adj.

pneumoconiosis (ˌnumaw,kawni’yawsis) n., pl. pneumoconioses (ˌnumaw,kawni’yawsis) cudur ku dhaca sanbabbada oo sababsaday boor macdan ama saxarro bireed (mineral or metallic particles) qof joogto uga shaqeeya ama u neefqaatay. Barbardhig black lung.

black lung n. dhuxul boorkeed oo sanbabbada fariista: pneumoconiosis.

pneumocyte (ˈnuma,saayt) n. mid ka mid ah unugyada dulduleelka (alveoli of the lungs) shaandhada hawadu marto ee sanbabka.

polycythemia vera (ˌpaalii,saay’thiimiya ˈvira) n. abbr. PV xaalad dhif ah oo dhuuxu (bone marrow) sameeyo tiro aad  u badan ee unugyada dhiigga cas iyo dhiigga cad. kale loogu yeeraa erythremia.

erythremia (ˌera’thiriimiya) n. eeg polycythemia vera.

polygenic (ˌpaalii’jenik) adj. in ka badan hal hidda-side ayaa xukuma (multiple genetic variants), sida dhererka iyo midabka jirka waxaa xukuma labo ama ka badan hidda-sidayaal.

polyglandular autoimmune syndrome n. abbr. PGA laba cudur ama ka badan ee endocrine system oo iskugu timid hal bukaan.

endocrine disorder n. cillad ku timaada shoqo xumo habka endocrine system, sida haddii heerka dheecaanku sarreeyo ama hooseeyo.

endocrine system n. hab kormeer oo qanjirro aan lahayn xidid, wareegga dhiigga ku sii daayaan dheecaanno, taas oo saamaysa unugyo ku jira xibno gaar ah (pituitary, thyroid, parathyroids, adrenals, ovaries, and testes). 

polymorphonuclear (ˌpaalii,morfa’nukliyar) adj. bu’ qoolaaban oo qaab kala qaybsan leh; xariirna la leh polymorphonuclear leukocytes. -polymorphonuclear n.

polymorphonuclear leukocyte n. nooc unug dhiigga cad ah oo leh bu’ qoolaaban ama kala qaybsan, waxaana ka mid ah: neutrophils, eosinophils, basophils, iyo mast cells.

polyneuritis (ˌpaaliinu’raaydhas) n. barar dhawr dareemayaal.

porcine (ˈpor,saayn) n. la xariira doofaar: piggish.

porphyria (por,firiya) n. dhawr cilladood oo la firsado iskudhiska porphyrin uu soo raaca kaadida.

gastrinoma (ˌgaastara’nawma) n., pl. gastrinomas also gastrinomata (ˌgaastara’nawmadha) nabar dhusha gidaarka mindhiciryaraha ama xididka ganaca (pancreas) oo ay keento dheecaan badan oo gaastirik (gastric-acid): gastric hypersecretion. eeg Zollinger-Ellison syndrome.

Zollinger-Ellison syndrome n. cillad dhif ah oo dheefshiidku sameeyo dheecaanno badan (gastric acid): gastric hypersecretion.

zolmitriptan (ˌzawlmi’tiri,taan) n. daawo (triptan) loo qaato (tablet or as a nasal spray) madax-wareer daran ee goon-jab (migraine attacks).

zomig n. eeg zolmitriptan.

zoophilia (ˌzawa’filliya) n. qof u kacsada ama jecel in  uu u galmoodo xoolo.

Zovirax (zaw’vaay,raakis) trademark daawo afka laga qaato oo faayras la dagaasha (antiviral drug).

zygote intrafallopian transfer n. abbr. ZIFT hab la mid ah gacan-ku-rimis (in vitro fertilization) oo abuuranka loo gudbiyo ninka (embryo transfer).

ZIFT n. abbr. zygote intrafallopian transfer.

chrono- comb. form la xariira waqti (time): chronometer.

cataphoric (ˌkaadha’foorik) adj. 1 la xariirta cataphora. 2 nooc anaphora; naxwo ahaan ugu baddalid magac-uyaal (pronoun). e.g. If you want them, there are oranges in the basket. Barbardhig anaphoric.

cataphora (ka’taafara) n. eray u laabanaya eray kele. e.g. ‘she’ in the sentence. “When she saw me, Ubah smiled.”

anaphora (a’naafra) n. eray weedh (sentence) ku soo noqnoqda e.g. “Give me liberty or give me death.” Barbardhig cataphoric. –anaphorically (ˌaana’fooriklii).

endophagous (ˈendhaafagas) adj. 1 dulan ku dhala kuna kora xibnaha gudaha. 2 bulunbulyo ama xorre ah, siiba dixiri ku dhasha gudaha geedaha. Barbardhig ectophagous.

ectophagous (ˈektaafagas) adj. dulan ku kora dusha noole kale ama dhir. Barbardhig endophagous.

necrophagous (na’karafagas) adj. bakhticune ah; cuna hilibka uray. e.g. Necrophagous insects and birds.

endophilic (ˌenda’filik) adj. ku nool meel xiran, sida god, qaxaab, ama guri; la nool dadka. Barbardhig exophilic. –endophily (en’dhaafalii) n.

exophilic (ˌendha’filik) adj. ku nool meel kabaxsan deegaan dadeed (human habitations). Barbardhig endophilic. –endophily (en’daafalii) n.

endophasia (enda’fawshiya) n. islahadal; hadal aan la maqlikarin: internal speech.

exophasia (ˌeksaw’fawshiya) n., pl. exophasias hadal la maqalikaro: audible speech. –exophasic (eksaw’fayzik)

malapropism (ˈmaala,paraa,pizam) n. 1 hafid; kahid; isku khaldid ama isku kahid laba eray oo dhawaaq ahaan iskugu dhaw. 2 malaprop. –malapropist (ˈmaala,paraapisti) n.

malaprop (ˈmaala,paraap) n. kahis; isku khaldis erayo isku dhaw.                                                        -adj. or malapropian (ˌmaala’paraapiyan) adeegta erayo la isku kaho ama la isku khaldo: malapropisms.

protasis (ˈparaadhasas) n., pl. protases (ˈparaadha,siiz) 1 hordhac riwaayad ama gabay. 2 weedho aan dhammayn (subordinate clause) oo wadata sababayn haddii (conditional sentence). Barbardhig apodosis. –protatic (paraa’taadhik) adj.

subordinate clause n. waxay leedahay subject iyo verb, laakin aan kaligeed istaagikarin weedh (sentence) ahaan. e.g. if you see my teacher (you = subject; see = verb); saddex nooc ayaa jira: noun, adjective, iyo adverb.

apodosis (aˈpaadhasas) n., pl. apodoses (aˈpaadha,siiz) weedho dhan (main clause) oo wadata sababayn haddii (conditional sentence). e.g. If it rains, we will get wet. We will get wet if it rains. Barbardhig protasis.

main clause n. koox erayo ah oo wata subject iyo verb samayn karana weedh (sentence) dhan. e.g. I am very happy. (I = subject; happy = verb).

predicate (ˈparedhiket) n. 1 naxwe eray ama erayo fudud oo sharraxaya ficil gaar ah (specific action) oo fale ama faacilka (subject) weedhu samaynayo. e.g. The girls play in the house. The simple predicate would be 'play.' 2 logic wax la yeelayo ama la diidayo. –predicative (ˈparedhikativ) adj.; -predicatively adv.

linking verb n. or copular verb ficil wax kama sheego ee faacilka falka ayay ku xiraan falka. e.g. “He seems happy,” the verb “seems” links the faacil (subject) “He” to the adjective “happy.”

predicate nominative n. or predicate noun magac ama magac-u-yaal oo yimaada gadaasha faacilka falka (linking verb). e.g. “Ahmed is a good teacher.” Here, Ahmed is the subject (faacil), ‘is’ is the verb (simple predicate), and a good teacher is the predicate nominative that describes Ahmed.

preform (ˈpirii,foorm) v. preformed; preforming; preforms siiqaabayn; siidiyaarin.                                -n., plural preforms siiqaabays; siidiyaaris.

prepositional phrase n. weedh meeleeye; weedh ka bilaabata preposition (meeleeye) kuna dhammaata noun, pronoun, or noun phrase. e.g. "He is from Somalia," "from Somalia" is a prepositional phrase.

premodifier (ˌpirii’maadha,faay) v. or pre-modify premodified or pre-modified; premodifying or pre-modifying eray wax ku sii  dara magac ama ficil.

postmodifier n. eray loo adeegtay gadaasha eray kale si uu u xadiddo ama macnihiisa wax ugu daro. e.g. “the tall man left,” “left” is the postmodifier for the noun “the man.”

modal verb n. main verb la shaqeeyaan muujiyaanna possibility (may, could, can, might), ability (can, could), permission (may), or necessity (need, must). e.g. “you must clean,” “must” is a modal verb indicating that it's necessary for the subject (“you”) to perform the action of the verb (“clean”). kale loogu yeeraa modal auxiliary verb.

modal auxiliary verb n. eeg modal verb.

count noun n. magac tirsamikara, sida shinbir, kursi, iwm. Barbardhig mass number.

dative (ˈdheydhiv) adj. waxay muujisaa cidda wax la siiyay ama yeelanaysa (recipient or beneficiary) ee falka. e.g. She gave him the keys,' 'him' is in the dative case as it is the indirect object of the verb 'gave' and answers the question 'to whom?'

active transport n. dhaqaaqa maalikiyuulada ay uga tagaan meel ribbanaan hoose (lower concentration) una aadaan meel ribbanaan sare (higher concentration). Barbardhig passive transport.

passive transport n. dhaqaaqa maalikiyuulada ay uga tagaan meel ribbanaan sare (higher concentration) una aadaan meel ribbanaan hoose (lower concentration), ayaga oo aan dhumin tamar. Barbardhig active transport.

adventitious root n. xididdo geed oo ka soo baxa meelo aan caadi ahayn, sida geed laamihiisu xididdo soo ritaan. Barbardhig aerial root.

aerial root n. xididdo bannaanka geed ka soo baxa. Barbardhig prop root.

 prop root n. xididdo soo laalaadsada oo caawiya qotonka geed.

phage (‘feyj) n. also (‘faash) pl. phages also phage fayras (virus) keena bakteeriya (bacteria).

bacteriophage (baak’tiriya,feyj) n., pl. bacteriophages fayras (virus) keena bakteeriya (bacteria): PHAGE. –bacteriophagy (ˌbaak,tirii’yaafajii) n.

-phage n. comb. form fayras (virus) ama unug laaya unugyada. e.g. microphage.

microphage (ˈmaaykra,feyj) n. unug dhiigga cad oo cuna walxaha, sida bacteria, viruses, fungi, iyo parasites.

base pairing n. laba base oo xambaarsan nitrogen ama (nucleotides) oo lammaanooba si ay u sameeyaan qaabdhiska DNA.

biodiversity hotspots n. meel ay ku noolyihiin xayawaan badan oo qaarkood meel kale aan laga helin ama sii dabargo’aya.

bioremediation (ˌbaayawri,miidii’yeyshan) n. hab loo adeegto noolaha, sida bacteria, fungi, plants, enzymes in ay yareeyaan suntan ama wasakhda badan ee ku jirta biyaha, ciidda, hawada, iwm.

biotic factor n. noole wada nool oo qaabeeya bii’adda (environment).

bryophyte (ˈbaraaya,faayt) n. fuf; cagaaran; dhir aan lahayn xidid iyo caleen oo hawda ka qaadata nafaqada (mosses, liverworts, and hornworts). –bryophytic (ˌbaraaya’fidhik) adj.

calcitonin (ˌkaalsa’tawnan) n. dheecaan uu sameeyo thyroid gland, sii daayana si uu wareegga dhiigga caadi uga dhigo. Barbardhig thyrocalcitonin.

thyrocalcitonin (ˌthaayraw,kaalsa’tawnan) n. eeg calcitonin.

capsid (ˈkaapsadh) n. fayras (virus) qobkiisu protein yahay (protein shell of a virus), oo nooca uu yahay (genetic material) ay ku aaburantahay.

capsomer (ˈkaapsamar) n. or capsomere (ˈkaapsa,miir)  walxo aad u yaryar oo sameeya protein dusha wax looga dhoobo (protein coat).

centriole (ˈsentarii,yawl) n. laba lammaane oo ku jira gudaha unugga xoolo agaggarka bu’da.

centromere (ˈsentara,miir) n. dhextaal; labada (chromatids) hidde-side (chromosomes) nudda dhexda iskaga haysa. –centromeric (ˌsentara’miirik).

centrosome (ˈsentara,sawm) n. qaab wareeg qayb ka qaata iskala qaybinta unugga (cell division); inta aan qaybsanku bilaabanna laba nuqul buu iska dhigaa (duplicates), ka dibna isqaybinta ayaa bilaabata.

chlorophyll (ˈkaloora,fiil) n. midabka dabiiciga ah (pigment) ee dhirta siiya cagaarka, kana caawiya in ay cunto ka samaysato cagaariyaha (photosynthesis); astaan C55H72MgN4O5 ama cagaar takhi ah C55H70MgN4O6. kale loogu yeeraa chlorophyll a, chlorophyll b (sida astaantu u kala horrayso). –chlorophyllous (kaloora’fiias) adj.

chlorophyta (kalaw’raafata) plural noun qayb ama nooc kale cagaarleyda cagaanran (green algae).

chordate (ˈkoor,dheyt) n. xayawaan la isku jamciyo oo leh udub cargo ah oo tiiriya dhabarkooda ama saableydooda. –chordate adj.

chromosomal mutation n. tiro baddalis ama hidda-sidayaal (chromosomes) qaabkood; afar nooc ayaana jira, sida deletion, duplication, inversion, iyo translocation.

ciliate (ˈsiliyat) n. noole hal-unugle ah oo dhawr qaab mara noloshiisa.

climax community n. sabo dhir ama xoolo ku nagaadaan kuna haystaan nolol isdheelitirta bii’addooda.

codominant (ˌkaw’dhaamanant) adj. 1 genetics laba astaan ama ka badan (alleles) hidda-sidayaal oo labada dhinacba (aabbe iyo hooyo) ka yimid leh (equally dominant). 2 laba isku awood leh. e.g. Codominant leaders. -codominant n.

codominance n. genetics xaalad labada astaamood (both alleles) ee laba hidda-side oo kala duwan isku si loo soo bandhigikaro, ayada oo aan mindkoodna ahayn shiiqiye ama shiiqsane (dominant or recessive).

heterozygote (ˌhedharaw’zaay,gawt) n. qof, xoolo, ama noole kale oo leh labo hidda-side oo kala duwan (qayb ka mid ah unugga waxay xambaarsan tahay xogta DNA) taasna waxay xukuntaa wax gaar ah, waalid kastana hal baa laga soo hiddaqaatay, labadabana waa la sii dhaxlikraa.

contractile vacuole n. noole hal-unugle ah oo unugga ka saara wasakhda iyo biyaha dheeraadka ku ah.

cyanobacterium (ˌsaayanawbaak’tiriyam) n. bakteeriya (bacteria) cagaarley ah oo ku dhalata meelaha biyo fariisiga iyo dhagaxda. kale loogu yeeraa blue-green alga. –cyanobacterial (ˌsaayanawbaak’tiriyal) adj.

blue-green alga n., pl. blue-green algae also blue-green algas eeg cyanobacterium.

dark reaction n. dhawr falgal kiimiko (chemical reactions) oo cagaariyuhu (photosynthesis) uu san u baahnayn ilays oo ay saamaynayso yaraynta carbon dioxide si loo sameeyo carbohydrate; (khaasatan Calvin cycle).

Calvin cycle n. botany dhawr falgal kiimiko oo dhaca samaysanka cagaariye (photosynthesis), taas oo glucose (6-carbon sugar) ka dhalatay carbon dioxide.

deoxyribose (ˌdii’aaksi’raay,baws) n. sunkor pentose  C5H10O4 oo ah DNA walxaha ay ka samaysantahay, lehna qaabdhismeed DNA.

derived character n. wax absaxan laga soo hidda raacay: descendant.

dermal layer n. lakab maqaar, kan sare papillary dermis, kan hoosana reticular dermis.

papillary dermis n. maqaarka labkabiisa oo gudbiya nacfiga, xukumana heerkulka.

reticular dermis n. maqaarka culus oo hoose (inner layer of the skin), waxa uuna leeyahay xididdada dhiigga, salka timaha (hair follicles), qanjirrada, dhididka iyo saliidda.

dermal tissue n. dhirta diirkeeda sare (epidermis) oo ay ku jiraan xididdada, jirridda, caleemaha, ubaxa, khudaarta iyo miraha, mana xambaarsana cagaarside (chloroplast).

dichotomous key n. qalab cilmiyaysan oo muhiim ah laguna kala caddeeyo noolayaal kala duwan, laguna saleeyo hidda-raacyada muuqda.

endosymbiosis (ˌendaw,simbaay’yawsas) n. laba wada nool oo mid midka kale ku dhex noolyahay. –endosymbiont (ˌendaw’mimbay,aanti) n.; -endosymbiotic (ˌendaw,simbaay’aantik) adj.

dinoflagellate (ˌdaaynaw’falaajalat) n. hal-unugle (algae) ilma’aragto oo leh laba sayn-jeedalley.

mixotrophic (‘miksataraafik) adj. noole cunto samaysankara, haddana cunto cunikara.

symbiont (ˈsinbi,yaanti) n. noole la noolaada noolayaasha kale.

reverse transcriptase n. hab unugyada enzyme ay nuqul (copy) DNA ah ka sameeyaan RNA.

pinocytosis (ˌpinasa’tawsas) n. unug cabbe; hab unuggu u dhuuqo dareere iyo macdan ay maalikiyuullo yaryar mileen. –pinocytotic (ˌpinasa’taadhik) or -pinocytic (ˌpina’saaydhik) adj.; -pinocytotically (ˌpinasa’taadhiklii) adv.

endocytosis (ˌendasaay’tawsas) n. hab unugyadu ku dhuuqaan waxyaalaha dibadda ah ayaka oo xuubka gudaha (cell membrane) unugga isku wareejiyo. –endocytotic (ˌendhasaay’taadhik) adj.

essential amino acid n. wax jirku samaysankaro ma ahan ee waxay ka timaaddaa cunnada; sagaalka essential amino acid, waxaa ka mid ah: histidine, isoleucine, leucine, lysine, methionine, phenylalanine, threonine, tryptophan, iyo valine. Barbardhig nonessential amino acid.

nonessential amino acid n. jirku wuu samaysankaraa xataa haddii uusan ka helin cuntada aan cunno; waxaana ka mid ah: alanine, arginine, asparagine, aspartic acid, cysteine, glutamic acid, glutamine, glycine, proline, serine, iyo tyrosine. Barbardhig essential amino acid.

essential vitamins n. vitamins jirka waxay siiyaan in uu koro shaqeeyana; waxaana jira 13 nooc oo gundhig ah: vitamins A, C, D, E, K, iyo B vitamins (thiamine, riboflavin, niacin, pantothenic acid, biotin, B6, B12, and folate).

homeostasis (ˌhawmiyaw’isteysas) n. physiology awoodda habdhiseed ee noolaha oo dhan jirkooda caadi uga dhigaan si ay ula qabsadaan hadba bii’adda ay ku noolyihiin. e.g. Removing waste products from the body to maintain homeostasis. –homeostatic (ˌhawmiyaw’istaadhik) adj.

excretory system n. hab jirku ku saaro wasakhda iyo waxyaalaha kale ee dheeraadka ah oo aan loo baahnayn, sida kaadi, dhidid, ama saxaro (urine, sweat, ama feces).

exocytosis (ˌeksawsaay’tawsas) n., pl. exocytoses (ˌeksawsaay’taw,siiz)  unugga ka sii dayn qashinka gudihiisa ku jira. –exocytotic (ˌeksawsaay’taadhik) adj.

folding (ˈfawdhing) adj. laablaamma. e.g. A folding chair.

frameshift mutation n. baddalis hidda-side gaar ah, keentana tiris ama ku daris xariirka DNA akhriskeeda.

gene pool n. isku darka hidda-sidayaasha oo dhan iyo kuwa gaarka ah (alleles) oo ku jira taran ama sinjiyo (species).

glycolysis (galaay’kaalasas) n. hab glucose loo jajabiyo si ay u noqoto tamar (energy). –glycolytic (ˌgalaayka’lidhik) adj.

gradualism (ˈgaraajawa,lizam) n. marxaladaha kala duwan oo ay soo maraan isbaddalka sinjiyo tartiibtartiib u maraan.

homochromosomes n. eeg autosome.

homologous chromosomes n. laba hidda-side (chromosomes) oo lammaan oo mid ka yimid aabbe kan kalana hooyo.

parliamentary system n. parliamentary government.

parliamentary government n. nooc dawlad madaxeedu taahay ra’iisal wasaare (prime minister) ayna doorteen, mas’uulna ka yihiin sharcidajiyayaal (parliament).

integumentary system n. lakabka sare ee jirka, kana mid yihiin maqaarka, timaha, ciddiyaha, iyo qanjirrada; jirkana kala dirira jeermiska, qorraxda, iyo dhaawacanka.

karyotype (ˈkeriya,taayp) n. 1 muuqaalka guud ee hidda-side dhan oo ku jira unugyada sinjiyada ama noole kaligiis, ayada oo laga eegayo qiyaasta, tirada, qaabka, iwm. 2 diiwaan galinta hidda-side, siiba sawir ahaa                                                              -v. karyotyped; karyotyping; karyotypes baaris iyo diiwaangalin lagu sameeyo hidda-side. –karyotypic (ˌkeriya’tipik) adj.; -karyotypically (ˌkeriya’tipiklii) adv.

lungfish (ˈlang,fish) n. kalluunn sanbab uu ku neefsado leh, qaab kalluunna biyaha ugu neefsada.

lysogenic (ˌlaaysa’jenik) adj. martigaliya fayras (virus) gala unugga bakteriya (prophage). –lysogenicity (ˌlaaysaja’nisatii) n.

lysogeny (laay’saajanii) n. heerka martigalis lysogenic.

prophage (ˈparaw,feyj) n. fayras (virus) gala unugga bakteriya (bacterial cell) oo cidda martigalisay kala qaybisa ayada oo aan la burburin.

viral reproduction n. isbadin (istarmin) virus.

lysosome (ˈlaaysa,sawm) n. unug gudihiis qolqol kiish oo kale ah oo ay ku jiraan dheecaanka enzymes oo burbursha unugyada u baahan in laga takhaluso. –lysosomal (ˌlaaysa’sawmal) adj.

medusa (mi’dhuusa) n., pl. medusae (mi’dhuu,sii)  also medusas bahal yar oo bad-ku-nool ah madax dallad u egna leh. eeg jellyfish. –medusan (mi’dhuusan) adj. or n.; -medusoid (mi’dhuu,soydh) adj. or n.

meristematic tissue n. ka samaysan koox unugyo ah oo joogto isku badiya si ay u sameeyaan unugyo badan oo koriya geedaha.  

multiple allele n. qaabab kala duwan ee isku hidda-side (same gene) saamaynna ku yeesha isku astaan (same trait).

myelin sheath n. dufan (protein) ku dahaaran unug dareeme (nerve cell). kale loogu yeeraa medullary sheath.

medullary sheath n. eeg myelin sheath.

nondisjunction (ˌnaandhis’jangshan) n. lammaanaha hidda-sidayaasha (homologous chromosomes) oo kala fullaci waaya, taas oo ay samaysmato ayagii oo kale (daughter cells) oo wata tirooyin aan caadi ahayn ee hidda-side. –nondisjunctional (ˌnaandhis’jangshanal) adj.

phosphate group n. atom phosphorous oo afar atom oo oxygen ah wata, waxayna sameeyaan nucleic acid, sida DNA iyo RNA, qaybna ka yihiin tamar qaadayaasha.

phospholipid bilayer n. maalikiyuullo isku saaran laba lakab oo phosphate iyo lipid ah qaabeeyana xuubka unug. kale loogu yeeraa lipid bilayer.

lipid bilayer n. polar membrane khafiif ah oo ka samaysan laba lakab oo lipid molecules.

phylogeny (faay’laajanii) n., pl. phylogenies 1 barashada xariirka hidda-side ee ka dhexeeya kooxo noolayaal kala duwan ah iyo marxaladihii kala duwanaa ee abuurankooda. 2 taariikhdii iyo soo yaalkii koboca wax soo mareen, sida oraah, dhaqan iyo caado (custom).

phylogenetic (ˌfaay’lawja’nedhik) adj. 1 la xariira ama ah phylogeny. 2 ku salaysan xariirka ka dhexeeya marxaladaha caadiga. –phylogenetically (ˌfaaylawja’nedhiklii) adv.

pilus (ˈpaaylas) n., pl. pili (ˈpaay,lii) gas (xaad, timo) saaran unug ama bakteriya (bacteria). kale loogu yeeraa fimbriak.

fimbria (ˈfimbiriya) n., pl. fimbriae (ˈfimbirii,ii) 1 gas (xaad) saaran bacterium ama unug: PILUS. 2 afka hore ee dhuunta minka (fallopian tubes). –fimbrial (ˈfimbiriyal) adj.

biomarker (ˈbaayaw,maarkar) n. maalikiyuul (molecule) ku jira dhiigga, dareerayaasha kale, ama nudaha (tissues) oo ifafaale u ah fayaqab ama cudur in uu jirka ka jiro. kale loogu yeeraa molecular marker, signature molecule.

prognostic (paraag’naastik) n. 1 sii sheegis; sii ogaansho: portent. 2 prognostications, prophecy. –prognostic adj.

pharmacodynamics (ˌfaarmakawdhaay’naamikis) n. laan ka mid ah caafimaadka (pharmacology) oo gooni u eegta daawooyinka iyo falgalyada (reactions) kala dhexeeya habdhisyada noolaha (living systems). –pharmacodynamic (ˌfaarmakawdhaay’naamik) adj.; -pharmacodynamically (ˌfaarmakawdhaay’naamiklii) adv.

extrachromosomal (ˌekistara,karawma’sawmal) adj. abbr. ecDNA waxyaalo ka baxsan hidda-sidaha oo xukuma, sidii la rabana loo khaldo. e.g. extrachromosomal DNA molecules.

plasmid (ˈpalaazmad) n. goobo (ring) ka baxsan hidda-sidaha DNA, siiba bakteeriya (bacteria) iskeed isku badisa. e.g. Some bacteria have extrachromosomal DNA known as plasmids, which are self-replicating genetic material.

trisomy (ˈtaraay,sawmii) n., pl. trisomies hidda-side dheeraad ah oo la socda qaar ama unugyada jirka oo dhan; taas oo keenta saddex nuqul oo hidda-side (three copies of chromosome), meeshii caadiga laga rabay laba nuqul (two copies). –trisomic (ˌtaraay’sawmik) adj. or n.

plasmolyze (ˈpalaazma,laayz) v. plasmolyzed; plasmolyzing dhadid ama jawrarid, siiba unug dhashuuma.

endosmosis (ˌen,dhaas,mawsas) n. dhaqaaqa milangudeedka maalikiyuulada (molecules). Barbardhig exosmosis. –endosmotic (ˌen,dhaas’maadhi) adj.; -endosmotically (ˌen,dhaas’madhiklii) adv.  

deplasmolysis n. fuuris unug hore u dhaddanaa.

exosmosis (ˌek,saas’mawsas) n. qulqulka biyo ka baxa unugga markii unugyada la dhexdhigo milan hoose (hypotonic solution). Barbardhig endosmosis. –exosmotic (ˌek,saas’maadhik) adj.

point mutation n. baddalis hidda-side gooni ah, siiba ku daris ama tirtiris hal nucleotide base.

pollinator (ˈpaalana,neydhar) n. 1 faxal (pollen) qaade; wax kasta oo qaada faxal lab (stamen) una geeya dhaddig (stigma). 2 pollenizer.

pollenizer (ˈpaala,naayzar) n. also pollinizer 1 geed dhala faxal lab (pollen). 2 pollinators.

primary succession eeg prisere.

prisere n. meel aan wax ka soo bixijirin oo dhir isbajoog ah ka soo baxdo.

protein synthesis n. hab unugyo ku samaystaan proteins; waxayna martaa: transcription, translation, and post-translational events; transcription waa marka laga soo qaado DNA lana geeyo mRN ee bu’da (nucleus) oo aysii marto saddex tallaabo: initiation, elongation, iyo termination.

pseudocoelomate (ˌsuudhaw’siila,meyt) n. lafdhabarla’ (invertebrate)  khaanado-beeneedyo maran (false body cavities) gudaha jirka ku leh. pseudocoelom. –pseudocoelomate adj.

pseudocoelom (ˌsuudha’siilam) n. or pseudocoel (ˌsuudha,siil) pl. pseudocoeloms or pseudocoels lafdhabarla’ (invertebrate) khaanado jirka ah dareere buuxiyo.

punctuated equilibrium n. aragti oranaysa abuuranku dhaqsiyo ayuu u dhacaa inta uu tartiib tartii ahaan lahaa.

radial symmetry n. wanqar dhir, xoolo, ama noole kale laba isle’eg leh u kala goyn kor ilaa hoos. Barbardhig bilateral symmetry. -radially symmetrical adj.

stroma (ˈistarwma) n., pl. stromata (ˈistarawmadha) unug ama nud ka caawiya xibnaha, qanjirada, iyo meelo kale qaab dhiskooda jireed. –stromal (ˈistarawmal) adj.

thallus (ˈthaalas) n., pl. thalli (ˈthaa,laay) or thalluses doog; cagaar aan lahayn xidid, jirrid, ama caleemo, sida algae, fungi, ama mosses.

haptotropism (haap’taatra,pizam) n. biology taabad-dareeme; qaybo ka mid ah geed oo tabashada dareenta, siiba geed-saar (tendril).

tendril (ˈtendaral) n. 1 geed-saar (stem tendrils, iyo leaf tendrils). 2 wax kasta oo fanta ama qabsada. –tendrilled or -tendrilled (ˈtendaraldh) adj.; -tendrilous (ˈtendaralas)

hydrotropism (haay’daraatra,pizam) n. biya-raac (positive hydrotropism), siiba xidid geed; biyo-diid (negative hydrotropism), siiba geed laanti dhul ka soo baxda. –hydrotropic (ˌhaaydra’tarawpik) adj.

stereotropism n. 1 taabad-raace; aada dhinaca taabashada adke, siiba dhir. 2 stereotaxis. Barbardhig haptotropism.

stereotaxis (,isteriyo’taaksas) n., pl. stereotaxes dhaqaaqa xibin markii la taabto.

stereotactic (ˌisteriya’taaktik) adj. la xariira ama loo adeegto qalab qalliin oo aad u yar, sida irbad ama dhud kaah (beam of radiation). –stereotactically (ˌisteriya’taaktiklii) adv.

three-chambered heart n. saddex-qolqol wadne; xamaarato (reptiles) iyo barribiyood (amphibians), sida rah (frog) iyo qallajis (lizard) ayaa ah kuwa saddex-qolqoleyda ah (two atria and one ventricle).

allantois (a’laantawas) n., pl. allantoides (ˌaalan’tawa,dhiiz) makaan ama meel kiish oo kale ah (sac-like) oo uu ka buuxo dareere saafi ah oo qaabeeya shaharka ilmaha abuurmaya (developing amniote's). –allantoic (ˌaalan’tawik) adj.

binary fission n. biology dhanbalan; hab taran unuggu laba isle’eg u kala qaysamo (two daughter cells). Barbardhig multiple fission.

binomial nomenclature n. magacaabis labaysan; habdhis cilmiyaysan oo la siiyo noole, kana kooban laba magac, tusaale: magac cilimiyeedka tiger waa panthera tigris; meesha penthera = Genus tigirs = sinji (species).

biochemistry (,baayaw’kemastarii) n. 1 kimistariga noolaha; chemistry gooni u eega iskudhisyada kiimiko iyo habdhiyada ka dhexdhacaya noolayaasha. 2 dabeecadaha kiimiko iyo falgalladooda siiba noolayaasha. -biochemist (ˌbaayaw’kemsti) n.

biological control n. yaraynta tirada ama baabi’inta cayayaanka ayada oo la carqaladaynayo.  

biology factor n. isir biology; da’da, jinsiga, firsashada mataanaha, culaabta, dhererka, iwm.

biosynthesis (,baayaw’sinthasas) n. noole samayn ama dhis; soo saarka (production) ama samaynta iskudhisyo kiimikaad ee noolayaal nool (living organism). –biosynthetic (ˌbaayawsin’thedhik) adj.; –biosynthetically (ˌbaayawsin’thedhiklii) adv.

biotic community n. beel nafley; noole sabo ku wada nool oo isdhexgal bii’adeed ka dhexeeyo.

blood serum n. sayax dhiig; dareere saafi ah oo soo hara marka dhiigga xinjirta laga saaro.

body cavity n. moqor jireed; biyo jirka ku jira oo difaaca xibnha muhiimka ah: coelom.

bony fish n. kalluun lafeed. kale loogu yeeraa teleost. 

teleost (‘teelii,aasti) n. eeg bony fish. -teleost adj.; -teleostean (ˌtelii’aastiyan) adj.

book lunge n. sanbab buug; xibinta neefsashada ee caaro (spider), hangarale (scorpion), iyo bahda (arachnid) oo dhan.

Bowman's capsule n. moqorka Bowman; qayb ka mid ah shaandhada kallida (nephron) oo ah moqor oo kale, kuna wareegsanyihiin shabakad xididdo ah: glomerulus.

brain system n. jirrid maskaxeed.

Brownian motion n. dhaqdhaqaaqa Brownian; walxaha ilma’aragtada ah (microscopic particles) oo dhex miririfleya biyaha ama neefaha (gases) oo isku dhaca maalikiyuuladooda. kale loogu yeeraa Brownian movement.

Brownian movement n. eeg Brownian motion.

bulbil (‘balbal) n. eeg bulblet.

bulblet (‘balbalat) n. quwaax; buruq ama bari geed cusub ka soo baxo.

parenchyma (pa’reenkama) n. 1 aasaaska ama nudda (tissue) abuuranka xibinta. 2 cargo; nuddo (tissue) dhirta oo ka kooban lakab yar oo cagaariyuhu ku nool yahay (living photosynthetic) ama kaydka walxaha caleemaha, xididdada, buruqda miraha (pulp of fruits), iyo qaybaha laamaha. –parenchymal adj.; –parenchymatous (ˌperan’kaaymadhas) adj.

collenchyma (‘kaleenkama) n. nudda (tissue) adkaysa xajmina u yeesha gidaarada unugga, cargada ka dib. –collenchymatous (ˌkaalan’kimatas) adj.

sclerenchyma (iskala’renkama) n. nud (tissue) adkaysa geed oo ka kooban unugyada looxa adag. –sclerenchymatous (ˌiskaleran’kimatas) adj.

mesophyll (‘meeza,fiil) n. laba dhexda dubka sare ee caleen cargo ah. –mesophyllic (ˌmeza’filik) or – mesophyllous (ˌmeza’filas) adj.

bundle sheath n. kiish xirmo; lakab sameeya cargada geed quudisa.

bursa (‘barsa) n. dhareerey; dheecaan ku kala dhexjira kala goysyada xibnaha. –bursal (ˈbarsal) adj.

calcicole (‘kaalsa,kawl) n. dhir ku baxda nuuradda ama carrada kaalsiyamka leh (require calcium-rich soils). –calcicolous (kaal’sikalas) adj.

calcifuge (‘kaalsa,fiyuuj) n. dhir ku baxda ciidda aysidh leh oo kaalsiyam ku yaryahay (acid soils with low calcium). –calcifuge or –calcifugous (kaal’sifagas) adj.

canal system n. habdhis kelli; marinno isku xira meelo kala duwan oo jirka xoolaha ka mid ah.

carapace (‘keera,peys) n. 1 qolof; qob, siiba mid diin ama carsaanyo (turtle or crab). 2 shay wax difaaca, qurxiya, ama qariya.

cardinal vein n. aroore (xidid) wadneed.

vertebrate embryos n. uurjiif lafdhabarleey.

notochord (‘nawdha,koordh) n. arax; unugyo tax dheer ah oo qaabeeya dhiska jirka uurjiifta lafdhabarley. –notochordal (ˌnawdha’koordhal) adj.

carotid arch n. qaanso wadneed; halbawlayaasha waaweyn oo dhiigga ka qaada wadnaha geeyana madaxa.

carotid artery n. halbawle buufiye; halbawlaha weyn oo dhiigga ka qaada wadnaha gaarsiiyana madaxa.

cartilage bone n. laf carjaweed; laf ka qaabowday ama ka abuurmatay carjaw. Barbardhig membrane bone.

membrane bone n. laf ka samaysmatay nudaha (tissues) ku xirma ayada oo aan soo marin carjaw (cartilage). Barbardhig cartilage bone.

catalase (‘kaadha,laays) n. ladagaalaha sunta jirku sameeyo; dheecaanka enzyme ayaana soo dadajiya falgalkaas kiimiko. –catalatic (ˌkaadhalaadhik) adj.

cauline (‘koo,laayn) adj. la xariira ama ka baxa laan qaybteeda sare.

cell body n. jir unugeed; bu’da iyo inteeda xambaarsan qaybta dhexe ee dareeme.

cell cycle n. meerto unug; habdhiska unug maro markasta oo uu iskala qaybiyo ama tarmo.

cell membrane n., pl. cell membranes xuub unug; qaybta gudaha unug ayuu ka dahaara dibadda. kale loogu yeeraa plasma membrane ama cytoplasmic membrane.

cell cap n. fuuq ama fur unug

cell sap n. 1 dareere ama dheecaan ku jira unugga dhirta. 2 cytosols.

cytosol (‘saaydha,saal) n. dareere ku dhex jira unugga. kale loogu yeeraa ground substance.

ground substance n. 1 walxo dhagdhag ah oo laga helo xuubka isku xiryada ama carjawda. 2 walxo xuubka unugyada ku dhex jira. kale loogu yeeraa cytosol.  

cell theory n. aragti unug; unuggu waa aasaaska dhismaha waxa nool, nooluhuna waxa uu ka koobanyahay unugyo xor ah (autonomous cells) waxa ay leeyhiinna ay tahay nudda unugga isku darkooda unugyadaas.

cellular organelles n. xubnayaro unugeed; qaabdhisyo yaryar oo ku dhexjira unug, kuna wareegsanyahay xuub oo qabta shaqo gaar ah.

neoplastic (,niiya’palaastik) adj. buro aan caadi ahayn oo qaabaysmata markii unugyadu koraan oo sii qaybsamaan.

neoplasticism (ˌniiya’palaasta,sizam) n. eeg de Stijl. –neoplasticist (ˌniiya’palaastasisti) n.

de Stijl (dha’staayl) n. dugsi farshaxan (art) oo Holland laga aasaasay 1917 oo adeegsada qaabab laydi (rectangular forms) oo adeegta madaw iyo caddaan iyo midabyada asalka ah (primary colors).

neoplasia (,niiya’paleyshiya) n. abuuranka buro; siiba mid aan noqon ama noqota kaankaro (may be benign (not cancer) or malignant (cancer).

cellular transformation n. doorin unugeed; unug wax uu isku baddali karaa buro (neoplastic cell) oo shaqada jirku (body process) wax hawl ah uusan ku lahayn.

Cenozoic (ˌsiina’zawik) adj. 66 million sano oo hore ilaa maanta nolosha ah (recent life). – Cenozoic n.

cephalochordate (,sefalaw’koor,dheyt) n., pl. cephalochordates madax araxley. –cephalochordate adj.

cephalothorax (,sefala,thoor,aakis) n. madaxsaabley; madaxa iyo saableyda oo qayb ahaan iskugu xiran.

subphylum (‘sab,faaylam) n. ka hooseeya dabaqadda: phylum.

taxonomy (taak’saanamii) n. 1 biology kala heerayn cilmiyaysan (scientific classification) ee wax barashadooda guud. 2 barashada noolaha sida xayawaan, dhir, ilama’aragto (microorganisms), iyo dad kala dabaqadayntooda si wax looga sii barto. –taxonomic (ˌtaaksa’naamik) or -taxonomical (ˌtaaksa’naamikal) adj.; -taxonomically (ˌtaaksa’naamiklii) adv.; -taxonomist (taak’saanamisti) n.

cervical groove n. xordan luquneed; dureertada xulan ee jeegada iyo qalfoofka (carapace) kala qaybisa.

cestode (‘se,stawdh) n. gooryaan mullaax; gooryaan ballaaran oo ku noolaada marinada caloosha dadka. kale loo yaqaan tapeworm.

chemoreceptor (,kiimawri’septar) n. dareeme kiimikeed; dareeme gaar ah oo dareema waxyaalaha kiimikeed ee dhigga, una dira maskaxda si loo caadi yeelo wareegga dhiigga iyo hawsha neefsashada (regulate cardiovascular and respiratory functions). kale loogu yeeraa chemosensory.

chemosensory (,kiimaw’sensarii) adj. la xarira dareeme kiimiko (chemosensor), dirana baaq dareen ee xagga ur iyo dhadhan (olfaction and taste).

chemosynthesis n. habdhis samayn tamar kiimikaad (chemical energy) oo loogu baddalo carbohydrates cunto noole. -chemosynthetic (ˌkiimawsin’thedhik) adj.

Chondrichthyes (kaan’dhirikthii,iiz) n. kalluun carjawweed; nooc kalluun daameed (jawed fishes) oo leh qalfoof carjaw ah (cartilaginous skeleton). Barbardhig Cyclostomata.

Cyclostomata (,saaykalaw,istawmadha) noun plural noocyo kalluun lafdhabarla’ (invertebrates) oo aan lahayn daaman, laakiin leh ilko iyo af wareegsan (round mouths). Barbardhig Chondrichthyes.

Chordata (koor’dhaadha) noun plural araxley. –Chordate (ˈkoor,dheyt) n. or adj.

chorion (‘koori,yaan) n. xuub gudeed ugxan ama uurjiif; xuub ku dahaaran uurjiif; qayb weynna ka qaataa isku gudbinta dhiigga iyo neefta (gases) ka dhexeeysa hoyada iyo uurjiifta.

chromatid (‘karawmadhidh) n. mid ka mid ah labada miiq oo isku eg (two identical halves) ee hidda-side (chromosome), kaas oo isku diyaariya iskala qaybin unugeed.

chromatin tissue n. nud DAN iyo proteins qaabeeya hidda-sidayaasha (chromosomes) laga helo unugyada dadka.

chromoplast (‘karawma,palaasti) n. nudo xambaarsan midabka casaan ama hurdi (yellow).

chromomere (ˈkarawma,miir) n. wax yar oo kuulo u eg oo ku dhaggan hidda-side (chromosome). –chromomeric (ˌkarawma’merik) adj.

ciliary muscles n. muruqyada baarka indhaha.

ciliated cell n. unug ganley; dixiri tin le’eg oo gala dusha unugyada naasleyda oo dhan.

circular canals n. kelliyo wareegsan; saddex dhuumood oo yaryar kuna dhexjira dhagta oo shaqadooduna tahay in ay habeeyaan dheellitiranka iyo dareen jihaynta madaxa (sense head position).

citric acid cycle n. eeg Krebs cycle.

Krebs cycle n. meertada aashitada citric; hab isdabaxig ee ka dhexdhasha jajabinta cuntada (mitochondria), taas oo unugyada noolaha oo dhan ka samaystaan tamar ku dhexlaran neefsashada. kale loogu yeeraa citric acid cycle, tricarboxylic acid cycle.

tricarboxylic acid cycle n. eeg Krebs cycle.

cloaca (kalaw’eyka) n., pl. cloacae dabo, siiba meesha wax ka baxaan ee xaar, kaadi, ama marin taran (genital tracts) ee barribiyood (amphibians), xamaarato (reptiles), shinbiro, iyo kalluun. –cloacal adj.

monotreme (ˈmaana,tiriim) n. dir (class) ka mid ah naasleyda oo ukun dhasha.

coelom (‘siilam) n., pl. coeloms also coelomata (sa’lawmata) qaaxo; meel jir ka duleesha oo dareere mareen ah. -coelomate (ˈsiila,meyt) adj. or n. –coelomic (si’laamik) adj.

coelomic cavity n. moqor qaaxeed; meel dareere iyo hawo buuxiso oo noole badan leeyahay, waxayna difaac u tahay xibnaha uur ku jirta (internal organs).

colloidal system n. habdhis kala firdhis; nooc iskuqas qayb ka mid ah joogto tankale loogu kala firdhiyo, laakiin aysan isku milmin.

companion cell n. unugyo weheleed; unug bu’eed noole oo xiriir asaleed, meeleed, ama shaqeed leh oo sameeya marinnada geedaha dhuumaha leh (vascular plant).

comparative physiology n. fiisiyoolaji isgarabdhig; barashada isbarbardhigga sida jirka nooluhu iskugu baddalo ku xirnaanta baya’ddooda.

compensation point n. heer dheelitiran; barta dhaqsaha samayska cagaariyaha (photosynthesis) geedku marka uu la mid noqodo, dhaqsaha neefsiga (rate of respiration).

complete metamorphosis n. qaabrogosho dhan; marka noole maro afarta qaabrogosho: metamorphosis. egg larva, pupa, adult.

complex cells n. unugyo murakab ah; waxaa wax soo gaarsiiya dhawr xididdo fudud ah (simple cells) n.

conceptacle (kan’septikal) n. sati; duleel dibadda ah oo xambaarsan taranka.

conditional reflex n. falcelis ku xiran; ka jawaabis wax hore loo bartay ee dad ama xayawaan kale; tusaale: koor baa layeershay, hilibana waa la keenay, eeygiina waa cunay hilibkii; markii koor la yeersho eygu waxa uu filyaa in la keeno hilib.

connective tissue n. nudo iskuxirayaal; isku xirayaasha caawiya isku xirka nudaha jirka, kaydiyana dufan, kabana nudaha dhaawacan.

contractile (kan’taraaktal) adj. rooriya; ururiya ama uruuray; rooray. e.g. Contractile vacuoles.

control of cell division n. caynaaninta qaybsan unugga; habdhiska hal unug isku sii qaybiyo labo.

convoluted tubule n. dhuun-yaro laablaaban; kulli ama qaybteed ka mid ah shaandhada (nephron).

luteum (‘luutiyam) n. eeg corpus luteum.

corpus luteum (‘koorpas ‘luutiyam) n. abbr. CL pl. corpora lutea unugyo garooray; dheecaan hurdi (yellow) ee habdhiska taran dumar (female reproduction system) sii daayo meertada caado kasta.

CL n. abbr. corpus luteum.

crop rotation n. dalag gaddis; hab abuurka loo kala geddiyo beer xilliyadeed.  

cross-fertilization (‘karoos,fartala’zeyshan) n. bacrin tallow; bacranka lab iyo dheddig unugyadooda jinsi (sex cells) qaabeeyaan laba qof oo kala duwan, laakiin isku sinji (species) ah.

crossing-over n. isku-tallaw; iswaydaarisiga lammaanaha DNA ee ka dhexeeya waalid oo mid kasta hal hidda-raac ka yimid (paired homologous chromosomes one from each parent) samaysmana inta lagu gudajiro bacranka ukunta iyo unugyada xawada (sperm cells).  

cross-pollination n. faxlid-tallow, tallaabin faxal (pollen) lab ubaxeed midka dhaddigeed (stigma).

crustacea (,kara’steysha) noun plural noole badan oo biyo-ku-nool ah (aquatic arthropods), kana mid yihiin carsaanyo (crabs), aragoste (lobsters), iyo shrimps oo intooda badan leeyhihiin afar ama ka badan lammaane addimood (pairs of limbs) iyo dowr kale oo ku dhaggan (appendages): crustaceans.

crustacean (ˌkara’steyshan) n. noole badan oo biyo-ku-nool ah (aquatic arthropods), kana mid yihiin carsaanyo (crabs), aragoste (aragostes), iyo shrimps. –crustacean adj.

cytolysis (saay’taalasas) n. buqis ama burburis unug: pathological breakdown of a cell. –cytolytic (ˌsaadha’lidhik) adj.

osmotic lysis n. buqis ama dillaacis nud unug ayada oo ay ku soo furteen biyo hoose (hypotonic).

lysis (‘laaysas) n., pl. lyses (ˈlaay,siiz)1 tartiib u yaraada, siiba xummad. 2 burbur iyo baaba’ ku yimaada unugyo: destruction.

-lysis n. comb. form 1 kalabax (decomposition) ama jajab (breakdown). 2 milanyo: dissolving. 3 baaba’; burbur: disintegration.

aquaporin (ˌaakwa’pooran) n. marin biyood, dhawr proteins oo laga helo xuub unug oo si xulasho leh u ogolaada in biyo soo galaan ama ka baxaan.

pyrimidine (paay’rima,diin) n. 1 iskudhis noole (organic base) ah aasaasi C4H4N2 ur adagna leh. 2 iskudhis cytosine, thymine, ama uracil oo ay ka samaysanyihiin DNA ama RNA.

daughter cells n. unugyada mataanaysan; unugyo ka yimid qaybsanka hal waalid unugeed (a single parent cell).

daylight vision n. aragti ilays maalmeel; aragtida maalmeed oo ku filan hummaag: photopic vision.

photopic vision n. iftiin ku filan indhaha.

decomposer (,diikam’pawsar) n. bulunbulyayn; baqticunayaal; noole kasta oo cuna dhir ama bakhti.

decortication (,dii,koordha’keyshan) n. 1 dhilis fiiqis; murxis; diiris, siiba laan, jiirrid, xidid, ama mir. 2 fiiqis amd diirqaadis, siiba qalliin xibin jirka ah, sida maskaxda ama kallida. –decorticator (ˌdii’koordha,keydhar) n.

thoracotomy (,thoora’kaadhamii) n., pl. thoracotomies qalliin lagu sameeyo xabadka, siiba laba dhexda feeraha, si loo eego sanbabka ama uur-ku-jirta kale.

deficiency disease n. nafaqo yaraansho; cudur yimaada markii jirka ay ku yaraato vitamins ama macdan (minerals).

dehisce (di’hiis) v. dehisced; dehiscing 1 biliqin ama bujin mir, siiba soo baxaysa oo furmi weyday. 2 bujin ama dillaacin meel dhaawacan.

germinability (,jarmana’biladhii) n. soo bixis; soo dhalasho, siiba mir: germinate.

dehiscence (dihisantis) n. 1 dhambalme, siiba mir. 2 buqis, bujis, siiba nabar. –dehiscent (di’hisanti) adj.

dehydrogenase (,dii,haay’daraaja,neys) n. ka saarista hydrogen; dheecaan (enzyme) oo dedejiya ka saarista hydrogen ka cuntada (metabolites) una baddela walxo kale (other substances). kale loogu yeeraa succinate dehydrogenase.

denitrification (,dii,naaytrafa’keyshan) n. nitrogen tirid; dhumis ama saaris nitrogen ama iskudhis nitrogen (nitrogen compound). –denitrifier (dii’naaytra,faayar) n.; -denitrify (ˌdii’naaytra,faay)v.

dental formula n. jid ilkood; hab lagu qeexo tirada iyo isku aadka ilkaha dadka iyo xoolaha, ayada oo la isticmaalo xarfo iyo jaantusyo; tusaale: i (incisor), c (canine), pm (premolar) ama b (bicuspid), iyo m (molar).

dental groove n. xordan ilkood; jeexjeexyada mara gawsaha korkooda.

deoxyribonuclease (,dhii’aaksi,raaybaw’niyuuklii,eys) n. eeg DNase.

DNase (dnii,een’eys) n. or DNAase (dii en eeys).

guanosine (‘guwaan,siin) n. nucleoside C10H13N5O5 ka kooban guanine iyo ribose (ribofuranose).

guanine (‘guwaa,niin) n. purine base C5H5N5O oo xambaarsan xogta noolahaas (genetic information) ee ku jirta silsiladda polynucleotide ee DNA ama RNA. Barbardhig adenine, cytosine, thymine, uracil. 

uracil (ˈyuura,sil) n. purine base C5H5N5O oo xambaarsan xogta noolahaas (genetic information) ee ku jirta silsiladda polynucleotide ee DNA ama RNA. Barbardhig adenine, cytosine, guanine, thymine.

thymine (ˈthaay,meen) n. purine base C5H5N5O oo xambaarsan xogta noolahaas (genetic information) ee ku jirta silsiladda polynucleotide ee DNA ama RNA. Barbardhig adenine, cytosine, guanine, uracil.

adenine (ˈaada,niin): purine base C5H5N5O oo xambaarsan xogta noolahaas (genetic information) ee ku jirta silsiladda polynucleotide ee DNA ama RNA. Barbardhig cytosine, guanine, thymine, uracil.

cytosine (ˈsaaydha,siin) n. purine base C5H5N5O oo xambaarsan xogta noolahaas (genetic information) ee ku jirta silsiladda polynucleotide ee DNA ama RNA. Barbardhig adenine, guanine, thymine, uracil.

polynucleotide (,paalii’nuukliya,taaydh) n. silsilad maalikiyuullo (polymeric) oo ka kooban nucleotides badan.

depauperate (di’poparat) adj. 1 botany ragaas ah; aan korin. 2 cilin ah. 3 impoverished.

dicotyledon (,dhaay,kaadha’liidhan) n., pl. dicotyledons laba-beerjiifle; mir gudaha ku leh laba caleemood oo mataan. kale loogu yeeraa dicot. Barbardhig monocotyledon. –dicotyledonous (ˌdhaayˌkaadha’liidhanas) adj.

monocot (‘maana,kaat) n., pl. monocots hal beerjiifle; mir gudaha ku leh hal caleen beerjiif. Barbardhig dicot.

dicot (ˈdhaay,kaat) n., pl. dicots laba-beerjiifle; mir gudaha ku leh laba caleemood oo mataan. Barbardhig monocot.

digestive enzyme n. dheecaan (enzyme) dheefshiid; proteins jirka ku jira oo burburiya cuntada, caawiyana dheefshiidka.

digestive glands n. qanjirro dheefshiid; qanjirro sii daaya dheecaan oo ka qaybqaata dheefshiidka, sida: salivary glands, gastric glands, liver, pancreas, and intestinal glands.

digestive system n. habdhis dheefshiid; meesha jirku ku baduugo cuntada kana dhuuqo nafaqada.

dihybrid (,dhaay’haaybradh) adj. iskadhal; waxay iska dhaleen laba ku kala duwan labada lammaanayaasha hidda-side (two pairs of genes). –dihybrid n.

dimorphous (dhaay’moorfas) adj. labaqaable; laba qaab oo kala duwan leh. e.g. dimorphous leaves.

diploblastic (,dhiblaw’balaastik) labaduuble; xayawaan unugyadoodu u samaysanyihiin laba lakab oo uurjiifeed (two embryonic layers), kan ugu sarreeya (ectoderm), kan gudaha ahna (endoderm).

 diploid number n. tiro lammaane; xambaarsan 46 hidda-sidayaal (chromosomes) marka haploid yahay 23 hidda-sidayaal (chromosomes).

discontinuous distribution n. filqan; aan is-haysan, siiba meel xoolo ku noolaanjiray ay ka dabargo’een.

DNA cycle n. meertada DNA; habka unugyadu isku badin karaan oo laba unug oo cusub u noqdaan.

eukaryotic (,yuu,keerii’aadhik) adj. la xariira unug ama noole (cell ama organism) kasta oo leh bu’ la tilmaamikaro.

DNA replication n. dheegidda DNA; habdhis maalikiyuullada DNA sameeyaan nuqul (copy) kale oo la mid ah.

DNA synthesis n. samaynta DNA; dabeeciyan ama samays maalikiyuullada deoxyribonucleic acid (DNA).

dominant character n. astaan shiiqiye; hidda-sidaha awoodda badan oo tiisa la raaco.

dorsal aorta n. xidid duleed; xididdada in ay shaqeeyaan ugu horreeya ee uurjiif (embryonic blood vessels).

dorsal vessel n. dhuun duleed; habdhiska wareegga cayayaan.

double circulation n. wareeg lammaan; dhiigga oo laba jeer mara wadnaha halkii wareeg gudihiis.

double fertilization n. bacrin lammaan; la xariira laba unug xawo, mid waxa uu xalliyaa unugga ukunta (egg cell) si uu u sameeyo bacrimane (zygote), kan kalana wuxu xariiriyaa (two polar nuclei).

drosophila (daraw’saafala) n. diqsi mireed; bahda Drosophilidae, inta badanna la dhahaa "small fruit flies" ama pomace flies, vinegar flies, ama wine flies.

ear ossicle n. laf dhageed; saddex lafood oo yaryar oo ku dhexjira dhagta, una sii gudbiya gariirka hawada si cod loo sameeyo.

echinoderm (i’kayna,darm) n. bad-ku-nool lafdhabarla’ oo ay ka mid yihiin sea stars, sea urchins, sea cucumbers, brittle stars, iyo feather stars. –echinodermatous (i,kaana’darmatas) adj.

effector neuron n. unug dareen dhaqaaqe, siiba qanjir ama muruq.

effector organ n. xibin dhaqdhaqaaq, siiba meel jirka ka mid ah oo ka jawaabta taabasho ama qunjayn kale.

retinue (redha,nuu) n. 1 koox raacda qof madax ah. e.g. The boxer came with a retinue of five, and his friends. 2 koox la socota boqor.

folderol (‘faal,daraal) n. or falderal 1 aan macna lahayn (nonsense). 2 shay qurxineed aan wax qayme ah lahayn.

efferent branchial arteries n. halbawlayaasha ka fula; dhiig oxygen wata ayay qaybaha jirka oo dhan gaarsiiyaan.

efferent loop n. qool fula (taga); qoolka cuntada ka qaada caloosha; kan caloosha sarana (upper stomach) waxaa la dhahaa afferent loop.

egestion (i’jesshan) n. saxarood; xaaris, siiba cunto aan la dheefshiidin (undigested food material): defecation. –egest (i’jesti) v.; -egestive (i’jestiv) adj.

egg membrane n. xuub ugxaneed; xuub dahaara ukunta: vitelline membrane.
