vitelline membrane n. xuub kala qaybsha ukunta qaybteeda hurdiga (yolk) iyo xabka (albumen).

elastic cartilage n. carjaw loolsanta; carjaw jaalle xigeen ah oo jiidmata, sida: external ear, eustachian tube, larynx iyo epiglottis.

embryogenesis (,embariyaw’jenasas) n. qaabaw (formation) iyo korintaan uurjiif (embryo). –embryogenetic (ˌembiriyawja’nedhik) adj.

embryo sac n. kiish uurjiifeed; abuuranka makaan u-eke unugga hidda-sidaha dhaddig ee qaybta taransamaynta geed mirtiisa.

embryonic membrane n. xuub uurjiifeed; qayb kalkaalisa difaacdana uurjiif; kamana qayb qaadato qaabayn iyo koboc toona.

embryonic period n. sida uurjiifeed; inta badan ka bilawda asbuuca saddexaad ee uuraysiga ilaa asbuuca siddeedaad.

embryophyte (‘embiriiya,faayt) n. uurjiifley; dhir uurjiiftu ku harto gudaha makaanka.

decidua (dhi’sijawa) n., pl. deciduae (dhi’sija,wii) xuub ku jira minka uurleyda (hooyada) qayb weynna ka qaata difaacidda uurjiifta, siiyana nafaqo. –decidual (dh’sijawal) adj.

encyst (in’sisti) v. encysted; encysting; encysts dahaarmid; kuusmid, siiba meel nabar ama feex noqtay. –encystment (in’sismanti).

deciduate (dhi’sijawat) adj. la xariira ama leh xuub ku jira ninka uurleyda: decidua.

endocrine system n. habdhis qanjir marin la’; qanjirrada iyo xibnaha (organs) sameeya dheecaannada (hormones) oo toos ugu sii daaya dhiigga, sida: pituitary, thyroid, parathyroids, adrenals, ovaries, iyo testes.

endoderm (‘enda,darm) n. kan ugu hooseeya saddexda lakab: ectoderm (lakab sare) iyo mesoderm (lakab dhexe) ee uurjiifta oo qaabeeya (epithelium) marin dheefshiid (digestive tract) iyo qaybaha kale ee jirka. –endodermal (ˌenda’darmal) adj.

endodermal cells n. unugyo dubgudeed; unugyada dubka sare xayawaan (animals), taas oo uurjiifta siisa lakabka sare, unugyada ectoderm joogto ayayna isku badbaddalaan.

endoplasm (‘enda,palaazam) n. bu’da gudeed ee unugga qaybtiisa dareeraha; unug qaybtiisa guddaha hoose, gudihiisa sarena waa (cytoplasm). –endoplasmic (,enda’plaazmik) adj.

endoplasmic reticulum n. iliilo unug gudeed; gudaha unug marinnada gudbiya nafaqooyin (proteins) iyo dhaqdhaqaaqa kale ee bu’eed.

lipopolysaccharide (,laaypaw,paali’saaka,raaydh) n. maalikiyuul (molecule) weyn oo ka kooban dufan (lipids) iyo sonkor oo kiimiko ahaan iskugu dhaggan.

heat-stable substance n. walxo ku jooga qaabkooda, habdhiskooda, iyo shaqadooda xataa haddii heerkul sare lagaarsiiyo.

endotoxin (,endaw’taaksan) n. mariid gudeed; waa lipopolysaccharides (LPS) (maalikiyuullo waaweyn) oo keena Gram-negative sepsis. –endotoxic adj.

entomophilous (,enta’maafalas) adj. cayayaan faxliye; cayayaan-jecle (insect-loving); dhir ubaxoodu soo jiito cayayaan si ay u faxliyaan: zoophilic. –entomophily (ˌenta’maafalii)

zoophilic (,zawa’filik) adj. or zoophilous (zaw’aafalas) soo jiita xayawaan ama cayayaan, siiba dhir.

endophyte (‘enda,faayt) n. bu’ la’aan; noole ama jeermis (fungi ama bacteria) ku dhexnool unugga geed nool. –endophytic (ˌenda’fidhik) adj.

epicotyl (‘epi,kaadhal) n. caleen soo baxday qoorteeda wali dhulka ku jirta.

epididymis (,epa’didamas) n., pl. epididymides (ˌepa’didhama,dhiiz)  xidid isku jaruursan oo xaniin kasta ku dul wareegsan, kaydiyana xawada (sperm). –epididymal (epa’dhidhamal) adj.

goose bumps plural noun jariiraco, siiba xaadda ama timaha oo kaca (qabaw, naxdin, ama baqdin): piloerection.

piloerection (ˌpaaylawi’rekshan) n. jariiraco xaadda ama timuhu istaagaan, siiba qabaw, naxdin, ama baqdin: erector muscle.

goose pimples n., pl. eeg goose bumps.

erector muscle n. muruq xaad-taag; muruq yar oo ku yaal salka xaadda ama timaha oo kiciya: goose bumps.

red blood cell n. or red blood corpuscle or red cell or red corpuscle unug dhiig cas. kale loogu yeeraa erythrocyte.

erythrocyte (i’rithra,saayt) n. eeg red blood cell. -erythrocytic (i,rithra’sidhik) adj.

erythropoiesis (i,rithrawpoy’iisas) n. samaysanka dhiigga cas gudaha dhiigga oo shan heer mara: (proerythroblast, erythroblast, normoblast, reticulocyte iyo erythrocyte (noqda dhiig cas oo dhan). –erythropoietic (i,rithrawpoy’yadhik) adj.

proerythroblast (‘paraw’rithra,balaasti) n. unug dhiigga cas oo ku jira heerka horraanta abuurmadkiisa (erythropoiesis). –proerythroblastic (ˈparawi,rithra’balaastik) adj.

hemocytoblast n. jirrid xidid oo samaysa dhiig. kale loogu yeeraa lymphoidocyte. -hemocytoblastic adj.

lymphoidocyte (lim’foydha,saayt) n. eeg hemocytoblast.

erythroblast (i’rithra,balaasti) n. unug dhiig oo ku jira dhuuxa oo qaabeeya unugga dhiigga cas (red blood cell). –erythroblastic (i,rithra’balaastik) adj.

normoblast (‘noorma,balaasti) n. unug dhiigga cas oo aan wali qaangaarin, laakiin qaada oxygen. –normoblastic adj.

reticulocyte (ri’tikyalaw,saayt). unug dhiig cas oo aan shin dhammaysan (immature red blood cell), maalinta horana ka qaybgala wareegga dhigga, kadibna loo aqoonsado unug dhiigga cas ka mid ah.

etiolate (‘iidhiya,leyt) v. etiolated; etiolating 1 dhadin, siiba geed koristiisa laga qarshay ilayska oo caleemihii dhadeen ama caddaadeen. 2 dhaday; caddaaday. –etiolation (ˌiidhiya’leyshan) n.

evagination (i,vaaja’neyshan) n. guda-kor-soomaris; gaddis, siiba gudaha kor soo marin (inside out).

gastrulation (,gaastara’leyshan) n. habdhiska hore ee uurjiif  ka baxdo lakab hal-wajiyaale unugyo ah (blastula cells) iskuna qaabayso dhawr lakab iyo dhawr waji oo la dhaho (gastrula). –gastrulate (ˈgaastara,leyt) intransitive verb.

gastrula (‘gaastarala) n., pl. gastrulas or gastrulae   (ˈgaastara,lii) qaab-haruubeed (cup-shaped) saddex-lakabeed ah oo uurjiifta horteed ka samaysmata dhaqdhaqaaqa unugyo lakabyo ah si ay u abuuraan (ectoderm, mesoderm, iyo endoderm). Barbardhig blastula, morula. –gastrular (ˈgaastaralar) adj.

morula (ˈmooryala) n., pl. morulae (ˈmooryalii) also morulas calaq; xinjir samaysmata markii ilmuhu abuurmaan. –morular (ˈmooryalar) adj.; -morulation (ˌmoorya’leyshan) n.

ectoderm (‘ekta,daram) n. 1 kan sare saddexda lakab ee uurjiif oo qaabab iyo nudo kala duwan xambaarsan. 2 qaybta sare ee unugyada (jellyfish). –ectodermal (ˌekta’darmal) adj.

blastula (‘balaasjala) n., pl. blastulas or blastulae (ˈbalaasja,lii) moqor ama kubbad maran oo unugyo ah (blastomeres), samaysmana markii uurjiiftu abuurmato. Babardhig gastrula, morula. –blastulation (ˌbalaasja’leyshan) n.

invaginate (in’vaaja,neyt) v. invaginated; invaginating 1 dahaarid; galayn. 2 gaddin; rogid, siiba gudaha soo kormarin: invagination.

excretory organs n. xibnaha qashinsaarka jirka, sida: skin, liver, large intestine, lungs, iyo kidneys.

excurrent (,ek’iskaranti) adj. 1 toos u baxa, siiba qulqul danab. 2 toos ubaxa, siiba geed yuuqan oo jiirridu hoggaamiso. Barbardhig deliquescent sense 2.

decurrent (di’karanti) adj. aan toos u bixin, siiba geed; hoos-u-bax. e.g. Decurrent leaves. Barbardhig decurrent.

excurrent growth n. toos-u-bax; geed jirriddu aanay qaybsamin oo tiir leh.

exodermis (,eksaw’darmar) n. dub sare, dub-duleed; lakabka sare  ee unugyada dhirta nool oo qabta shaqada xididdada aan wali weynaan.

extensor (ik’istensar) n. fidiye, siiba muruq kala bixiya addin (limb). kale loogu yeeraa extensor muscle. Barbardhig flexor.

flexor (‘faleksar) n. muruq laaba meel jirka ah, sida addin (limb). kale loogu yeeraa flexor muscle. Barbardhig extensor.

external auditory canal n. dalool duleelka hore ee dhagta ilaa durbaanka (eardrum) maqalka gudaha. kale loogu yeeraa external acoustic meatus or external auditory meatus.

external auditory meatus n. duleel duleedka hore ee dhagta ilaa durbaanka (eardrum) maqalka gudaha. kale loogu yeeraa external acoustic meatus or external auditory canal.

external acoustic meatus n. duleel duleedka hore ee dhagta ilaa durbaanka (eardrum) maqalka gudaha. kale loogu yeeraa external auditory meatus or external auditory canal.

extracellular (,ekistar’selyalar) adj. dibadda unugga ah ama ka dhaca. e.g. extracellular fluid. –extracellularly adj.

extracellular digestion n. dheefshiid duleed unug; qaab dheefshiideed oo nafaqada aad loo jajabsho si looga duldhuuqo unug.

extraembryonic (,ekstara,embrii’aanik) adj. uurfjiif duleed; ka dhaca ama dibadda ka ah uurjiif.

eyelid (‘aay,liid) n., pl. eyelids xirrib; daboolka isha; haragga xira/fura gurux ileed (eyeball).

eye muscle n. muruq ileed.

facial nerve n. dareen side waji; todobada dareen side oo xukuma dhaqdhaqaaqa wajiga.

faeces n. (British spelling of feces) xaar, saxaro.

fat body n. 1 jir dufaneed; nudo dufaneed tamar ahaan cayayaanku u isticmaalo waqtiga hurdadheer (hibernation) iyo waqtiga isdhalanrogga (metamorphosis). 2 nudo la mid ah oo adeegtaan xamaarato (reptiles) iyo baribiyood (amphibians).

fat cell n. unugyo dufaneed; unugyo gaar ah oo ka kooban unugyada adipose (adipose cell) oo u kaydiya tamarta dheeraadka ah qaab dhibco dufaneed (triglyceride droplets): adipocyte.

fatty acid n. asiidh dufaneed; meesha dufanka laga soo saaro cuntada aan cunno; inta lagu jiro dheefshiidka, jirku cuntada marka uu jajabiyo waxa uu soo saaraa fatty acid, kadibna dhiigga ayaa dhuuqa oo sameeya koox maalikiyuullo saddex iskugu jira oo la dhaho triglyceride.

fertile soil n. carro san; carro leh nafaqo ku filan koritaanka geed.

fertility (,far’tilatii) n. 1 bacimin: fertile. 2 dhaqaal; dhalis; awood ilma dhalis.

spermatozoon (,ispar,maadha’zaw,aan) n., pl. spermatozoa (ˌispar,maadha’zawa) 1 manida (semen) lab oo dhaqaaqikarta, lehna madax iyo sayn ay ku sabbayso. 2 spermatozoid. –spermatozoal (ˌispar,maadha’zawal) adj.

fertilization membrane n. xuub bacramin; xuub ka abuurma korka gudaha xuubka jilicsan (vitelline membrane) ee ukuntu marka xawadu gasho si xawo kale oo soo gasha looga hortago.

fibrous root n. xidid miiqyo; xididdo baaha oo badan, sida kuwa caws iyo geedgaab kale.

fin ray n. baalbiyood, siiba mid kalluumeed.

flatworm (‘falaat,woorm) n. gooryaansuun; bah dixiriyo balballaaran ah: platyhelminth.

platyhelminth (,paladhi’hel,minth) n. eeg flatworm. –platyhelminthic (ˌpalaadhihel’minthik) adj.

flame cell n. unugyo holaceed leh; gooryaan habkiisa qashinsaar (excretory system) oo leh dhuumo cas.

floral diagram n. jaantus ubaxeed; sawir ubaxeed muujiya qaybihiisa kala duwan.

floral formula n. jid ubaxeed; dhismaha ubax ayaa loo isticmaalaa tirooyin, xarfo iyo calaamado kala duwan (various symbols).

flower bisexual n. ubax labeeb; ubax leh qaybaha taranka ee lab (stamen) iyo dhaddig (pistils). kale loogu yeeraa androgynous flower.

flower imperfect n. ubax dhantaalan; ubax leh hal xibin taran (lab ama dhaddig); kale la dhahaa ubax lab (staminate flower) ama ubax dhaddig (pistillate flower), hadba midka uu yahay ubaxaas.

flower pistillate n. ubax dhaddig; ubax/geed xambaarsan xibin taran dhaddigeed (unisexual female flower) oo xambaarsan (carpels ama pistil).

flower staminate n. ubax lab; ubax leh hal xibin taran (unisexual flower) oo lab ah (staminate flower).

unsexual (,an’sekshawal) adj. la xariirin; aan ahayn; bari ka ah shukaansi ama galmo. e.g. They have unsexual relationship.

flower unisexual n. ubax hal jinsile; ubax leh hal taran xibineed (lab ama dhaddig), sida papaya ama qare (papaya or watermelon).

flowering plant n. dhir ubaxley; dhir nooceeda kasta oo dhala ubax, khudaar (fruits) iyo miro (seeds) wax sii dhalikara. kale loogu yeeraa angiosperm.

fetus (‘fiidhas) n. uurjiif; ilmo aan dhalan wali ama ukun aan bilqin (unhatched). Barbardhig embryo.

fetus membrane n. xuub uurjiifeed; xuub ku dahaaran ilamaha, dillaacistiisuna muhiim u tahay dahashada (dhalashada) ilmaha.

food pyramid n. gunbur cunto; habdhis buureed oo qaabka cuntada loo helo midba mid ku xiranyahay.

food vacuole n. dalool cunto; kiish ku dhex xiran xuub oo cuntada dheefshiida, siiba waxaa leh gooryaan (amoeba).

food web n. shabakad cunto; habdhis iskuxir cajiib ah ka samaysan silsiladda cunnada (food chain) oo muujinaya deegaan bulsho xiriirkooda quudasho.

forebrain (‘foor,bareyn) n. maskax horaad; qaybta ugu weyn maskaxda, waxayna ka koobantahay saddex qaybood: cerebrum, thalamus iyo hypothalamus. Barbardhig diencephalon, telencephalon. kale loogu yeeraa prosencephalon.

prosencephalon (,paraasen’sefa,laan) n. eeg forebrain. –prosencephalic adj.

diencephalon (,dhaayan’sefa,laan) n. qayb-danbeedka sii kala qaybsanka maskaxhoraadka; xiriiriyaha ka dhexeeya cerebrum ka iyo habdhiseedka maskaxda inteeda kale iyo xangullaha (spinal cord), waxayna xogta u soo diraan cerebrum-ka ayada oo loo soo marinayo diencephalon. –diencephalic (ˌdhaayansa’faalik) adj.

telencephalon (,telen’sefa,laan) n. sii kala qaybsanka hore ee maskaxhoraadka (forebrain) ama qaybta xiriirinta maskaxhoraadka oo ay ku jirto qalbacyada cerebral (cerebral hemispheres) iyo qaabdhisyada la xariira. –telencephalic (ˌte,lensa’faalik) adj.

fraternal twin n. mataano kala duwan; laba ukumood oo kala duwan oo ay bacramiyeen laba madax oo shahwo; kala nooc (lab iyo dhaddig) iyo kala ekaansho ayayna noqonkaraan.

funicle (‘fiyuunakal) n. eeg funiculus.

funiculus fi’nikyalas) n., pl. funiculi (fi’nikya,laay) 1 xubno dareemayaal ah oo xuub isku xiro ama qaabeeya marinka xangullaha (spinal cord) qaybtiisa cad. 2 samayn ugxan side.

galactose (ga’laak,taws) n. sonkor milmata kana macaan yar glucose, lehna asataan kiimiko C6H12O6.

gametangium (,gaama’taanjiiyam) n., pl. gametangia (ˌgaama’taanjiya) xibin ama unug sameeya taran (gametes).

gamete (‘gaa,miit) n. unug taran oo lab ama dhiddig (xoolo ama dhir), gaarayna xilligii uu tarmi lahaa; ukunta unugga dhaddig (ova ama egg cells), labkuna shahwo/xawo (sperm); ova iyo sperm isbacramintooda haploid cells. –gametic adj.; -gametically adv.

gametogenesis (ga,miidha’jenasas) n. samayn unug taran (gametes). –gametogenic (gamiidha’jenik) or -gametogenous (ˌgaama’taajanas) adj.

gemma (‘jeema) n., pl. gemmae (‘jee,mii) 1 baxan celeen: bud. 2 qayb istarmin (asexual reproductive) oo ka go’da hooya-geedeedka (parent plant).

gametophyte (ga’miidha,faayt) n., pl. gametophytes waqtiga rimayga dhirta haploid phase, unugyaduna waa hal hidda-side (single set of chromosomes). Barbardhig sporophyte. –gametophytic adj.

genetics (ja’nedhikis) n. laan ka mid ah biology oo gooni u eegta hiddo barashada iyo kala duwanaanta noolaha. –geneticist (ja’netasisti) n.

genotype (‘jiina,taayp) n. 1 nooc sinji (type species). 2 hiddo sheeg; astaan hiddo-side oo gaar u ah DNA qofkuna ka soo dhaxlay hooyo iyo aabbe. Barbardhig phenotype. –genotypic (ˌjiina’tipik) adj.; -genotypically (ˌjiina’tipiklii) adv.

geotropism (jii’aatra,pizam) n. dhul-raac; xididka iyo caleenta dhir oo aada dhinca dhulku u jiito: gravitropism

gravitropism (gara’vitra,pizam) n. dhul-raac; xididka iyo caleenta dhirta oo aada dhinca dhulku u jiito: geotropism.  

germ cell n. unug jinsi; unug abuura unug taraneed (reproductive cell), kaas oo ah ukun dhaddigeed (female) iyo shawo labeed (male).

germ layer n. lakab jinsi; koox unugyo ah oo ku jira uurjiif (embryo) oo u wada jira dhismaha uurjiifta oo qaabeeya dhammaan xibnaha iyo nudaha (organs and tissues).

germ tube n. dhuun jinsi; dhuun dhuuban oo ka soo baxda unug abuurka soo baxaya (spores in germination).

gill fungus n. waafyo fungus; nooc bahda fungus (basidiomycete) oo mushroom ka mid tahay oo waafyo ku leh hoosta madaxa koofida.

glomerulus (gala’meryalas) n., pl. glomeruli (gala’meryal,laay)  shabaq kalliyood; shabakad xididdo yaryar ah (capillaries) oo la dhaho tuft reebtanna wasakhda.

glycogenesis (,galaayka’jenasas) n. samaysanka glycogen; marka carbohydrate lagu keydiyo beerka iyo unugyada murqaha ayda oo macaan (glucose) ah.

gonad (‘gaw,naad) n. qanjir taraneed (reproductive gland), sida min ama xaniinyo (ovary or testis). –gonadal (gaw’naadhal) adj.

gonadotropin-releasing hormone n. dheecaan (hormone) qayb maskaxda ah ay samayso oo la dhaho hypothalamus.

gonadectomy (,gawna’dhektamii) n., pl. gonadectomies qalliin ku saarid minka ama xaniiyaha (ovary or testis). –gonadectomized (,gawna’dekta,maayzidh)  adj.

gonadotropic (gaw,naadha’taraapik) adj. or gonadotrophic (gaw,naadha’tarawfik) jila (acting) ama kiciya qanjirka taraneed (gonads)

graafian follicle (‘garaafiyan ‘faalikal) n. ugxanayn (ovulation); dareere shin dhammaystay oo buuxiya minka, xambaarsanna ukumaha (female gamete/ovum), marka meertada ciddada (menstrual cycle) ayaana la sii daayaa.

green gland n. qanjir cagaaran ama qashin-saar; noole badan oo biyo-ku-nool ah (aquatic arthropods), kana mid yihiin: carsaanyo (crabs), aragoste (lobisters), iyo shrimps, uguna shaqeeya sida kalyaha xibin qashin-saar.

guard cell n. unug ilaaliye; unugyada mataanaha ah midkood ee ku jira dubka sare ee geed, fura ama xirana duleelka caleen (stoma a leaf).

stoma (‘istawma) n., pl. stomata (‘istawmadha) or stomas 1 duleel yar ee ka dulleela cayayaan. 2 duleed yar ee caleen. 3 duleel yar oo qalliin ahaan calool looga duleelshay.

hemocoel (‘hiima,siil) n. god yar oo dhiigfariisad, siiba cayaqaanka qaarkood, una shaqeeya qaabka dhiigwareega jirka: hemolymph.

hemocyanin (,hiimaw’saayanan) n. nafaqo (proteins) jirka lafdhabarla’da (invertebrates) u xambaarta oxygen.

haemophilus (hii’maafalas) n., pl. haemophile (hii’maafalii) ma-xinjiraw; hab dhaxaleed oo dhiigu uusan sidii la rabay u xinjiroobin.

Hib (‘hiib) n. soo gaabin (Haemophilus influenzae type B) waxaana sababa jeermiska (bacterial meningitis iyo pneumonia) siiba carruurta: Hib disease; Hib vaccine.

hair follicle n. qotin tineed; salka tintu ka soo baxdo.

papilla (pa’pila) n., pl. papillae (pa’pi,lii) kuus; buruq, ama meel yar oo jirka ka soo foocsan. –papillate (‘paapaleyt; pa’pilat) adj., -papillose (‘paapa,laws) adj.

hair papilla n. unug tineed.

halophyte (‘haala,faayt) n. geed cusbeed; dhirta ku baxda cusbada iyo meelaha xeebaha badda ah. –halophytic (,haala’fidhik) adj.

haploid number n. tiro jeex hiddo-side; unug xambaarsan hal jeex oo hiddo-side (single set of chromosomes) tiradiisuna tahay n = 23.

Haversian canal (ha’varshan ka’naal) or haversian canal n., pl. Haversian canals also haversian canals xirmo dhuumo ah oo marin cariiryoon oo xuub ama nud (lamella) isku xirto.

lamella (la’meela) n., pl. lamellae (la’mee,lii; la’mee,laay) or lamellas xuub, diir, ama nudo aad u yaryar, inta badanna isku xira unuyada dariska ah.

hemichordate (,hemi’koordhit) n. bararafley; koox kasta oo lafdhabarla’ ah oo gooryaan-u-eke (wormlike) ah, bad ku noolna ah.

hepatic artery n. halbawle beer; qayb ka mid ah halbawlayaasha dhiigga siiya beerka.

hepatic portal system n. habdhiska dhiigsiinta beerka; koox xididdo ah oo dhiigga ka soo qaada caloosha, mindhicirka, beeryarada (spleen), iyo ganaca (pancreas) ilaa beerka.

herbaceous plants n. dhir hoosaad; geed-gaab; dhir sanad ama labo aan ka weynaan oo caleen iyo laamo ka kooban.

herbalist (‘harbalisti) n. geedagooye; qof dhirta wax ku daaweeya.

immotile (,im’mawdhal) adj. aan dhaqaaqin; aan lahayn socod. e.g. Immotile eggs.

oogamous (aw’aagamas) adj. la xariirta shahwada yar ee labka oo sabbaysa (motile) iyo ukunta weyn ee dhaddig oo aan dhaqaaqin (immotile). –oogamy (aw’aagamii) n.

heterogamete (,hedharaw’gaa,miit) n. labada unug taran midkood oo ku kala duwan qiyaasta (size) iyo dabeecadda oo unugga taranka dhaddigu wenyahay dhaqaaqinna iyo shahwo sabbaysa oo yar.

heterotroph (‘hedhara,tarawf) n. isma-quudiye; noole cuna dhir ama xayawaan si uu uga helo tamar iyo nafaqooyin (energy and nutrients).

autotroph (‘awdha,tarawf) n. isquudiye; noole samaysan kara cuntadiisa asaga oo ka faa’iidaysta ilayska, biyaha, carbon dioxide, iyo kiimikooyinka kale.

autotrophic (,awdha’tarawfik) adj. isquudiye ah; noole samaysta tamar iyo nafaqooyin (energy or nutrients)  uu u baahanyahay. Barbardhig heterotrophic. –autotrophically (,aawdha’tarawfiklii) adv.; -autotrophy (aaw’taatrafii) n.

heterotrophic (,hedhara’tarawfik) adj. ismaquudiye ah; noole aan samaysan karin tamar ama nafaqooyin (energy or nutrients) oo ka hela dhir ama xayawaan. Barbardhig autotrophic. –heterotrophically (,hedhara’tarawfiklii) adv.; -heterotrophy (,hedha’raatrafii) n.

X chromosome n. mid ka mid ah labada hidda-side (two sex chromosomes) ee dadka (kan kale Y chromosome); waxayna qaabeeyaan midkoodiiba 23 lammaane ee unug kasta oo hidda-sidaha dadka. Barbardhig Y chromosome.

Y chromosome n. mid ka mid ah labada hidde-sideed (two sex chromosomes) ee dadka (kan kale X chromosome); waxayna qaabeeyaan midkood 23 lammaane ee unug kasta oo hidda-sidaha dadka. Barbardhig X chromosome.

 hilum (‘haaylam) n., pl. hila (‘haayla) xuddun mireed; tan digirta waxaa la dhahaa il (eye).

hindbrain (‘haaynd,bareyn) n. maskax danbeed; saddexda qaybdanbeed ee waaweyn oo maskaxda middood oo ay ku jiraan (cerebellum iyo medulla oblongata). Barbardhig metencephalon, myelencephalon. kale loogu yeeraa rhombencephalon.

metencephalon (,medh,en’sefa,laan) n. abuuranka qaybta hore ee maskaxdanbeedka (hindbrain) lafdhabarleyda (vertebrate). –metencephalic (,medh,ensa’faalik) adj.

myelencephalon (,maayalen’sefa,laan) n. abuuranka qaybta danbe ee maskaxdanbeedka (hindbrain) lafdhabarleyda (vertebrate). –myelencephalic (,maaya,lensa’faalik) adj.

rhombencephalon (,raam,been’sefa,laan) n. eeg hindbrain.

oblongata (,aab,lon’gaadha) n., pl. oblongatas or oblongatae eeg medulla oblongata.

medulla oblongata n., pl. medulla oblongatas or medullae oblongatae maskaxda ku taal jeegada salkeeda hoose ama afweynta oo xangulluhu uga xirmo.

hindgut (‘haaynd,gat) n. calool danbeed; qaybta danbe ee marinka dheefshiidka (digestive tract).

hind limb n. addin danbe, siiba afar addinle (quadruped).

histogen (‘histajan) n. koox unugyo ah oo geed korisa ama siisa nudo cusub: cambium ama cork sense 3.

dermatogen (dar’maatajan) n. mayrax ama xuubka sare ee koriya laan maa xidid geed. kale loogu yeeraa protoderm. 

protoderm (‘parawdha,dharm) n. diirka sare; xuubka sare ee geed korriimo siiya.

histogenesis (,hista’jenasas) n. abuuranka iyo qaabaysmadka nudaha geed. –histogenetic (,histaja’nedhik) adj.

histology (hi’staalajii) n. 1 laan ka mid ah cilmiga qaabdhiska (anatomy) oo gooni u eegta dhismaha xoolaha iyo nudaha (tissues) dhirta ayada oo lagu eegagyo (discernible) weynayso. 2 nadaamka iyo dhismaha nudaha. –histological (ˌhista’laajikal) or -histologic (ˌhista’laajik) adj.; -histologically (ˌhista’laajiklii) adv.; -histologist (hi’staalajisti) n.

holophytic (,hoola’fidhik) n. quudasho geedle; samaysasho cunto marka dhirta cagaaran nafaqo ka samaysato cagaariyaha (photosynthetic activity): autotrophs.

holozoic (,hoola’zooik) n. quudashada xayawaanle; quudasho dhir ama xoolo cunto ahaan.

homothermal (,hawma’tharmal) adj. also homothermic (ˌhawma’tharmik) or homothermous eeg warm-blooded.

homologous structure n. isku dhisme wadaaga, laakiin shaqo ahaan ku kala duwan, sida: addinka dad, bisad, nibiri, iyo fiidmeer (bat).

homozygous (,hawm’zaaygas) adj. hidda-side isku kaan; tusaale: haddii aad labada waalid ka dhaxashay hidda-side isku nooc ah, hidda-sidahaas waa homozygous gene. –homozygously adv.

hookworm (‘huk,warm) n. gooryaan jillaabeed; dulin ku noolaada mindhiciryaraha dadka.

humus (‘huyuumas) n. biir; dhoojaan madaw oo dhir dhimatay iyo bakhti xoolaad iskugu jirta.

hypha (‘haayfa) n., pl. hyphae (‘haay,fii) buul fangas (fungus) oo bixiya farraaqsho badan. –hyphal (‘haayfal) adj.

hypertonic (,haaypar’taanik) adj. 1 milan sare; kuwa kale marka loo eego (solution) caddaadis sare leh (high osmatic pressure). 2 muruq-tigtig (muscle tension). e.g. A hypertonic baby.

hypertonia (ˌhaaypar’tawniiya) n. tigtig; muruqyo tigtigan oo aan caadi u laabankarin.

cerebral palsy n. abbr. CP dhibaato adeegsiga muruqyada; cudur qofku tigtigan yahay, siiba lugaha iyo/ama socod iyo fadhi ku adagyihiin.

hypertonic solution n. nooc milan oo leh mile (solute) ribbanaan sare (higher concentration) ee kan dibadda unuggu ka badanyahay kan gudaha unugga.

hypotonic (ˌhaaypa’taanik) adj. 1 milan hoose; kuwa kale marka loo eego (solution) caddaadis hoose leh (lower osmatic pressure). e.g. A hypotonic solution. 2 naafo ah; murqo jileec leh. e.g. A hypotonic tetraplegia. –hypotonicity (ˌhaaypata’nisadhii) n.

identical twin n. mataano mid ah; mataano isku eg oo hal ukun (single egg) ka wada beermay.

impermeable (,im’parmiiabal) adj. mahabe; aan dareere gudbin; biyo magudbiyaan. –impermeability (ˌim,parmiya’bilatii) n.

incomplete dominance n. shiiqis dhimman; astaan hidda-side aan dhammayn ka timid.

incomplete metamorphosis n. qobrogosho dhimman; qaab cayayaan marka uu ukun ka baxo sii xuubsiibta ilaa uu ka weynaado.

incus (‘inkas) n., pl. incudes (ing’kiyuu,dhiiz) laf dhexaad dhageed; saddex lafood oo dhagta ku jira teeda dhexe. kale loogu yeeraa anvil.

indehiscent (,indi’hisanti) n. bisayl xigeen; cargo; koris dhammays u dhaw. e.g. Indehiscent fruits. –indehiscence (ˌindi’hisanis) n.

independent assortment n. isdoorasho; astaan gaar ah (allele) ka timid hal hidda-side (one gene) waxbana kama baddalikarto astaan ka timid hidda-side kale (another gene).

inflorescence (,infala’resanis) n. rakibaad ubaxeed; qaabka abuuranka iyo isku aad aadka laamaha ubaxeed.

inheritance of acquired characters n. dhaxlid; isbaddalka jireed ee nooluhu maro noloshiisa una sii gudbiyaan carruurtooda.

insect pollination n. faxlin cayayaan; cayayaan ayaa qaada faxalka (pollen) labka (male anther) ee ubax, geeyana qaybta taranka ubax dhaddig (stigma), tanina waxay keentaa bacramin (fertilization) iyo diyaarin mireed (seed).

intercellular space adj. dulaalaati unug; la xariira ama ka dhaca meelaha u dhexeeya unugyada maalikiyuullada ama unuygada isla xariira.

internal environment n. dareere ku jira jirka, kan gudaha unugguna waa (intracellular fluid).

internode (‘intar,nawdh) n. laba xibnood dhexdood; inta u dhexaysa laba xibnood (two nodes). –internodal (ˌintar’nawdhal) adj.

interstitial cell n. unug ka agdhaw unugga xawada:  Leydig cell.

Leydig cell (‘laaydhig ‘seel) n. also Leydig's cell unug aad muhiim u ah oo ku jira xaniinyo lab. kale loogu yeeraa cell of Leydig, interstitial cell of Leydig.

interstitial fluid n. dareere dusha (bannaanka) unugyada jirka ah (extracellular) iyo dibadda xididdada dhiigga (blood vessels).

interstitial gland n. qanjir xaweed; mid kasta oo ka mid ah kooxa unugyo xaweed (Leydig cells) ah ee xaniinyaha.

intracellular (‘intara’selyalar) adj. gudaha unug ah; la xariira, ka jira ama ka dhaca gudaha unug. e.g. intracellular solutes. –intracellularly adv.

intramembranous (,intar’membaranas) adj. 1 la xariira adkaanta ama lafawga xuub. e.g. intramembranous ossification. 2 gudaha xuubka ah. e.g. intramembranous proteins.

interventricular septum n. gidaarka saddexagalle ee xuubka wadnaha ee kala qaybiya bidix iyo midig qolqollada hoose ee wadnaha (left and right ventricles). kale loogu yeeraa ventricular septum.

invagination (in,vaaja’neyshan) n. gudanoqod; hab wareegga goobada unugga qaybteeda dibadda ugu noqoto unugga oo ay samayso fanax, kiish, ama dhuun (cavity, pouch or tube).

irregular flower n. ubax aan caadi ahayn; ubax qaabdhiska koofiyadda ay ka duwan tahay caadiga.

ischium (‘iskiyam) n., pl. ischia (‘iskiya) gees hoosaadka misigeed. –ischial (‘iskiyal) adj.

isogamous (aay’saagamas) adj. la xariira ama ah unugyo taran (lab iyo dhaddig) oo isle’eg iskuna eg: isogametes. –isogamy (aay’saagamii) adj.

heterogamous (,hedha’raagamas) adj. la xariira ama leh unugyo taran (gametes) oo kala duwan. Barbardhig anisogamous, isogamous.

isogamete (,aaysaw’gaa,miit) n. unugyo taran (gametes) ee lab iyo dhaddig oo aan la kala garaankarin xag weynaan ama dabeecad. –isogametic (,aaysawga’me dhik) adj.

labium (‘leybiyam) n., pl. labia 1 faruuryo siil middood. Barbardhig labia majora; labia minora. 2 bushinta ubax: labiate. 3 qalka hoose ee af cayayaan.

labia minora (‘laybiyama’noora) plural noun bushin ama furuur gudaha siil.

labia majora (‘leybibiyama’joora) plural noun faruur ama bushin sare siil.

labiate (‘leybiyat) adj. 1 ubax leh bushima isasaaran oo kala sarreeya. 2 wax bushimo oo kale ah leh. 3 bahda reexaan (mint family): geedo badan oo carfa oo leh wax bushimo u ekoon.                           -n. labiate geedaha bahda reexaan (mint family).

lacrimal duct n. marinka ilmada ee isha.

medial angle of the eye n. xagasha ay qaabeeyaan xirribaha (eyelids) isha ee sanka ku dhaw.

laryngeal cartilage n. carjaw qulaanqul ama booc (larynx).

larynx locomotion n. dhaqdhaqaaq qulaanqul ama booc, siiba marka wax la laqayo.

latent period n. 1 kal dahsoonaan cudur; inta aan wali cudur soo ifbixin. 2 waqtiga u dhexeeya salaax ama xaxanto (stimulation) iyo ka falcelinteeda (response) ama dareenkeeda.

lateral root n. xidid dhinaceed.

lateral tooth n. ilig miciga ka sokeeya.

slippage (‘islipij) n. 1 sinbiririqasho; sinbiririxasho. 2 sinbiririqo inteed; inta shay sikaday ama siibtay. 3 dibdhac wax qabad. 4 inta u dhexaysa wax qiyaastood iyo qaymaha dhabta ah. 5 dhumin awood, siiba matoor.

leaf blade n. baabaco caleen; caleen inteeda ballaaran oo samaysa cagaariye (photosynthesis). kale loogu yeeraa lamina.

foliage (‘fawliiyij) n. caleemo dhir ama geedo. –foliaged (ˈfawliyij) adj.

foliage plant n. dhir u wada baxday quruxdeed.

leaf disease n. 1 cudur caleemeed; cudur ku dhasha caleemo. 2 cudur qaxwo (coffee disease) oo ay sababto daxal fangas (rust fungus). kale loogu yeeraa coffee disease.

leaf scar n. haar caleemeed; nabar ku hara laan marka caleemuhu ka daataan ama dhacaan.

leaf sheath n. qotin caleemeed; salka caleen uga dhaggantahay laan.

leafstalk (‘liif,istook) n. samay caleemeed; lafdhabar caleemeed oo salkeedu ku dhago laanta. kale loogu yeeraa petiole.

legume (‘lee,gyuum) n., pl. legumes 1 miro qalalan ee bahda dirgirta (legume family), sida peas ama beans. 2 khudrad ama miro laws (peanuts or tamarind) oo cunto ahaan loo cuno.

lenis (liinas) adj. khafiifsan; tartiiban, siiba dhawaaq eray. e.g. English has lenis consonants (b, d, g, j, v, th, z, iyo zh). Barbardhig fortis.

fortis (‘foodhas) adj. shidan; adkan, siiba dhawaaq eray. e.g. English has fortis consonants (p, t, k, ch, f, th, s, sh) iyo (h) mararka qaakood. Barbardhig lenis.

lenticel (‘lenta,sel) n. duleel yar, siiba laamo ama xididdo geed ku yaal oo uu ka neefsado, hawana ka soo gasho (gases are exchanged).

leukocyte (‘luuka,saayt) n. unug kasta oo ka mid ah unugyada dhiigga cad oo la dagaala cudurrada, sida  (neutrophils, lymphocytes, monocytes, eosinophils, basophils): white blood cell. –leukocytic (,luuka’sidhik) adj.

basophil (‘beysa,fiil) n. nooc dhigga cad ka mid oo si dhaw ula shaqeeya habdhiska difaaca cudurrada (immune system), jirkana ka difaaca xasaasiyadda (allergens), cudur wadayaasha (pathogens) iyo dulinka (parasites).

neutrophil (ˈnutra,fil) adj. or neutrophilic (ˌnutra’filik) nooc ka mid ah unugyada dhiigga cad oo sameeya asal midab dabiici ah. -neutrophil n.

monocyte (‘maana,saayt) n. unugyo waaweyn oo dhiigga cad ka tirsan oo raadiya burburiyana jeermiska (viruses, bacteria, fungi iyo protozoa), kana takhalusa unugyada qaaday cudur (infected cells). -monocytic (,maana’sidhik) adj.

limb girdle n. tax addin; isku xiranka addinka iyo dhexda.

limb skeleton n. qalfoof addin; isku xiranka lafaha sare iyo lafaha hoose ee addimada (lower limbs), lafaha cududda iyo garabka (pectoral girdle) iyo lafaha misigta (pelvic girdle).

limiting factor n. qodob koobe; wax kasta oo xaddada tirada dadka oo hakiya ama joojiya badashadooda.

lipase (‘laay,peys) n. dheecaan (enzyme) jirku cuntada uga burburiyo dufan (fats) si mindhicirku uga dhuuqo.

living organism n. noole nool; wax kasta oo nool lehna qaybo dhisan oo aasaasi ah, ayna ka mid yihiin: humans, fungi, algae, trees, animals, bacteria, protozoa, iyo insects.

locomotor organs n. xibno dhaqaaq; xibnaha nafleyda ka caawiya dhaqaaqa, sida: fins, wings, muscular foot, legs, pseudopodia, etc.

longitudinal ducts n. marino dheraran.

lumbar vertebra n. riciraha lafdhabarta oo ka korreeya lafaha dabagibinta.

lung fluke n. faraqle sanbab; dulan (flatworm) asiiba sanbabka dadka, kana raaca cunista hilib ceeriin ama yacyacood.

lungworm (‘laan,worm) n. gooryaan-sanbabeed; mid kasta oo ka mid ah bahda gooryaan (nematodes) oo sanbabka naasleyda ka gala marinda hawda.

lymphatic organ n. nudaha iyo xibnaha sameeya, kaydiya oo qaada unugyada dhiigga cad oo la dagaala cudurrada.

macrogamete (,maakraw’gaa,miit) n. ukumaha taranka middooda weyn oo ah tan dhaddig. Barbardhig microgamete.

macronucleus (,maakraw’nuukiyas) n. bu’da weyn. –macronuclear (,maakraw’nuukiyer) adj.

macrospore (‘maakraw,ispawr) n. boorweyne (faxalweyne); labada boorfaxleed (spores) kooda weyn oo geedaha qaarkood dhalaan. kale loogu yeeraa megaspore. Barbardhig microspore.

malaria parasite n. dulin duumo; dulin (Plasmodium) ilma’aragto oo 100 isir leh kaneecaduna qaadsiiso dadka, xoolaha, xamaaratada, iyo shinbiraha.

malleus (‘maaliyas) n., pl. mallei (‘maaliyaay) laf-dubbe; saddexa lafdhagood ee dhagta teeda hore. kale loogu yeeraa hammer.

Malpighian corpuscle (maal’pigiyan ‘koor,pasal) n. qayb ka mid ah shaandhada kallida. kale loogu yeeraa Malpighian body.

Malpighian body (maal’pigiyan ‘baadhii) n. eeg Malpighian corpuscle.

Malpighian tubule n. koox xidido ah ee ka furma qaybta danbe ee marinka dheefshiidka cayayaan, una isticmaalaan xibinta qashinsaarka (excretory organ). kale loogu yeeraa Malpighian tube.

 Malpighian tube n. eeg Malpighian tubule.

mandibular arch n. qaanso-daan; waxa ugu horreeya ee uurjiifta lafdhabarleydu abuurto waa bushinta hoose, daanka hoose, muruqyada calalinta (masticatory muscles) iyo qaybta hore ee carrabka.

maturation (,maaja’reyshan) n. baaluq, qaangaar. e.g. Physical growth and maturation. –maturational (ˌmaaja’reyshanal) adj.

menstrual cycle n. meerto ciddo; wareegtada bilawga iyo dhammaadka caadada oo afar waji marta: menstruation, follicular phase, ovulation phase, luteal phase.  

ovulation phase n. waji ka mid ah meertada ciddada oo la xariirta ku sii daynta ukunta (ovum) mid ka mid ah makaanka; inta badan waxay dhacdaa laba asbuuc ka hor inta aan meertada ciddadu bilaaban (menstrual period).

follicular phase n. waji ka mid ah meertada ciddada, waana marka ukuntu shin dhammaysato (egg matures), diyaarna u noqota uur qaadis.

luteal phase n. wajigaan waxa uu waaraa 14 maalin, waxana uu diyaar u yahay in uur la qaado; waxa uuna dhammaadaa inta aan meertada ciddadu bilaaban.

meristem (‘mera,stem) n. caydiyo; unugyo yayar oo geed, joogtana isku badiya ama iskala gooya si geedku u koro. –meristematic (,merasta’maadhik) adj.; -meristematically adv.

mesenchyme (‘mezan,kaaym) n. unugyo caawiya uurjiif oo xibnaha abuurmaya siiya xoog iyo qaabdhiskooda, sida dhiig, lafo, carjaw, iyo nudo isku xira.

mesentery (‘mezen,terii) n., pl. mesenteries  xuub mindhicireed; xuub ku haya mindhicirka gidaarada caloosha. –mesenteric (,mezan’terik) adj.

mesoderm (‘meeza,daarm) n. maqaar dhexaad; unugga lakabkiisa dhexe ee xoolaha uurjiiftooda (embryonic animal), taas oo muruqyada iyo qalfoofku ka koraan. –mesodermal (ˌmeza’darmal) adj.

mesoglea (,meza’giliya) n. or mesogloea bahal badeed u eg jellyfish.

mesophile (‘meza,faayl; ‘miiza,faayl) n. or  mesophil (ˈmeza,fiil) noole (bacteria) ku kora heerkul la mid ah 20 ilaa 45 °C (68 to 113 °F). Babardhig psychrophile, thermophile.

psychrophile (ˈsaaykraw,faayl) n. qabaw ku noole, siiba heerkul aad u hooseeya. Barbardhig mesophile, thermophile.

 thermophile (ˈtharma,faayl) n. kul-ku-noole; heerkul aad u sarreeya ku noolaada. Barbardhig mesophile, psychrophile.

thermophilic (ˌtharma’filik) adj. also thermophilous (ˌthar’maafalas) or thermophile (ˈtharma,faayl) heerkul aad u sarreeya ku noolaada. e.g. thermophilic bacteria. –thermophile n.

psychrophilic (ˌsaaykraw’filik) adj. qabaw aad ah ku noolaada. e.g. psychrophilic bacteria.

mesophyte (‘meza,faayt) n. geed oomane; geed ku kora meel xoogaa biyuhu ku yaryihiin. –mesophytic (,meza’fidhik) adj.

metaphase (‘medha,feyz) n. waji labaad ee iskala qaybinta unug, una dhexaysa prophase iyo anaphase oo ah marka hidda-siduhu (chromosomes) uu ku xirmo labada miiq ee lammaane.

microgamete (,maaykraw’gaa,miit) n. midda yar ukumaha taranka oo ah tan lab. Barbardhig macrogamete.

micropyle (‘maaykra,paayal) n. 1 duleel yar ee ugaxsidaha mirta geed. 2 duleel dusha ugxanta ah oo shawadu ka gasho ama ka bacramiso. –micropylar (ˌmaaykra’paaylar) adj.

microsporangium (,maaykraw-ispa’raanjiyam) n. roor side yar; cisil geed oo ah xibin taran lab, meesheeda faxalku ka dhaco. –microsporangiate (ˌmaaykrawspa’raanjiyat) adj.

megaspore (‘meega,spoor) n. faxalweyne, siiba geedaha labada faxal dhala (heterosporous plants) midka weynna yahay ukunta dhaddig. –megasporic (,meega’spoorik) adj.

heterospory (‘hedhara,ispoorii) n. samaynta faxalyare iyo faxalweyne (microspores and megaspores) ee mir geed. -heterosporous (,hedhara’ispooras) adj.

midbrain (ˈmidh,bareyn) n. maskaxdhexo; xarunta dhexe ee habdhiska dareemayaasha, hoosta cerebral cortex iyo qaybta topmost jirridda maskaxda (brainstem). kale loogu yeeraa mesencephalon.

mesencephalon (,me,zen’sefa,laan) n. eeg midbrain. –mesencephalic (,me,zensa’faalik) adj.

middle lamella n. lakabeeye; lakab isku xabkeeya gidaarada hore unug ee laba unugyo dhireed oo isqabsanaya.

midgut (‘mid,gat) n. calooldhexo; qaybta dhexe ee marin dheefshiid.

midrib (‘midh,rib) n. aroore caleen; xidid-dhexaad caleen.

migratory nucleus n. bu’guurto; dhaqaaq toos ah oo bu’du uga aaddo unugga gudihiisa meel cayiman.

milky disease n. or milky spore disease cudur caanood; cudur dadku laayo dixirti cad oo sangaallaha ka weyn.

mineral salt n. 1 cusbo inorganic acid ah; cusbo ay quutaan noolaha nool (living organic) oo ku koraan kuna dheefsadaan. 2 cusbo dhagaxeed (rock salt).

miracidium (,mira’sidhiyam) n., pl. miracidia (,mira’siidhiya) dhal dixiri oo tin le’eg gashana xaaxeeyo (snail).

monocotyledon (,maana,kaadha’liidhan) n. hal-beerjiif; mir leh hal caleen beerjiifeed. Barbardhig dicotyledon. –monocotyledonous (ˌmaana,kaadha’liidnas) adj.

monohybrid (,maanaw’haaybaradh) n. halbarax; mono = single gen; hybrid = two different alleles; taran ka soo baxa laba qof oo ku kala duwan hal hidda-side (single gene). –monohybrid adj.

morphogenesis (,moorfa’jenasas) n. qaabaysmadka iyo kala soocnaanta nudaha iyo xibnaha jirka. Barbardhig organogenesis.

organogenesis (,oorganaw’jenasis) n. unkunka ama abuuranka iyo koboca xibno jireedka. Barbardhig morphogenesis. -organogenetic (,oorganawja’nedhik) adj.

mosaic disease n. caleen barabareeye; cudur ku dhaca caleemaha geed oo dulduleeliya ama midabdooriya.  

motor nerve n. dareen wade dhaqaajiye.

neuronal (‘nuuranal) adj. unug dareen hele iyo dareen qaade ah. kale loogu yeeraa nerve cell.

motor neuron n. unug dareen-wade dhaqaajiye; dareeme maskaxda ama xangullaha ku xiran oo xukuma muruqyada iyo qanjirrada. kale loogu yeeraa motoneuron.

motoneuron (,mawta’nuu,raan) n. eeg motor neuron. –motoneuronal (,mawdha’nuuranal) adj.

interneuron (,intar’nuur,aan) n. dareen wade dareemyaal ukala qaada. –interneuronal (,intar’nuuranal) adj.

muscle tissue n. mud muruqeed; nudo gaar ah oo aad u xoogbadan kana samaysan unugyo dheraran (muscle fibers).

musculature (‘maskila,juur) n. muruqyo jireed; dhammaan muruqyada ama qaarkood ee jirka xoolaha.

umlaut (ˈuum,laawt) n. 1 calaamad ¨ oo la kordhigo shaqal. 2 baddalis shaqal, sida goose, geese. Barbardhig diaeresis.                                                                     -v. umlauted; umlauting; umlauts 1 duldhigid calaamad, siiba shaqal. 2 wax ka baddalid eray.

diaeresis (dhaay’erasas) n. or dieresis plural diaereses (dhaay’era,siiz) calaamadda ¨  oo la kordhigo shaqal si loo tuso in shaqalkaas si gooni ah loogu dhawaaqayo, sida ä, ö, ü. erayga  “naïve”  ayaa tusaale fiican ah. Barbardhig umlaut. –diaeretic (ˌdhaaya’redhik) adj.

mycelium (maay’siiliyam) n., pl. mycelia (maay’siiliiya) baanjeer suuf oo kale ah dhulna ku baxda oo fangas (fungus) dhalay. –mycelial (maay’siiliyal) adj.

naked bud n. ruqur murduggan.

nasal cavity n. moqor saneed; duleel sanka oo dalqada ka sii baxa

natural selection n. xulasho dabiici; hab dabiici ah oo ku noolaansho iyo ku tarmid bii’adda kali ahaan iyo koox ahaanba.

nectary (‘nektarii) n., pl. nectaries qanjir dhabaq; qanjir ubax oo sii daaya dareere macaan (nectar); lagana helo gunta (pistil) ama dusha salalka (petals).

nekton (‘nektan) n. dabaashayaal; noolayaal noole oo biyo caadi ugu noolaankara, sida kalluun, nibiri, iwm. –nektonic (nek’taanik) adj.

nephroid (‘nee,foydh) adj. qaabkalyoodle ah; eeg   reniform.

reniform (‘riina,foorm) n. meegaar  ama qaab kalyood leh.

nerve root n. xidid dareen wade.

nervous tissue n. nud dareen wade.

net-veined adj. xididdo qaab sidii shabakad aroorayaal iskugu habaysan leh. e.g. Net-veined leaves. Barbardhig parallel-veined. -net venation n.

parallel-veined (,pera,lel’veynd) adj. xididdo qaab sidii barbarro xididdeed iskugu habaysan leh: neurology. Barbardhig net-veined.

nuclear division n. qaybsan bu’eed; meertada kala tagga unug taas oo keenta in la gooniyeelo unugga genome ee DNA xambaarsan, waana bilawga qaybsanka unugga. Barbardhig proteome.

proteome (‘parawdhi,awm) n. nafaqo (protein) dhan oo waqti gooni ah u samaysmata unug (genome) ama nud khaas ah.

nuclear membrane n. xuub bu’eed; laba xuub oo ku dahaaran bu’da unug iyo qaybta bannaanka oo wali la sii haysata endoplasmic reticulum. kale loogu yeeraa nuclear envelope.

genome (‘jii,nawm) n. unugga DNA oo dhammaan wixii macluumaad ah ku jiraan; dadka hal xarig oo hiddo-side, waxana uu ka koobanyahay 23 lammaane hiddo-side (23 pairs of chromosomes) oo ku dhexjira bu’da unugga. Barbardhig proteome.

nucleolus (nuu’kliyalas) n., pl. nucleoli (nuu’kliya,laay) bu’yaro; meel ka mid ah gudaha bu’da unug oo loo sameeyay RNA iyo proteins lagu sameeyo ribosomes. –nucleolar (nuu’kliyalar) adj.

nucleoprotein (,nuukliyaw’paraw,tiin) n. nafaqo (protein) bu’eed; iskudhis ka kooban protein, sida histone laguna xaglay nucleic acid, sida DNA taas oo gundhig u ah walxaha hiddaha ee ku jira hidda-sidayaasha (chromosomes).

nymph (‘nimf) n. koronkoro; cayayaan kasta oo heer isbaddal koritaan wali ku jira. –nymphal adj.

nympho (‘nim,faw) n., pl. nymphos [informal] naag kacsibood hayo.

oil gland n. 1 qanjir saliideed: sebaceou gland. 2 uropygial gland.

uropygial gland n. qanjir weyn oo ku jira gadaasha shinbiraha oo ay ku dhaashadaan baallaha. kale loogu yeeraa oil gland.

olfactory cell n. unug ureed; unug leh dareen gaar ah oo kala ogaado urka.

neurosensory (,nuuraw’sensarii) adj. la xariira dareengeeyayaal (afferent nerves).

olfactory epithelium n. nudo ku jira duleelka san oo xambaarsan unugyo ureed (olfactory cells).

olfactory nerve n. dareen wade ureed; mid ka mid ah lammaanaha dareeme oo ka baxa unugyada dareengeeyeyaasha (olfactory neurosensory cells).

oocyte (‘awa,saayt) n. ugxan aan wali korin (immature ovum or egg cell); female gametocyte or germ cell.

ovocyte (‘awva,saayt) n. eeg oocyte.

oogenesis (,awa’jenasas) n. tax isdabajoog ee diyaarsanka ugxanta dumar (female gametes or ovum), kuna jirto midda aan shindhammaysan (oocyte). –oogenetic (,awaja’nedhik) adj.

oogonium (,awa’gawniyam) n., pl. oogonia (,awa’gawniya) xibin taran dhaddig ee dhir hoosaadka qaarkeed. –oogonial (,awa’gawniyal) adj.

archegonium (,aarki’gawniyam) n., pl. archegonia (,aarki’gawniya) xibin taran dhaddig ee geedgaabyada qaarkood oo sida tib u likaysan. –archegonial (,aarki’gawniyal) adj.

diploid cell n. unug xambaarsan laba nuqul (two copies) ee hidda-side kasta (each chromosome).

monozygotic (,maanazaay’gaadhik) adj. mataano isku eg; kana yimid hal ugxan oo ay bacrimasay hal shahwo (sperm), kadibna ugxantii bacrantay ay laba ugxan isku sii kala qaybisay; markasta waa isku jinsi (laba wiil ama laba gabdhood). e.g. monozygotic twins. –monozygosity (,maanazaay’gaasadhii) n.

uniovular (,yuunii’aavyalar) adj. or uniovular eeg monozygotic.

oospore (‘awa,spoor) n. budo faxal fangas (fungus) oo ka samaysan faxal lab iyo dhaddig: heterogamous fertilization.

ootid (‘awa,tidh) n. ugxantii aan shinkeedu dhammaan (oocyte) aayaa gashay wajigeedii labaad oo laba isku sii qaybisay, noqotayna laba unug oo kala go’an oo midkood weynyahay, ka kalana  yaryahay; midka weyn oo shindhammaystay ayaa la dhahaa ootid.

blastocyst (‘balaasta,sisti) n. ukun bacrantay oo iku sii kala qaybisay unugyo badan.

open pollination n. faxlid furan; dhir ay faxliyeen cayayaan, shinbiro, dabayl, ama gacma dadeed.

optic nerve n. dareen wade arag; dareen qaade arag oo gaarsiiya maskaxda.

organelle (,oorga’nel) n. unugyare; unugyare (subcellular) waxa uu qabtaa shaqo gaar ah oo hal ama laba ah, sida bu’da unug nuclei oo keydisa xogta hiddaha, mitochondria oo sameeya tamar kiimiko, ribosomes oo isku duwa proteins.

origin of species n. isir sinjiyo.

osmoregulation (‘aazmaw,regya’leyshan) n. horis-siimow; waxay dheellitirtaa biyaha iyo cuntada kale ee jirka noolaha ku jirta, ayada oo aan loo eegin xaaladda degaankaas. –osmoregulatory (,aazmaw’regyala,toorii) adj.

osmotic pressure n. cadaadis siimow; biyaha oo u dareera xagga ribanaanta (concentration).

osteocranium (‘aastiyaw‘kireyniyam) n., pl. osteocraniums or osteocrania qayb ka mid ah lafta madaxa. Barbardhig chondrocranium.  

ostium (ˈaastiyam) n., pl. ostia (‘aastiya) 1 af-u-yaal; af-u-eke, sida xidid ama dhuun afkeed. 2 dulduleel yaryar ee isbuunyo (sponge). 3 afka wabiyeed.

ovipositor (‘awva,paazatar) n. sabiil cayayaan; duleel unug oo cayayaan ukunta ku rimmiyo.

ovisac (‘awva,saak) n. eeg graafian follicle.

ootheca (,awa’thiika) n., pl. oothecae (,awa’thii,kii) gal ukumeed, siiba baranbaro (cockroach). –oothecal (,awa’thiikal) adj.

ovotestis (,awvaw’testas) n. labeeb; xibnihii taran ee lab iyo dhaddig oo qof ku wada yaal (hermaphrodite gonad).

ovule (‘aa,vyuul; ‘aw,vyuul) n. ugaxan side yare.

floral (‘falooral) adj. ubaxeed; la xariira ama ku lug leh ubax.                                                                     -n. floral naqshad ubaxeed.

perianth (‘perii,aanth) n. ubax intiisa aan taran ku jirin.

ovum (ˈawvam) n., pl. ova (ˈawva) ugxan taran dhaddig: macrogamete. kale loogu yeeraa egg cell.

ova (ˈawva) n. jamac (plural of) ovum (ˈawvam).

egg cell n. eeg ovum.

oxyhemoglobin (,aaksi’hiima,galawban) n. unugyada dhiigga cas (hemoglobin) oo wata oxygen gaarsiiyana jirka. Barbardhig deoxyhemoglobin.

deoxyhemoglobin (,dhi’yaaksi’hiima,galawban) n. unugyada dhiigga cas (hemoglobin) oo aan wadin oxygen. Barbardhig oxyhemoglobin.

inflow (ˈin,falaw) n. 1 dhex qulqula, siiba dareere ama neef: the inflow of gas. 2 qulqul lacageed ama dadeed. e.g. There was a massive inflow of foreign investment.

columnar (ka’lamnar) adj. qaab taxaal ama qotoneed leh. e.g. The cells were thin and columnar.

palisade parenchyma n. lakabka sare ee caleen oo sameeya cagaariye (photosynthesis).

pectoral fin n. baalbiyood garabeed; baalalley yaryar ee kalluun.

pelvic girdle n. lafo misigeed; misigta qaybteeda hoose labada lafood oo duleela.

peptone (’pep,tawn) n. mid kasta oo ka mid ah dhawr walxood oo biyo ku mile (any proteins) qaarna biyaha ka saara.

pericardial (,pera’kaardhiyal) n. la xariira ama saameeya xuub wadnaha ku wareegsan.

pericardial cavity n. qolqolka dusha wadnaha; dareere buuxiya labadhexda labada lakab ee ku wareegsan wadnaha: pericardium.  

peripeteia (,perapa’tiya) n. isbaddal dhaqsiyo ee xaalad.

petiole (‘peedhi,yawl) n. 1 samay caleeneed; lafdhabar caleeneed oo salkeedu ku dhago laanta. 2 peduncle. kale loogu yeeraa leafstalk. –petioled (ˈpedhi,yawldh) adj.

phagocytosis (,faagasa’tawsas) n., pl. phagocytoses (ˌfaagasa’taw,siiz) unug cune; hab nooc unugyada dhiigga cad (phagocyte) isku wareejiyaan oo burburiyaan cudur (bacteria). -phagocytotic (,faagasa’taadhik) adj.

phenotype (‘fiina,taayp) n., pl. phenotypes muuq-sheeg; astaan muuqata, sida dherer qof, midab indho, iwm.                                                                -v. phenotyped; phenotyping; phenotypes eegid, baarid, saadaalin qof astaamaha u gaarka noqonkara. –phenotypic (ˌfiina’tipik) or -phenotypical (ˌfiina’tipikal) adj.; -phenotypically (ˌfiina’tipiklii) adv. Barbardhig genotype.

phototropism (faw’taatra,pizam) n. ifraac; awood dhirtu ku raadsato ilays.  

aphototropic (ey,fawdhataraapik) n. ilaysdiid; ka weecda ama ka carara iftiin. -aphototropism (eyfaw’dhaatra,pizam) n.

phylum (‘faaylam) n., pl. phyla (‘faaylla)1 weedh cilimiyeed oo la isku jamciyo noolaha isleh oo abtirsiinyo isku dhaw isku raaca. 2 luuqadaha xariir isku dhaw leh.

plasma membrane n. xuub ilxireed; xuub laga helo unugyada oo dhan oo kala qaybiya gudaha unug iyo dibaddiisa. kale loogu yeeraa cell membrane.

cell membrane n. eeg plasma membrane.

 Phospholipid (,faasfaw’lipad) n. iskudhis lipids ah oo ka kooban phosphoric acids, nitrogen base, alcohol iyo fatty acids.

plasmogamy (palaaz’maagamii) n. isku dhagista dareerayaal (cytoplasm) ku jira laba iyo ka badan unug oo lagu ogaankaro isku dhagga bu’da (nuclei).

karyogamy (,keri’yaagamii) n., pl. karyogamies isku dhagista laba bu’ood ee isbacramiya: fertilization.

plasmolysis (palaaz’maalasas) n. dhadid unug; hab unugyadu dhadaan oo dhumiyaan biyo, markay dhexgalaan milan sare (hypertonic solution). –plasmolytic (palaazma’lidhik) adj.

plastid (‘palaastidh) n. nudo mataanood oo laga helo gudaaha unugga dhir; waxayna mas’uul ka yihiin kaydinta cunto iyo baddalaad midabka. –plastidial adj.

peduncle (‘pii,dhankal) n. 1 samay ubax; laanta dhuuban ee haysa ubax. 2 laan ama gacan; qayb dhuuban oo ku dhagta qabyweynta. –peduncled (ˈ(pii,dhangkaldh) adj. -peduncular (pi’dhangkyalar) adv.

pleural cavity n. moqor sanbabeed; meel ka dhexsamaysmata markii laba lakab ee xuubka (pleura) daboola sanbabka kala qaadmaan. kale loogu yeeraa pleural space.

pleural space n. eeg pleural cavity.

plumule (ˈpuluu,miyuul) n. botany xiddo keen; caleenta kawaad oo mir ka soo baxda dhammaystirana geedka.

pollen grain n. budo faxal; bito ilma’aragto ah ee xibinta taranka labka ubax wato.

pollination (,paala’neyshan) n. botany faxalayn; faxal (pollen) ka qaadis labka ubax (anther) una gudbin dhaddig (stigma), inta badanna ay sameeyaan cayayaan, shinbiro, ama dabayl, iwm.

polysaccharide (ˌpaalii’saaka,raaydh)  silsilad dheer oo carbohydrate kana samaysan carbohydrates yaryar oo la dhaho monosaccharides oo jirku u isticmaalo tamar ama qaabdhiskiisa.

prophase (‘paraw,feyz) n. waji tabaabusho; wajiga hore ee iskala qaybiska unug, ka hor wajiga metaphase; oo ah marka bu’du qarsoonto oo hidda-sidayaashu (chromosomes) u muuqdaan lammaane miiqyeed (paired chromatids).

telophase (‘tela,feyz) n. wajiga u danbeeya ee iskala qaybiska unug, una dhexeeya anaphase iyo interphase oo hidde-side (chromosomes) u guuro lidka unugyada meelaha ugu danbeeya iyo samaysmadka laba bu’ood (two nuclei).

proteinase (‘parawdha,neys) n. eeg protease.

protease (‘parawdhii,eeys) n. noocyo dheecaan (enzymes) oo sii burburiya nafaqooyin (proteins) kana mid yihiin: serine, cysteine. kale loogu yeeraa proteinase.  

protoplasm (‘parawdha,palaazam) n. biyo iyo dareere (protein) dhag-dhag ah oo aan lahayn midab kuna jira bu’da unug noole: cytoplasm. -protoplasmic (,parawdha’palaazmik) adj.

protoxylem (,parawdha’zaaylam) n. abuur horaad; abuurka hore (xylem developing) oo samaysma bilawga koritaan.

pseudopodium (,suudha’pawdhiyam) n., pl. pseudopodia  1 gacan, siiba mid ku taal unug. 2 laan dhuuban oo caleenla’ waddana istarmiska geed.

acoelomous (ˈeey,siilamas) adj. eeg acoelomate.

ptyalin (‘taayalan) n. dheecaan ama dhareer (enzyme) ku jira calyada xayawaan badan oo ka   caawisa ku darista sonkor.

pulmonary aorta n. gar sambabeed; laba xidid oo waaweyn oo wadnaha ka qaada dhiig aysan ku jirin oxygen (deoxygenated blood) geeyaanna sanbabka.

pulmonate (‘puulma,neyt) adj. 1 anatomy sanbabley ah; sanbab leh ama xibno la mid ah. 2 biology la xariira ama la bah ah xaaxeeyo (snails): gastropod.

gastropod (‘gaastara,paadh) n. bahda (Gastropoda) xaaxeeyada (snails). -gastropod adj.

aqua pura (,aakwa’piyuura) n. saafi biyood.

pura culture n. cadaanyo aan la tarraxin; ciidan unugyo ama noole kale oo meel ka wada baxa ahna hal nooc ama isir.

pyloric sphincter n. hunguri; dhuun muruqeed caloosha uga gudbisa qaybta sare mindhiciryaraha (small intestine). kale loogu yeeraa pyloric valve.

pyloric valve n. eeg pyloric sphincter.

-biotic (baa’yaadhik) adj. dibgale (suffix) qeexa hab nololeed: endobiotic.

endobiotic (ˌendaw’baay’aadhik) adj. ku dul nool noole kale: parasite. e.g. endobiotic fungi.

abiotic (ˌeey,baa’yaadhik) adj. aan la xariirin ama ahayn noole, siiba xariirkooda bii’adeed. -abiotically (ˌeey,baa’yaadhiklii) adv.

abiological (ˌeey,baaya’laajikal) adj. aan lahayn nool; ma-noole ah.

biotic potential n. awood noole u leeyahay in uu dib u tarmo ama u sii jiro.

abiotic factor n. waxyaalo ma-noole ah oo qayb ka qaata jiritaanka bii’ad, sida water, sunlight, oxygen, soil iyo temperature.

acoelomate (ˌeey’siila,meyt) n. lafdhabarla’ (invertebrate) aan lahayn meel ka duleesha jirka: animal without a coelom. –invertebrate adj.

acquired trait n. waxyaabo aan la firsan ama la hidda raacin, sida akhrinta buug, barashada xirfad, gaari wadaw, iwm.

activation energy n. inta ugu yar oo tamar dheeraad ah in ay ku dhaqaajiso maalikiyuul falgal kiimiko (chemical reaction).

radially symmetrical wanqaran gacneed; laba ama ka badan oo isku eg u kala dhanbalmikara. –radially symmetrical adj.

radula (‘raajala) n., pl. radulae (‘raaja,lii) also  radulas carrab-ilkeed; carrab cayayaan, sida xaaxeeyo (snails). –radular (‘raajalar) adj.

radular sac n. kiish carrabeed, siiba midkiisa hoose carrab cayayaan.

radula tooth n. ilig carrab cayayaan.

rat flea n. huunyo jiireed; tagfi jiir.

recessive character n. astaan hidda-side shiiqsane; calaamadaha hidda-sidaha isqariya.

recessive gene n. hidda-side shiiqsane; hidda-side isqariya; xaalad ka dhacda inta badan laba waalid oo xigta ah (related), carruurtoodana u keenta xab sanbabka ah (cystic fibrosis) iyo phenylketonuria (PKU).  

phenylketonuria (ˌfenal,kiitn’uuriya) n. abbr. PKU cudur  dhimanaansho (disorder) oo la dhaxlay, sababtayna amino acid loogu yeero phenylalanine oo ku abuurmatay dhiigga. –phenylketonuric (ˌfenal,kiitn’uurik) n. or adj.

phenylalanine (ˌfenal’aala,miin) n. amino acid (C9H11NO2 jirka caadig ah ayaa u baddala (tyrosine) waxaana laga helaa caanaha hooyada iyo cuntooyinka hilib, kalluun, digaag, laws, iyo miraha sisin (sesame seeds).

cystic (ˈsistik) adj. 1 la xariira kaadihays. 2 la xariira, ka kooban, ama xambaarsan kiish (cyst).

cystic fibrosis n. cudur wata xab oo xira sanbabka, marinnada dheefshiidka, iyo meelo kale oo jirka ah.

fibrosis (brōfaay’brawsas) n. xaalad nudaha (tissues) gudaha jirka ay koraan. –fibrotic (faay’baraadhik) adv.

reflex action n. fal fal-naq; fal fal-celis dhaqsa ah, sida haddii dab la taabto dhaqsa looga boodo.

regeneration (ri,jena’reyshan) n. 1 dib isku habayn. 2 dib u soo bixis ama dhalasho, siiba dhir ama geedo. 3 dib u soo kabasho ama bogsasho, siiba dhaawac ama jirro.  

reductive (ri’dhektiv) adj. 1 la xariira ama keena yarayn. 2 la fududeeyay ama la sahlay: reductionistic. –reductively adv.; -reductiveness n.

reductionism (ri’dhaksha,nizam) n. fududayn; arrin adag ku sheegis si fudud oo la fahmikaro. reductionist (ri’dhakshanisti) n. or adj.; -reductionistic (ri,dhaksha’nistik) adj.

reproductive organ n. xibin taraneed; habdhis xibno iyo qaybo shaqadoodu tahay samaynta taranka oo ka kooban, labka: testes, penis, seminal vesicles, prostate, iyo urethra); dhaddigana: ovaries, fallopian tubes, uterus, vagina, iyo vulva.

reproductive system n. habdhis taran; iskudar xibno koreed iyo xibno gudeed ee lab iyo dhaddigba oo ka wada shaqeeya waalid noqosho.

respiratory pigment n. midab-side neefsasho; walax (substance) caawisa awoodda dhiiggu ku xambaaro oxygen, sida hemoglobin oo maalikiyuullo protein ku jiraan unugyada dhiigga cas (RBCs).

vinyl chloride n. neef aan lahayn midab oo guban’og, astaan kiimiko C2H3Cl.

vinyl resin n. mid kasta oo ka mid ah noocyo badan oo walxo caag jilicsan ah (thermoplastic).

respiratory tube n. dhuun neefsasho; hunguriga cad ilaa sanbabbada dhuumahooda.

reticulum (ri’tikyalam) n., pl. reticula (ri’tikyala) also reticulums calool labaad; qolqolka labaad ee caloosha oo ay adeegtaan xayawaanka soo calaanjanaqsada (ruminant). Barbardhig abomasum, omasum, rumen.

abomasum (,aabaw’meysan) n., pl. abomasa (,aabaw’meysa) calood afaraad; qolqolka afaraad ee caloosha oo ay adeegtaan xayawaanka soo calaanjanaqsada (ruminant). Barbardhig rumen, reticulum. –abomasal (,aabaw’meysal) adj.

omasum (aw’meysam) n., pl. omasa (aw’meysa) caloosha saddexaad; qolqolka saddexaad ee caloosha oo u dhexeexaya qolqolka reticulum iyo abomasum oo ay adeegtaan xayawaanka soo calaanjanasada (ruminant). Barbadhig rumen.

Rh factor n. lahaansho Rh; nafaqo (protein) laga helo dusha unugyada dhiigga cas; haddii ay leeyihiin protein kaan waa “Rh positive”, haddii aysan lahaynna waa “Rh negative”; halkaas ayayna ka timid (O positive ama A negative).

rhizome (‘raay,zawm) n. geed-jiif; geed jirriddiisu jiif dhulka ugu baxdo oo caleen iyo xididba samaysta. –rhizomic (raay’zawmik) adj.

RNA (,aar,en’eey) n. maalikiyuul (molecule) laga helo noolayaasha nool (living organisms), waxayna ka samaysanyihiin nucleotides ah sonkorta ribose (ribose sugars) oo ku dhaggan nitrogenous bases iyo phosphate groups. Barbardhig messenger RNA, ribosomal RNA, transfer RNA.

ribosomal RNA n. qayb ka mid ah protein dhisayaal unugga; waxayna mas’uul ka yihiin tarjumista ama habka unugyadu u sameeyaan proteins. kale loogu yeeraa rRNA.

messenger RNA n. abbr. mRNA nooc RNA maalikiyulladeeda ah oo laga helo unugyada, waxayna qaadaan xogta hidda-sidaha oo sameeya proteins. Barbardhig transfer RNA.

genetic information n. ugu badnaan dhammaan xogta qof caafimaadkiis iyo jiritaankiisa jir ahaaneed (gender, race, height, weight, iyo waxyaalaha kale ee la xariira). Barbardhig transfer RNA.

transfer RNA (‘taraanis,far ,aar,en’eey) n. maalikiyuul yar ee RNA oo mRNA ka caawiya furfurista xogaha iyo taxanka koraya ee amino acids oo sameeya protein. kale loogu yeeraa tRNA. Barbardhig messenger RNA.

ribosome (‘raayb,sawm) n. dhisme ka dhexeeya RNA iyo proteins, waana dhinaca samaynta protein ka ku jira unug. –ribosomal (,raayba’sawmal) adj.

codon (‘kaw’dhaan) n. iskusohan DNA iyo RNA ee saddexda nucleotides (trinucleotides) oo qaabeeya hal lug oo hidda-side.

genomic (ji’nawmik) adj. la xariira genome ama genomics.

genomics (jii’nawmikis) n. laan ka mid ah biotechnology oo gooni u eegta barashada dhammaan DNA oo ay ku jiraan hidde-sideyaasha qof ama noole kale. Barbardhig proteomics.

proteomics (,parawdhii’yawmikis) n. laan ka mid ah biotechnology oo gooni u eegta barashada xirfadaha maalikiyuulka, biochemistry, iyo falanqaynta dhismaha hidda-siyadaaysha, shaqada, iyo isdhexgalaka proteins sameeya unug hidda-side khaas ah. Barbardhig genomics. –proteomic (,parawdhi’yawmik) adj.

biotechnology (,baayawtek’naalajii) n. 1 addegsiga biology si loo horumariyo habab iyo wax soo saar cusub. 2 ergonomics. –biotechnological (,baayaw,tekna’laajikal) adj.; -biotechnologically (,baayaw,tekna’laajiklii) adv.; -biotechnologist (,baayawtek’naalajisti) n.

root cap n. koofi xidid; fur yar oo daboola madaxa hore ee xidid. kale loogu yeeraa calyptra.

calyptra (ka’liptara) n. koofi daboosha ubax, xidid, ama mir oo tuurmata marka ay weynaadaan.

root nodule n. eeg nodule sense 2.

symbiosis (,simbi’yawsas) n., pl. symbioses (,simbi’yaw,siiz) 1 kala faa’iidaysi, siiba laba noole oo kala sinji duwan: mutualism. 2 xariir wadaag ama wada shaqayn ka dhexayso.

root pressure n. cadaadis xidid; cadaadis siimaw (osmotic pressure) oo biyaha xididdadu kor ugu soo kacaan jiridda geedaha.

root system n. habdhis xidid; habka geedku ku qotonsado ugana helo ciidda biyo iyo milan macdan; waana laba qaybood: taproot, fibrous.

taproot (‘taap,ruut) n. 1 xidid udub; xidid ama buruq toos hoos ugu baxda oo xididdo yaryar samaysa, sida dabacasaha (carrot). 2 udub dhexaadka wax korriinkooda ama kobocood.

sap (‘saap) n. 1 dareere dheecaan biyood oo dhirta ku jira. 2 dareeraha jirka ku jira, sida dhiig ama dheecaan kale. 3 nacas; qof jilicsan ama la sirikaro: gullible person.

alburnum (aal’barnam) n. eeg sapwood.

sapwood (‘saap,wuudh) n. qori dheecaan; qori dhuux jileec ah oo biyo leh. eeg alburnum.

schistosomiasis (,shisatasaw,maayasas) n., pl. schistosomiases (,shistasaw’maaya,siiz) cudur uu keeno gooryaan dixiriyeed. kale looygu yeeraa snail fever, bilharzia, and Katayama feve.

sea cucumber n. qajaar badeed.

secondary wall n. gidaar danbeed; qaab dhismeed laga helo unugga dhir, kuna kala dhexjira xuubka gidaarka sare ee unugga (primary call wall) iyo xuubka ilaxireed (plasma membrane).

seed plant n. geed mirood. eeg spermatophyte.

seedstalk n. samayda mirta geed ubaxeed.

segmentation cavity n. eeg blastocoel.

blastocoel (‘balaasta,siil) n., pl. blastocoele dareere buuxiya moqorka uurjiif (blastula). –blastocoelic (,balaasta’siilik) adj.

self-differentiation (.selef,difa,renshi’yeeshan) n., pl. self-differentiations iska soocid; iska saaris inta kale (saaxiib ama qof qoyskiis).                          self-differentiate (,selef,dhisfa’renshi,yeyt) intransitive verb self-differentiated; self-differentiating; self-differentiates

self-fertilization (,selef,fardhala’zeyshan) n. isbacriminayn; isbacriminta unugyada taraneed (gametes ama sex cell) ee lab iyo dhaddig oo isku shakhsi ku yaal, siiba ubaxa geedaha qaarkood. -self-fertilize (,selef’fardha,laayz) v.

self-pollination (,selef,paala’neyshan) n. isfaxlis; laba ubax oo isku geed ku taal oo faxalka labku (pollen) u gudbiyo dhaddigga (stigma).

semen (ˈsiiman) n. mani (xawo); dareere (spermatozoa) ka yimaada marinka taranka lab oo bacrimiya ukunnta dhaddiga.

seminal duct n. marin xawo; xididdada manidu soo marto.

seminiferous tubule n. dhuumo isku jaruursan oo ka kooban unugyo aan caadi ahayn (Sertoli cells) waana meesha uu ka dhaco qaybsanka unug hidde-side (meiosis), ama ka dhaco samaysanka unugyada taranka (sex cells).

Sertoli cell (ˌsar’tawlii ‘seel) n. unugga ugu muhiimsan oo labka u sameeya xawada (sperm).

sensory neuron n. dareeme dareen wade ka dira xibnaha dareenka una dira masxda. Barbardhig interneuron, motor neuron.

sepal (“siipal) n. dhago; ubax marka uu dillaacayo dhagaha ku xeeran. kale loogu yeeraa calyx.

penal code n. xeer ciqaabeed; sharciyo sheegyada danbiyada iyo ciqaabtooda.

silent system n. habdhis aamus; hab eedaab ciqaabeed oo mamnuuca in lala sheekaysto maxaabiis.

sessile (‘se,saayl) adj. 1 zoology joogto ugu dhaggan; aan dhaqaaq samayn. 2 botany samayla’; caleen saynla’; saddex ayay caleen u qaybsantaa: sessile leaf (saynla’ ama samayla’), subsessile leaf (sayn gummadley); iyo petiolate leaf (samayoleey ama saynley).

subsessile adj. caleen sayn yar leh.

sex cell n. 1 unug taran (gamete). 2 unug noqday xaabuq gaamuray (stem cell) oo gaaray heer uu sameeyo unugyo dhiig oo cusub.

Barr body n. eeg sex chromatin.

sex determination n. hab abuurista jinsi laga hidda-raaco waqtiga bacriminta.

sex differentiation n. kala soocis jinsi; habdhiska xibnaha taranka lab iyo dhaddig ka abuurmaan qaabdhiska uurjiif.

sexual organ n. xibin jinsiyeed; qayb ka mid ah noolaha oo la xariirta taranka galmoodka; waana xibinta jinsiyeed ee lagu garto nooca noolaha jinsigiisa. Barbardhig genitalia.

sex transformation n. beddelaad jinsi; jinsiga waxaa baddalan jeermis (bacteria) iyo wixii aan xoolo ahayn (non-animal).

sexual generation n. jiil jinsi; jiil noole ku sameeya jiil kale tarankooda galmeed.

sexual reproduction n. taran jinsi; soo saarka noole cusub ayada oo la midaynayo hidda-sidayaasha laba shakhsi oo jinsi ahaan kala duwan.

sexual selection n. xulad jinsi; habdhis shakhsiyadu ku tartamaan cidda ay taran la samaynayaan.

shoot system habdhis xiddeed; qayb ka mid ah geed oo dhulka kor uga soo baxsan, sida jirridda iyo caleemaha.

shoulder joint n. kala goys garab; cududda iyo lafta garab isku xirankooda.

sieve cell n. unug shaandho. Barbardhig tracheid.

tracheid (‘tareeykiyad) n. dhuun unug oo geed gaarsiisa biyo iyo macdan ka yimid xididka.

sieve tube n. dhuun-caleen shaandho; unugyo nool oo leh dhuumo khafiif ah oo ay caleen geed (phloem) u mariso biyo iyo macdan.

sinus venosus (ˈsaaynasvi’nawsas) n. duleed aroor; maqor ballaaran oo ku dhaggan wadnaha oo ay qaabeeyeen kulan xididdo isku habaysan, waana meesha dhiigga xididdadu ka soo galo wadnaha ee lafdhabarleyda hoose (lower vertebrates).

lower vertebrates n. lafdhabarley hoose; shinbiro, xamaarato, barribiyood, iyo kalluun: non- mammalian vertebrates (birds, reptiles, amphibians and fish).

siphon (‘saayfan) n. also syphon dhuun; tuubbo.

skeletal system n. habdhis qalfood; qaabdhis caawiya wadashaqaynta jirka.

smooth muscle n. muruq sisiban; muruq aan lahayn daliigyo, sida mindhicirro (intestines, min (uterus), iyo calool (stomach). Barbardhig striated muscle.

cardiac muscle n. muruq wadneed.

striated muscle n. muruq miiqle; muruq daliigyo leh. Barbardhig smooth muscle, voluntary muscle.

voluntary muscle n. muqur toosan (striated muscle) oo la xukumo ama la nuuxinkaro.

somatic cells n. unugyo jireed; unugyada jirka oo dhan, unugyada ukumo (egg cells) iyo xawo (sperm) mooyaane.

somite (ˈsaw,maayt) n. jireed; hab dheraran oo loo qaybiyo jirka xayawaan badan qaarkood: metamere.

metamere (ˈmedha,miir) n. hab hore oo dhuubyo isku eg ee jirka lafdhabarla’da ama lafdhabarleyda loo qaybin jiray.

metamerism (me’dhaama,rizam) n. mululuqsan; jir dhuuban oo is wada leh, sida ciidagale ama gooryaan.

space biology n. laan ka mid ah biology oo gooni u eegta noolayaasha nool, sida ay hawada sare saamayn ugu yeelankarto iyo raadinta in nolol kale ka jirto.

speciation (ˌispiishii’yeyshan) sinjiyeyn; abuuranka isirro noole qaabaysmaan. –speciate (ˈispiihii,yeyt) intransitive verb; -speciational (ˌisiishii’yeyshnal) adj.

spermatogenesis (ˌispar,maadha’jenasas) n. koridda xawada; habka abuuranka manida (sperm) oo unugyo xawo cargo ah ay isdaba joog isku kala jaran (mitotic and meiotic divisions) si ay u bataan. –spermatogenic (ˌispar,maadha’jenik) adj.

spermatophyte (,ispar’maadha,faayt) n. iniinley; geed kasta oo ah bahda dhasha miro. –spermatophytic (,ispar,maadha’fidhik) adj.

gymnosperm (‘jimna,sparm) n., pl. gymnosperms dhirta dhasha miro furan oo aan qob ku jirin. Babardhig angiosperm. –gymnospermous (,jimna’sparmas) adj.; -gymnospermy  (‘jimna,aparmii) n.

spermatozoid (,ispar,maadha’zawadh) n. shawada dhaqaaqda ee labka dhirta (motile male gamete) oo ay samayso xibinta taranka lab ee dhireed (antheridium).

sperm cell n. unug xawo (male gamete): spermatozoon.

spermiation (ˌisparmii’yeyshan) n. xawo keen; biyabixis oo xawo soo marto xaniinyaha.

sperm nucleus n. bu’ xawo; bu’da unug xawo (sperm cell) waxa uu xambaarsanyahay barka walxo hidda-sidayaal (DNA).

spinal nerve n., pl. spinal nerves dareen wade; mid kasta oo ka mid ah dareen wadayaasha mataanaha ah ee lafdhabarleyda, caawiyana muruqyada saableyda iyo addimada, iskuna xirta habdhiska dareen wadayaasha jirka, dadkuna leeyahay 31 lammaane.

sponge parenchyma n. nooc nudo (tissues) isbuunyo oo laga helo dhir iyo xayawaan. kale loogu yeeraa spongy layer, spongy tissue.

spontaneous generation n. iski-taran; arrin hadda huuhaa noqday in nooluhu uusan ka imaanin ma-noole.

sporangium (ispa’raanjiyam) n., pl. sporangia (ispa’raanjiya) budo faxal side; moqor yar oo kaydiya boor faxal (spore) ubax. –sporangial (ispa’raanjiyal) adj.

spore mother cell n. unug hooyeed faxal.

archespore (ˈaarka,ispawr) n. or archesporium plural archespores or archesporia unug ama koox unugyo ah oo unug hooyeed faxal (spore mother cell) abuurto. –archesporial (‘aarka,ispawriyal) adj.

staminate (ˈisteymanat) n.1 dhala ama leh labnimo (stamens). 2 ubax lab laakiin aan la hayn dhaddig (pistils).

stem cell n. unug xaabuq; unug aan lahayn xirfad oo kaalmeeya kuwa kale.

stipule (ˈisti,piyuul) n. baarumo; caleenyaro; samayda caleen salkeeda (petiole) caleen yar oo ka soo baxda.

stolon (ˈistawlan) n. 1 laanjiif; laan dhulka seexata oo madaxa xididdo iyo geed hor leh ka bixisa. 2 fangas bixiya farraaqsho badan (hypha).

stoloniferous (ˌistawla’nifras) adj. keena ama abuura laanjiif (stolon). e.g. stoloniferous branches.

struggle for existence n. loollan jiritaan; tartan noolaansho oo ka dhexjira noolaha xagga cuntada, hooyga, iyo nabadda.

style sac n. moqor dhuun ubbeed.

sucrase (ˈsuu,kareys) n. eeg invertase.

invertase (in’var,teys) n. dheecaan (enzyme) kalkaaliya jajabinta (hydrolysis) sonkorta (sucrose).

cytokinesis (ˌsaydhawka’niisas) n. wajiga ugu danbeeya ee qaybsanka unug oo uu laba isle’eg u kala go’.

survival of the fittest noun phrase eeg natural selection.

tarsal bone n. lafo cageed; 7 lafood oo yaryar kana bilawda cirib ilaa gadaasha faraha cagaha.

taste bud n. ruqur dhadhan; unugyo carrabka ku jira oo dhadhanka sheega, sida sweet, salty, sour, bitter iyo umami.

umami (uu’maamii) n. dhadhan hilib; dhadhanka shanaad (sweet, salty, sour, bitter and umami).

tetrapoda (te’trapadha) n. afar addinley

testcross (ˈtes,karoos) n. iskutalaal hubin; barashada hiddaha si loo ogaado noole noociisa hidde ee muujiya shiiqiye (dominant).

testis (ˈtestas) n., pl. testes (ˈte,stiiz) xaniin; lab labadiis qoorood oo ah qanjirka taranka (reproductive gland).

thallophyte (ˈthaala,faayt) n. geed ku sheeg; cagaar, siiba aan lahayn xidid, caleen, iyo jirrid toona (fungus). –thallophytic (ˌhaala’fidhik) adj.

therophyte (ˈhira,faayt) n. xilli-jire; geed sanadle noolaada, sanad kana ka taga miro soo baxa sanadka kale, siiba dhul abaareed.

thrombin (ˈtharaamban) n. nafaqo (proteins) dhafaagisa (coagulation) ama xinjiraysa (clotting) dhiig.

proteolytic (ˌparawdhiiya’lidhik) adj. la xariirta burburinta proteins si ay wax ugu milmaan: proteolysis. –proteolytically (ˌparawdhiya’lidhiklii) adv.

proteolysis (ˌparawdhi’yaalasas) n. jajabin nafaqo (proteins) qaab fudud oo ay u milmikarto.

tissue culture n. nud beeris; hab ama xirfad nud jireed baaris ahaan meel jirka ka baxsan loogu abuuro.

tobacco mosaic disease n. cudur buuri; cudur (virus) ku dhaca caleenta keedka tubaako.

trace element n. curiye raadguris; aasaaska curiyayaasha ku jira nafaqada dadka iyo xayawaanka kale oo ka mid yihiin iron (Fe) (hemoglobin), copper (Cu) (respiratory pigments), cobalt (Co) (Vitamin B12), iodine, manganese (Mn) and zinc (Zn) (enzymes).

tracheal gill n. waafyo hunguri cad; waafyo neefqaadasho (branchial respiration) ee cayayaan biyo-ku-nool (aquatic insect).

tracheal system n. habdhis hunguri cad; habka neefsiga noolaha oo dhuumaha hawada iyo faracoodu ay qaadaan.

tracheole (ˈtareyki,yawl) n. farac dhuun hawo; dhuumo qayb ka ah habdhiska neefsiga cayayaan. –tracheolar (tarey’kiiyalar) adj.

transamination (ˌtaraanis,aama’neyshan) n. amino gudbin; koox amino (animo group) ka guurin maalikiyuul una rarid maalikiyuul kale.

transmigrate (ˌtaraanis’maay,gareyt) v. transmigrated; transmigrating; transmigrates 1 ka guurid meel una guurid meel kale. 2 dhimatin oo noqotin noole kale (reincarnate). –transmigration (ˌtaraansmaay’gaareyshan) n.; -tranismigrator (ˌtaraanis’maay,gareydhar) n.; -transmigratory (taraanis’maaygra,toorii) adj.

trematode (ˈtarema,tawdh) n. gooryaan-ballaar; bah gooryaan ballaar (Trematoda). –trematode adj.

trichina (taray’kaayna) n., pl. trichinae (taray’kii,nii) also trichinas dixiri aad u yar oo hilib-cun ah. –richinal (taray’kaaynal) adj.

triploid (ˈtiri,ploydh) adj. seddexan; tiro hidda-side (chromosome) oo saddex laab leh. -triploid n.; -triploidy (ˈtiri,ploydhii) n.

monoploid (ˈmaana,paloydh) adj. 1 haploid. 2 tirada hidda-sidayaal (chromosomes) ee qof laga rabo (46), qof barkeed (23) leh, taas oo aan caadi ahayn. -monoploid n.

pollen grain n. unug kali ah oo xambaarsan laba lab unug tarameed (two male gametes).

tube cell n. unug ku dhexjira (pollen grain) oo ka dhexsamaysma dhuunta qaadda taran lab (pollen tube).

tube nucleus n. bu’dhuumeed; bu’da (pollen grain) oo xukunta korista (pollen tube).

tuber (ˈtuubar) n. 1 bari; buruq; waana laba nooc: buruq xidid (root tuber) iyo bari jirrid (stem tuber). 2 tuberosity. Barbardhig bulb, corm.

tubule (ˈtuu,biyuul) n. dhuun-yaro: a little tube.

tuberosity (ˌtuuba’raasatii) n., pl. tuberosities soo kuusan; soo foocsan

turgor (‘targar) n. foocsan; fuursan. e.g. Some cells maintain a very high turgor pressure.

turgor movement n. siqad fuursanaan, siiba qaybta dhirta ah: nyctitropism.

turgor pressure n. cadaadis fuursanaan; cadaadis gudaha ah oo unug foocsamo. kale loogu yeeraa hydrostatic pressure.

nyctitropism (nik’titra,pizam) n. caleemaha oo habaynkii dhada maalintiina fida: sleep movement. Barbardhig nyctinasty.
