directly proportional adj. saamiyaal qumman; ka dhexeeyo toos isbaddal (direct variation); way wada kordhaan ama way wada yaraadaan. Barbardhig inversely proportional.

inversely proportional adj. ka dhaxeeyo isbaddal lid isku ah (inverse variation); haddii mid kordho kan kale wuu yaraadaa. e.g. As we increase the speed, the time is reduced. Barbardhig directly proportional.

disaccharide (,dhaay’saaka,raaydh) n. walax kasta oo ka kooban laba maalikiyuul oo sonkor ah, iskuna xiran; sonkorta caadiga ah, sonkorta caanaha; lactose (milk sugar), iyo sonkorta maltose (malt, or beer sugar).

monosaccharide (,maana’saaka,raaydh) n. nooc ah carbohydrate (walxaha nasiiya tamarta) oo ka samaysan hal maalikiyuul (walax keeda ugu yar) oo sonkor ah, sidaa darteed aan la sii jajabinkarin si ay u samaysmaan sonkoro kale. kale loogu yeeraa simple sugar.

dissociation constant n. madoorsoomaha kala furanka; joogtada dheeltir ka dhaxeeya kala furmad iyo kala furmad la’aanta iskuxirnaanta kiimiko.

distribution coefficient n. eeg partition coefficient.

partition coefficient n. weheliyaha qaybsanaanta; samiga celcelis dhexdhexaad ee laba walax oo aan isku qasmikarin isdheellitirayaan; partion coefficient = (C1/C2)equil.

divalent (,dhaa’veylanti) adj. laba kaaftoonle; awood (valence) kiimiko oo laba ah leh; laba qurub (atom) ama kooxood ku xirmikara. e.g. Oxygen is divalent while hydrogen.

domain name n. magaca cinwaanka xariirka internet.

double bond n. dabar lammaane; iskuxir kiimiko oo laba lammaane oo electrons ay kala qaybsadeen laba qurub (atoms).

double decomposition n. kalabax lammaan; falgal kiimiko (comical reaction) oo dhexmara laba iskukdhis (compounds) oo midba qayb ka baddalato midda kale si ay u sameeyaan iskudhisyo nooc kale ah. e.g. AB + CD = AD +BC. kale loogu yeeraa metathesis.

electrical engineering n. injineeriyanta danab; nooc ka mid ah injineernimada oo gooni u eegta danabka.

electron affinity n. 1 xiiso electron; xadka qurub (atom) ama maalikiyuul ku soo jiito electrons dheeraad ah. 2 tamarta ugu yar in electron looga saaro aayon taban (negative ion) si loo sameeyo atom ama maalikiyuul caadi ah.

electron cloud n. xayaabo electron; hab electrons ku wareegsanyihiin bu’da (nucleus) qurub (atom).

electromagnetic wave n. hir birlabdanabeed; hirar ka abuurmay gariiryo u dhexeeya badad birlabdanabeed oo ay ku jiraan (radio waves, infrared, visible light, ultraviolet, X-rays, and gamma rays).

electrovalence n. also electrovalency eleketaroon-kaaftoomis; tirada electrons ka la kala baddasho xilliga lagu jiro qaabsoonka aayoonka (ion). kale loogu yeeraa ionic valence. -electrovalent adj.; -electrovalently adv.

covalency (‘kaw’veylansii) n. eeg covalence.

electrovalent bond n. dabar elektaroon-kaaftoon; iskuxir kiimiko oo ay qaabeeyeen aayoonno (ions) lid charge leh (opposite charges). kale loogu yeeraa ionic band.

elementary analysis n. saafidda fudud; baaris wax ka koobnaantooda. e.g. Elemental analysis is a must.

emergency contraception n. daawooyinka ka hortagga uur (morning-after bill, IUD).

superpose (,suupar’pawz) v. superposed; superposing dulsaarid. e.g. The artist superposed different layers of colors and textures. -superposable (ˌsuupar’pawzbal) adj.

superimpose (ˌsuuparim’pawz) v. superimposed; superimposing; superimposes kor-ka-saarid; dulsaarid. e.g. We superimposed the map onto the satellite image. -superimposition (ˌsuupar,impa’zishan) n.

superimposable (,suuparim’pawzabal) adj. la isdul saarikaro, siiba wax isle’eg. e.g. The two shapes are almost superimposable.

nonsuperimposable (,naan,suuparim’pawzibal) adj. aan isdul saarmikarin, siiba wax aan isku sargo’nayn: chiral. e.g. The two molecules are nonsuperimposable.

chiral (‘kaayral) adj. la xariira muulikiyuullo aan isku sargo’nay. e.g. Chiral molecules have a nonsuperimposable mirror image. -chirality (kaay’raaladhii) n.

electric charge n. saldanab danabeed; laba nooc baajira, mid togan (positive charge) iyo mid taban (negative charge).

chemical affinity n. xiisa kiimikeed; walxo electrons oo isir kiimiko ku kala duwan oo awooda in ay qaabeeyaan iskudhisyo kiimiko (chemical compounds).

 

chemical balance n. miisaan kiimikeed; cabbirid saxnaanata culaabta walaxo aad u yar. kale loogu yeeraa analytical balance.

analytical balance n. eeg chemical balance.

chemical band n. dabar kiimikeed; isasoojiidasho waarta oo ka dhaxaysa atoms ama ions taas oo suurtagal ka dhigta qaabayn maalikiyuullo.

chemical change n. isbaddal kiimikeed; isbaddal kasta oo keena in walxo cusub qaabaysmaan, sida burning, cooking, rusting, and rotting.

charge-mass ratio n. saami saldanab-cuf; (Q/m) tirade (quantity) saldanabka oo loo qaybiyay cuf (mass) isla shaygii.

chemical compound n. iskudhis kiimikeed; iskudhis ka samaysan laba iyo ka badan walxo kiimiko oo kala duwan, kuna midoobay hab saamiyeed. e.g. water (H2O), it has 2 atoms of Hydrogen combined with 1 atom of oxygen.

chemical constituent n. taariikh kiimikeed; qeexidda atom ka noociisa iyo ku xirmadka maalikiyuul (molecule).

chemical energy n. tamar kiimikaad; tamar ku kaydsan isudhis kiimiko ee atom iyo maalikiyuulkal iskudhisankood.  

chemical equation n. isle’eg kiimikeed; qaab wakiil ka ah falgal kiimikeed. e.g. Al2(CO3)3 + H3PO4 → AlPO4 + CO2 + H2O.

chemical equilibrium n. dheelitiran kiimiko; marka falgal horsocod (orward reaction) uu la mid yahay falgal dibsocod (reverse reaction).

chemical symbol n. summad kiimikeed; soo gaabin astaan walax kiimiko oo gaar ah. e.g. Mg is the chemical symbol of magnesium.

chloral (‘kaloral) n. saliid ur adag oo aan lahayn midab, lagana sameeyo sunta DDT; waxay leedahay iskudhis organic ah ee formula Cl3CCHO.

 

chlorate (‘kaloor,yet) n. iskudhis ( ClO3−) ku jira basasha.

chloride (kaloor,aaydh) n. 1 iskudhis chlorine oo curiye kale ku jiro. 2 cusbada caadiga ah sodium chloride oo wadata chemical formula NaCl.

chlorine oxide n. iskudhis kasta oo labaale chlorine iyo oxygen ka kooban.

chlorine dioxide n. iskudhis kiimiko oo wata formula ClO2 ahna neef hurdi-cagaar ah, loona isticmaalo warnkiilada (bleach) wax lagu nadiifiyo.

oxide (‘aak,saaydh) n. chemistry iskudhis kiimiko oo xambaarsan ugu yaraan hal atom oo oxygen iyo hal curiye oo kale formulada kiimikadiisa; afar nooc ayaan jirta: Basic, Acidic, Amphoteric iyo Neutral Oxides. -oxidic (aak’sidhik) adj.

chromate (‘karaw,meyt) n. cusbo ah chromic acid.

chromic (‘karawmik) adj. la xariirta ama laga keenay curiyaha chromium.

cooling curve n. xood qaboojineed; xarriiq garaaf oo ka taagan isbaddalka wajiga walxaha, siiba neef isku baddasha adke ama adke isku baddala dareere.

copper carbonate n. iskudhis kiimiko oo leh astaan kiimiko Cu2(OH)2CO3.

copper chloride n. also cupric chloride iskudhis kiimiko oo leh astaan kiimiko copper(I) chloride CuCl2 iyo copper(II) chloride (CuCl2).

copper oxide n. iskudhis kiimiko oo leh astaan kiimiko Cu2O, dabeeciyanna loo helo, waana casaan ama hurdi maarxigeen ah.

copper sulfate n. also cuprous sulphate iskudhis kiimiko oo ka kooban sulfate iyo copper, lehna astaan kiimiko CuSO4·5H2O.

cracking process n. habka burburinta maalikiyuul weyn ee hydrocarbon oo laga dhigo maalikiyuullo yar-yar (light hydrocarbons) oo faa’iido leh.

cuprous chloride n. eeg copper chloride.

equation of state n. isle’eg wajiyeed; isle’eg muujisa xariirka ka dhexeeya cadaadis (pressure), heerkul (temperature), iyo mug (volume) neef ama dareere.

equilibrium constant n. madoosoome dheellitiran; dhaqaaqa falgalaha horsocodka ah waxa uu la mid yahay dhaqaaqa falgalaha dibsocodka ah.

equilibrium state n. waji dheellitran; wajiga dhaqaaqa falgal horsocod uu la mid yahay falgal dhaqaaqa dibsocod.

equimolecular (ˌiikwama’lekilar) adj. 1 maalikiyuullo (molicules) isle’ekayaal; xambaarsan tiro isle’eg oo maalikiyuullo ah. 2 equimolar.

equimolar (ˌiikwa’mawlar) adj. 1 la xariira ama leh tirooyin mole oo isle’eg. 2 isku molar (equal molar) ribnaan (concentration) leh.

equivalence point n. bar iskudhigan; milan la ogyahay ribnaantisa mark uu dhammaystiro milanka lagu daray.

titration (taay’tareyshan) n. hab milan la ogyahay ribnaantiisa (concentration) loo isticmaalo in lagu ogaado ribnaanta milan aan la aqoon ilaa falgalku dhammaystirmo.

titrate (‘taay,tareyt) v. titrated; titrating adkayn; ku darid milan (titration). -titratable (ˈtaay,tareydhabal) adj.; -titrator (ˈtaay,tareydhar) n.

equivalent weight n. culays iskudhigan; cufka mid le’eg walax la keenay, taas oo ku darmidoonta ama baddalidoonta tiro cayiman ee walax kale: the atomic or molecular weight divided by the valence.

eremacausis (,erama’kawsas) n. falgalgaabis; walax noole oo tartiib ogsijiintu uga baxdo (gradual oxidation) marka qoyaan ama hawo loo bandhigo.

erythron (‘eera,tharaan) n. caseeye; unugyada dhiigga cas iyo hababkooda ay dhuuxa ugu jiraan.

esterification (e,sterafa’keyashan) n. hab kiimikaad oo isku dara alcohol (ROH) iyo acid walxo noole (RCOOH) si ay u qaabeeyaan ester (RCOOR) iyo biyo.

ethylamine (‘ethala,miin) n. dareere gubata oo uumibixi’og aan la haynna midab, astaan kiimiko C2H5NH2. kale loogu yeeraa monomethylamine.

monomethylamine n. eeg methylamine.

ethyl (‘ethal) n. chemistry alkyl radical CH3CH2 oo laga soo qaatay ethane. -ethylic (e’thilik) adj.

ethylene (‘etha,liin) n. chemistry hydrocarbon aan lahayn midab, neef guban’og ah oo leh astaan kiimiko C2H4 ama H2C=CH2. -ethylenic (ˌetha’liinik) adj.

ethylenediaminetetraacetate (ˌetha,liin,dhaaya,miin,tetra’aas,teyt) n. cusbo ah EDTA (ethylenediamine tetraacetic acid).

ethylenediamine tetraacetic acid (ˌetha,liin,dhaaya,miin,tetra’sidhik) n. eeg EDTA.

EDTA (ˌii,dhii,tii’eey) n. waxay ka hortagtaa muunadaha dhiigga (blood samples) in aysan xinjiroobin iyo in ay jirka ka saarto calcium iyo lead.

 

euchlorin (yuu’kalawriin) n. chemistry macdan iskugu jirta (K,Na)8Cu9(SO4)10(OH)6 sulfate ah copper, sodium, iyo potassium.

eudiometer (ˌyuudhii’aamatar) n. chemistry qalab sheybaar oo lagu cabbiro isbaddalka cuf iskudar neefaha (gas mixture) ayada oo loo eegayo isbaddal kiimiko iyo walax ahaanba. -eudiometric (ˌyuudhiya’metrik) adj.; -eudiometrically (ˌyuudhiya’metriklii) adv.

excitation state n. waji didsan; atom ama maalikiyuul haysta tamar (energy) ka sarraysa caadiga.

quantum numbers n. hormo tiro ah oo lagu qeexo rugta iyo tamarta electrons ku jira atom; waxaa jira afar quantum numbers (principal, azimuthal, magnetic iyo spin quantum numbers). Barbardhig radial quantum number, azimuthal quantum number.

Principal quantum number        n        n = 1, 2, 3, …

Azimuthal                            ℓ        for n = 3: ℓ = 0, 1, 2 (s, p, d)

Magnetic                                 mℓ        for ℓ = 2: mℓ = −2, −1, 0, 1, 2

Spin                                              ms         s = 12, so ms = − 12, + 12

exclusion principle n. mabda’ka baxsanaanta; ma jiro laba walax, sida electrons ama atoms oo ku wada jirta maalikiyuul oo yeelan kara isku hormo tirooyin (quantum numbers). kale oo yaqaan Pauli exclusion principle.

faraday (‘fera,dhey) n. halbeeg (unit of electricity) lagu cabbiro saldanab danabeed (electric charge).

fermentation (,ferman’teyshan) n. khamiir; burburka kiimiko ee ku dhaca walax, sameeyaanna jeermis ama khamiir. e.g. The process of making canjeero involves fermentation.

ferrosolferric oxide n. bir madaw oo birlab ah (iron magnetic oxide Fe3O4) oo dabeeciyan loo helo ama samays ahaan.

first-order reaction n. dhaqso horsiimo kowaad; falgalka kiimiko, kaas oo dhaqsaha falgalku kala dhexeeyo isbaddal toos ah falgalka walaxda ribanaanteeda (concentration). Barbardhig order of a reaction.

second-order reaction n. chemistry dhaqso horsiimo labaad; falgalka kiimiko, kaas oo dhaqsaha falgalku kala dhexeeyo isbaddal toos ah falgalka walaxda ribanaanteeda (concentration) ee labada maalikiyuul oo falgalaysa (two reacting molecules. Barbardhig order of a reaction.

third-order reaction n. chemistry dhaqso horsiimo saddexaad; falgalka kiimiko, kaas oo dhaqsaha falgalku kala dhexeeyo isbaddal toos ah falgalka walaxda ribanaanteeda (concentration) ee saddexda maalikiyuul oo falgalaysa (three reacting molecules. Barbardhig order of a reaction.

zero-order reaction n. chemistry falgal kiimiko (chemical reaction) ee dhaqsaha falgalku (rate of reaction) madoorsoome yahay (constant), xorna ka yahay ribanaanta walxaha falgalaya (reacting substances). Barbardhig order of a reaction.

nonvolatile (naanvaalatal) adj. 1 aan dhaqsa uumibixin. 2 computer memory xog aan dhumin markii danabka la dansho.

fixation of nitrogen n. xayiridda natrajiin; hab nitrogen ka laga soo qaatay hawada, loo baddalo iskudhis kiimiko oo faa’iido u leh adeegsiga noolaha kale.

fixed air n. hawo xayiran; carbon dioxide.

fixed oil n. saliid xayiran; dufanka xoolaha ama saliidda dhirta oo aan dhaqsa u uumibix. Barbardhig essential oil.

flash point n. 1 bar big; heerkulka ugu yar ee dareere bilaabo uumibax kuna holcikaro dusha dareeraha. 2 tinderbox.

tinderbox (ˈtindar,baakis) n. meel qarxikarta ama qarax.

formalin (ˈformalan) n. milan saafi ah oo ah formaldehyde iyo methanol oo loo adeegto kaydinta (preservative), siiba ka ilaalin qurmid ama bololid.

formic acid (ˈformik’aasidh) n. dareere uumi ah oo ur adag, astaan kiimiko CH2O2 lagana  helo qaniinyada shinni, quraanyo, iyo dhirta qaarkeed, badanaa loo isticmaalo dhehyada.

fractionate (ˈfaraaksha,neyt) v. fractionated; fractionating 1 qaybayn; kala qaybqaybin (dareere). 2 jajabin ama qaybin. – fractionation (ˌfaraaksha’neyshan) n.; -fractionator (ˈfaraaksha,neydhar) n.

 

fractionating column n. joogtax xareedayn; dhululubo lagu xareedeeyo iskudar kala qaybaysan. kale loogu yeeraa fractional column.

fractional column n. eeg fractionating column.

free energy n. 1 tamar xor ah; tamar habka laga helikaro oo qabankarta hawl faa’iido leh, weyna ka duwantahay tamarta guud ee falgalka kiimiko baddalay: internal thermodynamic potential. 2 available energy.

free path n. eeg mean free path.

free valence n. kaaftoon xor ah; walaxa qaarkood sida copper (maar), electrons dusha aad uguma dhaggana atom, kuwa darariska ahna waxaa ku adkaada in ay gartaan atoms, sidaas darteed kaaftoonka xorta ah (free valence) hadba atom dariska ah buu ku boodaa.

gallic acid (ˈgaalik ‘aasidh) n. wirqe (crystalline) cad oo aasidh ah C7H6O5 aadna looga helo dhirta, inta badanna loo adeegto dheeha (dyes).

glucoside (ˈguluuka,saaydh) n. eeg glycoside. –glucosidic (ˌguluuka’sidhik) adj.

glycerol (‘galisa,rool) n. dareere macaan (sweet liquid) oo aan lahayn ur iyo midab toona, astaan kiimiko C3H8O3, waxaa laga helaa saabuunaynta baruurta dabiiciga ah (saponification of natural fats) iyo saliidda, waxaana loo adeegtaa macaanaynta iyo kaydgalka cuntada (preserving food), warshaduhuna jir qurxinta (cosmetics), catarada, khadda, iyo koolada (glues) qaarkeed.

graduated cylinder n. dhululubo cabbiran; dhalo dheer oo cabbirada muggu kor uga qoranyihiin lagun cabbiro dareeraha.

gram-atomic weight (‘garaama’taamik ‘wayt) n. also gram-atom cufka (mass) hal mole ee curiye (element) waxa uu la mid yahay grams ka atomic weight; tusaale: gram atomic mass iyo gram atom waa isla meeshii.

gram equivalent n. chemistry garaam iskudhigan; tirada curiye (element), koox, ama iskudhis (compound) oo wata cuf grams ah, waxay la mid tahay culaab teeda u dhiganta; tusaale: grams waxaa lagu cabbiraa cuf (mass), teaspoons lagu cabbiraa mug (volume); xajmiga (density) biyo waa 1 g/ml, marka iskubaddalka (conversion), 1 gram waa 1 milliliter, kaas oo u dhigma (equivalent) 0.2 teaspoons.

ground state n. waji deggan; heer tamareed teeda ugu yar ee atom ama atomic nucleus haysto. kale loogu yeeraa ground level.

ground level n. 1 la sinaadka dhulka oo looga cabbir qaato. 2 guri dabaq kiisa hoose. 3 heer tamareed teeda ugu yar ee atom ama atomic nucleus haysto: ground state.

Haber process n. habka Haber; hab falgal kiimiko oo adeegta neefta nitrogen iyo neefta hydrogen in ay abuuraan iskudhis kiimiko ee ammonia.

 

Haldane apparatus n. saabaanka Haldane; qeexid saxan ee tirade carbon dioxide ee hawada ku jirta daqiiqadaha la adeesankaro.

half-cell n. unug-bar; samays xambaasan qotin gudbiye (conductive electrode) iyo gubiyayaasha ku xeeran ee milangudbiye (electroyte) oo aan caadi wax u xariirin.

half-life (‘half,laayf) n. (summad t1/2) cimri-bar; goorta tirada wax laga rabo in ay yarayso bartamaheeda. e.g. The half-life of a radioactive substance.

half-reaction n. falgal-bar; qayb ka mid ah guud ahaan falgalka, si kala qaybsan, ama ogsijiin ku darista ama ka yaraynta.

halide (‘haa,laaydh) n. iskudhis labaale oo xambaarsan halogen oo leh curiyaal dhumiya electrons (electropositive element).

halogen (‘haalajan) n. mid kasta oo ka mid ah shanta curiye oo aan birta ahayn (fluorine, chlorine, bromine, iodine, or astatine) kulligoodna waa kaaftoon-kaliyaale (monovalent), qaabeeyana ion togan. -halogen adj.

halogenate (‘haalaja,neyt) v. halogenated; halogenating ku xirid curiyayaasha halogen. -halogenation n.

haloid acids adj. dhadhan adag leh.

heating curve n. xoodka kululaynta; xariiqa isbaddalka heerkulku muujiyo uu kulaylku kordhaba.

heat of adsorption n. kulka la nuugay; kulka la xariira marka walax tiradood la sheegay la dhuuqo.

heat of combustion n. kulka gubashada; falagal kulayl oo keena walax gubashadeed dhan.

heat of crystallization n. kulka wiriqaynta; tirada kul oo laga siidaayay hal gram oo dareere xilliga barafawgeeda.

heat of dilution n. kulka badhxan; kulka saameeya cabbirka milme markii milanku aad u baraxsanyahay.

mole4 (‘mool) n., pl. moles lahabeeg lagu cabbiro walax kiimiko inteed, hal mole ee walax waxa uu lamid yahay 6.022 × 10²³ units walaxdaas (sida atoms, molecules, irons, electron, iyo photons). e.g. one mole of helium contains 4 grams.

heat of formation n. kul samays; kul intiisa la dhuuqay, ama iskudhis halkiis mole ee walax.

heat of ionization n. kulka aayanoobiska; kulka looga baahanyahay walax aayanoobiskeed oo ah hal mole.

heat of neutralization n. kulka dhexdhexaadinta; falgalka kul oo keena dhexdhexaadinta acid ama base barxan.

heat of reaction n. kulka falgalka; kulka la dhuuqay marka lagu jiro falgal kiimimo ee heerkul aan isbaddalin.

heat of solution n. kulka milanka; kulka la dhuuqay marka walax milanto.

heat of transformation n. kulka isbededlka; kulka la dhuuqay marka lagu jiro walax isbadalkeeda waji ee cadaadis iyo heerkul joogta.

heavy hydrogen n. haydarojiin culus; eeg deuterium.

heavy metal n. bir culus; curiyayzal xambaarsan cuf-isjiidad sare iyo culaab atomeed.

heavy water n. 1 biyo culus; iskudhis D2O oo ka kooban deuterium iyo oxygen. kale loogu yeeraa deuterium oxygen. 2 biyo ay ka buuxaan deuterium.

hemihydrate (,hemi’haay,dareyt) n. bar haydareyt; hydrate ka wadata (half mole of water) halkii mole ee iskudhisna (compound) qaabayn karo hydrate buuxa. -hemihydrated adj.

hydrate (,haay’dareyt) n. 1 chemistry iskdhis (compound) ka qaabaysmay midawga biyo iyo walax (substance) kale. 2 (inorganic chemistry) biyo (water).                                                                           -v. hydrated; hydrating 1 ku darid biyo ama curiye (element) wata biyo. 2 dharbin; ku darid dareere. 3 cabbid biyo. e.g. in hot weather, you need to hydrate your body properly. -hydration n.; -hydrator n.

heptane (‘hep,teyn) n. biyo laga dhexhelo petroleum ka oo wax lagu milo (isomeric alkanes C7H16).

heptose (‘hep,taws) n. mid kasta oo ka mid ah monosaccharides C7H14O7  oo xambaarsanyahay maalikiyuulkii todoba carbon oo atoms.

heterotopic (,hedhara’taapic) adj. ka samaysma ama ka dhaca meel aan caadi ahayn. e.g. Heterotopic liver transplantation.

heteroatomic atom n. atom kasta oo aan ahayn carbon ama hydrogen.

heterogenous (,hedha’raajanas) adj. eeg heterogeneous.

hexane (‘hek,seyn) n. dareere laga helo petroleum ka.

hexavalent (,heksa’veylanti) adj. lix-kaaftoonle ah (valence of six).

 

hexose (‘hek,saws) adj. sonkor; monosaccharide (sida glucose) oo maalikiyuulkii xambaarsanyahay lix carbon oo atoms.

 

homogeneous mixture n. iskujir isku kaan ah.

homogeneous catalyst n. kalkaaliye isku kaan ah; hab kalkaalin oo walxihii falgalka iyo iskudhiskii hal waji la iskugu keenay, inta badan waji dareere.

homogeneous reaction n. habka falgal isku kaan ah.

homologous series n. taxa homologous; tax iskudhisyo guud ahaan isku mid ah, se ku kala duwan kali ah, dhererka silsiladda carbon (carbon chain length).

homopolar (,hawma’pawlar) adj. 1 la xariira atoms isku cirif ah. 2 adeegsada ama dhala danab toos ah ayada oo aan la isticmaalin diinimo (commuter).

nonionic (naan,aayaanik) adj. aan lahayn ionic, siiba kiimikooyinka wax lagu nadiifiyo. e.g. Nonionic surfactants.

homopolar bond adj. dabar isku cirifle. eeg covalent bond.

hydrate (‘haydareyt) adj. cokan ah; iskudhis ka samaysan biyo iyo walxo kale.                                  -v. hydrated; hydrating cokanayn; biyayn; ku darid biyo; qoyn. -hydration n.; -hydrator n.

hydrated ion aayoon cokan; aayoon biyo ku milan.

hydrated oxide n. ogsaydh cokan; iskudhis oxide oo biyaysan.

hydride (‘haay,daraaydh) n. aayoon hydrogen; nooc kasta oo iskudhis kiimiko (chemical compound) oo hydrogen uga jirto curiye (element) kale. 

hydrofluoric acid (,haydaraw’faloorik ‘aasidh) n. iskudhis kiimiko oo xambaarsan fluorine, kana samaysan neef aan ur laahyn, ama uumi dareere. kale loogu yeeraa hydrogen fluoride.

active hydrogen n. haydarajiin firfircoon; hydrogen kaligeed jirta. kale loogu yeeraa atomic hydrogen.

hydrogenate (haay’daraaja,nayt) v. hydrogenated; hydrogenating ku darid hydrogen, siiba maalikiyuulka iskudhis noole oo aan dharagsanayn (unsaturated organic compound). -hydrogenation n.

hydrogenated oil n. saliid haydrarajiinaysan; hab warshaduhu ku daraan hydrogen dufanka dareeraha ah (liquid fat), sida saliidda kariska ee dhir laga soo tuujiyay (vegetable oil).

hydrogen atom n. atom curiye kiimiko oo hydrogen, kana kooban hal proton iyo hal electron.

electrostatic attraction n. isa soo jiidadka danabka negi oo ka dhexeeya protons iyo electrons.

hydrogen bond n. dabar haydarajiin; isa soo jiidashad ka dhexaysa hydrogens. -hydrogen bonding n.

hydrogen bromide n. neef daran oo aan lahayn midab, oo sameeysa hydrobromic acid marka ay biyo ku milmato, astaan HBr.

hydrogen chloride n. neef ur daran oo aan lahayn midab, oo sameeysa hydrocloric acid marka ay biyo ku milmato, astaan CHI.

hydrogen electrode n. qotin haydarajiin ah; qotin lagu cabbiro awoodda tabareed ee curiyayaasha kale.

hydrogen equivalent n. iskudhiganka haydarjiin; hydrogens ku dhaggan carbon atom markay isku kiimiko yihiin.

hydrogen fluoride neef daxalkeena ah oo aan lahayn midab, oo samaysa iskudhis neefo hydrofluoric acid marka ay biyo ku milmato, astaan HF.

hydrogen iodide n. neef acid ah oo aan lahayn midab, oo sameeysa hydriodic acid marka ay biyo ku milmato, astaan HI.

hydrogen ion n. bu’da atom-ka hydrogen oo ka goosatay electron kii wehlinayay.

hydrogen sulfide n. neef guban’og oo sun ah, leh ur ukun quruntay ah oo laga helo biyaha nadiifka ah: astaan H2S.

hydrolysis constant n. madoorsoome falgalbiyood; madoorsoome dheellitiran ee falgal hydrolysis.

hydronium ion n. aayoonka hydroniyam; maalikiiyuul biyood ku darmay hydrogen ion togan. e.g. H2O+H+ → H3O+ maxsuulka (the product) H3O+ ayaa ah hydronium ion.

hydrophile (‘hydrafaayl) adj. also hydrophil biya-jecel ah.

hydrophobe (‘haaydarfoob) n. biyo-diid; aan ku milmin biyaha.

hydrophobic colloid n. colloid biyo-uma-xiise; saxarro aan aad isku soo jidan markay biyo ku dhexjiraan.

hydrosol (‘haardara,saal) n. dareere qasbiyood ah. e.g. Hydrosol can be used room freshener. -hydrosolic adj.

hydrosulfuric acid n. eeg hydrogen sulfide.

hydroxide (haay’daraak,saaydh) n. 1 kaaftoon kaliyaale aayon taban leh OH-, kana kooban hal atom oo hydrogen ah iyo hal atom oo oxygen ah. 2 iskudhis aayoon oo hydroxide ah oo wehliya koox ama curiye.

hydroxyl ion n. eeg hydroxide sense 1.

hygroscopic (,haaygara’iskaapik) adj. sayaxnuug ah; qaata ama ceshada qoyaanka. e.g. Hygroscopic materials. -hygroscopicity n.

hypochlorite (,haaypa’kol,raayt) n. aayoon ka kooban chlorine iyo oxygen oo leh astaan kiimiko CIO-.

hypophosphite (haaybaw’faas,faayt) n. cusbo laga helay aayonka hypophosphorous acid oo leh base cusbaysan.

hypophosphoric acid (haaypaw’fasfoorik ‘aasidh) n. acid aan daganayn H4P2O6 oo wata afar hydrogen atoms oo la baddalikaro, inta badanna lagu helo qaab cusbooyin.

hypophosphorous acid (haaybaw’faasfaras ‘aasidh) n. iskudhis aan lahayn midab oo heerkul hoose ku milma biyaha, dareere sun ah (diaxane), iyo alkoloda

monobasic (,maana’beysik) adj. hal hydrogen atom kali ah leh oo la baddalikaro.

low-melting (law’meltin) adj. heerkul hoose ku milanta.

linkage (‘linkij) n. taxnaan; xariir; iskuxir ka dhexeeyo. e.g. there is genetic linkage.

dioxane (dhaay’aak,seyn) n. also dioxan dareere sun ah oo guban’og, xambaarsanna C4H8O2 oo wax lagu milo.

diether (,dhaay’iithar) n. iskudhis xambaarsan laba atom oo oxygen ah.

hyposulfite n. eeg sodium hyposulfite.

sodium hyposulfite (sawdhiyam,haaybaw’sal,faayt) n. eeg sodium thiosulfate.

sodium thiosulfate (sawdhiyam,thaaya’sal,feyt) n. iskudhis kiimiko oo lagu caddeeyo sawirrada. kale loogu yeeraa fixer, hypo.

thiosulfate (,thaay’sal,feyt) n. cusbada ku jirta basasha S2O32−.

hydrosulfuric acid n. eeg hydrogen sulfide.

hyposulfurous acid n. 1 thiosulfuric acid. 2 hydrosulfurous acid.

thiosulfuric acid n. acid H2S2O3 aan deganayn oo laga keenay sulfuric acid, ayada oo laga baddalay hal oxygen atom oo yeeshay qaab cusbo ama esters.

hydrosulfurous acid n. acid H2S2O4 aan deganayn oo kali ah looyaqaan milan biyood, lagun yareeyo sulfurous acid ama qaab cusbooyin.

imino (‘ima,naw) adj. la xariira ama xambaarsan NH group ama baddalkeeda NR united.

inactive gases n. neefaha wahsada. e.g. Gases that do not react with certain substances.

incomplete reaction falgal aan dhammayn; falgal ama hab u baahan shidaal qaar gubta kali ah.

organic base n. iskudhis aasaasi oo xambaarsan carbon.

alkaloid (aaka,loydh) n. mid kasta oo ka mid ah iskudhisyo xambaarsan carbon oo aan lahayn midab, sida morphine iyo caffeine oo xambaarsan nitrogen. -alkaloidal adj.

indole (‘in,dhawl) n. iskudhkis noole oo wata astaanta C 8H 7N.

induced reaction n. falgal saaqan; falgal kiimiko oo cadiga aad uga dhaqsabadan.

inductor (in’dhaktar) n. 1 saaqe; kaydiye; duub (a coil of wire) tamar ku kaydiya badad birlabeed (magnetic field). 2 ku darme; ku biire koox.

inert oxide n. ogsaydh wahsada; oxide aan samayn falgal kiimiko.

infinite dilution n. barax xad la’; xaalad milanku xambaarsanyahay mile ku filan oo uu san baddalmayn haddii mile lagu siidaro.

inorganic chemistry n. laan ka tirsan kimistariga oo gooni u eegta walxaha aan xambaarsanayn noole.

inorganic (,in,or’gaanik) n. 1 ka kooban wax aan ku jirin noole (dhir ama duunyo). 2 laan ka mid ah chemistry oo gooni u eegta walxaha aan noole ku jirin. -inorganically (ˌin,or’gaaniklii) adv.

inorganic compound n. iskudhis orgaanik ma ahe; walax aan xambaarsanayn carbon iyo oxygen.

inorganic matter n. maatarka orgaanik ma ahe; iskudhisyo kiimiko oo aan xambaarsanayn carbon.

insoluble salts n. cusbooyinka mamilme; iskudhisyo aan ku milimin biyaha.

inspissate (in’ispiseyt) v. inspissated; inspissating dhafaagid; dhafaagin; adkayn ama adkaatin, siiba uumibixid. -inspissation n. -inspissator n.

interionic attraction n. isjiidasho aayoonada; isa soo jiidad ka dhexeeya iskudhiyada ionics.

intermediate compound n. iskudhis dhexe; walax loo warshadeeyay cunis ama loo isticmaalay hab kiimiko si loogu baddalo walax kale.

iodate (‘aaya,dheyt) n. cusbo iodic acid, isukuna xiran saddex oxygen atoms iyo maalikiyuul formula ah IO3-.

iodoethane (aay,awdhaw) n. eeg ethyl iodide.

ethyl iodide n. dareere holca oo aan lahayn midab, ahna iskudhis kiimiko.

organic synthesis n. laan ka mid ah kimistariga oo gooni eegta samayska kiimikooyinka iyo dhisidda iskudhisyada noolaha.

organic chemistry n. laan ka mid ah kimistariga oo gooni u eegta carbon ka iyo iskudhiyada carbon oo laga helo waxyaabaha nool.

iodoform (aay’yawdha,foorm) n. sunta-dharka; iskudhis huri ah oo uumibixi’og oo leh ur adag oo joogta ah.

diiodomethane n. eeg methylene iodide.

methylene iodide n. iskudar kiimiko lehna formula CH3I oo ah khareere aan midab lahayn. kale loogu yeeraa diiodomethane.

ion activity n. firfircoonaanta aayon; milan kasta oo aayoono oo firfircoon.

ion antagonist n. iskasoohorjeedka aayoon.

ion complex n. aayoon murakab; aayoon dhexda ku leh bir iyo tiro kale oo maalikiyuullo ah.

ion concentration n. ribanaan aayoon.

ion hydrated n. aayoon cokan; aayoon biyo lagu milay.

ion hydronium n. maalikiyuul biyood oo wata aayoon hydrogen oo togane ah, keentayna isle’egtaan H2O+H+→H3O.

ionic (aay’aanik) adj. 1 la xariira, la mid ah ama xambaarsan aayoon. e.g. Ionic compounds. 2 ku salaysan ama u shaqeeya sidii aayoon.

ionic bond n. dabar aayoon; iskudhis kiimiko oo ka dhexeeya isa soo jiidasho walxo lid isku ah. e.g. The ionic bond between the two atoms was very strong.

ionic bonding n. dabrid ayooneed; qaab xariir kiimiko taas oo hal atom dhumiyo electrons kaaftoon (valence electrons) kana soo kororsado ayagii meel kale.

ionic charge n. saldanab aayooneed; togane ama tabane saldanab (charge) atom.

ionic compound n. iskudhis aayooneed; iskudhisyo ka samaysan ions kaas oo qaabeeya saxarro saldanabaysan (charged) markii atom kororsado ama dhumiyo electrons.

ionic concentration n. ribnaan aayooneed; xariirka ka dhexeeya ion kasta oo milanka ku jira, laguna muujiyo moles per liter.

oxidation-reduction (,aaksa’dayshan ri’dhakshan) n. (redox); marka falgale dhumiyo electrons inta lagu guda jiro falgalka, waxaa la yiraa oxidation. Marka falgale kororsado electrons inta lagu guda jiro falgalka, waxaa la yiraa reduction. e.g. Oxidation-reduction reactions are responsible for color changes in some leaves.

 

ionic crystal n. wiriqle aayooneed; iskudhis kiimiko oo qaab wiriqle ah.

ionic displacement n. barabixin aayooneed; nooc falgal kiimiko ee markii ion ama curiye (element) kabaxo iskudhis (compound).

ionic equations n. isle’eg aayooneed; isle’eg kiimiko oo muujiya aayoonada kali ah ee ka qaybgalaya falgalka kiimikaad.

ionic equilibrium n. dheellitiran aayooneed; dheellitiran ka dhex abuurma maalikiyuulada aan ahayn aayoon iyo kuwa aayoon ee ku jira milan gudbin tabardaran leh.

ionic lattice n. raso aayooneed; rasayn caadi ah ee aayoonada.

ionic migration n. hayaamid aayooneed; dhaqdhaqaaqa aayoonka oo ay keento beerta danabaysan.

ionic mobility n. dhaqdhaqaaq aayooneed; xawliga kala duwan oo ay sameeyaan aayoonada neef ay samayso beer danab.

 

ionic product n. maxsuul aayooneede; xariirka ka dhexeeya tirada ka qaybgalaysa falgal, ama qaabaynaysa iskudhis, siiba isbarbardhigga tirooyinka oo dhan.

ionic radius n. gacan aayooneed; fogaanta u dhaxaysa bu’da aayoonka iyo qobka sare ee aayoonka.

ionic reaction n. falgal aayooneed; falgalka aayoonda taban iyo togan oo qaabeeya iskudhis ay ku milmaan.

ionic saturation n. dheregsanaan aayooneed; xambaarsan tirade ugu badan ee milme milay milan.

ionic strength n. quwad aayooneed; cabbirka ribanaanta (concentration) aayoonada ku jira milan.

ionic substitution n. aayoonnada wax baddalaya isku saldanab (charge) ayay yihiin kuwa ay baddalayaan. e.g. Fe2+ iyo Mg2+ way isbaddali karaan.

ionic theory n. aragtida aayooneed; aragti oranaysa magudbiyada milan waa aayoonis, kuwaas oo xambaarsan qaab isku mid ah oo la yiraa raso wiriqle (crystal lattice).

ionic valence n. kaaftoon aayooneed; eeg electrovalence.

ionization (,aayana’zayshan) n., pl. ionizations  aayoonaysan; hab atom/molecule ay u baahanyihiin saldanab togan/taban (positive/negative charge) ayaga oo electrons  dhuminya ama kororsanaya. e.g. ionization occurs when substances split up into ions.

ionization coefficient n. weheliyayaasha aayooneed; tirade electrons ee ay samaysay jidka xarriiq dheer ee jihada bed (direction of field).

 

ionization constant n. madoorsoomaha aayoonaynta; madoorsoome (constant) ku xiran dheellitiranka ka dhexeeya aayoonnada iyo maalikiyuullada ee milanku aanu aayoonayn. Astaan K. kale loogu yeeraa dissociation constant.

ionization, degree of n. also degree of ionization darajada aayoonaynta; hab matalaya acid ka xoogiisa.

ionization temperature n. heerkulka aayoonayn;

tamarta ama kulka looga baahanyahay in uu birta ka saaro electrons si uu u qaabeeyo togane bir (metal cation).

ionize (‘aaya,naayz) v. ionized; ionizing 1 kulli ama qaar u badalid aayoon (ion). 2 noqotin aayoon. -ionizable adj.; -ionizer n.

electrophoresis (e,lektarafa’riisas) n. hab lagu kala sooco DNA, RNA ama maalikiyuullada protein kooda ayada oo lagu saleeyay qiyaastooda. -electrophorese v.; -electrophoretic adj.; -electrophorectically adv.

nucleic acid (nuu’kliyik aaysidh) n. iskudhis kiimiko oo caadi u yimaada keenana xogta kowaad ee unugga maalikiyuulka ka koobanyahay.

 

ionophoresis (aay,aanafa’reysas) n., pl. ionophoreses aayoon guuris, siiba dhaqaaqa aayoonno yar-yar; electrophoresis. -iontophoretic adj.

irreversible reaction n. falgal ma-gadisme; falagale wuu noqdaa maxsuul, laakin maxsuul dib looguma celinkaro falgale.

isobutane (,aaysaw’biyuu,teyn) n. iskudhis kiimiko oo leh naanays (formula) HC(CH3)3  oo aan lahayn ur iyo midab toona, loona adeegto shidaal ahaan.

isomer (‘aaysamar) n. iskunaanays; iskudhisyo leh naanays (formula) maalikiyuullo isku mid ah, laakiin ku kala duwan qaabdhiskooda.

ketene (‘kii,tiin) n. neef sun ah oo aan lahayn midab, naanays (formula) C2H2O.

kindling temperature n. also kindling point heerkul shide. eeg ignition temperature.

fire point n. also combustion point heerkulka ugu hooseeya ee walax holacda ay sii wadi karato gubasho shan ilbiriqsi marka dab caadi ah oo furan lagu shido. Barbardhig ignition temperature.

kinetic theory n. aragti socod; walax kasta waxay ka koobantahay saxarro yar-yar oo meelo u dhaxeeyaan, kuna jira dhaqdhaqaaq kala duwan.

Kipp’s apparatus n. saabaanka Kipp’s qalab yar oo lagu diyaariyo mugag (valuems) yar-yar ee neefo (gases).

k-shell n. heertamarta-k; gudaha hoose ee qobka electrons oo ku wareegsan bu’da qurubka (atom), samaysana tamar heerkeeda ugu hoosaysa ee electrons-ka. Barbardhig L-shell, M-shell.

L-shell n. lakabka labaad ee gudaha hoose ee qobka electrons oo ku wareegsan bu’da qurubka (atom). Barbardhig K-shell, M-shell.  

M-shell n. lakabka saddexaad ee gudaha hoose ee qobka electrons oo ku wareegsan bu’da qurubka (atom). Barbardhig K-shell, L-shell.

laboratory test n. also lab testing hubsashada shaybaar; baaris cilmiyasan oo lugu sameeyo shaybaarka.

miscible (‘misabal) adj. milmikara; qasamikara. e.g. Water is miscible in all proportions. -miscibility n.

lactic acid n. also milk acid organic acid leh astaanta C3H6O3.

lox (ˈlaakis) n. liquid oxygen.

liquid phase n. waji hoor; wajiga dareere, xoogga maalikikuullada ka tabar daranyarihiin kan adkaha.

liquid state n. waji hoor; wajiga dareere, saxarro aan aad iskugu dhaganayn markii loo eego adke.

lithium bromide n. abbr. LBr iskudhis kiimiko oo ka kooban lithium iyo bromine.

antimanic (,aanti’maanik) adj. ka hortaga; celiya ama horjoosada, cudur-maskaxeed keena karbo, kacdoon, iyo xiiso (mania), siiba bipolar disorder.

lithium chloride n. cusbo (LiCl) qoyaandhuuq ah oo loo isticmaalo warshadaynta, wiriqda alxamidda biraha lithium iyo hab biyood xakameeya hoorka qaboojiyaha (air condition).

lithium fluoride n. dhagax cusbo (LiF) wiriqda oo laga jaro dhagaxda (prisms) iyo marmarka.

lux (‘lakis) n., pl. lux or luxes lux (astaan lx) haleeg lagu cabbiro iftiinka oo halkii meter ay ifiso hal shumac ama la mid ah halkii luman per square meter (lm/m2).

illuminance (iluuminantis) n. iftiin intiisa meel la cayiman ku dhacda. e.g. We measured the illuminance of light.

luminance (‘luumanantis) n. 1 iftiimid; tayada ama xaaladda iftiinka. 2 meel cayiman iftiin inta ay haysato cabbirkii.

luminous energy n. tamar ifineed; tamarta loo baddalay kaah muuqda (visible radiation).

macroanalysis (‘maakrawa’naalasas) n., pl. macroanalyses saafid weyn; baaris (tayo ama tiro) oo qiyaasta la eegayo ay ku xirantahay inta grams. Barbardhig microanalysis.

microanalysis (maaykrawa’naalasas) n. baaris kiimiko oo yar una baahan xaalad khaas ah oo aad xasaasi u ah ama adeegsiga qalab yar.                       -microanalyst n.; -microanalytical adj.

macromolecule (,maakraw’maalikiyuul) n. maalikiyuul weyne (protein ama rubber).                  -macromolecular (ˌmaakrawma’lekilar) adj.

magnesia (maag’niisha) n. budo cad oo aad u milanta, loona adeegto walxaha u adkaysta kulka. Barbardhig milk of magnesia. -magnesian (maag’niishan) adj.

serpentinite (‘sarpan,tii,naayt) n. dhagax leh midabo kala duwan (dhagax-maseed).

magnesite (‘maag,saayt) n. macdanta loo yaqaan magnesium carbonate (MgCO3).

eutrophic (yuu’tarawfik) adj. 1 hodan ka ah nafaqo iyo macdan oo aad loogu koro (eutrophication). 2 medicine keenta nafaqo; waxtar leh. Barbardhig mesotrophic, oligotrophic. -eutrophy (ˈyuutrafii) n.

oligotrophic (‘aaligaw,tarawfik) adj. 1 physiology nafaqadu ku yartahay. 2 geography meel dhirta nafaqadeedu (plant nutrients) ku yartahay, siiba nitrogen ama phosphorus.

stratification (,istaraatafa’keyshan) n. qaybqaybis; kooxayn; qoloqolayn. e.g. social stratification.

stratify (‘istaraadhafaay) v. stratified; stratifying 1 rasayn; lakabayn; isasaarsaarid. 2 qaybin; qolayn; dabaqadayn, siiba bulsho. e.g. Some bad politicians stratified our communities by tribes. 3 qaybin heer-heer. 4 la qaybqaybshay.  

mesotrophic (,meeza’tarawfik) n. nafaqo dhexdhexaad ah oo milantay leh. e.g. Mesotrophic lakes play a crucial role in water purification. Barbardhig eutrophic, oligotrophic.

eutrophication (yuu,tarawfa’keyshan) n. hab biyo fariisi macdan badan ku milanto oo geedo-biyood ka soo baxaan oo marisa (gurisa) oxygen tii milantay.

 magnesium ammonium phosphate n. phosphate ayna ku jirin wax noole, taas oo ah cusbada ammonium magnesium ee phosphoric acid, loona adeegto nafaqeeye (fertilizer).

magnesium bicarbonate n. cusbo ah carbonic acid oo xambaarsan ion Mg(HCO3)2.

magnesium carbonate n. carbonate ah magnesium; cusbo cad oo wiriqda MgCO3 oo dabeeciyan nuurad ahaan ugu samaysmata.

dolomite (‘dawla,maayt) n. 1 macadanta CaMg(CO3)2 oo ka kooban calcium magnesium carbonate laguna helo wiriqnaan nuurad ahaan u goglan dhul baaxad weyn. 2 magnesium carbonate oo nuurad ahaan ama dhagaxa marmarka uga buuxo. -dolomitic (ˌdhawla’midhik) adj.

magnesium chloride n. cusbo kharaar oo milanta MgCl2 loona adeegto soo saarka magnesium metal.

sellaite (‘sela,aayt) n., pl. sellaites macdanta MgF2 oo ka kooban macdantana magnesium fluoride noqdanna dhagax afargees wirqa ah.

magnesium fluoride n. cusbo cad MgF2 oo wiriqda, muraayad ahaanna wax looga arkikaro.

magnesium hydroxide n. iskudhis Mg(OH)2, inta badan loo adeegto calool bixis (laxative) iyo aashita caloosha (gastric acid).

infusible (,in’fiyuuzabal) adj. aan milmin; adagtahay in la milo. e.g. The metal was infusible and had a high melting point. -infusibility (ˌin,fiyuza’bilatii) n.; -infusibleness (ˌin’fiyuzabalnas) n.

magnesium oxide n. iskudhis MgO cad oo aan milmin, loona adeegto sibirka, kabista tarrarka, nafaqeeye (fertilizer), rabarka warshadaha, iyo daawooyin.  

magnesium peroxide n. budo cad MgO2 oo aan lahayn dhadhan, kuna milmin biyaha, loona adeegto warankiilo (bleaching) ahaan, dishana jeermiska.

magnesium silicate n. iskudhis magnesium oxide and silicon Mg2Si3O8·nH2O, ahna budo cad oo loo isticmaalo daawooyinka.

magnesium sulfate n. cusbo cad MgSO4 oo loo isticmaalo daawooyinka iyo sancooyinka (industry).

magnetic moment n. also magnetic dipole moment maroojis birlabeed; cabbirka janjeerka ashyaadu ugu taxmaan beer danab.

quantize (‘kuwaan,taayz) v. quantized; quantizing siiqaybqaybin tamar (energy), siiba qaybo yar-yar oo la cabbirikaro. e.g. It is important to quantize the market data. -quantization (ˌkuwaanta’zeyshan) n.; -quantizer (ˈkuwaan,taazar) n.

magnetic quantum number n. tiro kuwaantam birlabeed; tiro tilmaanta tirada iyo jihadeeda, waxayna ku xirantahay xagasha meeraysiga ee beerta danabeed.

magnetic susceptibility n. nuglaan birlabeed; saamiga danabaynta walax xariirka ay la leedahay xoogga danabaynta.

malic acid n. wirqe dicarboxylic acid C4H6O5.

plasticize (palaasta,saayz) v. plasticized; plasticizing caagayn; ka dhigid wax la qaabaynkaro. e.g. to plasticize a toy. -plasticization (ˌpalaastasa’zeyshan) n.

plasticizer (‘palaasta,saayzar) n. walax (mile) lagu daro xabkaha (rubbers and resins)wax laga sameeyo, si ay uga dhigaan wax la qaabaynkaro.

malonic acid n. budo acad oo wiriqda, dicarboxylic acid CH2(COOH)2.

maltose (‘mool,taws) n. also loo yaqaan maltobiose ama malt sugar; laba maalikiyuule oo sonkor khamiirsami karata ah C12H22O11 ganacuna (pancreas) sameeyo.

dextrorotatory (,dhekistaraw’rawdha,torii) adj. midigta u jeesta ama dhinaca saacadda (clockwise). Barbardhig levorotatory.

levorotatory (,liiva’rawdha,torii) adj. bidixda u jeesta ama lidka saacadda (counter clockwise). Barbardhig dextrorotatory.

manganese carbonate n. chemistry iskudhis kiimiko oo leh astaan kiimiko MnCO3 ahna macdan dabeeciyan ah.

manganese chloride n. eeg manganous chloride.

manganese dioxide n. chemistry manganiis laba ogsaaydh; iskudhis kiimiko MnO2 oo madaw aan milmin ah, loona isticmaalo oxidizing agent, batariyada qallalan (dry cells), samaynta quraaradaha, iyo weelasha dhoobada (ceramics).

manganese heptoxide n. ogsaaydh; iskudhis kiimiko oo leh astaanta kiimiko (formula) Mn2O7, ahna dareere saliid ah oo uumibaxa, ahna gacaar madaw. kale loogu yeeraa manganese(VII) oxide.

law of mass action n. xeer fal cuf; dhaqsaha falgalka kiimiko uu saami qumman ula yahay ribanaanta (concentrations) maalikiyuulka (molecule) sida uu ula falgalo walxaha.

mass concentration n. ribnaan cuf; cabbirka milmaha ee grams per 1 liter ama 1 milliliter ee milanka.

mass defect n. iin cuf; farqiqa u dhexeeya cufka la saadaaliyay iyo cufka dhabta ah ee bu’da atom ka. Barbardhig binding energy, packing fraction.

packing fraction n. cabbirka kororka ama naaqiska cufka guud ee xayn nucleons ah markii la isku keeno si ay u qaabeeyaan atomic nucleus.

nucleon (‘nuukli,yaan) n. isku darka proton iyo neutron = (nucleons), wada sameeyana atomic nucleons. -nucleonic (ˌnukli’yaanik) adj.

mass energy n. tamar cuf; haddii walax (body) dayso tamar (energy) baddalka taas maxsuulkeeda, cufka walaxda inteeda kale waa yaraanayaa.

mass-energy equation n. isle’egta iswaydaarsiga tamarta (energy) iyo cufka (mass), E=MC2 meesha E ay tahay tamarta (energy), M ay tahay cuf (mass) grams, C ay tahay keynaan (velocity) ee light centimeter per second. kale loogu yeeraa Einstein equation ama conservation of energy.

conservation of energy n. tamar la abuurikaro lamana baabi’inkaro – kali ahaan qaab tamar baa qaab kale loogu baddalikaraa.

mass spectrometer n. jeegaanbeege cuf; hab lagu caddeeyo walax dhismaheeda kiimiko, ayada oo la kala saarayo aayoonada neefaha (gaseous) cufnaanta kala duwanaantooda iyo saldanbkooda (charge). -mass spectrometric adj.; -mass spectrometer n.

univalent (,yuuni’veylanti) adj. hal kaaftoonle ah: monovalent. -univalent n.

Maxwellian distribution n. also Maxwell distribution ama Maxwell-Boltzmann distribution filiqsanaanta keynaanka; xawaaraha neef (gas) samaynayo ee heerkul sheegan.

mean free path n. marin xor ah; celceliska marin bannaan; fagaanta celceliska shay ku dhaqaaqidoono ku dhaca labadhexyada.

melting point curve n. xoodka barta dhalaalka; xoodka u taagan dhexdhexaadka dheelitiran ee adke iyo dareere.

methane (,me’thayn) n. neef gubata oo aan ur iyo midab toona lahayn, lehna astaan kiimiko ee hydrocarbon CH4 oo ah walxo noole oo qurmay.

mercury thiocyanate n. chemistry iskudhis mercury (mercuric compound) Hg (SCN)2 oo wirqa sunna ah, loona adeegto baaruudda cirka loo tuuro (fireworks); looguna yeero maskii Fircoon (Pharaoh's serpent).

mercurous chloride n. eeg calomel.

mercury cathode n. chemistry qotin tabane markurii.

methyl (‘methal) n. chemistry waxaa laga keenay methane, watana hal carbon atom oo ku dhaggan saddex hydrogen atoms, lehna astaan kiimiko CH3; (methane caadiga ah CH4). -methylic (ma’thilik) adj.

methyl acetate n. chemistry dareere carfoon oo holci’og (flammable), lehna astaan kiimiko C3H6O2, wax mila, rinjigana dhaqa (paint remover).

methylsulfate (methal’sal,feyt) n. eeg hexocyclium methylsulfate.

modulus (‘maajalas) n., pl. moduli 1 qiime sugan; magac kale oo loo adeegto baaqi (reminder). e.g. 13 mod 4 = 1. 2 xagga saacadda, the modulus is 12, macnahoodu waa after 12.

mol n. also mole chemistry 1 halbeegga asaasiga ah ee cabbirka walax saafi ah oo loo qeexo in ay tahay 6.02214076 x 1023 cuf (mass) aan la sii qaybinkarin (sida atoms ama molecules) ee walaxdaas; formula: mole = mass / molecular weight. 2 abbreviations: molecular; molecule.

solute (‘saal,yuut) n. milme; qasme; mile (solvent) + milme (solute) = milan (solution). e.g. Salt and water are two of the most common examples of solutes in your daily lives.

molal (‘mawlal) adj. la xiriira ama xambaarsan cuf (mass) la-mile (solute) ee 1,000 grams ee mile (solvent). -molality (maw’laalatii) n.

molal solution n. chemistry milan molal; 1 molal oo milan (solution) waa hal mole oo walax lagu milay (dissolved) 1 kg oo mile ah (solvent); tusaale: haddii aan biyo ku milayno (dissolving water) methanol, markaas biyuhu waa mile (solute), methanol kuna waa mile (solvent). e.g. molar mass of water is 18.02 grams per mole.

molecular concentration n. chemistry ribnaan maalikiyuuleed; habka lagu caddeeyo la-mile inta uu ribnaan (concentration) milan (solution) uga jiro per liter; tusaael: Molar Concentration = Amount in Moles / Volume of Solution (M = mol/L).

structural formula n. chemistry waxay muujisaa atomada (atoms) iyo maalikiyuulada qaabka ay iskugu dhagganyihiin.

empirical formula n. chemistry saamiga (ratio) atomyada (atoms) ku jira iskudhis (compound); tusaale: haddii iskudhis ku jirto 4 carbon iyo 8 hydrogen, saamigu (ratio) waa, 4 carbon/8 hydrogen = 4/8 = ¼ = (CH2). xasuuso C=C1.

molecular formula n. chemistry naanays maalikiyuuleed; hawraar (expression) qeexda curiye kasta tirada atomyo (atoms) ee uga jirta hal iskudhis maalikiyuul (one molecule of a compound); tusaale:

haddii hal maalikiyuul ku jirto 4 carbon iyo 8 hydrogen, waa C4H8.

molecular orbital n. chemistry meeris maalikiyuuleed; fansaarka (wave function) ee meeraysiga electron ka maalikiyuulkiisa.

molecular spectrum n. chemistry jeegaan maalikiyuuleed; fal ka dhexdhaca maalikiyuulada (molecules) iyo kaah birlabdanabeed (electromagnetic radiation); taas oo ah qaab kaah (radiation) oo danabka iyo birlabtu ku la duwanyihiin, kaas oo electromagnetic radiation yahay if la arkikaro (visible light).

monochromatic radiation n. chemistry kaah hirkaliyaale; kaahyo leh hal hir ama rakaad (frequency) oo isle’ekaada.
