free radical n. chemistry maalikiyuul wareegga sare (outer shell) ku wata hal ama ka badan electron aan lammaanayn (unpaired electron).

nitric oxide n. chemistry ma degana oo waxa uu wataa electron aan lammaanay (free radical); maalikiiyuulku electron ayuu helikaraa ama dhuminkaraa si u qaabeeyo ions NO- ama NO+.

binary compound n. walax kiimiko oo ka samaysan laba curiye oo kala duwan kali ah.

electronegativity (i,lektaraw’negativ) adj. awood soo jiidasho ee electronics leh. -electronegativity (i,lektaraw,nega’tividhii) n.

nitride (ˈnay,taraaydh) n. chemistry nooc kasta oo iskudhisyo nitrogen ay isku dhagaan curiyayaal la mid ah ama kuwo awood soo jiidasho (electronegativity) hoose eh.                                      -v., nitrided; nitriding adkayn, sida bir ayada oo dusha looga shubo nitrogen.

nitr- comb. form also nitro- nitride; nitrobenzene kaaftoon kalyaale ah (monovalent).

nitrobenzene (naytrawpenziin) n. chemistry saliid hurdi ah oo sun ah lehna astaan kiimiko C6H5NO2.

nitrobenzoic acid n. chemistry iskudhis orgaanik ah lehna astaan kiimiko C6H4(NO2)CO2H, waana adke hurdi (yellow) ah.

nitroethane n. chemistry iskudhis ograanika ha lehna astaan kiimiko C2H5NO2, dareere saliid ah oo aan lahayn midab, lehna caraf khudaareed.

nitrogen cycle n. chemistry meerto nitrogen; habka biogeochemical oo baddala nitrogen wahsan (nitrogen inert) oo ku jirta hawada sare (atmosphere) si looga dhigo mid faa’iido u leh noolaha.

 

biogeochemical (,baayaw,jiiya’keemikal) n.

la xariira qaybsanka iyo wareegga curiyayaasha kiimiko iyo iskudhisyada qaybaha ka dhexeeya noolaha iyo manoolaha taas oo noloshooda midba midka kale ku xirantahay in uu noolaado. -biogeochemistry (ˌbaayaw,jiya’kemastarii) n.

nitrogen dioxide n. chemistry naytrojiin laba ogsaaydh; neef sun ah oo casaan-bunniyeed ah NO2 ahna ogsiydheeye (oxidizing agent) xooggan, gubashana sameeya oo hawadana qiic sun (smog) ah u dira.

nitronaphthalene n. chemistry laba wirqe oo hurdi ah midkood lehna iskudhis kiimikooyin ee astaan kiimiko C10H7NO2.

phenol (ˈfii,nawl) n. also carbolic acid chemistry wirqe sun ah iskudhis kiimiko acidic C6H5OH oo laga helo dhuxusha (coal tar) iyo qoryaha (wood) la shito, dheecaankana lagu barxo biyo (dilute solution) oo nadaafad ahaan jeermiska loogu dilo (disinfectant).

hydroxyl (haay’daraksal) n. chemistry koox iskudhisyo (compounds) yaryar ah oo la isku dhaho hydroxyl group, kana kooban hydrogen iyo oxygen atoms; waxaa ka mid ah maalikiyuulada alcohol oo xambaarsan hydroxyl group. -hydroxylic (ˌhaay,daraak’silik) adj.

nitrophenol n. chemistry iskudhis kiimiko O2NC6H4OH oo ah hurdi (yellow) wirqe inta badan loo isticmaalo waxyaalaha ay ku jiraan maalikiyuulada noole (organic synthesis). kale loogu yeeraa ortho-nitrophenol.

 

nitros- comb. form or nitroso- xambaarsan group NO. e.g. nitrosamine.

nitrosamine (naay’tarawsa,miin) n. chemistry noocyo badan oo ay ka mid yihiin iskudhisyada organic (organic compounds) oo koox la ah NNO qaarkoodna ay keenaan kaankaro (cancer).

nitroso group n. chemistry kooxda nitrotoluene; mid kasta oo ah bahda iskudhisyada orgaanik (organic compounds) oo leh dhismayaal maalikiyuul ay ku dhagganyihiin atomada carbon iyo nitrogen.

aqueous (‘eekwiyas) adj. 1 la xariira ama u eg biyo. 2 laga sameeyay biyo. e.g. Aqueous solutions. 3 Medical la xariira biyaha isha (aqueous humor).

nonelectrolyte (,naana’lektara,laayt) n. chemistry ma-gudbiye milme; iskudhis (compound) aan ku gudbin danab (electric current) milan biyood (aqueous solution) ama kulayl ku milid (molten state).

nonpolar (,naan’pawlar) adj. not polar.

 

nonpolar bond n. chemistry dabar cirif laawe; dabar u dhexeeya laba atoms oo hydrogen, waayo si isle’eg ayay u wadaagaan electrons ka.

nonradioactive (,naan,reedyaw’aaktiv) adj. chemistry ma-kaahfale; aan lahayn ama aan samayn khatar iyo kaah xooggan oo ka yimaada marka qurubyo (atoms) kala jabaan. e.g. I was given an injection of a nonradioactive substance.

nonyl alcohol n. chemistry mid kasta oo ka mid ah dhawr alcohols C9H19OH oo laga tuujiyay nonanes (ka yimid petroleum).

nonane (nawnayn) n., pl. nonanes chemistry mid kata oo ka mid ah dareerayaal shidaal paraffin (kerosene) hydrocarbons C9H20.

normal boiling point n. chemistry barta karka caadiga ah; heerkulka dareeruhu ku karkaro (99.61o C ama 211.3o F).

Elysium (i’lishiyam) n., pl. Elysiums ama Elysia 1 Ahlu Janno. 2 Janno.

normal pressure n. chemistry cadaadis caadi ah.

normal valence n. chemistry kaaftoon caadi ah; tirada qotomada (bonds) ee curiye (element) ee samaysmata, sida kaaftoon (valence) carbon waa afar, nitrogen waa saddex, iyo oxygen oo ah labo.

nuclear charge n. chemistry saldanab bu’eed; saldanab togan oo ku jira bu’da qurubka (nucleus of an atom), kaas oo la tiro ah protons bu’da.

nuclear chemistry n. chemistry kimistari bu’eed; eeg radiochemistry.

radiochemistry (ˌreydhiyaw’kemastarii) n. chemistry laan ka mid ah chemistry oo gooni u eegta walxaha radioactive (radioactive substances) ah iyo barashada dib-u-raacooda. kale loogu yeeraa nuclear chemistry. -radiochemical (ˌreydhiyaw’kemikal) adj.; -radiochemically (ˌreydhiyaw’kemiklii) adv.; -radiochemist (ˌreydhiyaw’kemisti)

nuclear reaction n. physics falgal bu’eed; hab bu’da qurub (nucleus of an atom) la kala dhanbalay ama agu darma bu’da qurub (atom) kale.

nuclear size n. jimri bu’eed; waa r = RoA1/3 meesha r tahay gacanka bu’da (radius of nucleus) A tahay tirada cufka qurubka (mass no. of atom) iyo R0 tahay madoorsoome qaymihiisu yahay (constant whose value is 1.5×10-13cm ama 1.5×10-15m). gacanku waa 10-14; waxaan lagu cabbiray Fermiunits.

fermi (‘feermii) n. halbeeg hore ee dherer oo caalami (SI unit) lana mid ah 10−15 meters: femtometer.

femtometer (‘feemta,miidhar) n. halbeeg dherer oo la mid ah 10−15 meters: one quadrillionth of a meter.

nuclear structure n. chemistry dhismaha bu’eed; qurub bu’diis (atomic nucleus) waxa uu ka koobanyahay protons iyo neutrons, wadajirna waxaa la isku yiraa nucleons.

octadecane (ˌaakta’de,keyn) n. chemistry mid kasta oo ka mid ah iskudhisyo iskunooc ah ee isomeric hydrocarbons C18H38 ee bahda paraffin series; siiba hydrocarbon CH3(CH2)16CH3.

octavalent (,aakata’veylan) adj. chemistry siddeed kaaftoonle; siddeed kaaftoon (valence) leh.

octet (‘aaktet) n. 1 koox siddeed ah. 2 marka wareegga sare ee atom buuxdado siddeed electrons.

octyl (‘aaktal) n. chemistry alkyl radical C8H17 laga soo qaatay octane; sida: 1 radical caadi ah CH3(CH2)6CH2−. 2 radical CH3(CH2)3CH(C2H5) CH2− lehna faracyo; 2-ethyl-hexyl.

octyl alcohol n. chemistry mid kasta oo ah bahda alcohols C8H17OH oo laga keenay octanes.

oleic acid (aw’liyik ‘aasad) n. chemistry mid kasta oo ah bahda alcohols C8H17OH oo laga keenay octanes.

oleum (‘awliyam) n., pl. olea chemistry (Latin oleum, meaning oil).

optical activity n. chemistry hawl bikaaceed; awoodda walax kiimiko (chemical substance) ay fallaaro iftiin ugu dalfiso midig ama bidix

optical isomerism n. chemistry isku naanaysnimada bikaaceed; inta badan waxay dhacdaa walxo maalikiyuullo isku mid iyo isku qaab formula ah, laakiin midba mid ma dul saarmikaro (cannot be superimposed).

optically negative n. bikaaco ahaan taban; haddii fallaarta ε (ε ray) ay gaabiso, macdantu waa bikaaco togan (optically positive); haddii ay dheeraysana bikaaco taban (optically positive).

uniaxial (ˌyuunii’aaksiyal) n. 1 hal dhidible ah (one axis). 2 la xariira hal dhidible; aan lahayn firraayo.

optical path n. physics marin bikaaceed; jidka fallaarta iftiin marto habka optical (optical system).

optical rotation n. physics wareeg bikaaceed; xagasha sallax (plane) oo uu dhexmaray (traverse) iftiinku lakabyo dareere markii la wareejiyayna dalfiyay.

optical spectrum n. physics jeegaan bikaaceed; fogaan baac-hireed (wavelength) ee birlabdanabeed (electromagnetic) oo indhaha lagu arkikaro.

orbital (‘oorbadhal) adj. physics meere ah; jid goobeed (circular) ama ukumeed (elliptical) uu shay ku wareego shay kale.

order of a reaction n. chemistry horsiimo falgal;

tirada la xariirta dhaqsaha falgalka kiimiko (chemical reaction) iyo walxaha falgalaya ribanaantooda, wadarta jibbaarada oo dhan ee tibxaha muujinaya ribanaanta maalikiyuulada ama atoms ka muujinaya dhaqsaha falgalka (rate of reaction). Barbardhig first-order reaction, second-order reaction, third-order reaction, zero-order reaction.

organic acid n. iskudhis noole oo wata walxo acidic ku jirto.

oscilloscope (aa’sila,iskawp) walhad-tuse;

qalab muujiya xariiqo danabeed dira baaq (signal) isla baddalana goorta. kale loogu yeeraa cathode-ray oscilloscope. -oscilloscopic (aa,sila’iskaapik) adj.

 

osmium tetroxide (ˈaazmiyam te’taraak,saaydh) n. iskudhis kiimiko oo uumi sun daran ah, astaan kiimiko OsO4.

oxalic acid (,aak’saalik aasidh) n. sun acid aad u xoogan ah, lehna astaanta (COOH)2 or H2C2O4 oo laga helo dhirta qaarkeed, loona isticmaalo warankiilo ama waxyaalaha wax lagu nadiifiyo.

oxamide (aaksa’maaydh) n. iskudhis orgaanik oo ah wirqe aad u milma, lehna astaan kiimiko (CONH 2) 2.

oxidation state n. waji ogsidhiyan; tirooyin togane ama tabane saldanab (charge) ah una diyaarsan atom ama curiye suuragalnimada oxidation.

ozonize (‘aw,zaw,naayz) v. ozonized; ozonizing oxygen u badalid ozone. -ozoniztion (ˌaw,zawna’zeyshan) n.; -ozonizer (ˈaw,zaw,naayzar) n.

 

paired electron n. elektaron lammaan; laba electrons oo ku wada jira isku maalikiyuul, laakiin lid u kala wareega.

palladium chloride n. iskudhis kiimiko oo loo adeegto kalkaaliye (catalyst).

 

partial valence n. chemistry kaaftoon qaybeed; curiyayaasha (elements) kooxaha kale kaaftoonkoodu qaar bay buuxiyaan wareegga, weyna kororsadaan ama dhumiyaan electrons si ay u buuxiyaan.

Pauli exclusion principle n. eeg exclusion principle. kale loogu yeeraa Pauli principle.

pentane (‘peen,teyn) n. chemistry mid kasta oo ka mid ah saddexda isomeric alkanes C5H12 oo laga helo batrool (petroleum).

polystyrene (,paalii’istaay,riin) n. adke ama abur (thermoplastic) ah, kuna fiican dahaaridda danabka.

thermoplastic (ˌtharma’palaastik) adj. caag (plastic) jilca markii la kululeeyo, dibna u adkaada marka uu qaboobo. Barbardhig thermosetting. -thermoplastic n.; -thermoplasticity (ˌtharma,palaa’stisatii) n.

thermosetting (‘thermaw,sedhing) adj. joogto u adkaada kadib markii la kululeeyay, siiba caag (plastic). Barbardhig thermoplastic.

pentavalent (,penta’vaylanti) adj. chemistry shan kaaftoonle (atoms having a valence of five).

pentene (‘peen,tiin) n. chemistry laba midkooda  amylenes oo laga helo gasoline. 

amylene (‘emi,liin) n. chemistry dareere aan lahayn midab oo uumibix’og, kana kooban iskudaryo isomers oo hydrocarbon ah, astaan kiimiko  C5H10.

amylene hydrate n. eeg tertiary amyl alcohol (inta badan pharmacy ayaa istacmaala).

tertiary amyl alcohol n. aalkahol saafi ah oo ur adag, aan lahaynna midab, CH3CH2C(OH)(CH3)2. kale loogu yeeraa amylene hydrate.

amylene hydrate n. eeg tertiary amyl alcohol.

pentose (‘pen,taws) n. chemistry monosaccharide C5H10O5 (sida ribose) oo maalikiyuulku (molecule) wata shan carbon atoms.

ribose (‘raaybaws) n. chemistry sonkor sahlan (simple sugar) iyo carbohydrate oo leh formula maalikiyuuleed (molecular formula) C5H10O5.

pentoxide (pent’aak,saaydh) n. chemistry shan ogsaydh; oxide maalikiyuul (molecule) xambaarsanyahay shan atoms oo oxygen ah, sida phosphorus pentoxide, P2O5.

pentyl (‘pental) n. chemistry five-carbon alkyl group astaan kiimiko C5H11.

peptize (‘pep,taayz) v. peptized; peptizing ku firdhin; ku dhexdaadin; keenid dhexdhexaad colloidal solution. -peptization (ˌpepta’zeyshan) n.; -peptizer (ˈpep,taayzar) n.

 

perchlorate (,par’kaloo,reyt) n. chemistry iskudhis kiimiko oo xambaarsan perchlorate ion, ClO4−.

perfect gas n. chemistry neef qumman; eeg ideal gas.

ideal gas n. chemistry neef maalikiyuullo aysan ka dhexayn isjiidasho (attract) ama kala carar (repel).

periodic law n. xeer falgalka chemistry; markii curiyayaal (elements) loo qaabeeyo kororka tirada atoms kooda, tusaale: argon (atomic mass 39.9), kaas oo laga hordhigo potassium (atomic mass 39.1).

periodic table n. tuse kalgal; jaantus muujiya curiyayaasha kiimiko (chemical elements) oo lagu saleeyay xeer kalgal (periodic law).

phase change n. chemistry isbaddal waji; markii heerkulku isbaddalo, walax (matter) isbaddal waji ayaa dhaca, taas oo qaab ka baddalmata una baddalmata qaabkale, sida ka baddalmay adke oo u baddalmay dareere (changing from a solid to a liquid).

phase equilibrium n. chemistry dheelitiran waji;

xaalad chemistry ee aan wax isbaddal kiimikaad ka dhicin, walxuhuna waxa ay ka koobanyihiin, sida neef, adke, iyo dareere (gas, solid, and liquid).

pH determination n. chemistry xaddiditaan pH (potential of Hydrogen); waxaa lagu qeexaa logarithm (base 10) oo taban (negative) ahna hydrogen ion concentration, tusaale pH = -log[H₃O⁺], a solution with pH < 7 is acidic, a solution with pH > 7 is basic, and a solution with pH = 7 is neutral.

basicity (bey’sisadhii) n. chemistry awoodda cabbir maalikiyuul aqbalo proton (H+) si uu u sameeyo walax deggan (stable product).

phenyl (‘fenal) n. chemistry kaafton kalyaale (monovalent) aryl radical C6H5− laga keenay benzene ayada oo laga saaray hal hydrogen atom —badanaa waxbuu la jiraa (combination). -phenylic (fi’nnilik) adj.

hyacinth (ˈhaaya,sinth) n. waa eray Greek ah (the blue larkspur flower ama the color purple); ubaxa yaaquut. -hyacinthine (ˌhaaya’sinthan) adj.

phenylacetaldehyde n. iskudhis dareere (liquid compound) C6H5CH2CHO ee carafta ubaxa yaaquut (hyacinth odor) loona adeegto catarada (perfumes).

organic acids n. chemistry iskudhisyo noole (organic) oo ay ku jirto walxo acidic.

monocarboxylic (,maana,kaar,baak’silik) adj. chemistry xambaarsan hal carboxyl group.

functional group n. koox hawleed; atoms khaas ah oo ku jira maalikiyuul oo hawshooda goonida u ah haysta, ayada oo aan loo dangalin atoms kale oo ku jira maalikiyuulka.

carboxyl (kaar’baaksal) n. chemistry kaaftoon kalyaale koox hawleed (functional group) ama

 a monovalent functional group or radical −COOH ee organic acids. kale loogu yeeraa carboxyl group. -carboxylic (ˌkaar,baak’silik) adj.

 

carboxylate (kaar’baaksa,leyt) n. chemistry cusbo (ester) ah carboxylic acid.                                          -v. carboxylate; carbamylating ku darid carboxyl ama carbon dioxide iskudhis (compound) samaysmadka carboxylic acid. -carboxylation (ˌkaar,baaksa’leyshan) n.

carboxylase (kaar’baak,saleys) n. chemistry iskudar (combination) ah iskudhis orgaanik (organic compound) oo ay wehliyaan carbon monoxide: carboxylation.

acetic acid n. chemistry monocarboxylic acid fudud oo xambaarsan laba carbons; formula CH3COOH.

acetate (‘aasa,teyt) n. 1 cusbo ama ester acetic acid. 2 cellulose acetate.

cellulose acetate n. dhawr iskudhisyo oo biyo ku milmikara oo ka samaysma acetic acid iyo sulfuric acid; astaan kiimiko C6H7O2 (OH)3.

endogenous (in’dhaajanas) adj. 1 ka abuurmay, ka bilawday, ama ka weynaada gudaha. 2 hab caadi ah, ama ay sababeen wax yaalo jirka ku jira. -endogenously adv.

metabolite (ma’taab,laayt) n. wax kasta oo abuura ama qayb ka qaata falgalka metabolic (metabolic reaction).  

 

anabolism (a’naaba,lizam) n. hab biochemical ee gudaha metabolism meeshaas oo maalikiyuullo yar-yar isku xirmaan si ay u sameeyaan (complex molecules). Barbardhig catabolism.

catabolism (ka’taabi,lizam) n. biochemistry metabolism burburiye, waxaa u sii raaca tamarta oo dhammeysa, iyo unugyada walxaha ku jira (protein ama lipids) oo baduuga. Barbardhig anabolism.

phenyl acetate n. chemistry cusbada acetate ester lagu helay uumihoor caadi ah (formal condensation) ee phenol wata acetic acid.

benzyl acetate n. dareere udgoon ee ester CH3COOCH2C6H5 lagana helo saliiddaa yaasmiin (jasmine oil) oo laga sameeyo barafuunada (perfumery).

phenylethyl alcohol (‘fenal’ethal) n. dareere carfoon ee alcohol C8H10O lagana helo saliidda ubaxa (rose oil and neroli oil), laakiin inta badan gacan-ku-samays ah, laguna carfiyo catarada (perfumes) iyo jeermisdilaha.

phenyl phenol n. chemistry benzene ring oo aan lahayn hydrogen atom ahna iskudhis aan deganayn, astaan kiimiko C6H5OH.

phosphide (‘faas,faaydh) n. chemistry nooc kasta oo iskudhisyo kiimiko ah ee phosphorus uu ay ku jirto bir, astaan kiimiko Ni5P2 and Ir2P.

phosphoric acid n. chemistry aan lahayn ur iyo midab toona, xambaarsanna iskudhis adke iyo manoolayaal (inorganic) lehna astaan kiimiko H3PO4.

phosphorus pentachloride n. chemistry cagaar-hurdiyeed adke ur adag iyo iskudhis wirqe crystalline compound PCl5.

photocell (‘fawdha,seel) n. chemistry unug footo; eeg photoelectric cell.

transducer (taraanis’dhuusar) n. qalab baddala tamar (convert energy) oo haddana u baddala qaab kale. e.g. A speaker is a transducer that transforms electrical signals into sound.

photoelectric cell n. chemistry qalab electronic oo qaybihiisa danabeed (electrical) laga dhigay ficil ifeed; sida switches light detectors (burglar alarms), devices to measure light intensity (light meters), and power sources (solar cells).

photochemical (,foodhaw’keemikal) n. chemistry la xariirta ama ka timaadda fal kiimiko ee hirar birlabdanabeed (electromagnetic waves) iyo waliba if (light). -photochemically (ˌfawdhaw’keemiklii) adv.

photochemical decomposition n. 1 chemistry kalabax footo kiimikaad; falgal (reaction) hal iskudhis uu u kalabaxa (decomposes) 2 ama ka badan oo curiyayaal (elements) ama iskudhisyo (compounds).

photoconductor n. chemistry footo gudbiye; walax (substance) ogolaata qulqulka danab (electric current) in uu fudayd u dhexmaro markii if lagu daaro.

photoelectric (ˌfawdhaw-i’lektarik) adj. chemistry footo danab; la xariirta saxarro danab ahaan saldanabaysan (electrically charged) oo la sii daayay markii ay dhuuqeen kaah birlabdanabeed (electromagnetic radiation). -photoelectrically (ˌfawdhaw-i’lektriklii) adv.

physical change n. chemistry isbaddal duleed; waxaa isbaddala qaab, qiyaas, ama xaallad, laakin walaxdii waa isku mid, sida baraf, dareere, ama neef (gas).

physical chemistry n. chemistry kemistari duleed; laan ka mid ah chemistry oo gooni u eegta dhexgal (interaction), qaab-baddal (transformation) walxo, iyo habkooda kiimiko.

physical properties n. chemistry astaamaha duleed; walax la cabbirikaro, la eegikaro ayada oo aan la baddalin walax ahaanteeda.

pi bond n. (π bond) dabar pi; dabar kiimiko oo ka dhexeeya atoms ku jira maalikiyuul wata dhawr pi oo ku meeraysanaya.

pipette (paay’peet) n. nuuge; qaade yar ee shaybaar oo lagu qaado wax yar oo la cabbirayo.

plane-polarized adj. sallax ilays cirifaysan; hirar u walhanaya gariir (vibration) isku jiho ayago oo dhan.

plane of symmetry n. sallax wanqaaran; sallax dhexmaray wirqe laba isku’eg u kala dhanbalay.

unvarying (,an’verying) adj. aan isbaddalayn; madoorsoome ah. e.g. They have strict quality and unvarying test. -unvaryingly adv.

Planck’s constant n. also Planck constant madoorsoomaha Planck; madoorsoome caalami ah oo qeexa dabeecadda tamarta quantum (nature of energy quantum) iyo xiriirka tamareed ee kala dhexeeya photon rakaadkiisa (photon to its frequency); the constant value is 6.62607015×10−34 joule-hertz−1 (ama joule seconds —symbol h).

polar bond n. dabar cirifle; dabar wadaag (covalent bond) ka dhexeeya laba atoms kaas oo ay electrons aysan u wadaagin si isle’eg, sidaas darteed waxay ku dhammaataa mid noqda tabane iyo mid noqda togane.

polarimeter (ˌpawla’rimadhar) n. cirifaw beeg; qalab lagu soo saaro xagasha plane-polarized light uu ku wareegay. -polarimetric (paw,lera’metrik) adj.; -polarimetry (ˌpawla’rimatarii) n.

polar molecule n. maalikiyuul cirifle; maalikiyuul dhinac danbe xoogaa togane (slightly positive) ka ah, marka uu dhinaca kale ee danbana xoogaa tabane (slightly negative) ka yahay.

polyvalent (,paalii’veylanti) adj. 1 chemistry kaaftoon badane; atoms ama maalikiyuullo leh kaaftoon (valency) saddex ama ka badan. 2 wajiyo ama ujeedooyin badan leh. 3 biology xambaarsan antibodies hal nooc ka badan oo pathogen ah. –polyvalence (ˌpaalii’veylanis) n.

pathogen (‘paathajan) n. cudurkeene; noolaha (viruses, bacteria, protozoans iyo fungi) jirrada u keenay bukaanka.

porcelain clay n. dhoobo shiino; eeg kaolin.

extender (ik’istendar) n. 1 kordhiye; badiye; walxo wax lagu kordhiyo. 2 wax cunto lagu daro ama lagu adkeeyo.

porcelain crucible n. qalab shaybaar oo adeegta  kululayn, milmis, jajabin, iyo gubis.

porcelain evaporating dish n. saxan uumibixin ee shaybaar.

porcelainite (‘porsala,naayt) n. dhoobo duban oo laga helo meelaha macdanta laga qodo.

positive charge n. chemistry saldanab togan; markii protons ay ka badanyihiin electrons.

positive electron n. chemistry elektaroon togan. eeg positron.

 

positron (‘paaza,taraan) n. chemistry saxar saldanab togan ah ee gudaha atom waxa uu  leeyahay cuf (mass) u dhigma cufka electron. kale loogu yeeraa antielectron.

antielectron (ˌaantiya’lekraraan) n. eeg positron.

metallic oxide n. oxide bir ah; iskudhis ay sameeyeen bir iyo oxygen, xambaarsanna ugu yaraan hal bir (metal) iyo hal oxygen atom. e.g. Magnesium reacts with oxygen and they form magnesium oxide.

positive ray n. physics kaah togan; shucaac ions togan ah oo ka yimid metallic anode oo u socda qotin tabane (cathode) neef laga sii daayay dhuun.

positive valence n. 1 kaaftoon togan (positively charged ion). 2 tiro electrons oo atom bixinkaro.

potassium acetate (pa’taasiyamˈaasa,teyt) n. chemistry kaaliyam asiteyt; astaan kiimiko CH3CO2K. kale loogu yeeraa Diuretic salt ama Potassium ethanoate, ama Acetic acid potassium salt.

retardant (ri’taardhanti) adj. daahiya; xanniba. e.g. fire-retardant materials. -retardant n.

polyatomic (,paaleeya’taamik) adj. maalikiyuul ama ion ka kooban saddex iyo kabadan atoms. e.g. some compounds have polyatomic ions.

potassium aluminate sulphate n. kaaliyam aluminayt sulfayt; metal sulfate oo ay ku jirto potassium, aluminum iyo sulfate ions ee saamiga (ration) 1:1:2. Astaan kiimiko K2SO4.Al2(SO4)3.

potassium bicarbonate n. chemistry cusbo wirqe ah oo ku milanta biyaha, lehna astaan kiimiko KHCO3 mararna loo adeegto antacid, iyo aashitada kaadida iyo potassium oo jirka ku yaraada (potassium deficiency).

alkalizer n. la dagaasha aashitada (acidity) caloosha.

alkalinize (‘aalkala,naayz) v. alkalinized; alkalizing samayn alkaline. -alkalinization (ˌaalka,lina’zeyshan) n.

potassium bisulfate n. or potassium acid sulfate cusbo wirqe (crystalline) ah oo leh astaan kiimiko KHSO4 oo falgal acid siisa milan.

potassium bitartrate n. or potassium bitartrate chemistry eeg cream of tartar.

cream of tartar n. chemistry budo cad oo wirqe lehna astaan kiimiko KC4H5O6, inta badan loo isticmaalo khamiir (baking powder).

potassium bromide n. abbr. KBr chemistry cusbo wirqe (crystalline) inta badan loo isticamaalo dejinta (sedative) maskaxda iyo photography.

potassium carbonate n. chemistry cusbo cad oo leh astaan kiimiko K2CO3 samaysana milanka alkaline (alkaline solution), loona adeegto samaynta quraarado iyo saabuun.

potassium chlorate n. chemistry cusbo wirqe (crystalline) lehna astaan kiimiko KClO3 loona adeegto oxidizing agent ee tarraqyada (matches), baaruudaha (fireworks), iyo qaraxyada (explosives).

potassium chloride n. chemistry cusbo wirqe (crystalline salt) lehna astaan kiimiko KCl macdanta iyo biyaha dabiiciga ahna laga helo, loona adeegto nafaqeeye (fertilizer).

potassium chromate n. chemistry cusbo hurdi wirqe (yellow crystalline) ah, lehna astaan kiimiko K2CrO4 isku sina loo adeegto sodium chromate.

potassium cyanide n. chemistry cusbo wirqe oo aad sun u ah, lehna astaan kiimiko KCN, gooni ahaanna loogu isticmaalo in birta looga saaro dahabka (gold) iyo qalinka (silver).

potassium dichromate n. chemistry cusbo milanta

(soluble salt) lehna astaan kiimiko K2Cr2O7 loona adeegto dheehaynta (dyeing), photography, iyo oxidizing agent.

potassium ferricyanide n. chemistry cusbo wirqe cas (red crystalline) ah, lehna astaan kiimiko K3Fe(CN)6 loona isticmaalo photographic bleach iyo coating blueprint paper. kale loogu yeeraa red prussiate of potash.

red prussiate of potash n. eeg potassium ferricyanide.

etching (‘ejin) n. xarar-dheehasho; hab sawir ama qoraal ku xardhan bir looga dheehdo meel shay kale.

potassium fluoride n. chemistry iskudhis kiimiko KF, inta badan fluoride ion oo ay isticmaalaan warshadaha iyo chemistry.

potassium hydroxide n. chemistry iskudhis orgaanik ma’ahe ah, astaan kiimiko KOH, adke cad oo dhalaala milmana (white deliquescent solid) lagana sameeyo saabuun. 

potassium iodate n. chemistry astaan kiimiko KIO3 

ahna oxidizing agent dabna dhalinkarta hadday holac u dhawaato.

potassium iodide n. chemistry cusbo wiriqda lehna astaan kiimiko KI kuna milanta biyo aadna loogu isticmaalo daaweynta: hyperthyroidism.

potassium manganate n. chemistry iskudhis ograanik ma’ahe ah oo cusbo cagaaran ah, lehna astaan kiimiko K2MnO4 iskuna baddala potassium permanganate.

potassium nitrate n. chemistry cusbo wiriqda (crystalline salt) lehna astaan kiimiko KNO3 dabiiciyanna looga helo ciidda, gaar ahaana looga sameeyo baaruudda qoryaha (gunpowder), nafaqeeye (fertilizer), iyo daawo (medicine).

potassium oxide n. chemistry iskudhis ionic ah oo ka samaysmay kudaranka potassium iyo oxygen; astaan kiimiko k2O; cidla’ lagama helo waayo hore ayuu ka falgalaa (too reactive).

potassium perchlorate n. chemistry cusbo wirqe ah (crystalline salt) lehna astaan kiimiko KClO4 loona isticmaalaa holacyada (flares) iyo baabuurta airbags.

thyroid inhibitor n. daawo xannibta dheecaandaynta qanjirka thyroid.

potassium permanganate n. chemistry cusbo (dark purple) iskudhis kiimiko oo orgaanik ma’ahe ah, lehna astaan kiimiko KMnO4 loona adeegto oxidizer iyo jeermisdile (disinfectant).

potassium peroxide n. chemistry aad u falgala, oxidizing ahna adke cad oo hurdi (yellow) noqda.

potassium silicate n. chemistry iskudhis orgaanik ma’ahe lehna astaan kiimiko K2SiO3.

potassium sulfate n. chemistry budo cad oo wiriqda (white crystalline powder) oo aan lahayn midab, ahna iskudhis orgaanik ma’ahe ah, lehna astaan kiimiko K2SO4, loona adeegto nafaqeeye (fertilizer).

potassium tartrate n. chemistry potassium slat of tartaric acid, lehna astaan kiimiko K2C4H4O6.

potassium thiocyanate n. chemistry cusbo wirqe sayaxnuug ah (hygroscopic crystalline salt) lehna astaan kiimiko KSCN loona isticmaalo (antihypertensive agent).

potential difference n. faraq kayd; tusaale: bateri kasta laba hog ayuu leeyahay (two terminals), voltage kooduna waa potential difference oo labadaas u dhexeeya.

potentiometer (pa,tenshi’yaamadhar) n. 1 kaydbeege; qalab lagu cabbiro xoog danabwade (electromotive forces). 2 voltage divider. -potentiometric (pa,tenshiya’metrik) adj.

voltage divider n. caabbiye (resistor) ama caabbiyayaal lagu xiray meelo cayiman oo bixiya potential forces kala duduwan oo ka imaanaya hal quwad ileed (single source).

electromotive force (i,lektaraw,mawdhiv ‘fooris) n. abbr. EMF xoog danabwade; xoog danabwade waxana abuura unug danab-kiimikaad (electrochemical cell) ama baddalista badad birlabeed (magnetic field).

potentiometric analysis n. chemistry saafid keydbeegeed; ogaanshaha isbeddalka (potential difference) ee ka dhaxaysa 2 unug qotineed (2 electrodes of a cell).

precipitant (piri’sipatanti) adj. da’a; daroora; hoora. -precipitately adv.; -precipitateness n.

preliminary test n. hubsasho gogolxaar; hubinta dabeecadaha guud ee iskudhis ee ay ku jiraan adke, dareere, midab, iyo ur.

propene (‘paraw,peyn) n. eeg propylene.

propylene (‘paraw,paliin) n. hydrocarbon neef oo kale ah (gaseous hydrocarbon) aan lahayn midab oo guban’og lagana dhex helo batrool (petroleum), lehna astaan kiimiko C3H6. kale loogu yeeraa propene.

propylene oxide n. sun (toxic) keentana kansar (carcinogenic), aan lahayn midab, ahna dareere uumibixi’og, iskudhis organic ee astaan kiimiko CH3CHCH2O.

 propyl (‘parawpal) n. labadaan midkood isomeric alkyl radicals C3H7 oo ka yimid propane, badanaana la isku daro.

propyl acetate n. iskudhis kiimiko (chemical compound) dareere saafi ah oo aan lahayn midab.

propyl alcohol n. labada midkood isomeric liquid alcohols C3H7OH: 1 caadiga alcohol oo inta badan loo isticmaalo mile (solvent). 2 isopropyl alcohol: holca oo uumibixi’og, astaan kiimiko alcohol C3H8O loona isticmaalo mile (solvent) iyo rugis (rubbing alcohol).

isopropyl alcohol n. eeg propyl alcohol.

proton acceptor n. proton qaate; waa magac kale ee ‘base’, kaas oo lid u ah ‘acid’; Broensted-Lowry definition, base waa negatively charged ion sidaa darteed way diidin, ama way ogaalaan positively charged hydrogen ion; maadaama hydrogen ion tahay proton, base waxaa la oran waa proton acceptor.

proton donor n. proton bixiye; Acids waa Proton Donors (bixiye); Bases waa Proton Acceptors (qaate ama aqbale).

proton magnetic resonance n. abbr. PMR iskudhis birlabeed ee proton; bedad birlabeed ee dibadda (external magnetic field) ah ayaa loo isticmaalay in ay ku khasbaan protons u jeesiga laba jiho oo suurtagal ah oo aan lahayn tamar isle’eg (equal energy).

pyrene (‘paay,riin) n. midablaawe hydrocarbon, C16H10 oo laga helo dhuxul (coal tar).

quadrilocular n. afar unug (cells) ama qolqol (compartments) leh.

tetravalent (tetra’veylanti) adj. afar kaaftoonle ah; atom afar kaafoon qotonle ah.

quadrivalent (,kuwaadra’veylant) adj. afar kaaftoonle ah: tetravalent.

qualitative analysis n. tayo saafid; baaris kiimiko oo ogaata ka koobnaanta walax ama iskudar (mixture).

 

qualitative test n. chemistry tayo hubsasho; waxay ogaataa waxa ka maqan iyo waxa jooga ee ka koobnaanatooda kiimiko kala duwan ee la eegayo.

quantitative analysis n. chemistry xaddi saafid; waxay ogaataa tirada waxa ku jira iyo ka koobnaantooda kiimikada kala duwan ee la eegayo.

quantity determination n. chemistry xadididda xaddi;

quick burning composition n. chemistry samayska dhaqasaha u gubta.

radioactinium n. chemistry raadiyoo aktiniym

sii dayn tamar (energy) isotope of thorium oo leh mass number 227 kana abuurmay burbur ku dhacay actinium, summad RdAc ama Th227.

radioactive elements n. chemistry curiyayaal kaahfale; sii daynta tamar ee bu’da boloshay (decay of the nuclei) ee atoms iyo isotopes qaarkood; bu’da atomic (atomic nuclei) waxay ka koobantahay protons iyo neutrons oo nud yar iskula xiran gudaha atoms ka.

transuranic (,taranisyuu’raanik) adj. or transuranium (ˌtaraansiyuu’reyniyam) la xariira ama ah curiye (element) tiro atomic (atomic number) ka badan leh tan uranium (92). -transuranic n.

transuranium (ˌtaraanisyuu’reyniyam). eeg transuranic.

actinide (‘aakta,naaydh) n. koox (series) curiyayaal bir ah oo tirooyin atomic (atomic number) ka bilawdo 89 ilaa 103 leh; kaah faliddooda (their radioactivity) ayayna caan ku yihiin.

actinoid (‘aakta,noydh) n., pl. actinoids mid kasta oo ka mid ah 15 curiye kiimiko (chemical elements) oo ka bilawda actinium ilaa lawrencium, tiro atomic-gooduna ka bilaabato 89 ilaa 103, waxayna caan ku yihiin kaah faliddooda (their radioactivity).

radioactive family n. bahda kaahfale; kooxda actinoid oo xambaarsan curiyayaasha kaah falidda (radioactive elements).

Radium salts n. cusbooyin raadiyam; iskudhis birma’ahe ah oo leh astaan kiimiko RaCl2, waana radium salt of hydrogen.

trisaccharide (,taraay’saaka,raaydh) n. walax kasta oo ka kooban saddex maalikiyuul (molecule) oo sonkor ah, iskuna xiran.

raffinose (‘raafa,naws) n. chemistry sonkor wiriqda oo xoogaa macaan, lagana helo miraha suuf iyo dhir kalaba, lehna astaan kiimiko C18H32O16.

noble gas n. mid kasta oo ka mid ah bahda ‘rare gas’ oo ay ku jiraan helium, neon, argon, krypton, iyo xenon, oo muujiya deganaan (stability) iyo falgal gaabis ah (low reaction rates). kale loogu yeeraa inert gas.

lanthanide (‘laantha,naaydh) n. or lanthanoid mid kasta oo ka mid kooxda curiyayaal oo leh tiro atomic (atomic numbers) ee badanaysa marka laga bilaabo lanthanum ama cerium ilaa lutetium.

 rare earth element n. abbr. REE curiye naadir ciidbireed; koox todoba-iyo-ban curiye bireedyo (metallic elements), waxaa kujira shan-iyo-toban lanthanides lagu daray scandium iyo yttrium; waxyna gundhig u yihiin qalab badan oo high-tech ah. kale loogu yeeraa rare earth metal.

rare earth metal n. eeg rare earth element.

linear burning rate n. waxaa loo rogay (converted) linear mass burning rate (kg/m2-s).

rate of combustion n. or burning rate dhaqsaha gubasho oo lagu cabbiro iskudhis (compound) ama walax kale, sida shumac (candle).

rate of oxidation n. chemistry dhaqsaha ogsaydh; habka wax ugu darmato oxygen, waxaana kor dhinkara dhawr arrin; sida heerkul sare (higher temperature), joogista kalkaaliyayaal (catalysts), oogada walaxda, iyo ridbanaanta oxygen (concentration of oxygen) ama oxidizing agent.

rate of reaction n. chemistry dhaqsaha falgalka; dhaqsaha ay uga qaybqaataan walxaha (products) falgalayaashu (reactants) falgalka kiimikaad (chemical reaction).

 

reactant (rii’aktanti) n. chemistry falgale; walax ka qaybgasha falgal kiimikaad (chemical reaction). e.g. The unabsorbed reactants were consumed.

reaction chain n. chemistry silsilad falgal; falgal keenay ficilqaad fal (reactive) oo sababay falgal kale in uu dhaco; tusaale: shaah kulul baa igu daatay, markaas baan booday oo tarmuuskii lug ku dhuftay wuuna jabay.

direct chemical reaction n. chemistry falgal kiimikaad toosan; falgal laba iyo ka badan curiye (elements) ama iskudhis midawbeen si ay u sameeyaan hal iskudhis (product).

reaction energy n. chemistry tamar falgal;

waxaa loo nasbeeyaa tamarta gudaha (enthalpy), taas oo ah tamarta isbaddalkeed ka dhexaysa walxaha (products) iyo falgalayaasha (reactants) oo la kala gooyo (subtraction); haddii tamarta falgaluhu (reactant energy) ay ka sarrayso walxaha, markaas tamarta oo dhan waxay noqonaysaa mid taban (negative), taas oo keenaysa falgal kulbixiye (exothermic reaction).

reaction mechanism n. chemistry tallaabooyin falgal; tallaabooyin isdabajoog ah oo tilmaama dhacdooyin falgal kiimiko (chemical reaction); haddii ay maraan laba iyo kabadan heer, waxaa la dhahaa multistep ama complex reaction.

reaction order n. chemistry horsiimo falgal; nadaam falgalka waa iskudarka jibbaarada (exponents) ee tibxaha ribanaanta (concentration terms); tusaale: falgalka (reaction) aA+bB → maxsuulka (products); nadaamka falgalka oo tixgalinay falgalayaasha (reactants) A iyo B waa a iyo b siday u kala horreeyaan oo ah falgal (reaction) a + b.

reaction products n. chemistry maxsuul falgal;

loona qoro: R e a c t a n t s → P r o d u c t s; tusaale: iron (Fe) iyo sulfur (S) isku darkood iron sulfide (FeS). Fe(s) + S(s) → FeS(s) the plus sign means that iron reacts with sulfur.

reagent (rii’eyjanti) n. falgalkeene; qaybta dhammaystirta (integral part) falgal kiimiko; walax ama iskudhis fududeeya ama sahla falgal (facilitate a reaction), inta badanna baarista ayaa loo adeegtaa, sida pregnancy test, blood glucose test, iyo COVID-19 test kits.

reducing agent n. yareeye; walax dhinta iskudhiska kiimiko, ayada oo bixisa ama ku deeqda electrons.

redox (‘rii,dhaakis) adj. chemistry falgal kiimiko kasta oo tiro oxidation ee maalikiyuul, atom ama ion uu baddalmo, asaga oo kororsada ama dhumiya electron.

reduction potential n. chemistry awood dhime; suurtagalnimada ay ku dhicikarto dhimis qotintabane (cathode) ee unug danab-kiimikaad (electrochemical cell).

regeneration of electrolyte n. cusboonaysiin gudbiye milme.

reoxidize (,rii’aaksa,dhaayz) v. also re-oxidize reoxidized also re-oxidized; reoxidizing also re-oxidizing chemistry dib-ugu-darid oxygen, siiba falgal ay electrons kororsameen kaaftonkuna (valence) uu  yaraaday, badanaa oxygen la saaray ama hydrogen oo kororta. -reoxidation (ˌrii,aaksa’dheyshan) or -re-oxidation n.; pl. -reoxidations also -re-oxidations.

rotor (‘rawdhar) n. qaybta ku wareegta shay.

rotorcraft (‘rawdhar,karaafti) n., pl. rotorcraft 1 dayaarad qurmmaati u kacda (helicopter) oo leh marwaxad wareegta. 2 baal dayaarad (helicopter) ama wax la mid ah.

airfoil (‘eer,foyal) n. 1 wax kicikara oo hawada ku dhaqaaqikara. 2 baal dayaaradeed (aircraft).

remanence (‘remananis) n. birlabaysan; shay biralabnimo ku harta markii birlab laga qaado. e.g. There must be some remanence in the rotor iron.

resorcinol (ra’zoorsa,nool) n. chemistry wirqe  phenol C6H6O2 lagana helo xabko (resins) kala duwan ama gacan ku samays ah, loona adeegto dheehyo (dyes), iyo daawooyin (pharmaceuticals).

eukaryote (,yuukeeriyawt) n. unug (cell) ama noole (organism) bu’ muuqata oo la arkikaro leh. Barbardhig archaea, bacterium, prokaryote.

prokaryote (,paraw’keeri,yawt) n. noole aad u yar oo hal unugle ah, ama archaea noole ilma’arto (micro-organism), iyo jeermis (bacteria). Barbardhig archaea, bacterium, eukaryote.

anaerobic respiration n. ogsijiin maneefsade; meefsashola’aan hawo; kana dhaca noole hal unugele ama ilma’aargto (prokaryotes iyo eukaryotes) oo unugyadu jajabiyaan oxygen la’aan maalikiyuulada sonkarta (sugar molecules) si ay tamar uga helaan.

aerobic respiration n. neefasho haweed; wareeg neefsashada oo ay ku jirto neefta oxygen si ay tamar uga samayso cuntada (energy from food); caadi bayna u tahay dhirta iyo noolaha oo dhan, taas oo biyo iyo carbon dioxide ka samaysmaan ugu danbayn.

anaerobic (,aana’rawbik) adj. 1 noolaada ama jira oxygen la’aan, siiba cayayaan ama organism. 2 la xariira jimicsi aan waba ugudbin habka neefsashada jirku uu ku qaato oxygen.

anaerobe (‘aanarawb) n. oxygen la’an, siiba jeermis noolaankara hawo la’aan.

aerobe (‘eerawb) n. noole, sida jeermis (bacterium) oxygen ku nool.

reversible reaction n. chemistry falgal gadismikara; falgal (reaction) labada dhinacba u dhicikara, tusaale: A iyo B waa falgalikaraan (react) si ay u qaabeeyaan C iyo D, markaas C iyo D waa falgalikaraan (react) si ay dib ugu qaabeeyaan A iyo B.

thermodynamics (,tharmawdhaay’naamikis) n. physics 1 cilmiga kala gadiska ee ka dhexeeya kul iyo qaababka kale ee tamar (energy). 2 habkaan waxyaalaha la halmaala thermodynamic. –thermodynamicist (ˌtharmawdhaay’naamasisti) n.

rhodamine (‘rawdha,miin) n. koox kasta oo ah bahda hurdi-cas (yellow-red) oo noqota dheeh buluug ah markii la ifiyo.

ring compound n. chemistry iskudh giraangarsan; iskudhis qaabdhismeed formula xambaarsan silsilad xiran ama atoms galaweysan (ring).

Rochelle salt n. chemistry cusbo Rochelle;

cusbo wiriqda (crystalline salt) KNaC4H4O6·4H2O xoogaana caloolbixis ah (mild purgative).

rocket fuel n. shidaal gantaal; waxay noqonkartaa adke (solid), dareere (liquid), ama neef (gas), inta badan waxaa la isticmaalaa dareere (fuel) ama oxidizer (caawiye gubasho shidaal gantaal).

oxidizer (‘aaksa,dhaayzar) n. 1 oxidizing agent. 2 mid loo isticamaalo caawin gubasho shidaal gantaal (rocket propellant).

specific rotation n. chemistry wareeg nooceed; baddalista jihada (orientation) ee kaah-hirkaliyaale (monochromatic) ee sallax ilays cirifaysan (plane-polarized).

natural rubber n. rabar (cinjir) dabiici; dareere caana cad ah (called latex) oo ka dhibicleeya jirrid geedaha qaarkood.

NCS n. abbr. noncaloric sweeteners.

saponification value n. also saponification number waxay muhiim u tahay saabuunaha iyo walxaha wax lagu nadiifiyo (detergent); waxayna caddaysaa inta alkali (KOH ama NaOH) ee looga baahanyahay in la saabuuneeyo (saponify) xayrta iyo saliidda si saabuun loo sameeyo.

saturant (‘saajaranti) n. dhargiye; fashaqiye; qooye.

kowtow (‘kaaw,taaw) v. kowtowed; kowtowing; kowtows 1 tusid baarrinimo; xushmayn; addeecid. 2 sajuudid; jilbo iyo waji dhigid dhulka. -kowtow n.

selective absorption n. chemistry nuugid xulasho.

selective extraction n. chemistry soo saaris xulasho; hab si doorasho ah oo iskudhiska la rabo ka saaraya isku qasanka (mixture) ayada oo la adeegsanayo mile solvent; si hawsha loogu guulasyto, iskudhisku waa in uu ahaado mid ku milmikara (soluble) mile-ha ee uu san ku milmin qasanka (mixture).

selective solvent n. chemistry mile xulasho; xagga heerkul iyo saami (ratios) la xariira walaxaha kale oo aad wax u mila.  

semipolar bond n. or semipolar double bond bar tamar cirifle. eeg coordinate bond.

coordinate bond n. chemistry dabar wadaag (covalent bond) oo ka kooban lammaane electrons (pair of electrons) oo uu quudiyay (supplied) labada atoms oo uu ku xirmay midkood kali ah.

bauxite (‘bawk,saayt) n. iskudar ciid ah oo aan saafi ahayn ee hydrous aluminum oxides iyo hydroxides oo ah gundhigga jiritaanka aluminum. -bauxitic (book’sidhik) adj.

Serpeck’s process n. chemistry habka Serpeck;

Bauxite xambaarsan tira badan oo silica ah waxaana lagu saafiyaynkaraa habka Serpeck; sida Bauxite la budeeyay ayaa lagu qasaa carbon waana la kulayliyaa ilaa 1800o C, nitrogen way baxdaa, markaas ayaa la helaa aluminum nitride.

shared electrons n. chemistry elektaron wadaagsan; wadaagga electrons oo ka dhexeeya atoms ayaa la yiraahdaa dabar wadaag (covalent bond), taas oo atoms-yada iskugu haysa maalikiyuul (molecule) ahaan.

side chain n. chemistry silsilad dhinac; xariir gaaban (short chain) ama koox atoms ah ayaa ku dhinac xirmata xariir weynaha (principal chain) ama galawga maalikiyuul (molecule).

side reaction n. chemistry falgal dhinac; falgal kiimiko waxa uu dhinac socdaa oo mar wada yimaadaan falgal weyne (main reaction). kale loogu yeeraa side effect.

siemens (‘siimaniz) n., pl. siemens halbeeg gudbiye (unit of conductance) ee habka meter-kilogram-second ah, una dhigma hal ampere per volt.

alternating (‘ooltar,neydhin) adj. dareerayal qoodo ah; xariir ah ama isdabasocda. -alternatingly adv.

conductance (kan’dhaktanis) n. physics 1 xariiris awood (conduction power). 2 awoodda cabbir ama se gudbiye (conductor) ku gudbiyo qulqul danab (electricity); lidkeeda caabbi (resistance).

producer gas n. iskudar neefo holca (flammable) oo xambaarsan (carbon monoxide iyo hydrogen) iyo kuwo aan holcin (nitrogen iyo carbon dioxide).

silica gel n. xab silika; wax u eg ciid cad oo dhuuqa qoyaan.

carbide (‘kaar,baaydh) n. 1 iskudhis (binary compound) iskugu jira carbon iyo bir (metal). 2 wax aad u adag oo ka samaysan carbon oo hal ama ka badan biro culus ah (heavy metals).

calcium carbide n. also calcium acetylide iskudhis kiimiko oo leh astaan kiimiko CaC2 ahna madaw danbasi ah oo wirqa.

calcium cyanamide n. chemistry iskudhis kiimiko CaCN2 loona isticmaalo nafaqeeye (fertilizer) ahaan iyo caws dhalato ah oo lagu dilo (weed killer).

alkyne (alkaayn) n. chemistry hydrocarbons xambaarsan carbon-carbon triple bonds, astaan kiimiko iCnH2n-2 molecules with one triple bond (and no rings).

silicon carbide n. dhagax wirqe ah oo aad iyo aad u adag ahna iskudhis silicon iyo caron ee astaanta CiC, loona adeegto warqadda xanafta leh ee (sandpaper), soofaynta, iyo jarista biro.

acetylide (a’seta,laaydh) n. chemistry heerar kala duwan oo iskudhisyo kiimiko oo bir ah iskulana xiran alkyne; astaan guud ee kiimiko RC≡CM, meesha R tahay dhinaca uga xirma organic.

artificial silk n. or art silk dun gacan-ku-samays ah oo u eg dunta xariirta, waxaana laga la mid dhigaa dunta rayon.

bromide (‘baraw,maaydh) n. 1 iskudhis kiimiko oo ka kooban laba walax (two elements) oo kala duwan (binary compound) oo ah bromine ay wehliso walax kale  (other element). 2 aan laahayn xiiso ama qof lagu daalo. 3 hadal in badan la istimaalay oo xiisa beelay: hackneyed statement.

silver bromide n. chemistry iskudhis AgBr oo aad ugu nugul ifka, loona isticmaalo waxyaalaha sawirada (photographic materials).

silver chloride n. chemistry iskudhis AgCl oo aad ugu nugul ifka, loona isticmaalo waxyaalaha sawirada (photographic materials).

halide (‘haa,laaydh) n. chemistry iskudhis kiimiko (binary compound) oo iskugu jira  halogen iyo curiye kala (other element), sida: fluoride, chloride, bromide, iodide, astatide, ama theoretic.

photohalide (‘fawtaw’haa,laaydh) n. chemistry mid kasta oo ka mid ah waxyaalo midab leh oo kala duwan oo ka yimid silver halide marka la diyaarinayo.

silver halide n. chemistry silver bromide (AgBr), chloride (AgCl), iodide (Agl) iyo laba kale oo silver fluorides; koox ahaan waxaa la iskula magacaabaa silver halides.

silver nitrate n. chemistry iskudhis kiimiko AgNO3 oo marka uu la kulmo walxaha noole (organic matter) isku baddala madaw loona adeegto falgalkeene (chemical reagent), siiba jeermisdile (antiseptic) iyo ashito jarta jirka (caustic).

simple distillation n. chemistry xareedayn sahlan; iskudar (mixture) la karkariyay si ay iskugu baddalaan uumi (vapor).

simple sugar n. chemistry eeg monosaccharide.

 

electrode (i’lek,tarawdh) n. qotin gudbiye (conductor) siiya danab walxaha aan ahayn bir  (nonmetallic), dareere, ama neef.

single electrode potential n. chemistry kayd qotin kaliyaale; kayd abuurma marka bir la daro milan (dipped solution) ka kooban ions kiisa, inta u dhexaysa milanka iyo birta.

slow-burning n. walxo u gigsada (adkaysta) gubashada (dab).

slow-burning powder n. budo gubasho gaaban; budo inta badan rasaasta culus, iyo qoryaha dhuunta dheer loo isticmaalo.

bicarbonate (,baay’kaarbaneyt) n. carbonic cusbo ah, xambaarsanna ion HCO3.

smalt (ismoolti) n. chemistry quraarad budaysan; rinji buluug takhi ah (deep blue pigment) oo ka kooban dhalo budaysan oo ay ku jirto oxide of cobalt.  

hard soap n. chemistry saabuun adag; saabuun laga sameeyo sodium hydroxide ama sodium carbonate.

soft-soap v. soft-soaped; soft-soaping; soft-soaps ku raadin jileec, qalqaalin ama shukaamin. e.g. She could not soft-soap me as easy as you think.              -n. 1 milan saabuun oo laga sameeyay potassium hydroxide. 2 flattery.

soft-soap v. qalqaalin; ku raadin dabac iyo soo jiidad.                                                                     -n. soft soap 1 chemistry saabuun jilicsan; saabuun dareere ah ama milanta, lagana sameeyo potassium intii laga samayn lahaa sodium hydroxide. 2 soo jiidasho; qalqaalo: flattery.

soda ash n. chemistry danbas soda; magac guud oo loo yaqaan sodium carbonate, oo leh astaan kiimiko Na2CO3, iskudhiskaan waxaa kale oo la dhahaa washing soda ama soda crystals; waana budo cad oo aan lahayn ur, makay biyo ku milantana noqota carbonic acid iyo sodium hydroxide.

slaked lime n. eeg hydrated lime.

hydrated lime n. chemistry budo cad oo qalalan kana kooban calcium hydroxide, laga keenay nuurad (lime) biyo ku qasan. kale loogu yeeraa slaked lime.

soda lime n. chemistry iskuqas sodium hydroxide iyo slake lime oo loo isticmaalo dhuuqis (absorb) qoyaan iyo neefaha (moisture iyo gases).

gold washing n. hab dahab looga dhaqo ciid ama dhagax.

auriferous (oo’rifras) n. ku jiro ama sameeya dahab. e.g. Several types of auriferous soils were found in Gedo region, Somalia.

soda washing n. chemistry sooda dhaqis;

iskudhis kiimiko Na2CO3, orgaanik ma’ahe hydrate sodium carbonate ah; kana yimid danbaska dhir ka baxda ciid sodium ka buuxo.

sodium bicarbonate n. chemistry kiciso ama khamiir (baking soda ama bicarbonate of soda), iskudhis kiimiko NaHCO3, cusbo ay ku jirto sodium cation (Na+) iyo bicarbonate anion (HCO3−).

sodium hydroxide n. chemistry adke cad oo kakan NaOH ahna aashito oo kale (caustic base), lagana sameeyo saabuun, dun (rayons) iyo waraaqo.

sodium hypochlorite n. chemistry cusbo aan deganayn (unstable salt) NaOCl milan biyoodna lagu qaso (aqueous solution) loona isticmaalo warankiilo iyo dilaa jeermis (bleaching and disinfecting agent).

sodium nitrate n. chemistry cusbo dhalaasha ama milanta (deliquescent crystalline salt) NaNO3, loona adeegto nafaqeeye (fertilizer), cusbaynta hilib solay (curing meat).

sodium peroxide n. chemistry iskudhis hurdi jariir sayaxnuug (pale-yellow hygroscopic granular compound) astaan kiimiko Na2O2 loona adeegto oxidizing iyo warankiilayn (bleaching).

sodium potassium tartrate n. eeg rochelle salt.

rochelle salt n. wirqe cusbo cad oo aan lahayn midab, lehna astaan kiimiko C4H4KNaO6·4H2O bixisana calool (purgative). kale loogu yeeraa potassium sodium tartrate, Seignette salt, sodium potassium tartrate.

sodium silicate n. chemistry mid kasta oo ka mid ah noocyo kala duwan oo walxo biyo-ku-milme ah lagana helo crystals, glasses, powder, ama milan biyoodyo ku milma silica iyo sodium carbonate ama sodium hydroxide, sida:

1) sodium orthosilicate, wirqe cusbada oo kale ah Na4SiO4 ama 2Na2O.SiO2 oo ah iskudar sodium metasilicate ku jirto sodium hydroxide.

2) sodium metasilicate, wirqe cusbo Na2SiO3 ama Na2O.SiO2 oo oomane (anhydrous) ama hydrated.

3) sodium sesquisilicate, cusbo u dhexaysa sodium orthosilicate iyo sodium metasilicate waxyaalo hawlo culus lagu nadiifiyo.

4) water glass.

water glass n. chemistry iskudhis xambaarsan sodium oxide (Na2O) iyo silica (silicon dioxide, SiO2) oo sameeya quraarad adke oo biyo ku milanta.

sodium sulfate n. chemistry cusbo kharaar (bitter sulfate) Na2SO4 loona isticmaalo waxyaalo wax lagu nafiiyo (detergents). Barbardhig Glauber’s salt.

sodium thiosulfate n. chemistry cusbo wiriqda oo sayaxnuug ah (hygroscopic crystalline) astaan kiimiko Na2S2O3, loona adeegto iskudar kiimkooyin kaalmeeya sawir-caddayn (photographic fixing agent) ama kaalmeeye warankiilo (bleaching agent). kale loogu yeeraa fixer, hypo.

fixer (‘fiksar) n. 1 kabe; xirxire; hagaaje. 2 dhexdhexaadiye, siiba qof. e.g. He used to be the president's foreign affairs fixer. 3 milan (solution) ah sodium thiosulfate.

solid-state adj. chemistry waji adke; xaalad walax ceshato qaabkeed (shape) iyo xajmigeed (density) markaan la xaddidin (not confined).

colloidal solution n. chemistry milan calwan; milan walxo yaryar oo aan qasmin ay ku jiraan oo dhex mirurifleeyaan.

space lattice n. chemistry dululaati raso; qaab saf dhibcood ay muujiyaan walxo, sida atoms, ions, ama molecules qaab saddex-wajile (three dimensional) loogu raseeyay meel.

specific gravity n. cufisjiidad gaar ahaaneed; walax cabbirkeed xajmi oo la barbardhigo xajmi biyood; formula specific gravity = density of the objet/density of water = Pobject/PH2O.

specific heat n. chemistry kulqaad gaareed; inta kulayl looga baahanyahay in uu kor u qaadaado herkul hal gram ee walax hal degree ee Celsius (oC).

spectroscopy (ispek’taraaskapii) n. 1 jeegaan barasho; hab la adeegto spectroscope ama spectrometer. 2 soo saar iyo darsid jeegaan (spectra).

spectrometer (ispek’taamadhar) n. qalab lagu cabbiro baacyohireed (wavelengths) ee iftiin jeegaan (light spectra). -spectrometric (ˌispektara’metrik) adv.; -spectrometry (ispek’taraamatarii) n.

spectroscope (‘ispektara,skawp) n. qalab aqoonyahanno ku kala saaraan samayska kiimiko ee iftiin muuqda. –spectroscopic (ˌispektara’skaapik) adj.; –spectroscopically (ˌispektara’skaapiklii) adv.; –spectroscopist (ispek’taraaskapisti) n.

spontaneous ignition n. gubasho iskeed u timaadda. kale loogu yeeraa spontaneous combustion.

spontaneous combustion n. eeg spontaneous ignition.

understatement (ˌandar’isteytmanti) n., pl. understatements 1 shay la xaqiro ama hoos looga dhigo mudankiis. 2 hadal aan dhammayn ama ceeriin ah; wax aan la wada sheegin oo kas loo qoriyo xog looga baahnaa. e.g. He is a good teacher, but also master of the understatement.

meiosis (maay’awsas) n. 1 shay la xaqiro ama hoos loo dhigo mudankiisa: understatement. 2 cytology qaybsan unug laba hidda-side unug (diploid) leh oo afar hidda-side (haploid) unugyo taranside (gametes) noqoda. e.g. The meiosis is a process of cell division. Barbardhig mitosis. -meiotic (maay’aadhik) adj.; -meiotically (maay’aadhiklii) adv.

interphase (‘intar,fayz) adj. chemistry inta u dhaxaysa laba wax dhammaadka mid iyo mid kale bilawgiis.                                                                    -n. taran unug inta u dhexaysa labada isdaba joog (miotic ama meiotic) ee qaybsankiisa.

stearic acid (istii’eerik ‘aasadh) n. chemistry xayr cad oo dareersan, lehna iskudhis kiimiko C18H36O2 lagana helo dareere xayr adag.

stearin (istiiriyan) n. dareere xaryr jilicsan ama wax u eg oo laga helo xoolo iyo dhir, loona adeegto samaynta saabuun, shumac, iyo caag.

stereochemistry (,isteeriyaw’kemastarii) n. 1 laan ka mid ah chemistry oo gooni u eegta isku habaynta atoms iyo kooxaynta maalikiyuullo (molecules).

2 habayn gooni ah ee atoms iyo kooxaynta maalikiyuullo (molecules) iyo xariirkooda kala dhexeeya iskudhisyo (compounds). –stereochemical (ˌisteriyaw’kemikal) adj.

stibium (ˈistibiyam) n. eeg antimony.

strontium acetate n. chemistry mid kasta oo ka mid ah dhawr iskudhisyo oo aan ku milmin biyo (insoluble water) oo qaabeeya acetic acid, anhydride of acetic acid, iyo sulfuric acid.

structural formula styrene n. chemistry dhis naanays maalikiyuul styrene; styrene astaanteed kiimiko  C8H8, laakiin dhismaheed qaaciido (structural formula) CH2 = CHC6H5, aad bayna adeegsiga ganacsi ugu faa’iido badantahay, sida vinyl —iskudhisyo orgaanik ah (organic compounds) oo maalikiyuulladdu xambarsanyihiin (double bond) oo u dhaxaysa laba carbon atoms.

vinyl (‘vaaynal) n. chemistry 1 kaaftoon kalyaale (monovalent) radical CH2 = CH ka yimid ethylene oo laga saaray hal hydrogen atom. 2 iskudhis polymer ama walaxo laga sameeyay polymer. –vinylic (aay’nilik) adj.

substituent (sab’istijawanti) n. chemistry barobixiye; atom ama koox baddasha atom kale ama maalikiyuul kooxeed. -substituent adj.

substitution reaction n. chemistry falgal barabixin;

 falgal koox hawleed (functional group) oo hal iskudhis kiimiko ah laguna baddalo koox kale.

sucrose (ˈsuu,kraws) n. chemistry sonkor wiriqda oo macaan, lahna astaan kiimiko C12H22O11, dabeeciyanna looga helo dhir, qasab ama buruq-macaan (sugar ace or sugar beets).

dibasic (,dhaay’beysik) n. chemistry wata laba hydrogen atoms oo la baddalikaro —waxaa loo isticmaalaa acids.

sulfuric acid n. chemistry astaan kiimiko H2SO4 ahna sayaxnuug (hygroscopic) iyo walxo oxidizing ah, waana macdan wax daxaleeysa oo aashito aad ah ku jirto (strong acidic nature and is corrosive). kale loogu yeeraa mattling acid ama oil of vitriol.

superconductivity (,supar,kaan,dhek’tivatii) n. chemistry  gudbin sare; awood waxyaalo qaarkood ay ku gudbinkaraan qulqul kaah oo toos ah caabbi la’aan (zero resistance).

supernatant (,supar’neytanti) n. chemistry labeen; heen; xargag; xuub dulfuula dareere. e.g. The supernatant was collected and saved in a cool place. –supernatant adj.

superoxide (,suupar’aaksaaydh) n. chemistry ogsaaydh sare; kaaftoonyaale aaniyon (monovalent anion) O2− ama iskudhiskeeda xambaarsan (compound containing it); sida potassium superoxide KO2.

supersaturation (,suupar,saaja’reyshan) n. dhereg dhaaf; xaalad dharagdhaaf (supersaturated).

supersaturated (,suupar’saaja,reydhid) adj. chemistry milan xambaarsan in ka badan intii ugu sarraysa ee milme oo awoodda lagu milo heerkul aad u qaybaw. e.g. Supersaturated solutions.

surface chemistry n. kemistari duleed; laan ka mid ah chemistry oo gooni u eegta waxyaalaha duleedka ah iyo isbaddalka kiimiko ee dhaca duleedyada iyo meelaha ay ka kulmaan (interface).

elastic membrane n. xuub ama tahar jiidmata.

surface tension n. chemistry gigsanaan oogeed; dusha dareere oo muujiya sidii in uu yahay xuub ama tahar jiidmata (stretched elastic membrane).

tantalum(V) chloride n. also tantalum pentachloride chemistry iskudhis orgaanik ma’ahe ah lehna astaan kiimiko TaCl5; waana budo cad inta badanna waxbaa lagu bilaabaa.

optical glass n. quraarad bikaaco; aad saafi u ah oo laga sameeyo muraayadaha aragga (lenses).

tantalum oxide n. wirqe leh shan oxygen (pentoxide) astaan kiimiko Ta2O5.

ignition temperature n. or ignition point heerkul birin (shidid); heerkulka ugu hooseeya ee shay ku bilaabikaro gubasho. Barbardhig fire point. kale loogu yeeraa autogenous ignition temperature.

tertiary education n. waxbarasho heer kulleejo ama jaamacadeed (college or university).

potting compound n. iskudhis milan oo lagu weeleeyo gudaha shay koronto ku shaqeeya si uu u ilaaliyo qoyaan ama qabashada danabka qof.

tertiary color n. midab lagu helay isku darka laba midab oo midabyada labaad (secondary colors); midabyada labaad waa (mixture of blue and green), magenta (a mixture of blue and red), iyo yellow (mixture of green and red).

tertiary compound n. chemistry iskudhis saddex-curiye; waxaa loo adeegtaa chemistariga orgaanik si loogu kala sooco dhawr nooc oo iskudhisyood, sida: alcohols, alkyl halides, amines, ama reactive.

tertiary alcohol n. chemistry aalkahool saddexaad;

aalkolo (alcohol) lagu tiriyo group ≡COH oo ka kooban carbon atom ku dhaggan hydroxyl group oo saddexddiisa kaaftoon (three valences) oo kale ku xariirsanyihiin carbon atoms xariirka ama wareegga (chain or ring).

tetragonal system n. hab wirqe (crystal system) leeyahay saddex dhidib (three axes) oo xagalo qumman ah (right angles) ee labada dhidib dhinacayadood (the two lateral axes) ay isle’egyihiin.

 

test-tube (‘testi,tiyuub) adj. eeg in vitro-n. test tube dhuun hubsasho.

tetragonal (te’traaganal) adj. afargeesle wiriqle ah. –tetragonally (te’traaganal) adv.

tetrose (‘te,traws) n. chemistry mid kasta oo ah bahda monosaccharides C4H8O4 (as erythrose)  oo wata afar carbon atoms.

thermal decomposition n. chemistry kul-kalabax; hab kiimikaad. eeg heat of decomposition.

heat of decomposition n. chemistry kalabax kululayn; tusaale caadi ah ee falgal ku kalabaxa kulaylin, sida CaCO3 → CaO + CO2. Marka uu kululaado, calcium carbonate waxa uu u kalabaxaa (decomposes) calcium oxide iyo carbon dioxide.

thermochemistry (,tharmaw’kemastari) n. laan ka tirsan chemistry oo gooni u eegta kulayl gudaha ah ee ka dhexeeya falgal kiimiko ama xaaladda isbaddalkooda qaab ahaaneed. -thermochemical (ˌtharmaw’kemikal) adj.; -thermochemist (ˌtharmaw’kemisti) n.

thermolysis (,thar’maalasas) n., pl. thermolyses (ˌthar’maala,siiz) kul-kalajabis; kulayl kala firdhiya, siiba jir noole. 2 kalabax kululayn (decomposition by heat). –thermolytic (ˌtharma’lidhik) adj.

toluene (‘taalya,wiin) n. chemistry dareere saafi ah oo aan lahayn midab oo sida benzene u soo ura; lehna astaan kiimiko C6H5CH3; waa iskudhis dabiici ah oo ka yimaada batrool (petroleum).

trans (‘taraaniz) adj. kaladhan; horgaleyaal (prefixes) "cis" iyo "trans" ka yimid Latin "this side of" iyo "the other side of", “dhinacaan” iyo “dhinaca kale”, siday u kala horreeyaan; xagga chemistry, cis waxay muujisaa kooxo iskudhisyo (substituents) isku dhinac sallax (plane) ah, marka trans qaadato kuwa dhinaca lidka (transverse) ah.

transition metal n. chemistry curiyayaal kalaguur; mid kasta oo ka mid ah curiyayaal bir ah oo kala duwan (various metallic elements), sida: chromium, iron, iyo nickel oo leh kaaftoon electrons oo laba wareeg ku jira (valence electrons in two shells) inta ay hal ku jirilahaayeen. kale loogu yeeraa transition element.

transition point n. bar wajiyo kala duwan ee walax ay ka wada jirikaraan si esle’eg. kale loogu yeeraa inversion point.

transition point n. eeg transition point.

transition temperature n. chemistry heerkul kalaguur; heerkul walaxi iskugu badasho hal heer wirqe (one crystal state (allotrope) heer wirqe kale.

triple point n. bar saddexley; xaalad heerkul iyo cadaadis (pressure) wajiyada (phases) ay ku jiraan neefo (gaseous), dareere (liquid), iyo adke (solid) uuna ahaan karo mid isku dheellitiran (equilibrium).

maladroit (,maala’darooyt) adj. aan lahayn xirfad ama xeeldheeri; aan ahayn xariif. e.g. And so much unlike the previous administration, the new government is maladroit at handling simple foreign issues. –maladroitly adv.;

unavailable energy n. tamar aan la helikarin; tamar (energy) aan wax shaqo ah qabankarin xaaladaha markaas lagu jiro. Barbardhig available energy, degradation of energy, entropy.  

available energy n. physics qayb ka mid ah tamar (energy) meel ama hab uga jirta xaalad shaqo la qabankaro. Barbardhig degradation of energy, entropy, unavailable energy.

degradation of energy n. tamar aan shaqo qabankarin xaalado markaas jira. Barbardhig conservation of energy, dissipation of energy.

dissipation of energy n. hab isqaboojin ee hawo caadi ah (open air) oo tamar (energy) noqoto wax aan la helikarin iyo wax aan dib loo celinkarin (unavailable and irrecoverable) qaab ahaan. Barbardhig conservation of energy, degradation of energy.

conservation of energy n. tamar (energy) aan la abuurin lana burburin laakin qaababkeedii isbaddaleen, sida potential to kinetic to thermal energy.

uncertainty principle n. heer hubid la’aan;

madhicikarto in iskumar (simultaneously) lakala garto ama sax loo arko meesha iyo dhaqaaqa uu kujiro saxar ama (electron). kale loogu yeeraa Heisenberg uncertainty principle.

Heisenberg uncertainty principle n. eeg uncertainty principle.

valence band n. heer tabareed ugu hoosaysa electrons, taas oo ka dhigan in uu wada buuxiyay ama qaar buuxshay electrons kii. Barbardhig conduction band.

conduction band n. lid gudbineed; heer tabareed ugu sarraysa electrons, taas oo ka dhigan ama waa eber ama qaar baa la buuxshay electrons kii. Barbardhig valence band.

valence electron n. elektaroon kaaftoon; hal electron ama ka badan, waxayna ku wareegaan wareegga sare (valence shell) ee atom.

Van der Waals forces n. xoogag Van der Waals; xoogag tamardaran atoms iyo maalikiyuullo (molecules) oo isa soo jiita una keenta isweydaarsi togan ama taban (positive or negative) walxaha (particles) kale ee jooga meesha.

vapor pressure n. cadaadis uumi; caadis ka abuurmay uumi dareere (ama adke) ee dusha dareere (surface of the liquid).

Vital force n. xoog nololeed; xoog ku jira noole iyo unugyo nool; élan vital.

volumetric analysis n. mug saafid; hab lagu baaro kiimiko ayada oo lagu saleeyay cabbir mug falgalka milanno (volumes of reaction in solutions).

washing soda n. chemistry soodo mayrid;

iskudhis kiimiko (chemical compound) lehna astaan kiimiko Na₂CO₃, waana cusbo carbonic acid ah. kale loogu yeeraa sodium carbonate.

sodium carbonate n. iskudhis noole ma-ahe (inorganic compound) lehna aastaan kiimiko Na 2CO 3 noocyadiisa oo dhan waa caddaan aan lahayn ur, kuna milma biyo.

water gas n. neef biyood; iskudar (mixture of CO + H2) neefo holca oo sun ah, kana kooban carbon monoxide iyo hydrogen. 

water hard n. biyo adag; biyo xambaarsan cusbada calcium iyo magnesium.

water of crystallization noun phrase biyo wiriqayn; tiro biyood maalikiyuullo (molecules) ku jira unug cusbo; waxaa kale oo la orankaraa maalikiyuullo biyood qaabeeya qayb ka mid ah dhisme wirqe (structure of crystal).

water-soluble oil n. saliid biyo ku milanta.

water softening n. biyo fududayn; hab biyo looga saaro cusbada calcium iyo magnesium oo biyaha cusleeya.

constituent atoms n. curiye dhan (all elements) waxay ka koobanyihiin protons, neutrons iyo electrons; protons and neutrons waxaa la isku dhahaa (nucleons) waxayna ku jiraan bu’da atoms (nucleus of atoms).

water vapor n. uumi biyood; markii biyo noqdaan heer neefeed, kiimiko ahaanna waxaa lagu muujiyaa H2O (g); waxayna u muuqdaan, ceeryaamo, dhado, daruur, ama uumi ahaan.

molecular weight n. abbr. MW culays maalikiyuul; wadarta cufaf atom (atomic masses) ee dhammaan atoms-yada ku jira maalikiyuul (molecule); tusaale: culaabta maalikiyuul biyo, watana laba atoms oo hydrogen iyo hal atom oxygen, waa: (2 + 16) = 18; kana timid: hydrogen has an atomic weight of 1, and oxygen's is 16.

stoichiometry (ˌistowiki’yaamatrii) n. laan ka mid ah chemistry oo gooni u eegta tirada falgalayaal (reactants) iyo waxyaalaha la xariira falgal kiimiko (chemical reaction); erayga “stoichiometry” ka yimid Greek “stoikhein” curiye (element), iyo “metron” cabbir (measure).

Weldon process n. chemistry hab Weldon;

hab uu hormarshay Walter Weldon, 1870 in dib loo falgalshay (reacted) manganese dioxide (MnO2) wadata hydrochloric acid (HCl) si loo helo chlorine (Cl).

wettability (,weedha’biladhii) n. qoyaan karid; awood dareere ku qooynkaro dusha adke (solid surface).

whale oil n. saliid nibiri; saliid cad oo bunni (brown) isku badasha lagana helo xayr nibiri oo lagu adkeeyo biro, laguna magdiyo saan (leather), saabuun iyo shumacyana laga samaysto. kale loogu yeeraa train oil.

train oil n. saliid laga helo biyo-ku-nool, sida nibiri, qubo, kalluun, iwm.

white lead n. budo cad oo ay ku jirto lead carbonate iyo lead hydroxide, astaan kiimiko 2PbCO3·Pb(OH)2, inta badanna loo isticmaalo rinjiyo (paints).

white metal n. bir cad; biraha cad waxaa ka mid ah antimony, tin, lead, cadmium, bismuth, iyo zinc (qaarkood baana sun ah).

wood alcohol n. alkolo geed; eeg methanol.

xanthate (‘zaan,theyt) n. chemistry cusubo ama ester oo ah nooc kasta ee thio acids C3H6OS2.

thi- comb. form or thio- xambaarsan sulfur: thiamine.

thio acid (‘thaayaw ‘aasadh) n. qayb ka mid ah acid ama maalikiyuulka oxygen atoms ku jira oo dhan oo lagu baddalay sulfur atoms.

xanthic (‘zaanthik) adj. 1 la xariira ama noqda midab hurdi (yellow) ah. 2 ubax leh midab hurdi (yellow) ah.

xanthic acid n. chemistry thio acid C2H5OCSSH saliidaysan oo aan lahayn midab, loona helo qaab ahaan cusbada potassium oo la falgashay potassium ethoxide, ayna la jirto carbon disulfide.

cryptoxanthin (,kirpta’zaanthan) n. casaan wirqe oo alcohol hurdi ah, astaan kiimiko C40H55OH taas oo laga helo dhir badan, sida galleyda hurdiga ah, papaya, ukun iyo subag, kaas oo iskudhiska kiimiko ka keenay (precursor) vitamin A.

zeaxanthin (,ziiya’zaanthan) n. casaan wirqe oo alcohol hurdi ah C40H56O2 lagana helo khudaar iyo fruits (sida kiwifruit iyo spinach) iyo ukun (egg yolks).

xanthin (zaanthiin) n. midab hurdi ah (sida cryptoxanthin ama zeaxanthin) oo ku milma alcohol.

xanthine (‘zaan,thiin) n. iskudhis caadi ah oo tabardaran (feebly) nitrogenous compound  C5H4N4O2 oo laga helo kaadi, dhiig, dhir iyo xoolaha qaarkood.

 

biphenyl (,baay’fenal) n. hydrocarbon carfa (aromatic), lana adeegto kaligi ama la raaciyo diphenyl oo ah hoor kulayl-gudbiye (heat-transfer fluid), astaan kiimiko C6H5C6H5.

xenyl (‘zenal) n. hal kaaftoonle (univalent) radical C6H5C6H4− kana yimid biphenyl.

x-radiation (,eekis,reydi’yeyshan) n. kaahfalid-x; kaah birlabdanabeed (electromagnetic) oo leh baacyohireed (wavelengths) oo aad u gaaban.

dimethylbenzene n. eeg xylene.

xylene (‘zaay,liin) n. iskudhis kiimiko noole (organic chemical compound); saddex nooc ayaa jira (ortho, meta-, and para-xylene) lana isku wada dhaho xylol.

xylol (ˈzaay,lool) n. eeg xylene.

phenolic resin n. iskudhis ka kooban phenol iyo formaldehyde oo abuura maalikiyuullo (molecules) aad isku haysta.

phenolic (fi’nawlik) adj. 1 la xariira ama dabeecad phenol leh. 2 xamabaarsan ama ka yimid phenol.

xylenol (‘zaaynla,nool) n. chemistry mid kasta oo ka mid lixda isomeric phenols C8H10O ama isku darkooda ka yimid xylenes, laga helo dhuxul  (coal tar), lagana sameeyo caag (phenolic resins) iyo jeermisdilayaasha. Barbardhig chloroxylenol.

chloroxylenol (ˌkalawraw’zaayla,nool) n. mid kasta oo ka mid ah dhawr nooc oo ka yimid xylenols, siiba C8H9ClO loona isticmaalo ka hortagga jeerimis (antiseptic) iyo kan faafaba (germicide).

zeolite (‘ziiya,laayt) n. mid kasta oo ka mid silicates xambaarsan biyo kala duwan isna-shabbaha (analogous), sida: analcime, chabazite, clinoptilolite, erionite, ferrierite, heulandite, laumontite, mordenite, iyo phillipsite. -zeolitic (ˌziiya’lidhik) adj.

aluminosilicate (a,luumanaw’sila,keyt) n. iskudar silicate iyo aluminate.

aluminate (a’luumanat) n. iskudhis alumina iyo oxide bireed (metallic oxide); hal ama ka badan aluminum iyo hal ama ka badan oxygen atoms.

coltan (‘kawl,taan) n. macdan dhagax madaw dilan (dull black) oo qayme leh, kana kooban iskudar columbite iyo tantalite: columbite-tantalite.

klaxon (‘kalaaksan) n. codbaahiye (horn) danab ku shaqeeya. e.g. After one hour, the fire klaxon sounded again.

bunkum (‘bangkam) n. or buncombe hadal cantarbaqash ah: nonsense.

gargoyle (‘gaar,gowyal) n. sibaab; sawir fool xun oo ama noole kale ah oo dhagax ka qoran ama sharraxaad kele. -gargoyled (ˈgaar,goyldh) adj.

orotund (‘oora,tandh) adj. 1 hadal cad, siiba mid qeexan, adag, lana fahmo. 2 pompous. -orotundity (ˌoora’tendhadhii) n.

chromatic aberration n. haydh midabeed; jeegaan fallaaro oo midabku midkood ka tago.

spherical aberration n. haydh kubbadeed; fallaaro iftiin qaybtood dibadda xigta, iftiinkuna kuma soo wada ururo meel qur ah (same focus), sida qaybta dhexe.

expansivity (ek,espaan’sivadhii) n. xaalad ama tayo fidis. e.g. Several thermal expansivity had been generated.

coefficient of expansion n. weheliye fidid; saami (ration) koror dherer, bed (area), ama mug (volume) ee degree uu kordhiyay heerkul (rise in temperature) dherer, bed (area), iyo mug (valume), inta badan 0° C. kale loogu yeeraa expansivity.

absolute expansion n. fidid sugan.

absolute humidity n. suyuc sugan; tiro uumi biyaha hawada ku jira cufkii halbeeg ee hawo (unit volume of air). Barbardhig relative humidity.

relative humidity n. saami uumiga biyo inta uga jirta hawada ee inteeda suurtagal ah oo ugu badan isku heerkul.

absolute magnitude n. laxaad sugan; awoodda ilays ee xiddig ama meere (celestial object) la muuqdo markii laga jeedaaliyo (absolute magnitude) fogaan jirta 10 parsecs (32.6 light-years).

absolute permittivity n. saamaxaad sugan; inta badan waxaa la dhahaa permittivity (ε) waxaana la siiyaa xaraf Greek oo ah ε (epsilon), waana cabbirka kala qaybsanka danabka magudbiye (electric polarizability of a dielectric).

absolute temperature n. heerkul sugan;

 heerkul lagu cabbiray miisaan sugan (absolute scale) —symbol T

absolute unit n. 1 physics halbeeg sugan; halbeeg dherer (length), cuf (mass), iyo waqti (time). 2 qof ama shay aad u weyn.

absorptance (ab’soortanis) n. physics nuugitaanimo; saamiga kaah (radiant) ama burqad iftiimeed (luminous flux) ee uu dhuuqay jir ama qalfoof uu ku dulburqaday.

absorption band n. physics liidad nuugideed; liil madaw ee jeegaan wax dhuuqda ah. kale loogu yeeraa absorption line.

absorption line n. physics liil madaw ee jeegaan wax dhuuqda ah. kale loogu yeeraa absorption band.

absorption chemical n. physics nuugis kiimikeed; hab atoms ama maalikiyuullo (molecules) ay dhex galaan neef (gas), dareere (liquid), ama walax adke ayna ka qaataan mug (volume).

absorption coefficient n. physics weheliye nuugeed; inta la dhuuqay iftiin ee shay dhumucdiis (thickness) la cayimay; dhuuqistu waxay fansaar (function) la tahay iftiin midabkiis (the color of light).

absorption of radiation n. physics kaah nuugeed; hab haak birlabdanabeed ee shay uu u baddalay shaygaas nooc kale oo haak ama uu keeno dhaqsaha kaah la dhaho dhuuqis.

absorption spectrum n. physics jeegaan nuugeed;

jeegaan kaahdanabeed (electromagnetic) taas oo yaraysa awoodda kaah ee baacyohireed (wavelengths) cayiman ama masaafo hirdhereryo wax nuuga oo ku cad liilal ama xarriiqo madaw (dark lines or bands).

absorptivity (ab,soorp’tivadhii) n., pl. absorptivities  physics nuugitaan; awood shay ama dul (material or surface) wax ku dhuuqikarto, sida dareere ama wax kale; ama dhuuqdo oo hayso kul (heat) ama tamar (energy).

abundance chemical n. physics helitaan kiimikaad; cabbiris saxnaanta curiyayaal kiimiko oo dhan (chemical elements) ee xariir kala dhexeeyo  curiyayaal kale oo dhan.

cosmic abundance of elements n. physics helitaan cireed; tirada atoms ee curiyayaal (atoms of elements) laga helay xiddigo iyo daruuro neef ah (clouds of gas) ee samadeenna (galaxy).

natural abundance n. physics helitaan dabiiciyeed;

curiyayaal kiimiko (chemical elements) oo haysta isotopes tirobadan oo si dabeeciyan ah looga helo meere (planet).

acceleration of gravity n. physics karaar cuf isjiidad; karaar shay soo dhacaya oo cufjiidad dhulka soo jiitay (Earth’s gravitational); lana mid ah 9.806 m (32.16 ft) per second. kale loogu yeeraa acceleration of free fall, g.

uniformly accelerated rectilinear motion n. abbr. UARM physics karaar xarriiqtoos; socod uu ku jiro shay dhaqaaqaya ee ku socda xarriiq toosan iyo karaar madoorsoome (constant acceleration).

acceleration curvilinear n. physics karaar xarriiqxood; inta badan waa wadajir karaar istaabasho (tangential acceleration) iyo karaar dhexda raaca (centripetal acceleration).

centripetal acceleration n. shay kasta oo ku dhexwareega goobo xawaare joogto ah.

uniform circular motion n. shay kasta oo ku wareega goobo xawaare joogto ah (constant speed), sida gacan saacad, daqiiqad, ama second.

accepter level n. physics heer guddoome; markii heerkaan lagu jiro ee aan electrons ka qabygalin isku xirmadka (antibonding) kiimikada heerka guddoonku wuu yaraadaa, falgalka kiimiko ayaana dhaca, iskudhis cusubna wuu dhashaa.

antibonding (,aanii’baandhing) adj. diida isku xirmadka ka dhexeeya atoms.

achromatic (,aakra’maadhik) adj. midab ka ah xor; dira (emit), gudbiya (transmit), ama aqbala (receive) iftiin ayada oo aan loo kala saarin midabyo. –achromatically (ˌaakra’maadhiklii) adv.; -achromatism (ˌeey’krawma,tiizam) n.; -achromatize (ˌee’krawma,taayz) transitive verb.

achromatic colors n. physics midabyo-haydh;

midabyo dhexdexaad ah (neutral colors) madaw (black), caddaan (white) iyo bey (gray).

achromatic fringe n. physics hariiro-haydh; if faraq (fringe) ah oo rugtiisu ka baxsantahay baac-hireed (wavelength) ifka la isticmaalay.

magnetic equator n. xarriiq mala’awaal ah (imaginary line) oo mara dusha dhulka, barbarana la ah dhulbaraha (equator) marana baraha irbadda birlabaysanna (magnetic needle) aysan tilmaamin.

cardinal directions n. afar jiho oo waaweyn, lagana bilaabo waqooyi, bari, koofur, iyo galbeed (N, E, S, W); marka laga bilaabo waqooyi 0 degrees, bari, koofur, iyo galbeed waxaana u wada dhexeeya 90 degree.

dip needle n. or dipping needle sida irbad jiheeye caadi ah (conventional compass), laakiin intii jiif ahaan (horizontally) loo akhriyi lahaa, ayada waxaa loo akhriyaa qoton ahaan (vertically), waxaana loogu safraa cirifyada waqooyi ama koofureed.

magnetic inclination n. waxaa la orankaraa magnetic dip ama dip angel, xagal ka samaysmatay xarriiqaha jiifa ee badadka birlabta dhulka; xagashaan waa kala duwantahay hadba dhulka dushiisa meeshii laga joogo.

magnetic needle n. birlab irbadeed oo dhex walhata jiheeye (compass) tilmaantana cirifk birlabeed ee dhulka.

magnetic meridian n. xarriiq mala’awaal ah oo mara dhusha dhulka oo wareeg weyn ku mara waqooyiga iyo koofurta cirifyada birlabeed (magnetic poles).

aclinic line n. physics birlab-badhe; xarriiq mala’awaal ah (imaginary line) oo mara dusha dhulka barbarrana la ah dhulbaraha (equator). Barbardhig agonic line, isoclinic line. kale loogu yeeraa magnetic equator.

pink noise n. cod lagu qariyo qaylooyin aan loo baahnayn ee bii’addaas.

black noise n. juuqla’; meel aan lahayn shanqar.

white noise n. 1 isku milan hirar codeed oo kala duwan, lehan dhawaaqyo kala fog. 2 buuq, qaylo, iyo sawaxan.

acoustic perfume n. or acoustical perfume meel deggan oo shanqaro dabacsan gadaal ka yeerayaan.

 

acoustic absorption n. nuugid jabaqeed;

marka shay (object) tamar jabaq (sound energy) ay ku dhacdo, nuuga inta uu dalfin lahaa; qayb ka mid ah tamrta la nuugay, waxayna noqotaa kul (heat) qaarka kalana shaygaas ayaa laqa.

acoustic filter n. kala-reebe jabaqeed; wax uu saafiyeelaa jabaqda aan loo bahnayn ee walhanaysa (oscillations).

acoustic grating n. isxoqis jabaqeed; samayn cod isxoqis ama gariir.

acoustic impedance n. xayir jabaqeed; waxaa lagu qeexaa inta caabbi ay la kulanto dhud cod-sare (ultrasound beam) marka ay shay dhexmarayso.

active component n. xibin kacsan; qayb ka mid ah mareeg (circuit) oo ku tiirsan awood didadda ah in ay xukunto ama wax ka badasho baaqyada kaaheed (electrical signals).

active current n. qulqul kacsan; awood danab oo la wada isticmaalo.

cohesive force n. xoog isjiidad; xoog iskuxirmad oo ka dhexeeya maalikiyuullo (molecules) isku nooc.

aerial array n. teed anteeno; dhawr anteeno (antenna) oo leh xargo barbarro (parallel wire) ah oo wax dira ama qabta (transmit or receive).

loop antenna n. or loop aerial qool anteena; anteena raadiyaw (radio antenna) ka kooban galaw wareegsan iyo fiilo (wire).

Johnson noise n. eeg thermal noise.

radio receiver n. qalab electronic oo qabta (receive) hirar raadiyo una baddala xog la anafacsankaro.  

thermal noise n. tashwiish (buuq) raadiye soo qabto oo ay keento kulayka electrons ku jira mareeg (circuit) iyo dhuumo (tubes).

airfoil (,eer’fooyal) n. British aerofoil wax u samaysan qaab dayaarad baalkeed oo loo qaabeeyay in uu caawiyo xoog soo noqda (reaction force) ee hawada ka hor imaanaysa dhaqaaqa.

aerometer (eer’aamadhar) n. hawobeeg; qalab lagu xaqiijiyo culaab ama xajmi (density) hawo ama neefo kale (other gases).

afterheat n. haraa kul; kulayl hara marka la damiyo nuclear reactor.

afterimage (‘aaftar,imij) n., pl. afterimages 1 haraa hummaag; ka sii muuqadka indhaha hummaag tagtay. 2 xasuus maskax ku harta oo sii muuqata.

air capacitor n. madhxiye hawo; qalab kaydiya danab oo isticmaala hawo.

air-core transformer n. dooriye hawa-dhuux; waxaa loo qaabeeyay gudbinta ququlyo rakaad-raadiyo (radio-frequency currents).

airglow (‘eer,gulaw) n. also nightglow ilays hawo;

iftiin naxuusay oo ka yimid xiddigaha hawada sare.

ground speed n. xawaaraha gudban (horizontal) ee dayaarad oo xariir la leh oogada dhulka; Airspeed = Ground Speed - Wind Speed. Barbardhig airspeed.

alpha decay n. mataatax alfa; kaahfal mataatax (radioactive decay) ee bu’da atom (atomic nucleus) oo siidaysa saxarka alpha (alpha particle).

alpha particle n. saxar alfa; ka kooban saxarro ka samaysan laba protons iyo laba neutrons oo aad iskugu dhaggan, waxayna daayaan qaarkood kaahfal isbeddalo (radioactive transformations). kale loogu yeeraa alpha, alpha radiation, alpha ray.

alpha rays n. fallaraha alfa; eeg alpha particle.

alpha ray spectrum n. jeegaan fallaaraha alfa.

alternating current bridge n. AC bridges kaabad qulqul talantaaliye (kaabad QT); waxaa lagu cabbiraa mareeg danab voltage keed (inductance) iyo caabbi (resistance).

inductance (in’dhektanis) n. physics mareeg danab oo voltage uu keeno u baddalista badad danabeed (magnetic field).

 

ampere balance (‘aam,pir) n. also current balance or Kelvin balance miisaan ampere; qalab danab oo lagu cabbiro saxnaanta halbeeg danab qulquleed (unit of electric current) ee ampere.

Ampere's law n. xeerk Ampere; badad danabeed (magnetic field) ee uu abuuray qulqul danab (electric current) waxa uuna saamigal (proportional) la yahay qiyaasta (size) qulqulkaas danab (electric current), oo ay lajirto saamigal madoosoome (constant of proportionality) oo la mid ah siinta meel xor ah. ∮→B. →dl = μ0∑i meesha i tahay wadar qulqullo ku xiran wareegga (enclosed currents by the loop). integral form of the law is: ∮Bds = μ0I; meesha μ0 tahay permeability of free space iyo ‘i’ tahay qulqul (current).

constant of proportionality n. saami toos laba tirooyin uga dhexeeya; laba waxood waa saami toos ah (directly proportional) marka ay wada kordhaan ama wada dhimmaan isku dhaqaaq (rate).

ampere-turn (‘aam,pir’tarn) n. duub ampere; maxsuul inta jeer ee duub (coil) wareegay iyo ampere ka qulqulkiisa oo halkii wareeg xambaarsan qulqul danab oo hal ampere ah.

magnetomotive force n. abbr. MMF maxsuul qulqul iyo inta jeer ee duub (coil) ku wareegay.

amplification factor n. saami kordhineed;

saamiga tira ahaan loogu dhufankaro taas oo qaar tirooyin kordheen; waxaana lagu helaa ayada oo voltage ka baxay (output) loo qaybsho voltage ka soo galay (input): output voltage/input voltage.

aneroid (‘aana,roydh) adj. hoorlaawe ah; aan isticmaalin ama dareere ku jirin. e.g. consisting of an aneroid barometer.

 aneroid barometer n. eeg barometer.

angle of friction n. xagal islis; sallax gudban xagashiis markii shay la duldhigo, sallaxuna waxa uu bilaabaa taraar caadi a.

angle of incidence n. xagal abbaar; xagal u dhexaysa xarriiq caadi ah iyo fallaar (ray) iftiin ah.

angle of reflection n. xagal noqod; xagal u dhexaysa fallaar noqod (reflected ray) iyo mid xarriiq caadi ah.

angle of refraction n. xagasha xarriiq dalfisan la sameeyo xarriiqa caadi ah.

angular acceleration n. karaar xagleed; dhaqaaq (rate) isla badalaya keynaan (velocity) waqti halbeeg xagleed (per unit time of angular).
