angular displacement n. barabax xagleed; in wareeg ah oo la qeexay (as of a disk) ee dhidib la qeexay (a specified axis); (symbol θ, ϑ, or φ) – kale oo la dhahaa angle of rotation, rotational displacement, ama rotary displacement; formula θ = s / r; meesha θ = Angular displacement; r = Radius of curvature of path; s = Distance curved.

angular distribution n. filiq xagleed; filiqsanaan jihooyin electrons loo siidaayay habdhis kulan ee tilmaaman (specific coordinate system).

sinusoidal (ˌsaanya’soydhal) adj. qaab hireed leh; xarriiq tuur iyo godan leh. e.g. Sinusoidal waves. -sinusoidally (ˌsaayna’soydhalii) adv.

angular frequency n. summad (ω) also radial or circular frequency rakaad xagleed; sida hirkii (sinusoidal) ah; waxaa lagu cabbiraa degrees (ama radians) per second; taas oo u dhiganta soo wereegga rakaad oo lagu dhuftay 2π.

torque (‘toork) n. 1 xoog abuura shay in uu wareego; halbeeg lagu cabbiro: Newton-meter ama kgm2sec-2. 2 xoog maroojis ama wareejis.                -v. torqued; torquing wareejin; maroojin. -torquer n.

angular impulse n. gujo xagleed; xoog la gashay shay (object) waqti kaleed (period of time) ayaa la dhahaa impulse, maroojis (torque) la gashay shay waqti kaleed (period of time) ayaa la dhahaa angular impulse; xisaab ahaan: Force (F) lagu dhuftay waqti (t) oo isla baddalaya waqti, torque (tau) lagu dhuftay waqtiga is baddalay.

anisotropic (,aa,naysa’taraapik) adj. physics waxyaalo muujiya tayo qayme kala duwan leh, markii laga cabbiro dhidib (axes) jihooyinkiis kala duwan; si kale aan u sheegno: qaab ahaan u kala baddalan jihooyin kala baddalan. –anisotropically (ˌaa,naaysa’taraapiklii) adv.; –anisotropy (ˌaa,naay’saatrapii) n.; also –anisotropism (ˌaa,naay’saatra,pizam) n.

annihilation radiation n. kaah liqid; markii kaah photon (photon radiation) abuuray saxar (particle) iyo lid-saxarkiis (antiparticle) isku dhacaan oo ayna islaqaan (annihilate).

characteristic of anode n. astaan qotintogane; qoton markii falgale dhumiyo electrons xilliga falgalka ama uu dhaco oxidation reaction.

oxidation reaction n. marka falgale (reactant) dhumiyo electrons xilliga falgalka (reaction).

anode current n. qulqul qotintogane; qulqul ku socda saxan mareegta (plate circuit) ee tuubada electron (electron tube) kaas oo la mid ah electoron ka imaanaya qotinkatogane oo u socda saxanka (from cathode to plate).

anode drop n. dhicid qotintonage.

anode load n. rar qotintogane.

anode modulation n. harbid qotintogane.

anode rays n. also positive ray ama canal ray fallaaro qotintogane; dhud (beam) ions togane oo ay sameeyeen neefo noocyo gaar ah oo laga sii daayay dhuun (tube).

saturation current n. qulqul dharagsan; ku xadidda qulqul maris ionized gas ama dhuun electron, taas oo kordhisa voltage-ka waxayna keentaa in aan wax danbe oo qulqul ah kordin (qulqul dhargay).

anomalous behavior of water n. biyo la yimid gad aan caadi ahayn.

anticathode (‘aan,taay’kaathoydh) n. 1 electrochemistry lid-qotintabane; an anode. 2 electronics yool (target) electrons ka yimid cathode ama dhuun x-ray (x-ray tube) lagu nishaabo ama lagu aadiyo.

antiparticle (‘aan,taay’paardhikal) n. lid-saxar; walax saxar ka sii yar (subatomic particle) oo u eg walax kale oo saxar ka sii yar cuf (mass) ahaan, laakiin lid ka ah danab iyo birlab ahaan, taas oo marka ay isku yimaadaan keenta inay si caadi ah isku laqaan (mutual annihilation).

antimatter (‘aan,taay’maadhar) n. lid-walax; walax ka ka kooban lid-walaxeed (antiparticles).

antinode (‘aantaay,nawdh) n. lid-guntin; hir tuurtiisa ugu sarraysa. -antinodal (ˌaantaay’nawdhal) adj.

aperture (‘aapar,jar) n. 1 dalool; dusmo; god. e.g. The snake entered the house through a narrow aperture. 2 isha sawirad iftiin ka baxo. 3 daloolka dhuun fogaan-dhaweeye (telescope).

aperture angle n. xagal duleel; xagal fogaaneed dareeme (sensor) wax ka akhrinkaro ama ka ogaankaro. kale loogu yeeraa scanning range.

scanning range n. eeg aperture angle.

aperture distortion n. qaablun; humaag (image) sawir marka qaab-muuqaalkeed saxda ah lumo oo ay noqoto qaab qallooc ama maroor ku jiro.

apparent expansion n. fidid muuqata; markii dareere kululaado, oo uu u ekaado in uu ka batay hoorkiisii hore.

apparent depth n. qoto muuqata; qoto run ah (real depth) ee taal gunta weel iyo qotada qof u muuqata (apparent depth) oo qallooca if (refraction of light) soo dhaweeyay.

apparent magnitude n. laxaad muuqda; iftiin shay muuqaalkiis qof dhulka jooga; sida qorraxda awood muuqaal (apparent magnitude) keedu waa −26.7, meesha dayax buuxa ka yahay −11. Barbardhig absolute magnitude.

arc-lamp n. laambad-qaanso; nal danab (electric lamp) oo bixiya iftiin qaanso oo leh laba qotin ifbire (two incandescent electrodes) oo ay ku xeerantahay neef (gas).

atmometer (aat’maamatar) n. uumiyawbeege; qalab lagu cabbiro dhaqsaha biyo ku uumibaxaan hawada. kale loogu yeeraa evaporimeter, evaporometer.

evaporimeter (a,vaapa’rimatar) n. also evaporometer eeg atmometer.

atmospheric circulation n. wareeg gibileed;

dhaqaaqa hawada ku wareegsan dhulka oo sheegta tamar kul (thermal energy) iyo habab roobabeed.

atmospheric convection n. islabarog gibileed; hawo kulul iyo qoyaan kor ugu baxa hawada sare, kaas oo gaara meel kasta oo dhulka ah.

atmospheric electricity n. danab gibileed; tamar birlabdanabeed ee u dhexaysa qorraxda iyo oogada dhulka oo ku lugleeyihiin daruuro, biriq, iyo neefo (gases) hawada ku jira.

atmospheric pollution n. aafow giblileed; wasakhayn hawada, siiba uuro warshadood.

atmospheric pressure n. cadaadis gibileed; hawada nagu wareegsan culaabteeda, wax kasta oo ay taabatana way ku riixdaa, inta  badanna waxaa lugu cabbiraa barometer.

atmospheric radio n. raadiyo gibileed; shanqaro ka yimaada hawda dabiiciga ah, siiba biriqda roobab oo in kabadan 3.4 millyan oo jeer ka dhacda adduunka maalintii.

atomic energy n. tamar bu’eed; tamar (energy) ka abuurmata kala bacramka bu’ atoms: nuclear energy.

atomic heat n. kul atomeed; awood kulayl ee culaab gram-atomic ee walax kasta (any element); tirada kul ee laga rabo inay qaaddo heerkul hal gram ee walax in le’eg hal degree Celsius kii. Barbardhig molecular heat.

molecular heat n. awood kulayl ee hal mole (6.022 × 10²³ units) oo walax saafi ah. Barbardhig atomic heat.

atomic orbital n. meeris atomeed; meel laga helo electron oo uu ku wareego, waana afarta nooc oo wareeg: s, p, d, iyo f.

atomic radius n. also radii gacan atomeed; guud ahaan fogaanta u dhexaysa bu’da qurub (atom) iyo wareegiisa dibadda.

atomic volume n. mug atomeed; mug hal mole ee qurub (element) buuxiyo ee heerkul caadi ah; waxaana lagu cabbiraa cubic centimeter per mole (cc/mol): atomic volume = atomic weight/density.

attenuation coefficient n. weheliye dhimid; inta kaah burqad dhudeed (radiant flux of a beam) ka yaraata marka uu ka dusayo ama dhexmarayo walax cayiman.

attenuator (a’tenya,weydhar) n. dhime; qalab

dhima awood baaq danab (electrical signal) ayada oo aan la dareemin.

audio signal n. baaq maqal; baaq danab (electrical signal) oo ka abuurma dhawaaq caadi ah ee codbaahiye (microphone) loogu baddalay tamar danab (electrical energy).

axial ratio n. saami dhidibeed; qaab dhismeed kasta oo leh laba iyo ka badan dhidib (axes), waana saamiga dherer ama lixaad (magnitude) dhidibadaas midba midka kale u yahay.

azimuth (‘aazmath) n. al-samuut (jiho); fogaan xagaleed (angular distance) kana bilaabata weqooyin ilaa koofur ee qoolaabka dhulku sameeyo. –azimuthal (ˌaaza’mathal) adj.; –azimuthally (ˌaaza’mathalii) adv.

azimuthal quantum number n. tiro quantum xagleed; tirada quantum oo lagu caddeeyay qaab xaddiga meere. Barbardhig quantum numbers,

radial quantum number n. abyoone quantum fallaared; tirada quantum oo lagu caddeeyay qaab xaddi meere. Barbardhig quantum numbers, azimuthal quantum number.

total quantum number n. tirooyin lagu caddeeyo rugta electron iyo xaririrka uu leeyahay atom. Barbardhig principal quantum number.

back electromotive force n. xoog-danabwade danbe; hab duub matoor danab uu dib u celiyo qulqul danabeed.

back focal length n. dherer kulmis danbe.

background noises n. buuq agagaareed; cod kasta oo aan ahayn midka aad dhagaysnaysid markaas.

band-pass filter n. abbr. BPF kalareeb liid-taf; qalab kala ogolaada in ay dhaafaan kali ah baaqyo (signals) rakaadyo cayiman (specific frequencies), diidana rakaadyaadaas wixii dibadda uga baxsan.

band spectrum n. jeegaan liid; kooxo liidad ah oo isku dhaw, kooxdii islehna waa isku liid.

taurine (‘too,raayn) adj. la xariira dibi: bovine.       -n. wirqe acid C2H7NO3S oo laga sameeyay cysteine iyo methionine, waxayna la mid tahay acids laakiin proteins kuma jiraan.

energy drink n. cabbitaan xambaarsan in badan oo sonkor ah, caffeine, iyo waxyaalo kale oo kiciya dareenka jir, sida taurine iyo ginseng.

ginseng (‘jiin,seng) n. 1 geed China ka baxa oo dhawr sano waara, caleentiisuna shan madax leedahay, loona isticmaalo daawo ahaan. 2 dhawr geed oo la mid ah kana baxda Waqooyiga Ameerika. 3 xididka geekaan.

bandwidth (‘baan,with) n. 1 electronics ballac liid;

rakaadyo (frequencies) la siiyo fogaan xaddidan oo wax laga diro. 2 tamar, waqti, ama awood maskaxeed ee wax lagu xallinkaro. e.g. She doesn’t have the bandwidth solve everything by herself,

beam current n. qulqul dhudeed; qulqul dhud (beam) waana karaar (accelerator) lagu qeexay, sida qulqul danab caadi ah (normal electric current).

beat frequency oscillator n. abbr. BFO walhade rakaad jiibeed.

heterodyne (‘hedhara,dhaayn) adj. la xariira laba walhade oo leh rakaad kala duwan (different frequencies) markii la isku darana sameeya jiib (beat) cusub.                                                               -v. heterodyned; heterodyning isku midayn laba raadiyo rakaad (radio frequencies), sameeyana jiib (beat) cusub.

homodyne adj. la xariira helis hir raadiyaw (radio wave) oo laga soo diray meelkale ayada oo isku rakaad (frequency) la yahay. eeg zero beat.

zero-beat reception n. qabasho jiideed; xaalad laba rakaadyo raadiyaw (radio frequencies) oo tayo ahaan la iskugu hagaajiyay oo jabaqdii loo sii yareeyay rakaad eber ah. Barbardhig homodyne.

bell jar n. gambis-dawan; quraarad qaab dawan leh oo wax lagu gambiyo ama haysa neefo (gases).

bel (beel) n. halbeeg (unit): ten decibels.

bending moment n. maroojis liiciye; xoog qalloociya shay, waxaana lagu cabbiraa: xoog × dherer (force × length).

beta (‘beydha) n. 1 xarafka labaad ee aliifba’da Greek (Greek letter β). 2 kaalin, heer, dabaqad, ama boos labaad. 2 qabyo ama hawl wali aan dhammaan.

beta particles n. saxarro beta; electrons (β-) ama positrons (β+) oo tamar iyo dheerayn aad ah leh, lagana soo tufay bu’da radionuclides oo laga soo daayay kaahfal mataatax (radioactive decay) oo la dhaho beta-decay.

beta decay n. mataatax beta; kaahfal mataatax (radioactive decay) kaas oo ah fallaar beta (beta ray) oo laga soo tufay bu’da atomic.

bias voltage n. xaglis fooltage; qulqul toos ah (DC) oo kas loo qulquliyay ama DC voltage qasdi ahaan laba barood lagu xadaday qulqul mareeg (circuit).

biconcave (,baay,kaan’keyv) adj. labagolxaale ah; laba dhinacba ka godan ama golxo ku leh. –biconcavity (ˌbaay,kaan’kaavadhii) n.

biconvex (,baay,kaan’vekis) adj. labatuuraale ah; laba dhinacba ka soo buuran ama tuur ku leh. –biconvexity (ˌbaaykan’veksadhii) n.

binding force n. xoog isuhayn; shaqo ay tahay in lagu qabto ama laga horgeeyo xoog iskuhaya shay.

blocking capacitor n. madhxiye xire; jid gooye (capacitor) qulqul toos u mara hal mareeg (circuit), kaas oo mareeg kale u ogolaada qulqulkeedu in gudbo.

bond energy n. chemistry tamar dabar; tamar (energy) inteeda laga rabo in ay ku kala jabiso maalikiyuullo (molecules) isku xirnaanta atoms kooda.

boson (‘baw,saayn) n. saxar (particle) sida photon ama meson ee tiradiisa quantum winiin (spin) tahay eber ama tiro madoorsoome (integer number). Barbardhig fermion.

fermion (‘fermi’yaan) n. saxar (particle), sida electron, proton, or neutron ee tiradiisa quantum winiin (spin) tahay kisi (odd) lagu dhuftay ½. Tusaale: laba neutrons (kiiba with spin 1/2) iyo laba protons (kiiba spin 1/2) isku dar waxay samaynkaraan helium nucleus, ama an alpha particle. Barbardhig boson. -fermionic (ˌfermii’aanik) adj.

boundary layer n. dub soohdin; xuub dareere ah oo ka dul samaysma dusha dareere maraya meel korkeed, sida baal dayuurad duulimaad ku jirta.

solipsistic (,sawlap’sistik) adj. aragti oranaysa nafi wax ma oga laakiin ayada kali ah ayaa is’og in ay jirto. -solipsistically (ˌawla’sistiklii) adv.

solipsism (‘sawlap,siizam) n. 1 philosophy aragti oraynaysa wax jira oo kali ah waa nafta ama waa la xaqiijinkara in ay jirto. 2 naf-iskumaqan (self-absorption), naf-jeclaysi; al-anaafiyah (egoism). –solipsist n.

Boyle's law (‘booyaliz ‘loo) n. xeer Boyle; cuf (mass) neef (gas) xaddidan ee heerkul joogto ah, cadaadis neef waxuu saamigal lid u yahay muggeeda (volume).

bracket series n. taxa sakallo; la muujiyaa marka kalaguur electron dhacayo ee tamar sare, oranayana (nh=5,6,7,8,9…) to nl = 4 heer tamar.

buffer circuit n. mareeg xijaab; wax kala qoqoba ama mareeg ka weeciya mid kale.

kilojoule (ˈkila,juul) n. abbr. kJ 1,000 joules; halbeeg nafaqo (nutrition) la mid ah 0.239 calorie.

calorific value n. or calorific power kulayl samaysma intii lagu gudajiro gubasho; kulaylkaas intii ka dhalatay gubasho dhan hal unug (one unit) oo shidaal kasta ah; tusaale: haddii la dhaho tamarta ku jirta kerosene waa 25000, macnaheedu waa haddii 1 kg kerosene wada gubto, waxa ay samaynayaa 2500 kilojoules oo tamar kulayl ah (heat energy).

candela (kaan’diila) n. abbr. cd halbeeg lagu cabbiro xajmi iftiin;1 candela qiyaas ahaa waxa uu la mid yahay iftiin ka yimid hal shumac (candle). kale loogu yeeraa candle.

candlepower (‘kaandal,paawar) n. also candela awood shumac; xajmi iftiin lagu muujiyay shumac (candle).

Carnot's law n. neef leh kulayl cayiman iyo cadaadis joogta ah oo laga jaray neef cayiman oo mug joogta ah leh

carrier wave n. hir-side; hir birlabdanabeed oo rakaad fudud (light frequency), kaas oo joogto u xambaarsan baaq maqallo (audio signals) meel ilaa meel kale ee oogada dhulka.

catalysis (ka’taalasas) n., pl. catalyses kalkaalis; falgal kiimiko oo lagu daray kalkaaliye si uu u caawiyo laba kiimiko wada falgalkood.

cathode-ray oscilloscope n. eeg oscilloscope.

cathode rays n. fallaaro qotintabane; saxarro (negatively charged) marka falaaraha anode ay caadi u yihiin (positively charged).

Cavendish experiment n. cabbiris cuf-isjiidad joogtaysan oo lagu saxay dheellitir nugul.

cavitate (‘kaava,teyt) v. cavitated; cavitating keenid abur hawo wata, siiba dareere burqanaya.

cavitation (,kaava’teyshan) n. xordin; hawo gasha burqad dareere.

celestial sphere n. kubbad cireed; mala’awaal (imaginary) qaab kubbadeed ah ama qoolaab ka dul muuqda meerayaal.

central force n. xoog xuduneed; xoog isasa soo jiidashada laba shay oo ku aaddan dhexda.

centrosymmetric (,sentarasa’metrik) adj. xuddun wanqar leh; wanqar leh xuddun dhexe (central point). e.g. Centrosymmetric materials/molecules.

 

centrosymmetry n. xuddun wanqar; la xariira ama leh qaab centrosymmetric.

characteristic curve n. xoog astaameed; xarriiq xoodan oo muujiya xariir ka dhexeeya laba doorsoome (two variables).

charge density n. cufnaan saldanab; inta danab (electric) uu ifinkaro meel, dherer ama ama mug ahaan (quantity of charge per unit).

chemical constants n. madoorsamayaal kiimikeed; madoorsamayaal aan qaymahoodu isbaddalin.

chemical reaction n. falgal kiimikaad; hab hal ama ka badan walxood, falgalyaal (reactants) hal ama ka badan loo baddalo walax ka duwan kuwii hore.

chemical reactivity n. falgalan kiimikaad; awood walax u leedahay in ay kiimiko ahaan walax kale kula falgasho.

chemical shift n. isbaddal kiimikaad; kala duwanaan bu’ birlab ee rakaad fasiix ah ee bu’ kale oo ay isku noocyihiin, iyo kala duwanaanta electrons.

choke coil n. duub ceeje; duub danab oo caabbi aad u yar leh, laguna ilaaliyo qulqul mareeg (AC circuit).

choke coupling n. sidkid ceeje; waxaa lagu horjoogsadaa rakaad sare (higher-frequency) marka uu gudbayo qulqul toos ah (direct current) iyo rakaadyada qulqul hoose (lower frequencies) ee qulqul AC mareegteeda danabeed (electrical circuit).

classical physics n. fiisikis qaraami;

Physics aan isticmaalin quantum ama aragtida relativity.

clinical thermometer n. kulbeege isbitaal; qalab lagu cabbiro heerkul jirka dad, kana kooban quraarad dhuuban iyo dhibic mercury (mercury bulb).

closed-circuit (‘kalawz’sarkat) adj. mareeg xiran; markii qulqul wareeg soo dhammaado.

closed shell n. heertamar buuxa; heer tamar xambaarsan tirada ugu badan ee electrons ka la ogolyahay.

coefficient of friction n. wehelliye islis; tirada cabbir islis ee ka dhexjira laba shay (two surfaces).

cohesive energy n. tamar bah-isjiidad; tamarta la helay amarka atoms la iskugu aadiyo marxaladda wirqe (crystalline state).

coincidence circuit n. mareeg kulandhac; qalab electronic hal output iyo laba (ama ka badan) inputs.

collision density n. cufnaan is-hirdi; dhaqsaha iskudhac uga dhacayo per unit volume per unit time; tusaale: dhaqsaha dubbe (hammer) ugu dhacayo madax mismaar (nail).

there are three types of collisions n. saddex is-hirdi ayaa jira: Perfectly elastic collision; inelastic collision; Perfectly inelastic collision.

elastic collision n. is-hirdis aan wax tamar socod ah (kenotic energy) ku dhumin.

inelastic collision n. is-hirdi dhumis ku timaaddo tamar socod (kinetic energy).

perfectly inelastic collision n. is-hirdi walxo isku dhagaan markay isku dhacaan oo ay dhumiyaan inta ugu badan tamar socod (kinetic energy).

collision probability n. itmaal is-hirdi.

factoring formulas n. real numbers: a, b, c. Natural number: n. a2 – b2 = (a – b)(a + b);

(a + b)2 = a2 + 2ab + b2; (a – b)2 = a2 – 2ab + b2;

a3 – b3 = (a – b)(a2 + ab + b2); a3 + b3 = (a + b)(a2 – ab + b2); (a + b + c)2 = a2 + b2 + c2 + 2ab + 2bc + 2ca; (a – b – c)2 = a2 + b2 + c2 – 2ab + 2bc – 2ca.

binomial formula n. (a+b)n = nC0an + nC1an-1 b + nC2an-2 b2 + nC3an - 3 b3 + ... + n ...

exponent formulas n. a0 = 1; a1 = a; am × an = a m+n; am / an = am−n; a−m = 1/am; (am)n = amn; (ab)m = ambm; (a/b)m = am/bm.

roots formulas n. √a = a1/n; √ab = n√a* n√b; √(a/b) = n√a / n√b; (n√a)n = a.

logarithms formulas n. logb 1 = 0; logb b = 1; logb (xy) = logb x + logb y; logb (x / y) = logb x - logb y; logb ax = x logb a; logb a = (logc a) / (logc b)

quadratic equation formula n. standard from:  ax2+ bx + c = 0, a≠0; x = -b ± √a2 − 4ac⁄2a

collision theory n. aragti is-hirdi; falgal kiimikaad waxa uu ka dhex dhicikaraa oo kali ah walxo (particles) marka ay is-hardiyaan (isku dhacaan).

colloidal emulsion n. furuuruc saxarro; nooc saxarro oo ka qaabsoomay laba dareere oo aan isku darsamikarin (qasmikarin).

colorimetry (,kala’rimadhar) n. midabsaafe; qalab kala sooca kalana sheega midabbo. -colorimetric (ˌkalara’metrik) adj.; -colorimetrically (ˌkalara’metriklii) adv.; -colorimetry (ˌkala’rimatrii) n.

psychoanalysis (ˌsaaykawa’naalasas) n. hab lagu daraaseeyo laguna daaweeye qof maskax ahaan iskugu dhexyaacsan (mental disorders). –psychoanalyst (ˌsaaykaw’aanalisti) n.

psychoanalyze (ˌsaaykaw’aana,laayz) v. sychoanalyzed; psychoanalyzing; psychoanalyzes daraasayn iyo daaweyn qof maskaxiyan iskugu dhexyaacsan: psychoanalysis.

color content n. midab lahaan; isdheellitir laba midab.

color contrast n. midab kala duwis; kala duwanaansho u dhexeeya midabbo kala duwan.

color filter n. midab kala reebe; markii iftiin cad dhaafo midab kala reebe midab leh, midabyada oo dhan waa la dhuuqaa, midka midab kala reebaha midabkiisa ah mooyaane.

color index n. muujiye midab; saamiga boqolley (ratio of the percentage) ee unuguyada dhiigga cas (hemoglobin) ku jira.

chromaticity diagram n. jaantus muujiya kala duwanaanta midabyo si caadi ah loo kala garankaro. kale loogu yeeraa color triangle, Maxwell triangle.

color triangle n. saddexagal midab eeg chromaticity diagram.

Maxwell triangle n. eeg chromaticity diagram.

color vision n. midab arag; awood kala saarid ama kala garasho midabyo.

column of air n. joogtax hawo; culaab ama cadaadis howo ee meel gaar ah.

combination tones n. laxanno wadajir; codod fog oo ka dhawaaqa dhag, kana yimaada laba dhawaaq oo kala duwan.

combustion engine n. matoor gubasho; matoor gudahiis ka abuura tamar gubaysa shidaad (burning fuel).

compound lens n. bikaaco laabaab quraarad aragtiyeed (lens) oo lammaan ama isku dhaggan. eeg achromatic lens.

achromatic lens n. quraarado aragtiyeed oo ka kooban iskudar quraarado ka kala duwan.

compound pendulum n. walhade isku dhisan. eeg physical pendulum.

physical pendulum n. shay meel ka soo laalaada gadaalna ka qodban oo walhada (hadba dhinac aada): oscillate.

compound microscope n. weynayso (microscope) leh laba quraarad aragtiyood oo si fiican u muujiya ilma’aragto.

rejig (,rii’jigar) v. rejiggered; rejiggering; rejiggers qaabayn; sikale u dhigid: rearrange.

auteur (aw’tuur) n. filim agaasime (film director) xeeldheere. -auteurist (aw’taristi) adj. or n.

compressional wav n. hirar diisma; hirar dheraran (sida hir cod) oo sabbeeya.

longitudinal wave n. hir dheraran; hir sabbeeya sida kan cod.

Compton effect n. physics koror dhererhireed X-rays ama gamma rays marka ay kala fidaan.

concave lens n. bikaaco golxo; quraarad golxo leh oo dalfisa dhud ifeed ee toos ah (straight light beam). Barbardhig displacement current.

displacement current n. qulqul barabax; ququl la socoda gudbiye (conductor) marka badad danab (electric field) muddo ku nagaadaan madoorsoome.

conduction current n. qulqul gudbineed; qulqul danab ee danb gudbiye (electric conductor).

heat conduction n. also thermal conduction kul gudbin; dhaqaaq kul oo shay ka taga aadana mid kale oo heerkul kala duwan leh.

 

electrical conductivity n. gudbitaan danab; walxo awood u leh in ay gudbiyaan qulqul danb; inta badan waxaa la siiyaa xarafka Greek σ (sigma), laakin κ (kappa) (especially in electrical engineering) iyo γ (gamma) oo mararka qaarkood la isticmaalo.

thermal conductivity n. 1 gudbitaan kul; awood gudbin kul. 2 awood shay ku gudbiyo kul ama kul uga guuriyo meel ilaa meel kale dhaqaaq la’aan shay gudbiynaya kul; waxaana lagu cabbiraa watts per meter kelvin (W/mK).

electronic configuration n. ratibaad electrons; isku hagaajin meeraysi electrons ku wareegaalaysi bu’ atomic (atomic nucleus).

conservation laws n. xeer waarid; waxa uu oranayaa: waxyaalo qaarkood (la cabbirikaro) waqti islama baddalaan hab faquuqid jiritaankood.

conservation of charge n. waarid saldanabeed;

dhammaan saldanab danabeed ee hab faquuqan (an isolated system) waxa uu ku nagaanayaa madoorsoome.

conservation of energy n. waarid tamareed; sharci physics iyo chemistry oranaya: hab go’doonsan (isolated system) tamartiis oo dhan waa joogto (constant) ayada oo aan loo eegin isbeddallada gudaha (internal changes).

conservation of linear momentum n. waarid daafad xariiqeed; markii laba shay (objects) iskugu dhacaan hab go’doonsan (isolated system), daafaddooda oo dhan (total momentum) isku dhaca ka hor iyo ka dib isku mid buu ku nagaanayaa.

conservation of mass n. waarid cuf; cuf ku jira hab go’doonsan (isolated system) lama abuurikaro lamana burburinkaro laakiin qaab ahaan mid kale waa loogu baddalikaraa. kale loogu yeeraa conservation of matter.

conservation of matter n. eeg conservation of mass. kale loogu yeeraa conservation of mass.

conservative field n. badad waarsan; badad xoog oo lagu qabtay shay meel looga dhaqaajiyay oo meel kale la geeyay, waa jid xor ah oo la qaatay.

consonance of music n. habsani-u-dhac miyuusikada; markii laba iyo ka badan dhawaaq oo isku macaan sameeyaan cod dhago qanciya.

coupled circuits n. mareego sidkan; markii laba iyo ka badan mareego danab (electric circuits) tamar (energy) midba mid iskugu rarikaro qaab danabeed (electrically) ama birlabeed (magnetically).

critical angle n. xagal qiirqiir; angle of incidence ugu yar oo noqod dhan (total reflection) ka dhaco; angle of incidence meeshiisa angle of refraction ka yahay 90°.

critical density n. cufnaan qiirqiir; celceliska cufnaan walax (substance) ee ay ku hayso kala baxisteed waqti aan dhammaan (an infinite time).

critical point n. bar qiirqiir; bar garaaf fansaar (graph of a function) ay derivate tahay eber ama ma’dhammaato (zero or infinite).

critical temperature n. heerkul qiirqiir; qayme heerkul ugu sarreeya ee walax (substance) ku sii ahaankarto dareere. kale loogu yeeraa transformation temperature.

negative glow n. ilays tabane; ilays meel cariiryon ka bira ee neef (gas) heerkul hoose danab ku sii daayay (as in a Crookes tube).

cathode glow n. liil dhuuban oo ilays, kuna xeeran qotin taban (cathode) gudaha Crookes tube.

transformation temperature n. heerkul waji (phase) isbaddal ka dhaco ama ka bilawdo.

Crookes dark space n. dululaati-mugdi Crookes; meel madaw oo u dhexaysa liil dhuuban oo ilays (cathode glow) iyo negative glow. kale loogu yeeraa cathode dark space.

cathode dark space n. eeg Crookes dark space.

crystal diode n. labaqotinle wiriqeed; elektaroonis casri ah (modern electronics) waxyaalo gundhig u ah oo uu ka koobanyahay.

crystal structure n. dhis wiriq; atoms (molecules or ions) iskugu nadaamsan qaab gaar ah oo soo laablaabta sameeyana wirqe.

crystal symmetry n. wanqar wiriq; noqod (reflection) isku nadaamsanaan atoms gudaha ah iyo wanqar (symmetry).

current density n. cufnaan qulqul; tiro qulqul danab (electric current) oo ku socota unit kii (per unit) meel qaybteed; formula: J = I/A (J = curranty density; I = current; A = area).

 

current transformer n. dooriye qulqul; qalab loo isticmaalo yarayn ama kordhin dareerin qulqul alternating current (AC).

cut-off-frequency n. rakaad gooyn; rakaad (frequency) oo awood baaqeed loo yareeyay bar qaymaheedii hore (original value).

Dalton's law of partial pressures n. xeer Dalton ee cadaadis qaybeed; isku-qas neefo (mixture of gases) caddaadiskooda oo dhan (total pressure) u dhikima iskudar (sum) barka cadaadisyo mid kasta oo neefaha meel ku jira.

damping of mechanical systems n. liciifis habdhis makiinadeed; cabbir ama hab tamar gariir loogu firirsho qaab cod ama kul.

Daniell cell n. unug Daniell; qalab tamar kiimiko (chemical energy) ee lagu sii daayay redox reaction u baddala tamar danab (electrical energy).

decay constant n. madoorsoome mataatax; tiro saami ee atoms kaahfal (radioactive atoms) ay waqtiyar ku baaba’ayaan, tirooyin atoms oo ay isku nooc yihiinna keenayaan in ay bilawdaan. kale loogu yeeraa disintegration constant.

 

disintegration constant n. eeg decay constant.

radioactive decay n. kaahfal mataatax; hab bu’ atomic aan degganayn ay kaah ku dhumiso tamar (loses energy by radiation).

decouple (,dii’kapal) v. decoupled; decoupling; decouples sidig-tirid; kala reebid; kala furid: separate.

elastic deformation n. qaabdoorsan loodsame; isbaddal qaab aan joogto ahayn ee shay xoog laga siidaayay oo ku soo noqday qaabkiisii caadiga ahaa.

inelastic deformation n. qaabdoorsan maloolsame; shay qaabkiisu ku baddalmo xoog dheellitiran uuna ku nagaado qaabkaas cusub marka xooggaas dheellitiran laga sii daayo.

demodulate (,dii’maaja,leyt) v. demodulated; demodulating; demodulates tacdiiltir; dib-u-baddalid; kalabixin xog. e.g. You don’t have to demodulate the signals. –demodulation (ˌdii,maaja’leyshan) n.; –demodulator (ˈdii’maaja,leydhar) n.

relative density n. cufnaan u-eegan; tiro aan lahayn qaab (dimensionless quantity) oo lagu qeexay walax saami cufnaan (ration of the density) kale la siiyay. kale loogu yeeraa specific gravity.

incident ray n. fallaar iftiin oo horjeed ah kuna dhacda duleed (surface).

angle of deviation n. xagal weecad ama dalfad.

diamagnetic (,dhaayamaag’nedhik) adj. ka-siq-birlabeed; diida ama ka carara birlab, sida: Copper, Zinc, Bismuth, Silver, Gold, Antimony, Marble, Water, Glass, iwm. –diamagnetism (ˌdhaaya’maagn,tizam) n.

dielectric (,dhaaya’lektirik) n. magudbiye (nonconductor) qulqul danab ee toos ah. –dielectric adj.

dielectric constant n. madoorsoome labadanab; eeg permittivity.

permittivity (,par,mi’tivati) n. waxay la xariirtaa xaddi khadad badad danab (density of electric field lines) uu u ogaalaado burqad danab khadad badad ee mara meel cayiman. kale loogu yeeraa dielectric constant, relative permittivity, specific inductive capacity.

relative permittivity n. eeg permittivity.

 

specific inductive capacity n. eeg permittivity.

 

dielectric strength n. quwad labadanab; cabbir itaal danab (electrical strength) ee magudbiye (insulator), laguna mujiyo kilovolts per millimeter.

diffraction of light n. gadaal baah ilays; qallooc yar oo uu sameeyo nal marka uu dhaafayo shay qarkiis ama jirjirkiis.

diffraction of sound n. gadaal baah jabaq; qallooc ama baahid hir codeed marka uu dhaafo shay.

diffraction spectrum n. jeegaan gadaal baah; baahid midabyo qaansaroobaad (rainbow).

electric dipole n. labacirifle danabeed; laba qotin oo saldanab danabeed (electric charges) isna baaxad le’eg se ku kala duwan calaamado.

dipole magnet n. labacirifle birlabeed; birlab nooca ugu sahlan oo leh laba cirif, mid waqooyi iyo mid koofur.

dip circle n. foorar goobo; cabbir xagal u dhexaysa gudboonaan ilqabad (horizon) iyo badad birlabeed ee dhulka (Earth’s magnetic field). eeg dip needle.

discharge coefficient n. weheliye danabtir. eeg coefficient of discharge.

coefficient of discharge n. wehliye danabtir; saami danabtir sax ah marka loo eego saami aragti ah (theoretical discharge).

discharge tube n. dhuun danabtir; dhuun xambaarsan neef ama uumi cadaadis hoose ah oo xariir danabeed la wareego markii voltage sare yimaado.

disintegration nuclear n. burbur bu’eed; hab bu’ atomic ee aan degganayn tamar ku dhumiso kaah (radiation).

dispersion of light n. kala leexad ilays; markii iftiin cad uu dhexmaro quraadad oo midabyo (violet, indigo, blue, green, yellow, orange and red) kala baxaan.

dispersive power n. awood kala leexaxad; awood lagu kala saaro midabyo ayada oo la qaloociyo.

dissociation energy n. tamar kala fur; tamar looga baahanyahay burburin iskuxir kasta ee kiimiko maalikiyuul iyo kala saarid dhammaan atoms kiisa.

fractional distillation n. qayb-xareedayn; hab walxo ka kooban iskujir kiimiko qaybo kala duwan loogu kala saaro kala duwanaanta barahooda karka (boiling points).

divergent rays n. fallaaro firirsan.

Doppler effect n. raad Doppler; koror ama yaraad (increase or decrease) ee rakaad cod, iftiin (frequency of sound, light) ama hir kale markii loo soo dhawaado ama laga fogaado.

drift velocity n. keynaan kaladurug.

Earth's core n. dhuux dhuleed; ubucda dhulka oo ah meel aad u kulul oo leh qaab kubbadeed, hoos u xulan ilaa 2,900 kilometers (1,802 miles).

Earth's crust n. lakab dhuleed; lakab sare ee oogada dhulka, laba nooc ayaana jira: lakab badeed iyo lakab dhuleed (oceanic crust and continental crust).

Earth's rotation n. also Earth's spin wareeg dhuleed ama winiin dhuleed.

Eddy currents n. qulqul Eddy; wax kasta oo sababa baddal itaal ama jaho badad birlabeed ee gude gudbiye (conductor).

elastic limit n. xad loolsan; meesha ugu danbaysa ee shay loolsamikaro.

elastic wave n. hirar loolsan; waxay ku xirantahay kala duwanaan walxo sida ay u kala jiidmid bataan.

 

electric current n. qulqul danab; dhaqaaq walxo danab oo togan ama taban, sida electrons oo keena kul, badad danab, ama isbaddal kiimiko.

electric discharge n. danabtir danabeed; hab saldanab danabeed (electric charge) meel ilaa meel ku aado.

electrical circuit n. mareeg danabeed; marin qulqul danab maro.

electrical load n. rar danabeed; qalab danab oo cuna tamar danab una baddala tamartaas qaab kale.

electrical network n. shabakad danabeed; xariir gudo (interconnection) ah oo ka dhexeeya waxyaalo danab ku shaqeeya, sida: batteries, resistors, inductors, capacitors, switches, iyo transistors.

electrical noise n. buuq danabeed; jabaq aan loo baahnayn oo uu keeno baaq danabeed (electrical signal).

electrical potential n. or electric potential kayd danabeed; shaqo inteed looga baahdo in ay ka dhaqaajiso unit charge gaysana bar cayiman oo lid ka ah badad danabeed (electric field).

electrical power n. awood danabeed; dhaqaaq shaqo lagu qabtay ama tamar lagu gudbiyay mareeg danabeed (electrical circuit).

electric field strength n. quwad badad danabeed; tiro lagu muujiyo quwad badad danabeed ee meel gaar ahaaneed; tusaale: E = F/q (E = electric field; F = force extracted per unit positive; q = electric charge at that point).

electric flux n. burqad danab; tirada guud ee khadad badad danabeed (electric field lines) oo ku gudbaya meel cayiman halbeeg waqti (unit time); electric flux ϕ = EAcosθ.

electric flux density n. cufnaan burqad danab; tiro burqad oo u gudba meel cayiman oo qoton (perpendicular) la ah jahada burqad.

electric induction n. daaqid danab; hab walax loogu abuuro danab deggan (static electricity) ayada oo loo soo dhaweynayo shay danab ahaan saldanabaysan (electrically charged object).

electric motor n. matoor danab; qalab tamar danabeed (electrical energy) u baddala tamar dhaqaaq (mechanical energy).

electric generator n. dhaliye danab; matoor (qalab) dhaqaaq tamareed (mechanical energy) oo meel kale kayimid u baddala soo saarid tamar danabeed (electrical energy).

 

electrochemical cell n. unug danab-kiimikaad; qalab awooda in uu falgallo kiimiko (chemical reactions) ka dhaliyo tamar danab (electrical energy) ama isticmaalo tamar kiimikaad si uu u sababo falgallo kiimikaad.

coulomb (‘kuu,laam) n. halbeeg meter-kilogram-second ee saldanab danab (electric charge) lana mid ah tirada danabeed (quantity of electricity) loo gudbiyay qulqul hal ampere hal ilbiriqsi gudihiis (one ampere in one second).                                      -adj. coulomb ama coulombic la xariira ama ah xoog danab (electrostatic force) ee isasoo jiidad ama kala carar ka dhexeeya walxo saldanabaysan (between charged particles).

electrochemical equivalent n. udhigan danab-kiimiko; cuf (mass) walax ee la duldhigay qulqul hal Ampere (1 Ampere) ah oo ku gudbaya hal ilbiriqsi (1 Second); si kale: (a quantity of electricity of one Coulomb is passed).

 

electrochemical series n. tax danab-kiimikaad. eeg electromotive series.

electromotive series n. or electromotive force series tax danab-kiimikaad; qoraal taxaal ah ee curiyayaal bir (metallic elements) ama ions ayada oo la sheegayo awoodaha qotimadooda (electrode potentials) xaaladaha u gaarka ah. kale loogu yeeraa electrochemical series.

electromagnetism (i,lektaraw’maagna,tiizam) n. 1 birlabdanabnimo; birlab ay samaysay danab qulqul  (current of electricity). 2 laan ka mid ah physics oo gooni u eegta xiriir jismi ahaan ee ka dhexeeya danab (electricity) iyo birlab (magnetism).

electromagnetic radiation n. kaah birlabdanabeed; tamar qaab electromagnetic wave.

electron beam n. dhud elektaroon; dhud ama shawlad electrons oo isku meelna ka baxay isku jaho iyo isku xawaarana ah.

 

electron configuration n. ratibaad elektaroon; lagu caddeeyo meel electrons ka ay agjoogaan bu’ qurub (nucleus of an atom).

electron current n. qulqul elektaroon; electrons waxay qulqul ka bilaabaan dhinac taban (negative terminal) ilaa kan togan (positive).

electron density n. cufnaan elektaroon; xajmi cufnaan electron waxay la xariirtaa wadar cufaf atomic per unit volume.

electron diffraction n. gadaalbaah elektaroon; xeelad ogolaata in lagu soo saaro walxo dhismahood wiriqood (crystal structure of materials).

electronegative (i,lektaraw’negadhiv) adj. elektaroontabane; damac soo jiidasho electrons leh. –electronegativity (i,lektaraw,nega’tividhii) n.

electron energy bands n. liidad tamar elektaroon;

electrons isku meel ku meeraysata waxay muujiyaan heerar tamareed kala duwan (different energy levels), isku kooxayntooda ayaa la dhahaa energy bands.

energy level n. or electron shells fogaanno joogto oo ka bilawda bu’ atom ilaa meesha eletrons laga helikaro. kale loogu yeeraa energy state.

energy state n. fogaanno joogto oo ka bilawda bu’ atom meesha cufnaan electron ku badanyahay. kale loogu yeeraa energy level.

electron gas n. neef elektaroon; electrons ku wareega meel xiran ama xariiriye bir ah (metallic conductor).

electron gun n. bunduq elektaroon; qalab ku shaqeeya danab oo sameeya dhudo electron (electron beam) lehna tamar socod (kinetic energy), inta badan television ka ayaa lagu badbaddalaa (tv remote control).

 

electron mass n. cuf elektaroon; cuf electron negi (stationary electron) waxaana la siiyaa me.

electron microscope n. weynayso elektaroon; weynayso leh dhud electrons (beam of electronics) si ay u weynayso wax la baarayo (specimen). -electron microscopist n.; -electron microscopy n.

electron radius n. gacan elektaoon  

electron shell n. qayb dibad ee ku xeersan bu’ atomic (atomic nucleus).

electron spin n. winiin elektaroon; electron ku wareega dhidibkiisa (axis).

electron transfer n. guurid elektaroon; falgal hal electron maalikiyuul (molecule) looga raray mid kale.

electron valency n. kaaftoon elektaroon; electrons jooga wareeg sare (outermost shell), ama heer tamareed (energy level) atom.

electron volt n. elektaroon volt; halbeeg tamareed (unit of energy) ama shaqo, lana mid: 1.60 × 10−19 joule.

electron wavelength n. baac-hireed elektaroon; hir electron baac-hireed (wavelength λ) baac-hireedkaan waxa uu ku xiranyahay elektaroon daafaddiis (momentum of the electron); momentum (p) waxaa lagu muujiyaa mass of the electron (m) iyo velocity of the electron (v). ∴ momentum of the electron (p) = m × v. Then the wavelength λ is. ∴ Wavelength λ = h/p.

elementary particle n. saxar saleed; saxarro kasta oo walax (matter) iyo tamar ay ka samaysanyihiin.

emergent ray n. fallaar baxdo; dhud qalloocsan (refracted bean) oo ka timid qallooc ama noqod (refraction or reflection).

emergent (i’marjanti) adj. 1 deg-deg ah. e.g. Emergent respond. 2 wax aan la filayn oo yimaada. 3 botany ka dheer dhirta kale ee ku agtaal. 4 botany caleemo ama ubax ka sarreeya biyo. e.g. emergent vegetation. 5 philosophy caadi ka sarreeya ama caqligal.                                                                      -n. 1 deg-deg. 2 geed ka dheer geedo ka ag dhaw.

emittance (i’mitnitis) n. bixitaan tamar; tamar ka baxda korka (surface) meel per second per unit area.

triglyceride (,taraay’gilisa,raaydh) n. nooc dufan (fat) oo la dhaho lipid kuna dhex wareegaalaysta dhiigga; waana nooca dufaneedka jirka ugu badan, kana yimaada subag (butter), saliid, iyo baruur.

 

energy bands n. liidad tamar; isbadbaddal tamar socota oo ay sameeyeen electrons gaaray heerarkii tamareed (energy levels).

internal energy n. tamar gudeed; wadar tamar socod (kinetic energy) uu leeyahay dhaqaaq maalikiyuuleed (molecular motion) iyo tamar kayd (potential energy) ee dhaqaaq gariireed (vibrational motion) iyo tamar danab (electric energy) ee atoms ku dhexjira maalikiyuullo (molecules).

random error n. gaf huban; wax dhawr jeer la cabbiray oo jawaabo kala duwan keenay ayaga oo isku xaalad ku sugan. lid (opposite): systematic error.

systematic error n. gaf habaysan; khalad dhab ah oo la ogaaday markii wax la cabbiray ama la tiriyay. lid (opposite) random error.

standard error n. gaf beeggallin; qorshayn (statistic) muujisa sida ay sax ugu dhawdahay muuna (sample) tiro dad oo la qaaday.

escape velocity n. keynaan ugu yar oo dayaxgacmeed laga rabo in uu cufisjiidad dhulka uga baxa is uu hawada sare ugalo.

 

Euclidean space n. dululaati Euclidean.

excitation energy n. 1 physics tamar didin; tamar ugu badan ee laga rabo electron gaar ah heerkiisa hoose (ground state) ilaa heerkiisa saree ee tamarteed (higher energy) ee gudo atom ama maalikiyuul (molecule). 2 chemistry tamar didsan oo lagu caddeeyo tamar falgal kiimiko.

excitation potential n. kayd didineed; isbaddal cabbir ee tamar electrons laga rabo in ay ku baddalaan heerkooda tamareed (to change their states of energy).

excited state n. waji didan; xaalad hab shay ahaaneed, sida atomic nucleus, atom, ama maalikiyuul ay tamartiisu sareeyso (higher energy), inta uu lahaan lahaa tamar hoose (lower state).

exothermic (,eeksaw’thermik) n. 1 kul-bixiye; falgal kiimiko oo sii daaya tamar (energy). 2 xayaanka kulaylka jirkoodu la qabsado meesha ay joogaan: cold-blooded. -ectothermically (ˌeksaw’tharmiklii) adv.; -extremity (ˌeksaw,thar’misadhii) n.

expanding universe n. koonka fidaya; aduunku wuu sii fidayaa ilaa bilawgiisii.

eyepiece (‘aay,piis) n. gobol ileed; isku dar laba quraad weynayso.

farad (‘feer,aadh) n. halbeeg danab kaydiye (capacitance), awood kaydin saldanab danabeed (electrical charge).

far point n. bar fog; il ku wareerto. e.g. The area was dense that our far point was only five or six feet away.

ferromagnetic (,feerawmaag’nedhik) adj. la xariira walxo si aan caadi ahayn ogolaansho aad ah oo birlabeed leh, sida: cobalt, nickel, neodymium magnet, and chromium dioxide. -ferromagnet (ˈfera,maagnat) n.; -ferromagnetism (ˌferaw’maagna,tizam) n.

field of vision n. badad muuqaal. eeg visual field.

field strength n. quwad (itaal) badad. eeg field intensity.

field intensity n. awood badad danabeed. kale loogu yeeraa field strength.

field theory n. aragti badad; aragti kasta oo physics xisaab ahaan ku muujiysa macluumaad meel ay saamaysay cufisjiidad (gravitation).

relative speed n. markii laba shay u socdaan isku jiho Relative Speed = Difference of Speeds (kala goyn xawaarahooda); laakiin markii laba shay laba jiho oo kala duwan u socdaan Relative Speed Adding Speeds (isku dar xawaarahooda).

Fizeau experiment n. tijaabooyin Fizeau; cabbir xawaare if dhexmarya biyo socda.

foot-candle n. (fc, lm/ft2, or ft-c) halbeeg cabbir ee ilays intiis buuxisa ama ifisa hal cag oo isku wareeg (one lumen per square foot).

forced oscillation n. also forced vibration walhin; shay meel suran hadba dhinac loo walfiyo. lid (opposite) free oscillation.

free oscillation n. walhatin; shay meel ka soo laalaada oo hadba iskiis dhinac u walfada. lid (opposite) forced oscillation.

inertial force n. xoog wahsiyeed; xoog lid ku ah jiho xoog karaar (accelerating force); horay u hinqasho markii gaari xoog loo joojiyo.

freezing mixture n. iskujir barafayn; nooc iskuqas ee walxo la isku daray si heerkul uga hoos maro bar barafaw (freezing point); tusaale iskudar milix iyo baraf (salt and ice): salt lower the freezing point of ice.

natural frequency n. rakaad dabiici; rakaad (frequency) ama dhaqaaq si caadi ah u gariira markii la taabtaabto (disturbed). kale loogu yeeraa natural wavelength.

natural wavelength n. eeg natural frequency.

fuel cell n. unug shidaal; qalab si joogto ah tamar kiimiko ugu baddala shidaal (sida hydrogen) iyo oxidant toosna ugu baddala tamar kiimiko.

fundamental physical constants n. madoorsoomayaal fisikaad asal; tiro jir ahaaneed (physical quantity) oo aan aragti ahaan lagu sharraxikarin, sidaas darteed waa in la cabbiro.

flip-flop circuit n. mareeg big-damlaysa ama wac-biglaysa.

gas constant n. madoorsoome neef; madoorsoome joogto ah ee R oo lagu muujiyo halbeeg energy per temperature increment per mole; formula: pV = nRT; R = E/nT = energy per mole/T. kale loogu yeeraa ideal gas constant or molar gas constant or universal gas constant.

ideal gas constant n. eeg gas constant.

molar gas constant n. eeg gas constant.

universal gas constant n. eeg   gas constant.

 

geomagnetic axis n. didib birlabdhuleed; labo dhidib oo dhulka u kala qaybiya waqooyi iyo koofur.

geomagnetic field n. badad birlabdhuleed: Earth's magnetic field.

geomagnetic pole n. cirif birlabdhuleed; labada cirif oo lidka isku ah ee oogada dhulka midkood.

geomagnetic optics n. laan ka mida ah cilmiga barashada arag iyo dabeecado fallaro ilyska.

gravitational acceleration n. karaar cuf-isjiidad; shay soo dhicitaan ku soo karaar qaadanaya, ayada oo cufisjiidadku dhulku soo jiidanayo, una taagan ‘g’ ee halbeegga m/s2.

gravitational constant n. madoorsoome cuf-isjiidad. eeg constant of gravitation.

constant of gravitation n. xoog isa soo jiidasho oo ka dhexeeya laba wax oo kasta cufkooda, ayna kala qaybisay kala fogaantoodu, waxaana la siiyaa G laguna cabbiraa Nm2/kg2.

gravitational field n. badad cuf-isjiidad; xoogag isjiidad oo ka jira hawada nagu xeersan ee cufkasta.

gravitational potential n. kayd cuf-isjiidad; tamar ku kaydsan shay kasta oo dhulka koryaal iyo badadkiisa cuf-isjiidad ee dhulka; formula: GPE = mgh (Gravitational Potential Energy = mass × Gravitational Acceleration Toward Earth (9.8 meters per second squared) × the height the object.

Newton's law of gravitation n. xeer cuf-isjiidad Newton: saxar kasta ee walax adduunkaan ah wax kasta oo kale xoog buu ku soo jiitaa saami la ah cufkooda iyo saamiga fogaantooda oo labajibaaran; formula: F (force) = (G × m1 × m2) / d2 (meesha ‘G’ ay tahay gravitational constant, m1 iyo m2 ay yihiin ‘masses’ of the bodies, iyo ‘d’ tahay fogaanta u dhexaysa (distance between them). 

group velocity n. keynaan koox: hirar waxay noqonkaraan kooxo, waxaana loogu yeeraa ‘wave packets’, keynaan (velocity) wave packets ku safraanna waxaa la dhahaa ‘group velocity’; keynaan (velocity) phase of a wave ku safrana waxaa la dhahaa ‘phase velocity’; xariirka ka dhexeeya ‘group velocity’ iyo ‘phase velocity’ waa saami (proportionate).

ground wave n. hir dhuleed; hir raadiyo (radio wave) oo ku dira ama tabiya (propagated) jabaq, gariir, ama if dhulka oogadiisa sare.

halation (hey’leyshan) n. 1 barcaddaadi; iftiin xad dhaafa hummaag sawir (photographic image). 2 gal goobo oo isku wareegjiya shay aad u ifaya.

half-wave n. hir-bar; nooc baddala qulqul danab (rectifier) u ogolaada AC (alternating current) voltage wareeg barki.

 half-life radioactive n. cimri-bar kaahfaleed; inta ay waqti ku qaadato cimi-bar mataatax (decay).

 

simple harmonic motion n. dhaqaaq ama ruxmad wadajira.

harmonic oscillator n. islabarog wadajira; shay kala baxa oo xoog soo celiya saamigal la yahay kii ka barabaxay meeshii dheellitiran; dhaqaaq hal islabarog; F=−kx.

 

hearing loss n. maqal-beel. kale loogu yeeraa sensorineural hearing loss.

heat conduction n. physics iyo chemistry kul gudbin; tamar kululeed u baddalid meel kale, waxayna noqonkartaa adke, dareere, ama neef.

heat content n. kul sid. eeg enthalpy.

heat exchanger n. kul iswaydaariye; hab loogu gudbiyo kul labadhex dareere kale ayaga oo aan iskudarmin, sida gaari biyaha radiator kiisa.

heat flow n. kul socod; gudbin tamar kuleed (heat energy).

heat transfer n. kul rar; hab maalikiyuulada ay meel kulul (higher temperature) uga guuraan, meel qabawna (lower temperature) uga aadaan, sida marka dab la kulaalyo, kulaylku u aado jirka qabaw.

henry (‘heenrii) n., pl. henrys or henries halbeeg meter-kilogram-second (unit) ee qulqul dhaqaaq mareeg (circuit) oo hal ampere u baddala xoog danabwade (electromotive force) ee hal volt; waxaana la siiyaa summad H.

relative humidity n. huur barbardhigeed; saami uumi biyo intiisa ku jirta hawada inta ugu badan oo isku heerkul ah.

hydrostatics (ˌhaaydra’istaadhikis) n. cilmi hoor-negiyayaal; laan ka mid ah physics oo gooni u eegta dareerayaal iyo cadaadis ka dhexjira wixii dhexgala. Barbardhig hydrodynamics.

hydrodynamics (,haaydrawdaay’naamikis) n. laan ka mid physics oo gooni u eegta qulqul dareeyayaal iyo xoogga ay la kulmaan walxo adke ah oo dhexgala. Barbardhig hydrostatics. –hydrodynamicist (ˌhaaydrawdhaa’naamasisti) n.

hydrostatic pressure n. cadaadis hoor-negiyeed; cadaadis ku dhexfiliqsan dareere ee dheellitiran meel biyo ka mid ah, ayada oo ay jirto xog cuf-isjiidad.

hysteresis loop n. qool dibdhac birlabeed; xariir ka dhexeeya cufnaan burqad birlabeed (B) iyo awood badad birlabaysan (H).

hysteresis loss n. dhumis dibdhac birlabeed; tamar ku dhunta kul ka imaanaya dibdhac birlabeed (hysteresis).

real image n. hummaag runeed; muuqaal dhabeed.

virtual image n. hummaag beeneed; muuqaal dhalanteed.

external impedance n. xayir dabadeed.

incandescent lamp n. guluub ifbire; nal.

self-inductance (selfin’dhektanis) n. fiilo wadda qulqul oo ka adkaysata gudbin qulqul dhaafaya ama maraya.

mutual induction n. iskiis saaqma; markii laba duub (two coils) isku soo dhawaadaan, badad birlabeed ee mid ka mid ah duubab uu xariiriyo midka kale, taas oo sababta in duubka labaad helo dab voltage.

induction coil n. duub saaqineed; nooc ka mid ah (electric transformer) oo high voltage ka sameeya low voltage.

inert gas n. neef wahsato. eeg noble gas.

infrared radiation n. abbr. IR kaah ka-hoos-casaan; qayb ka mid ah jeegaan birlabdanabeed (electromagnetic spectrum) ka baxsan baac-hireed dheer (long wavelength) if cas oo aan indhaha qaawan arkikarin, laakiin la dareemikaro diirimaadkiisa.

interaction (,intar’akshan) n. 1 physics falgalan, falcelin; qaab gaar ah ee walxo, midba mid ula falgalo. 2 wadaag; iswaydaarsi ama isdhexgal. e.g. There was interaction between new students. –interactional (ˌintar’aakshanal) adj.

interferometer (ˌintarfa’raamadhar) n. labidbeege, isdhexalbeege; qalab baaritaan oo loo isticmaalo meelo badan oo science ka iyo engineering ah. -interferometric (ˌintar,fira’metrik) adj.;

-interferometrically (ˌintar,fira’metriklii) adv.; -interferometry (ˌintarfa’raamatrii) n.

intermediate state n. waji dhexaad, marxalad dhexaad; waji dheellitiran wadashaqayn gudbiye sare (type-I superconductor) ugu kala dhanbalmo superconducting (S) iyo normal (N) phases.

ion density n. cufnaan aayoon.

ion exchange n. iswaydaarsi aayoon; ka saarid walxo ionic ku milmay biyo. -ion exchanger n.

ion radius n. gacan aayoon; fogaan u dhaxaya bu’ ion (nucleus of ion) iyo wareeg sare ee ion.

acquire (a’kuwaayar) v. acquired; acquiring helid; yeelatin. e.g. The new team acquire their own transportation.

ionization potential n. kayd aayooneeye; tamar inteed looga rabo in ay electron uga saarto atom ama maalikiyuul go’doonsan (atom or molecule isolated). kale loogu yeeraa ionization energy.

ionization energy n. eeg ionization potential.

isobar (‘aaysa,baar) n. 1 meteorology cadaadis ekeeye; xarriiqo ku dhigma khariirad oo isku xira meelo isku cadaadis hawo ah. 2 physics isku cadaadis; atoms isku tiro neutron ah, laakiin ku kala duwan tiro proton.

isotherm (‘aaysa,tharm) n. 1 kul ekeeye; isku heer kul; xarriiq ka muuqda khariirad oo isku xira meelo isku heerkul ah. 2 physics xood garaaf (curve on a graph) oo isku xirta baro isku heerkul ah.

Kirchhoff's law n. wadar voltages ee qool xiran (closed loop) waa eber; taas oo macnaheedu yahay, iskudar tiro tamar korortay waxay la mid tahay tamar dhuntay per unit charge.

lagging current n. qulqul dibdhac; markii qulqul ka dibdhaco voltage, saami awood shaqaynaysa ee marreeg ayaana la dhahaa logging power factor.

electric lamp n. electric light or bulb laambad danabeed.

mercury-vapor lamp n. laambad uumi-mercury; laambad danab oo sii daysa uumi mercury. kale loogu yeeraa mercury lamp.

mercury lamp n. eeg mercury-vapor lamp n.

leakage current n. qulqul daysma; qulqul aan shaqaynayn (non-functional), kana sii daysma mareeg (circuit) DC or Ac aadana dhulka.

leakage flux n. burqad daysmo; qayb ka mid ah burqad birlabeed oo aan raacin jidkii larabay ee mareeg birlabeed (magnetic circuit).

principle of least action n. xeer fal-u-yare; haddii hab ay wax u socdaan uu si isdabajoog iskugu rakibanyahay isbaddal la’aan, falku waxa uu qaadanayaa jidka ugu gaaban.

Fermat's principles n. also principle of least time xeer ammin-u-yare jid ay fallaar ilays u qaadato laba barood dhexdood, waa masaafoda ugu waqti yar.

focal length of lens n. dherer kulmis bikaaco; fogaan u dhexaysa bikaaco (lens) iyo bar kulan arag.

focal point of lens n. bar kulmis bikaaco.

power of lens n. awood bikaaco (lens).

formula lens n. qaacido bikaaco; lens formula: (1/v-1/u= 1/f), meesha v = distance of the image; u = distance of the object; f = focal length of the lens.

faradaic (fa’raadhik) adj. also faradaic qulqul danab oo uu keenay reduction ama oxidation ee qotin walxo kiimiko.

limiting current n. qulqul xadeeye.

linear expansion n. fidid dherer; koror dheeraan dherer marka shay la kululeeyo.

line of force n. xarriiq xoog; xarriiq mala’awaal (imaginary line) oo ka taagan xoog badad (field of force) sida bad danab ama birlab (electric or magnetic field).

line voltage n. xarriiq voltage; voltage u dhexeeya laba waji oo sheeggan (two given phase).

gas liquefaction n. hoorayn neef; neef ubaddalis dareere.

logic circuit n. mareeg loo qaabeeyay in ay qabato shaqooyin adag (complex functions).

low frequency n. rakaad gaaban; rakaad raadiyo (radio frequency) u dhexaya rakaad dhexe iyo rakaad aad u hooseeya.

luminous emittance n. bixin iftiimeed; burqad iftiimeed (per unit area) lagu shaaciyay meel.

luminous flux n. burqad iftiimeed; cabbir shucaac iftiin ee nal tamar (energy) ahaan u sii daayo; waxaana lagu cabbiraa lumen (lm) intii la adeegsan lahaa watts.

magma (ˈmaagma) n. dareere ama dhagax milmay, siiba hoosta oogada sare ee dhulka. -magmatic (maag’maadhik) adj.

magnetic axes n. dhidib birlabeed; xarriiq toosan oo isku xira dhulka labadiisa cirif ee birlabeed (magnetic poles of the earth).

magnetic dip n. foorar birlabeed. eeg magnetic inclination.

magnetic elements n. eeg magnetic inclination.

magnetic field n. badad birlabeed; meel ku dhaw birlab ama ququl wada xoogag birlabeed oo la dareemikaro.

magnetic pole n. cirif birlabeed; birlab kasta cirifkeed meelo dibad ah ee badad birlabeed ku badanyihiin.

magnetic energy n. tamar birlabnimeed; tamar ka timid saldanab guuraya (moving charge) oo xambaarsan electrons.

permanent magnet n. birlab waarto; walxo badad birlabeed ay sameeyeen dhismo gudo (internal structure) ee isla walxahaas.

temporary magnet n. birlab mawaarto; ka samaysan biro jilicsan (soft metals) oo biralbnimadood haya kali ah marka ay u dhawyihiin badad birlab waarto (permanent magnetic field) ama qulqul danab (electrical current).

mass effect fields n. badad iin cufeed; waxay ka abuurmeen adeegsi element zero. Element zero wuu kordhinkaraa ama yaraynkaraa space-time cufkiis markii dark energy ku yimaado qulqul danab; qulqul togane, cufku wuu kordhaa, qulqul tabanena cufku wuu yaraadaa.

dark energy n. magac la siiyo xoog aan la aqoon (mysterious force) oo sababa dhaqaaq fidis adduunkaan oo waqti la karaara (accelerate over time) inta uu gaabin lahaa.

element zero n. wax protons ah kuma jiraan bu’ atomic (atomic nucleus).

energy equivalent of mass n. cuf u-dhigan tamar; isku dhac electron iyo proton waxay laqdaa cufka saxarradooda, laakiin waxay abuurtaa tamar qaab photons ah.

relativistic mass n. cuf u-eegaal; wax dhaqaaq ku jira cufkood marka loo eego korjooge (observer).

mean life n. eeg average life.

average life n. celcelis cimri; celcelis waqti looga baahanyahay baaba’a qurubyo (atoms) oo dhan, noqonaysa 1.443 lagu dhuftay cimri-bar (half-life).

mechanical equivalent of heat n. kul udhigan makaaniko; xaalad kasta, hawl inteed waxay abuurtaa isku in kululeed, taas oo macnaheedu yahay, inta la baxshay kul iyo dhaqaaq (heat and motion) waa isku baddalmikaraan; formula: J = W Q.

mechanical impedance n. xayir makaaniko; waxaa lagu cabbiraa inta shay u adkaysankaro dhaqaaq marka ay jirto harmonic force.

melting curve n. xood dhalaashan; dheellitiran u dhexeeya adke iyo dareere.

mho (‘maw) n., pl. mhos halbeeg gudbiye (unit of conductance), la mid ah hal ampere per volt, taas oo u dhiganta rogaal ohm unit. kale loogu yeeraa siemens.

moment of a force n. xoog maroojis; cabbir shay u keena in uu ku wareego bar cayiman ama dhidib (specific point or axis); formula: moment = force × perpendicular distance.

moving coil instrument n. qalab duub socodle; qalab cabbireed qulqul ama voltage lagu ogaado laba duub oo yar oo ku dhex wareegsan cirifyo birlab xoodan cirifyadeed.

near point n. bar dhaw; shay u dhaw il, kaas oo si salhan loo arkikaro.

neutral surface n. gibil dhexdhexaad; meel (surface) saxarro dareere isdhexmarikaraan ayaga oo aan qaban wax shaqo ah oo ka soo horjeeda cuf-isjiidad.

neutrino (nuu’tirii,naw) n., pl. neutrinos saxarro aan saldanabaysnay (uncharged particle) lehna cuf (mass) aad iyo aad u yar oo aan ku darmin saxarro kale. –neutrinoless (nuu’tirii,nawlis) adj.

Newton's law of cooling n. xeer Newton ee qaboojin: dheerayn shay ku qaboobo waxay saami la tahay heerkul u dhexeeya shayga  iyo shayga hareerihiisa; tusaale: koob kulul oo biyo ah dhaqsa ayuu qol qabaw ku qaboobaa in ka yar qol kulul.

nuclear energy n. physics tamar bu’eed; tamar ka abuurmatay kala bacram bu’ atoms (nuclei of atoms).

nuclear forces n. xoogag bu’eed. eeg strong force.

strong force n. gundhig dabiici ah ee islafalgalid ka dhexaysa walxo saxarradood sii yaryar (subatomic particles of matter). kale loogu yeeraa strong interaction, strong nuclear force.

strong nuclear force n. eeg strong force.

strong interaction n. eeg strong force.

nuclear fusion n. iskudhag bu’eed; hab bu’o atoms (nuclei of atoms) ay isku dhageen.

interaction (,intar’aakshan) n. 1 iswaydaarsi; isdhaafsi. e.g. The interaction between the two cultures. 2 wada xariiris; sheekaysi. 3 physics hab gaar ah ee walxo, badad, iyo atomic ay isku saameeyaan. –interactional (ˌintar’aakshanal) adj.

nuclear physics n. laan ka mid ah physics oo gooni u eegta bu’ atomic (atomic nuclei), qaybaha ay ka koobantahay, iyo isasaamayntood.

nuclear reactor n. falgaliye bu’eed; warshad aad u weyn oo dhasha ama tayaysa nuclear energy.

nobby (‘naabii) adj. nobbier; nobbiest hubqaad wanaagsan leh; xirta dhar xarago leh: fashionable.

o.a.s.m system n. hab oasm; Ohm, Ampere, Second, Meter (system of units).

optical system n. habdis bikaaco, kana kooban: lenses, mirrors, light sources, detectors, projection screens, reflecting prisms, dispersing devices, filters and thin films, and fibre-optics bundles.

object space n. dululaati qalab; qalab ka kooban bikaacooyin (lenes) iyo quraarado oo xukuma qayb arag ee (microscope ama telescope). Barbardhig image space.

image space n. inta u dhexaysa bikaacooyin (lenes) iyo hummaag (image).

paramagnetic (ˌperamaag’nedhik) adj. ku-siq-birlabeed; la xariira waxyaalo aad u qaada birlabnimo, sida: magnesium, molybdenum, lithium, iyo tantalum. -paramagnetically (ˌperamaag’nedhiklii) adv.; -paramagnetism (ˌpera’maagn,tizam) n.

parallax (‘peera,laakis) n. shay sikale u muuqda marka meelo kala gooni ah laga jeedaaliyo (two different points).

parallax rays n. arag shay oo kala duwanaada marka xarriiqo toos ah meelo kala duwan laga soo eego.

partial pressure n. cadaadis qaybeed; haddii weel laga buuxiyo in ka badan hal neef (one gas), neef kasta ayadaa cadaadis xoog ula timaadda.

partial eclipse n. madoobaad dhimman; qarin aan hoos (shade) wada daboolin ee bar muuqdo.

Pascal's law n. markii shay la maquuriyo dareere, oogadiisa oo dhan waxay helaysaa cadaadis isku mid ah.

path of rays n. marin fallaaro; fallaaro illays mar kasta waxay ku safraan xariiqo toosan.

pencil of light n. dhud ilays (a beam of light) ama fallaar ilays (a pencil of light).

simple pendulum n. walhade fudud; formula T = 2π√L/g; meesha T= period; L = pendulum length; g = acceleration due to gravity.

pentode (ˈpen,tawdh) n. shanqotin; qalab danab (vacuum tube) oo leh shan qotin (five electrodes).

penumbra (pa’nambara) n., pl. penumbrae (pa’nam,barii) or penumbras 1 meel qaarkeed hoos leeyahay ee wareegga geesaha hoos, siiba madoobaad (eclipse). 2 astronomy meel ku wareegsan qar barmadaw ee qorraxda. 3 medicine faaliga (stroke) ka dib, meel maskaxda ka mid ah oo dhumisay qulqul dhiig. (ischemic penumbra). –penumbral (pa’nambaral) adj.

perfect gas law n. xeer neef qumman; xariir ka dhexeeya cadaaddis (pressure P), mug (volume V), iyo heerkul (temperature T) ee neef (gas) ku xaddadan cadaadisyo hoose iyo heerkulyo sare (high temperatures).

period of oscillation n. kal walhasho; waqti intiisa ay ku qaadato shay walhanaya ama lalmanaya in ku tago gees ilaa gees; kal walhasho (Time period) = 1 frequency.

permanent dipole n. chemistry labaqotinle waara; waxay dhacdaa markii laba atoms ee ku jira maalikiyuul (molecule), aad ugu kala duwanyihiin damaca soo jiidasho (electronegativity); atom ayaa ka soo jiidasho badan kan kale, waxa uuna noqdaa tabane (negative), marka kan kale inta badan noqdo togane (positive); maalikiyuulka noqda laba qotinle waara waxaa la dhahaa polar molecule.

perpetual motion n. socod waare; shay marka uu dhaqaaq bilaabo, waligiis wadaya asaga oo aan u baahan wax tamar dheeraad ah.

wave train n. hirar isku nooc ah oo mar wada dhaca.

phase shift n. sinqad waji; waji baddalasho walhasho (oscillation) ama hirar wada socda (wave train).

phase velocity n. keynaan waji; keynaan hal-baac-hireed hir (a single-wavelength wave), meesha “group velocity” lagu qeexo hirar raxaneed (a packet of waves) taas oo hirarku ku kala duwanyihiin baac-hireed (wavelength). kale loogu yeeraa wave velocity.

wave velocity n. eeg phase velocity.

phosphor (‘faas,far) n. or phosphore walax adke oo sii daysa iftiin ama nuurta, markii loo bandhigo kaah (radiation), sida ultraviolet light ama an electron beam.

photochemical cell n. abbr. PECs unug footokiimikaad; unugyo qorraxeed (solar cells) sameeya tamar danabeed (electrical energy).

photochemical equivalence n. gudboon footokimikaad; xeer asaasi ah oo la xariira falgallo kiimikaad if bayna keenaan, taas oo oranaysa: kaah kasta oo quantum la dhuuqay ah, hal molecule oo walax ah ayuu la falgalaa.  

photochemistry (,fawdhaw’kaamastarii) n. laan ka mid ah chemistry oo gooni u eegta kiimiko saamaysa if (light). -photochemist (ˌfawdahw’kemisti) n.

photoelectric absorption n. nuugis footodanabeed; electron la soo tufay (ejected) ama laga soo daayay (emitted) kadib markii walaxdaas laga nuugay tamartii photon (energy of photon).

photoemission (,fawdhaw-i’mishin) n. walxo adke ah, sida bir oo ku sii daaya electrons tamart ay ka heleen kaah, siiba iftiin. -photoemissive (ˌfawdhaw-i’misiv) adj.

photoelectron (,fawdhaw-i’lektaraan) n. footodanabyo; electron lagu sii daayay: photoemission. -photoelectronic (ˌfawdhaw-i,lek’taranik) adj.

photographic development n. or photographic processing caddayn masawir (sifeyn); hab kiimiko oo filim ama waraaq (film or paper) loo adeegto si loo sameeyo hummaag negative ama positive ah.

photovoltaic cell n. sida badan waxaa la dhahaa (solar cell) qalab si toos ah ilays qorraxda (sunlight) ugu baddala danab (electricity).

physical laws n. xeer dabiici; xeer muddo badan tijaabooyin lagu sameeyay aakhirkiina la isla qaatay.

physical optics n. laan optics ah oo gooni u eegta dabeecado ilays.

pico- comb. form summad p 1 horgale (prefix) halbeeg hab metric, lana mid ah hal trillionth (1 Pico = 10-12) qaybood: picogram 2 aad u yar: picornavirus.

picornavirus (ˌpii,korna’vaayras) n. faayras (virus) aad iyo aad u yaryar.

picofarad (,piikaw’faar,adh) n. abbr. pf hal trillionth oo farad.

pinhole camera n. sawirad (camera) aad u yar oo aan lahayn bikaaco (lens).

Planck's constant n. or Planck constant (summad h) madorsome Planck; madoorsoome gundhig caalami ah oo qeexa tamar dabiici ah ee quantum (quantum nature of energy) iyo tamar la xariirta ee photon rakaadkiis (a photon to its frequency), frequency leh qayme ah 6.62607015 × 10-34 joule seconds; formula: E = hf; meesha E = energy; h = Planck’s constant; f = frequency.

plane mirror n. muraayad sallax; duleed siman oo hummaag noqod celiya.

plane of incidence n. sallax abbaar; sallax xambaarsan fallaar iftiin (incident line), dushuna muraayad ahaan ka ah iyo bar fallaartu ku dhacday ama bar abbaar (point of incidence).

incidence line n. fallaar if (ray of light) oo ku dhacday dul muraayad; fallaar noqod (reflected ray); bar fallaar ku dhacdayna ama bar abbaar (point of incidence); haddii xarriiq bar qotin la sameeyo waxaa la dhahaa (the normal).

plane of reflection n. sallax noqod; sallax muraayadeed, fallaar iftiin oo ku dhacday (incident ray) oo samaysay fallaar noqod ama dalfis (reflected ray).

plane of refraction n. sallax qalloocan; markii hirar iftiin iskaga gudbaan hawo ilaa biyo ama biyo ilaa quraarad, oo ay qalloocdaan xawaarahana baddalaan.

pluton (‘puluu,taan) n. qar dhagax ah oo hoos ka soo hulaaqa (gubta).

point of incidence n. bar abbaar eeg incidence line.

point of reflection n. bar noqod; meel ama bar ilays fallaar uga dhacay muraayad oo uu noqod (dalfis) ka sameeyay.

point of refraction n. bar qalloocsan; meel uu ka qalloocdo ama jaho ka baddasho hir gudbaya meel.

point source n. il bareed; il kaah, hir, uuro, daad, ama wax kale oo hal il ka soo burqada. e.g. a point source of light.

polychromatic light n. midab-ilays dhafan; ilays baacyohireedyo (wavelengths) kala duwan leh.

positive ion n. aayoon togan; haddii atom haysto protons ka badan electrons, waa positive ion; ions haysta saldanab togan (positive charge) waxaa la dhahaa cations; kan haysta saldanab tabanna (negative charge) waxaa la dhahaa anions.

potential divider n. kayd qaybiye. eeg voltage divider.

power factor n. saami awood; saami awood hawl, laguna cabbiro kilowatts (kW).

apparent power n. wadar awood la haysto ee la isticmaalikaro sida, computer, ama lagu iftiiminkaro nal.

primary cell n. unug aasaasi; unug loo qaabeeyay in mar qur ah la isticmaalo lana tuuro, sida batari (battery).

primary coil n. duub asaasi; duub ku xariirsan il awood ka imaanayso (power source); secondary coil duub aan ku xirnayn il awood (power source).

primary focus n. kulmis asaasi; meel ay ku kulmaan fallaaro dhexmara bikaaco (lens) oo ah F1 iyo F2.

urinary pigment n. nooc kasta oo midab ah lagana helo kaadi.

urobilinogen (ˌyuurabaay’linajan) n. dheecaan aan lahayn midab oo ka yimaada mindhicir marka la burburiyo bilirubin oo ah burburin unuygo dhiig cas.

urobilin (,yuura’baaylan) n. also urochrome aashito (acid) sababa midab hurdi (yellow) ee kaadi.

stercobilinogen (,istrikaw’baaylinajan) n. eeg  urobilinogen.

 

bilirubin (,bili’ruuban) n. midab (yellow-orange) ah oo ka abuurmay burburin unugyo dhiig cas soona raaca kaadi ama saxaro. eeg jaundice.

 

primary pigment n. also subtractive primary rinji asaasi; saddexda midab oo asal ah (magenta, yellow, iyo cyan) loona soo gaabsho (red, yellow, iyo blue).

subtractive primary n. eeg primary pigment.

additive primary n. also component color waxay ka koobanyihiin (red, green, iyo blue light).

complementary color n. midab badan waxay ka koobanyihiin: Red iyo green; yellow iyo purple; orange iyo blue; green iyo magenta.

principal axis n. dhidib dhexaad; xarriiq mara kala bar ama dhex.

principal plane n. sallax dhexaad; sallax (plane) qoton la ah dhidib (bikaaco, muraayad ama muuqaal kale).

printed circuit n. mareego daabacan; loox (board) ay ku diyaarsan yihiin waxyaalo (components) mareeg ku xirmilahaa.

propagation of light n. baahid ilays; hab sharraxaya sida ilays ama hir birlabdanabeed (electromagnetic wave) ugu safro meel ilaa meel kale.

propagation velocity n. keynaan baahid; cabbir dhaqso intee le’eg buu waqti (time) ku safraa baaq (signal), ama xawaare baaq (signal) ku safro marka la barbardhigo xawaare if (speed of light).

quantum mechanics n. laan ka mid ah physics oo sharraxaad ka bixisa abtirsiimooyin walxo aad u yaryar iyo hirarkood saamayn ama gudbin tamar. kale loogu yeeraa wave mechanics. -quantum mechanical adj.; -quantum mechanically adv.

wave mechanics n. eeg quantum mechanics.

radiant energy n. tamar kaah; tamar (energy) u safarta sidii hirar birlabdanabeed (electromagnetic waves).

 

radiant flux n. burqad kaah; dhaqso siiddayn (emission) ama diris tamar kaah (radiant energy).

incident flux n. tamar (energy) dhulku helo ilbiriqsigii (per second).

radiant heat n. kul kaah; tamar kul oo meel looga gudbiyay meel kale, sida kul qorraxda ama nal.

radiating surface n. dul tamar kaah ku dhacayso.

radioactive chain n. silsilad kaahfal. eeg radioactive series.

radioactive series n. tax kaahfal; walxo xarira oo uu abuuray mataatax kaahfal (radioactive decay) ee thorium ama uranium, mid kasta oo ku siixigana mataataxaas ila curiye caadi ku soo noqdo.

radioactive contamination n. diiqow kaahfal; markii shucaac kaahfal gaaro dad iyo walxo kale.

radioactive constant n. madoorsoome kaahfal;

calaamaddan ayaa u taagan λ isle’eg (equation) It = Ioe−λ, meesha Io waa initial activity, It activity after time t, iyo e the natural logarithmic base.

radioactive equilibrium n. dheellitiran kaahfal; xaalad saami wax qabad ee ka dhexeeya hooyada bu’ (parent nuclide) iyo mid kasta ee mataataxeed kaahfal (its radioactive decay) oo ah mardoorsoome (constant).

radioactive source n. il kaahfal; tiro la ogyahay oo bu’ qurub sii daayso (radionuclide) nooc tamareed (ionizing radiation), sida: gamma rays, alpha particles, beta particles, and neutron radiation.

radioactivity (,reydiiyawaak’tivatii) n. kaahfalid; waxaa keeya mataatax bu’ (decay nuclei), taas oo joogto u sii daysa kaah (radiation).

artificial radioactivity n. kaahfal ay abuureen walxo xawli sare (high speed) isku jiiray, sida protons ama neutrons. kale loogu yeeraa induced radioactivity.

induced radioactivity n. eeg artificial radioactivity.

natural radioactivity n. kaahfalid dabiici.

radio wave hir raadiyaw; hir birlabdanabeed (electromagnetic) wehliya rakaad raadiyaw (radio frequency).

 

ray tracing n. fallaar raac; hab lagu xisaabo marin hirareed ama saxarro (particles) hab meelo kala duwan.

reflectance n. physics noqdin; saamiya birlabdanabeed inteed kaah, siiba ilays (light) ka dalfismatay dusha (reflected from surface) inteedii hore ee ku dhacday dusha meeshaas.

diffuse reflection n. noqod hablaawe; iftiin ku dhacay meel sallax ah oo dalfiskiisii dhalay fallaaro badan.

Snell’s law of refraction n. haddii ilays ku safro dhexda biyo ama quraarad qallooc (refraction) iyo dalfisba (reflection) waa imaan.

refractive index n. wehliye qalloocsan; cabbir qalloocan fallaar ilays marka ay dhaafayso meel ilaa meel kale (from one medium to another).

residual charge n. saldanab haraa; marka la damiyo mareeg, xoogaaga saldanab (charge) oo ku hara madhxiyaha (capacitor).

rest energy n. tamar fadhi; haddii tamar lagu kaydiyo shay (object), cufkeed (mass) wuu kordhaa; tamar fadhida waa: E0 = mc2, taas oo macnahaeedu yahay cufkaasi waa nooc tamareed (form of energy).

rheostat (‘riiya,staat) n. also variable resistor caabbi doorsoome; waxaa lagula socdaa socod qulqul danab (electric current) in uu kordhay ama yaraaday caabbi (resistance). –rheostatic adj.

 

ripple tank n. haan hirbiyood; haan weyn oo quraarad ah oo lagu soo bandhigo hirar aasaasi ah.

scalar quantity n. xaddi foolwaa; scalar waa tiro la qeexay oo kali ah lixaadkiis (magnitude); vector lixaad iyo jiho wax; mass (cuf) iyo speed (xawaare) waa xaddi foolwaa (scalar quantities).

 

searchlight (‘sajlaayt) n. also spotlight ilays-raadiye; dhud naleed (beam of light) oo aad u xoogbadan.

short-circuit (ˈshorti’sarkat) v. short-circuited; short-circuiting; short-circuits demin ama qarxin mareeg. e.g. To prevent short-circuiting, keep the batteries away from metal objects when carrying.

sideband (‘saaydh,baand) n. liid dhinac; mawjad rakaad, sida hirar raadiyaw oo dhinac kasta rakaad qaade u gudbiyo.

siren disk n. daawe sayran; farsamo gacmeed saxan dulduleela oo wareegaya hawo xoogganna ku afuumato si uu u sameeyo cod dawan.

smooth surface n. gibil siman; oogo siman oo aan lahayn xanaf, dalool, ama buurbuur.

solenoid (‘sawla,noydh) n. duub xaasow; dhulubo silig maroorsan oo marka uu qaadayo qulqul u shaqeeya birlab ahaan loona isticmaalo furis ama xiris, sida: door locking in hotels, offices and secure areas, vending machines, remote access systems, turnstiles, car parks and access barriers. –solenoidal (ˌsawla’noydhal) adj.

sound energy n. tamar jabaq; tamar dhaqaaq oo ku marta hawo ama biyo qaab hirareed (waves), taas oo uu keenay xoog gariir.

sonometer (sa’naamadha) n. jabaqbeege; qalab lagu ogaanjiray xariir ka dhaxeeya rakaad jabaq (frequency of sound) oo uu sameeyay xarig togan.

spectral line n. xarriijin jeegaan; mid ka mid ah hummaag xarriiq oo ku timid jeegaan midabyo laga soocay.

spectrum emission n. bikaacin jeegaan; curiye kiimiko (chemical element) ama iskudhis kiimiko (chemical compound) ee jeecgaan rakaadyo (spectrum of frequencies) uu sii daayay kaah birlabdanabeed (electromagnetic radiation emitted) atom ama maalikiyuul heer tamar sare (high energy state) una socda heer tamar hoose (lower energy state).

spectrum continuous n. jeegaan isujoog; jeegaan socota oo xambaarsan ilays baacyohirar (wavelength of light) oo dhan ilaa xad fogaaneed.

standing wave n. hir taagan; iskudar laba hir oo u kala socda jahooyin lid isku ah, mid walbana haysto isku awood iyo rakaad.

step-up transformer n. dooriye kordhiye; dooriye (transformer) kordhiya voltage: from primary to secondary.

step-down transformer n. dooriye yareeye; dooriye (transformer) naaqisiya voltage: from the primary coil into low voltage in the secondary coil.

stroboscope (‘istarawba,iskawp) n. 1 qalab lagu barto ama lagu eego tartiib-dhaqaaq (slow moving) shay socda. 2 saxan wareega oo duleello ku leh geesaha oo wax laga daawankaro.

superconductor (,suparkan’dhaktar) n., pl. superconductors gudbiye sare; walax aan lahayn wax caabbi (resistance) ah qulqul danab marka uu jiro heerkul aad u qabaw, sida: aluminum, magnesium diboride, niobium, copper oxide, yttrium barium iyo iron pnictides.

superposition principle n. markii hirar laba iyo ka badan ay meel iska jaraan, barabaxaha (displacement) bartaas waxay la mid tahay wadarta barabaxyada hal-hal hirar.

surface friction n. dul islis; caabbi ka horyimaada shay dhaqaaq ku jira ee oogada dhulka ama meel kale.

syphon (‘saayfan) n. also siphon dhuun dareere looga kala shubo laba weel oo midkood hooseeyo.

heterogeneous system n. hab kala duwan; waxyaalo isla baddala hab oo dhawr warji yeesha, sida biyo iskugu baddalaan adke (baraf).

homogenous system n. waxyaalo aan isla baddalin hab oo wajiga ay ku bilaabaan ku dhammada.

tangential acceleration n. karaar taabte; dhaqaaq isla baddala karaar taabasho (tangential velocity) ee walax ku jirta jid goobo ama wareeg (circular path).

tangential velocity n. keynaan taabte; xawaare xarriiqeed (linear speed) ee shay kasta oo ku dhaqaaqa jid wareeg ama goobo (circular path).

temperature scale n. cabbir heerkul; inta badan laba cabbir ayaa jira, Celsius scale iyo Fahrenheit scale.

terminal velocity n. keynaan dhammaad; keynaan ugu sarreeya shay ku dhexdhacay dareere; terminal velocity:  v = sqrt {(2×w) / (Cd×r×A)}; meesha v = velocity; w = weight; Cd = drag coefficient; r = density; A = frontal area.

thermal equilibrium n. dheellitiran kul; xaalad qaybo hab oo dhan ay isku heerkul wada yihiin.

thermal expansion n. kul fidin; dhumucda adke ama mug dareere oo kordha markii heerkul kaco.

thermal transmission n. tabin kul; dhaqsaha walax ku gudbinkarto kul.

thermionic emission (,tharmaay’aanik ii’mishan) n. kul bixin ayoon; hab electrons laga bixiyay bir (metal) taas oo heerkulkeeda la gaarsiiyay xad ku filan in ay ka takhalusto xoog soo jiidasho qurub bu’ bir (atomic nucleus); siidayntaan waxaa la dhahaa thermions.

thermocouple (‘tharma,kapal) n. labasaxan kul; qalab dareeme (sensor) wata oo cabbira heerkul; waxa uuna ka koobanyahay laba birood oo kala duwan oo dhinac-dhammaad iskaga guntan.

thermoelectricity (,tharmawi,lektarisadhii) n. kuldanab; danab (electricity) uu abuuray kul toos ah, sida kululayn aan isle’ekayn ee mareeg ka kooban laba birood oo kala duwan (two dissimilar metals).

gas thermometer n. kulbeege neef; qalab lagu cabbiro heerkul, asaga oo la soconaya isbaddal caddaadis (pressure) ama mug (volume) neef meel ku xiran.

liquid-filled thermometer n. kulbeege hoorkujir; kulbeeg leh dhuun quraaradeed oo labo dhinac ka xiran qaarkeedna laga buuxiyay dareere, sida mercury ama alcohol.

translational energy n. tamar rarid; tamar uu wato shay ku safraya jid toosan, sida wax soo dhacaya (free falling body). kale loogu yeeraa translational kinetic energy.

translational kinetic energy n. eeg translational energy.

transmission line n. xarig gudbin; xargo gudbiya danab ama hirar raadiyaw (radio frequencies).

transverse wave n. hir gudban; hir wax gariiray u dhaqaaqaan dhinac qotin (perpendicular) la ah jihada hir u socdo.

traveling wave n. hir socdaal; socdaal hir meel buu ka tagaa oo meel kale ayuu aadaa.

ultrasonic wave n. hir cod oo rakaadyo (frequencies) ka sarreeyaan hirar caadi ah ee dhago dad maqlikaraan.

unit vector n. halbeeg leeb; mid magnitude kiisu la mid yahay hal; calamddaan koofida ah "cap" symbol (^) ayaana lagu muujiyaa.

uranium series n. or uranium-radium series tax kaahfal; tax kaafal (radioactive series) oo ka bilawda 238 kuna dhammaada isotope lead ah oo deggan lehna tiro cuf (mass number) 206.

vapor density n. cufnaan uumi; xajmi uumi oo xariir kala dhexeeyo hydrogen.

vector field n. badad-leeb; urur leebab ah oo mid walba loo qoondeeyay in uu tilmaamo meel.

vector potential n. kaydfaraq leeb; badad birlabeed (magnetic fields) waxaa lagu cabbiraa hawl la qabtay si ay u dhaqaajiso qulqul walax; formula: B = ∇ × A, E = − ∇ ϕ − ∂ A ∂ t; meesha B tahay magnetic field; E tahay electric field.

Vernier scale n. mastarad Vernier; waxaa loogu magacdaray Pierre Vernier, waa mastarad leh akhrin cabbir sax ah.

vibrational energy n. tamar-gariir; tamar waxay ku jirtaa hab gariir, ama nasiino (rest).

voltaic pile n. dhagxan danab (electrical battery) ee si toos ah joogto qulqul danab u siisay mareeg. Waxaa alifay chemist Talyaani ah Alessandro Volta, 1799.

redox reaction n. redox yarayn; falgal kiimiko oo laba falgal dhexdood electrons lagu baddalo.

voltaic cell n. unug kiimiko danabeed oo u baddala tamar kiimikaad falgal kiimiko (redox reaction) ama u baddala tamar danab (electrical energy).

water equivalent n. udhigan biyood; tiro inteed biyood laga rabo in lagu kardhiyo tiro inteed le’eg oo kul ah oo halkii degree cunayo biyo.

wave analyzer n. hir tuse; qalab lalgu cabbiro ka koobnaan awood baaq kaah (amplitudes of single frequency) ee complex waveform.

wave energy n. tamar hireed; qaab tamar dabiici ah oo looga faa’iidaysan karo socod hir.

wave equation n. isle’eg hireed; qayb waa isle’eg xigsiineed (differential equation) second order oo maxsuulkeed (solutions) caddeeyo arrim hir.

wave filter n. hir miire; liil cariiryoon oo ogolaada gudbin baachireedyada gaaban ama dhaadheer ayada oo la dalfiyo (reflected) baachireeyada aan loo baahnayn.

waveform (‘weyv,foorm) n. qaab-hireed; garaaf (graph) muujiya waqti (time) isla baddala hir.

wave front n. hor hireed. kale loogu yeeraa waveshape.

waveshape n. eeg wave front.

wave function n. chemistry fansaar hireed (Ψ);

fansaar xisaabeed oo la xariira electron meel uu ka marayo bar lagu tilmaamay (identified by x, y, iyo z coordinates) awooddiis hireed (amplitude of its wave), oo ku xiran tamatiisa (its energy).

waveguide (‘weyv,gaaydh) n. dabaqad kasta oo qalabyo xaqiijiya ama jiheeya hirar birlabdanabeed (electromagnetic waves), sida radio waves, infrared rays, iyo visible light.

wave intensity n. itaal hireed; dhaqaaq tamar lagu xawilo oo loo qaybiyay meel (area) lagu baahiyay tamar.

hadron (‘haa,daraan) n. saxar ka sii yaryar (subatomic particle) oo ka samaysan  quarks, gluons iyo anti-quarks; waana kuwa ugu culus saxarro (particles); waxayna ka kooban yihiin laba iyo ka badan quarks oo uu aad iskugu hayo xoog birlabdanabeed (electromagnetic force). –hadronic (haa’daraanik) adj.

elementary particles n. waxa ugu yar wax jira adduunkaan, mana lahan wax dhisme gudaha ah mana buuxin karaan meel.

quark (ˈkuwork) n. protons waxay ka koobanyihiin (two up quarks iyo one down quark), meesha neutron ka kooban yahay (two down quarks iyo one up quark); kaligood ma jirikaraan laakiin waa qayb ka mid ah walxo.

weak interaction n. eeg weak force.

weak force n. hardi fudud; xoog gundhig u ah dabeecad oo qaabeeya kaahfalid (radioactivity), xukumana mataatax subatomic aan degganayn. kale loogu yeeraa weak interaction, weak nuclear force.

weak nuclear force n. eeg weak force.
