hysterectomy (,hista’rektamii) n., pl. hysterectomies  qalliin lagu saaro min: to remove all of or part of the uterus. -hysterectomized (ˌhista’rekta,maayzti) adj.

iatrogenic (,aay,aatra’jenik) n. wax aan kas ku imaan oo ay sababeen dhakhaatiir, daawayn, ama hab baaris. e.g. An iatrogenic illness. -iatrogenically (ˌaay,aatra’jeniklii) adv.

ice pick headache n. madaxa wareen aad u daran oo dhaqso ku yimaada kuna taga.

immunoglobulin E (,imya,naw’galaabiyalan) n. abbr. IgE (,aay,jii ii) walax mas’uul ka ah inta badan ka falcelinta xasaasiyad.

immunotherapy (,iminaw’therapi) n. kula diririd cudur ayada oo la xoojiyo habka isdifaaca jirka (body’s immune system). eeg adoptive immunotherapy.

implantable cardioverter defibrillator n. qalab lagu xiro xabadka, laguna xariiriyo wadnaha si uu uga hortago garaaca wadnaha oo khatar ku sugan.

adoptive immunotherapy n. qaab daaweyn oo adeegta unugya habka difaaca jirka (immune system) in ay ka takhalusaan kaankarada (cancer).

in situ (,in’saay,dhuu; ,in’sii,tuu) adv. or adj. sida caadiga ah ama rugtii (meeshii) hore.

incubation period n. kal huuris; waqtiga u dhaxeeya markii cudurka la qaaday iyo markii ifafaalihiisa la arkay.

infiltrating cancer n. kaankaro (cancer) faafaya.

ingrown toenail n. ciddi-jiifto; xaalad ciddida suulku duleeliso hilibka oo kenta xanuun, barar, ama hurgun.

inhibitory neurochemical n. kiimiko joojisa dhambaal isku dirka dareeme ilaa dareeme kale.

injectable fillers n. walxo lagu duro maqaarka si loo buuxiyo duuduubka ama loo buuriyo bushinta.

innate immunity n. difaaca aasaasiga ah ee jirku kula dagaalo cudurada ama hurgunka la socda umulidda. kale loogu yeeraa natural immunity. Barbardhig acquired immunity, active immunity, passive immunity.

insulin-dependent diabetes n. macaanka loo qaato daawada insulin. kale loogu yeeraa type 1 diabetes.

intense pulsed light n. qalab iftiin daaya oo jirka qurxiya ama rujiya timaaha aan loo rabin.

interleukin (,intar’luukan) n. abbr. IL dheecaan (cytokine proteins) yar-yar oo qanjiradu sii daayaan, uguna wada xariiran habka difaaca jirka.

intermittent claudication n. xanuun iyo muruq-go’ lugaha ah, watiga jimicsiga oo uu keeno cariiryaw ama xirmad halbawle.

intracerebral hemorrhage n. dhiig-bax dhiig-furan oo uu keenay dillaac xidid dhiigeed ama dhiig joogto ugu qulqula xuubka maskada.

intraocular lens n. bikaaco (lens) la gasho il bu’deed si ay u baddasho tii u dhalasho, inta lagu gudajiro qalliinka fiiqidda isha.

hyperthyroidism (,haaypar’thaay,roy,dhiizam) n. ganjirada luqunta (thyroid glands) oo qabta shaqo dheeraad ah, keentana ayaga oo barara, wadnaha oo aad u garaacma, iyo dhiigkar.

iodide (‘aaya,dhaydh) n. cusbo (milix) ay ku jirto iodine: binary compound of iodine and another element or radical.

ketonuria (,kiidha’nuuriya) n. medical kaadida oo ay ku badnaato ketone body. Barbardhig ketonemia.

ketonemia (,kiita’niimiya) n. medical xaalad aan caadi ahayn ee ketone body ku kororto wareegga dhiigga. Barbardhig ketonuria.

ketone body n. aasidh (acids) jirku sameeyo marka uu burburiyo baruur (fats) si uu uga helo tamar (energy); sida caadiga ah unugyada dhiiggu waxay isticmaalaan sonkorta dhiigga (blood glucose) si ay tamar uga helaan. Haddii ay ku fillaan waydo, markaas ayaa baruurta la burburshaa, waxayna keentaa ketones.

ischemic stroke n. cudurka faaligga oo uu sababay qulqulka dhiigga maskaxda aada oo xinjiroobay.

islets of Langerhans n. xirmo unugyada dheecaanka sameeya oo ay ku jiraan, alpha iyo beta oo kulligood ka soo muuqda ganaca (pancreas).

isotonic (,aaysa’taanik) adj. 1 la xariira laba muruq oo cadaadis isku mid ah leh. 2 laba milan oo ismile (solute) iyo isku ribbanaan (concentration) le’eg: isosmotic. e.g. isosmotic solutions. Barbardhig isometric. -isotonically (ˌaaysa’taaniklii) adv.; -isotonicity (ˌaaysataw’nisitii) n.

lacuna (la’kuuna) n., pl. lacunae (la’kiyuu,nii) also lacunas (la’kuunaz)1 dululaati yar; meel maran ama kalajeex. 2 ku yar ama dhimman. -lacunar (la’kuunar) adj., also -lacunate (la’kuunat).

lipoma (laay’pawma) n., pl. lipomas also lipomata (laay’pawmata) buruq aan ahayn kaankaro (nonmalignant tumor) ama wax ka soo baxa xididdada dufanka (fat cells). -lipomatous (laay’pawmatas) adj.

lymphoma (lim’fawma) n., pl. lymphomas also lymphomata (lim’fawmata) nooc ka mid ah kaankarada (cancer) waxyeeleeyana unugyada dhiigga cad (lymphatic system). -lymphomatous (lim’fawmatas) adj.

diglyceride (‘dhaay’gilisaraaydh) n. dufan laga helo saytun iyo mir suuf oo cuntada ka caawisa isku qasanka saliidda iyo biyaha.

emulsifier (i’maalsa,faayar) n. iskuqase; iskulabe.

additive identity n. asal madoorshe isugayn; tiro markii wax lagu daro, keenta tiradii hore. e.g. 4 + 0 = 4; sidaa darteed, 0 waa additive identity ee tiro kasta oo run ah (any real number).

additive inverse n. iswaydaar isugayn; tiro markii lagu daro tiro lagu siiyay ku siisa eber. e.g. The additive inverse of 5 is -5.

stearate (‘istiiya,reyt) n. budo cad oo laga keenay xayr adag iyo baruur.

magnesium stearate n. chemistry iskudhis kiimiko oo budo cad ah (magnesium salt) iyo xayr (fatty acid) laguna daro qobka kiniini (capsule); loona adeegto xayrayn iyo jilcin.

monoglyceride (,maana’gilisaraaydh) n. noocyo xayr ah oo wax lagu qaso.

rennin (rennan) n. garooriso; nafaqo dhafaagaysa caanaha.  

caseinogen (key’siinajan) n. protein ugu muhiimsan caanaha kuna jirto nafaqo (phosphoprotein) ee caanaha garoorisa.

macroalbuminuria (,maakrawal,biyuma’nuriya) n. nafaqo (albumin) oo in ka badan 300 milligrams per 24-hour raacdo kaadida. Barbardhig microalbuminuria.

macrophage (‘maakra,feeyj) n. nooc unugyada dhiigga cad oo burburiya jajabka unugyada, jeermiska, iyo walxaha qalaad. -macrophagic (ˌmaakra’faajik) adj.

histiocyte (ˈhistiya,saayt) n. eeg macrophage. -histiocytic (ˌhistiya’sidhik) adj.

macula (‘maakila) n., pl. maculae (ˈmaaki,lii)  also maculas il qaybteeda tusisa wixii horteeda ah oo kali ah. -macular (ˈmaakilar) adj.

macular degeneration n. cudur indhaha tartiib u beeliya araggooda fiican.

macular edema n. qoyaan isha ku dhasha oo ka yimid xididdada dhiigga oo dhashuuma.

bubble bath n. 1 saabuun-abureed (xunbo) gaar ah leh oo lagu qabaysto. e.g. He took a bubble bath. 2 saabuun samaysa abur.

major histocompatibility complexe n., pl. major histocompatibility complexes abbr. MHC maalikiyuullo (molecules) jirka ka difaaca walxaha dibadda uga yimaada. Barbardhig HLA.

malaise (ma’leyz) n. dareen guud ee jirro ama cudur u noqon kara calaamad.

malignant hypertension n. dhiigkar khatar ah oo dhaqso dhiigga u kiciya, badanaa wata madaxwareer, hummaag-arag, iyo suuxdin.

mastoid bone (‘maa,stoydh) adj. lafta dhagta-raadkeeda.

mastoidectomy (ˌmaa,stoy’dhektamii) n., pl. mastoidectomies qalliin dhagta ah lafta dhagta raadkeeda ah (mastoid).

mastoid cell (‘maa,stoydh) n. unur yar oo hawo buuxdo ku aadka gudaha dhagta-raakeeda (mastoid bone).

mastopexy (‘maastaw,peksi) n., pl. mastopexies qalliin naaso dhacay kor loogu qaado. kale loogu yeeraa breast lift.

breast lift n. eeg mastopexy.

megaloblastic anemia n. unugyada dhiigga cas oo ku yaraada wareegga dhiigga, keentanya yaraanta vitamin B12.

meglitinides n. nooc daawo oo loo qaato type 2 diabetes.

melanocyte (ma’laana,saayt) n., pl. melanocytes unugyo ku jira maqaarka hoostiisa oo sameeya midabka. Barbardhig melanophore.  

melanophore (ma’llaana,foor) n., pl. melanophores unug xambaarsan midabaynta oo laga helo kalluun, barribiyood (amphibians), iyo xamaarato (reptiles).

melatonin (,mela’tawnan) n. dheecaan joogteeya hurdada/toosidda waqtigeeda.

meninx (,miininkis) n., pl. meninges (ma’nin,jiiz) xuub maskaxeed; saddex xuub oo daboola, difaacdana maskaxda iyo xangullaha: dura mater (kan kore); arachnoid mater (kan dhexe); pia mater (kan hoose).

dura mater (ˈdura ,meydhar) n. xuubka sare oo daboola maskaxda iyo xangullaha, kana sii kala hooseeyaan xuubabka (arachnoid mater iyo pia mater).  

metabolic equivalent n. abbr. MET halbeeg lagu qiyaaso hawada la qaadanayo, iyo wax qabadka la samaynayo. e.g. 3.5 milliliters oo oxygen ah × kilogram culaabta qof × minute (3.5 ml O2kg/min).

metered-dose inhaler n. abbr. MDI qalab bixiya qiyaasta (dose) daawada neef laga qaadankaro.

methanobrevibacter smithii n. jeermis caloosha ku jira oo caawiya dheefshiidka sonkorta adag.

microaneurysm (,maaykraw’anii,rizam) n. or microaneurism laqan yar oo ku abuurma gudaha xididka dhiigga. -microaneurysmal (maykaw,aanii’rizmal) adj.

microdermabrasion (,maaykrawderma’bareyshan) n. abbr. MDA hab jirqurxis oo wajiga lagu buufiyo walxo dhaldhalaala, qariyana dildillaacayda wajiga.

microgram (‘maaykra’garaam) n. abbr. MCG halbeeg culaab oo la mid ah 1/1000 milligram.

micronutrient (,maykraw’nuutriyanti) n. walxo kiimiko (sida calcium iyo vitamin C) oo gundhig u ah korista iyo caafimaadka unuyada noolaha. Barbardhig macronutrient.

microvascular disease n. xaalad xididdada yar-yar ee gudaha gidaarka wadnaha ay cariiryoobaan ama kala baxaan.

microvasculature (,maaykraw’vaaskilar) adj. la xariira jirka xididdadiisa ugu yar-yar. – microvasculature (ˌmaaykraw’vaaskila,juur) n.

middle ear n. meel yar oo hawo buuxisay oo ka danbaysa durbaan-dhageedka (eardrum), taas oo xambaarsan saddexda lafood  ee yar-yar oo gudaha dhagta u sii gudbiya gariirka dhawaqa.

mild cognitive impairment n. shaqooyinka maskaxda oo qaar dhumo, sida xasuus, fakar, ama hadal, laakiin aan dhabqin hawl-maalmeedka kale.

miotic (maay’aadhik) n. also myotic dhibic daawo oo isku soo ururisa il bu’deed.                                   -adj. miotic also myotic la xariira wax il bu’deed soo ururiya.

miosis (maay’awsis) n., pl. mioses also myoses (maay’aw,siiz) or myosis isku soo ururis aad ah ee il bu’deed.  

mitochondrion (,maaydha’kaandariyan) n., pl. mitochondria (ˌmaaydha’kaandariya) walxo yar-yar oo ku jira unugyada, burburiyana nafaqooyinka (nutrients), tamarna u abuura unugyada. -mitochondrial (ˌmaaydha’kaandariyal) adj.

mitral (‘maaytaral) adj. laga aqoon koofi kor u yuumbaysan oo wadaad kaniisadeed u xirto xaflad.

mitral valve n. mid ka mid ah xuubabka wadnaha kala xira oo xukuma dhiiggu in uu hal dhinac u qulqulo, laga bilaabo wadnaha qolka sare ee bidix (left atrium) ilaa qolka bidix ee hoose (left ventricle). kale loogu yeeraa bicuspid valve.

bicuspid valve n. eeg mitral valve.

left atrioventricular valve n. eeg mitral valve.

monoamine oxidase inhibitor n. daawooyin loo qaadan jiray murugada iyo niyadxumida.

monounsaturated (,maanaw,an’saaja,reydhidh) n. xambaarsan hal dabar lammaane ama saddex dabar maalikiyuulkii (per molecule), inta badan saliid, dufan, ama fatty acid. -monounsaturate (ˌmaanaw,en’saajarat) adj.

polyunsaturated (ˌpaali,yaan’saaja’reydhidh) n. xambaarsan dabarro lammaane ama saddexan (double or triple bonds) maalikiyuul ahaan, siiba saliid ama dufan (an oil or fatty acid). Barbardhig monounsaturated.

Morton’s neuroma n. dareenqaadayaasha faraha lugaha oo adkaada, keenana cun-cun, kabuubyo, iyo hurid cagta ah.

motilin (maw’tillan) dheecaan ka caawiya mindhicir-yaraha in uu dhuuqsamo oo cuntada u gudbiyo marinka dheefshiidka.

motility (maw’tiladhi) n. 1 dhaqaaq awood, sida swimming, swarming, twitching, gliding, and sliding). 2 docosho; awoodda marinada dheefshiidku ay ku dhaqaajiyaan waxa ku dhexjira (contents).

flagellum (fala’jelam) n., pl. flagella (fala’jeela) also flagellums ilma-aragto sayn-jeedalley oo dhaqaajisa unug.    

mucosa (miyuu’kawsa) n., pl. mucosae (miyu’kaw,zii) or mucosas marinnada jirka gudiisa, sida marinada dheefshiidka, hawada, iyo xibnaha taranka. -mucosal (miyu’kawzal) adj.

mucocele (‘miyuuka,siil) n. nabar biyo wata oo afka ama meelo kale ka soo baxa, inta bushimaha la leefo ama la dhuuqo (lip biting, lip sucking). kale loogu yeeraa mucous cysts.  

mucocutaneous (,muyuukawkuu’teyniyas) adj. la xariira ama saameeya maqaarka ama gudaha dhuumaha marinnada jirka.

multi-infarct dementia n. xis-guur; xasuusta oo dhunta iyo fakarka oo wiiqma, sababtayna maskaxad oo dhigfuran yar oo aan la dareemikarin ku dhacay.

multinodular (moolti’naajalar) n. nudo ama guntimo badan leh: little knot or lump.

multinodular goiter n. cuna-bacuuc; qanjir-barar.

multiple sclerosis n. cudur dabadheeraada oo ku dhaca barta hoggaaminta dareemayaasha (central nervous system).

multiple sleep latency test n. hurdo-maalmeed lagu eego dhaqsaha qof u gami’karo markii la seexiyo meel deggan oo mugdi ah.

muscularis (,maskiya’leeras) n. 1 lakabka mulaaxda ah ee muruq. 2 lakabyada jilicsan ee qaabeeya gudaha hunguriga.

mydriasis (ma’draayasis) n. daawo ballaarisa il bu’deed. -mydriatic (ˌmidri’yaadhik) adj. or n.

myelography (,maaya’laagrafi) n., pl. myelographies baaris raajo (x-ray) oo lagu eego dhibaatada xangullaha (spinal cord).

myocardial infarction n. abbr. MI wadne-xanuun; dhimasho deg-deg ah oo qayb wadnaha ka mid ah hawo (oxygen) waydo.

MI n. abbr. myocardial infarction.

myocarditis (,maaya’kaardhaaydhis) n. hurgun wadnaha muruqiisa ah: myocardium.

dehort (,dii’horti) v. ka waanin; uga digid. e.g. His wife dehorted him from going Somalia: to dissuade.

myocyte (‘maaya,saayt) n. unug muruqeed: a single muscle fiber cell.

myosin (‘maayasan) n. nafaqo caawisa in muruqu adkaado ama dabco.

nanograms per milliliter n. abbr. ng/ml tiro walax aad u yar, lana mid ah 1/1000,000,000 gram (454 grams samaysa 1 pound).

ala (ey’laa) n., pl. alae (ˈeey,lii) baal shinbireed ama u eg. -alar (ˈeelar) adj.; alary (ˈeeylarii) adv.

nasolabial folds (,neysal’leybiyal) n. laba canjiid oo ka soo daga sanka labadiisa dhinac ilaa labada qawlal oo hoose.

natural killer cell n. unugyo dhiigga cad ah oo baabi’iya unugyada kale oo istilmaami waaya.

natural recovery n. qof balwadii uu lahaa iskiis uga haray.

neoadjuvant therapy n. sii bilaabid inta aan la gaarin daawaynta weyn ee cudur.

neoplasm (‘niiya’palaazam) n. balaq; cad weynaada, oo kaankaro soo wado ama caadi ah.

nerve block n. irbad lagu duro dareeme si xanuun looga qaado. kale loogu yeeraa nerve blocking.

neurofibrillary tangles n. nafaqooyin (proteins) unugyo dareemayaal ah oo isku tidcamay, dhintayna ama dhimanaya ee dadka qaba cudurka Alzheimer’s.

neuromuscular junction n. meel yar oo u dhaxaysa xididka dareemaha meesha uu ku dhammaado iyo muruqa dushiisa.

peptide (‘pep,taaydh) n. maalikiyuul (molecule) xambaarsan laba iyo ka badan amino acids, wayna isku xirxirmaan si ay u noqdaan proteins. kale loogu yeeraa polypeptides or proteins. -peptidic (pep’tidhik) adj.

polypeptide (,paalii’pep,taaydh) n. silsilad maalikiyuuleed (molecular chain) ee amino acids. -polypeptidic (ˌpaalii,pep’tidhik) adj.

neuropeptide (,nuura’pep,taaydh) n. nafaqo yar oo gargaarta gudbinta baaqyada ka dhaxeeya unugyada dareenqaadayaasha.

neurosyphilis (,niraw’siflas) n. caabuq dhif ah ee ku yimaada maskaxada iyo xangullaha markii aan la iska daawayn cudurka waraabawga.

nitrate (,naay’tareydh) n., pl. nitrates 1 cusbada nitrate acid. 2 sodium nitrate ama potassium nitrate. 3 daawo ahaan kala bixisa xididdada dhigga, inta badanna lagu daaweeyo xabad-xanuun.

nitroglycerin (,naytara’gilisaran) n. daawo dabcisa xididdada dhiigga oo gaarsiisa wadnaha dhiig iyo hawo (oxygen). Badanaa waxaa lagu daaweeyaa angina (xabad-xanuun aan waarin).

nociceptor (,nowsi’septar) n. dareemayaal dira wixii jirka khatar ku ah ama dhaawacaya.

nocturia (,naak’tuuriya) n. hal jeer ka badan kaadin u soo kaca habaynkii: nycturia.

nycturia (nik’tuuriya) n. eeg nocturia.

nocturia (naak’tuuriya) n. habayn kaadis badan. kale loogu yeeraa nycturia.

non-insulin-dependent diabetes n. macaanka dhiigga ku jira oo aad u sarreeyaa, waayo unugyadu ma qaadankaraan insulin. kale loogu yeeraa type 2 diabetes.

noninvasive test n. baarid caafimaad oo aan u baahnayn qalab caafimaad in jirka la galiyo.

nonketotic hyperglycemic hyperosmolar syndrome n. type 2 diabetes, dhif aadna khatar u ah, gaarana in ka badan (800 mg/dl) heerka macaanka dhiigga.

retinopathy (,reeta’naapathi) n., pl. retinopathies xaalad xididdada yar-yar ee isha gurexeeda ay dhashuumaan carun ama dhiig.

serum (‘siiram) n., pl. sera (ˈsiira) or serums 1 alax; biyo cad oo jirka xoolaha ku jira. 2 carun. 3 biyaha gala nabar ama meel gubatay. 4 geedaha biyahooda. 5 caanaha markay bur-iyo-biyo u kala baxaan, siiba qaybta biyaha (whey).                                                -adj. carun ah ama leh.

nonsteroidal anti-inflammatory drug n. abbr. NSAID daawo yaraysa bararka iyo xanuunka.

normal-pressure hydrocephalus n. dareere maskaxda ku dhurma oo u keena barar, socod dhib ah, iyo kaadida oo la haynwaayo.

nucleus pulposus (‘nuukliyas ,pal’pawsas) n., pl. nuclei pulposi (‘nuukliyaay ,pal’pawsaay) dhareer (dheecaan) ku jira xibnaha lafdhabarta.

obstructive sleep apnea n. abbr. OSA also obstructive sleep apnea syndrome or obstructive apnea khuuro culus oo qasta neefsashada, waxayna keentaa dhiigkar iyo dhiig-furan maskaxda.

sorb (soorb) v. sorbed; sorbing; sorbs ku-qaadid dhuuqid ama nuugis. e.g. They need to sorb more sodium fluoride. -sorbability (ˌsoorba’bilatii) n.; -sorbable (ˈsoorbabal) adj.

occlusion (a’kluushan) n. 1 xirmasho. e.g. Occlusion of the arteries. 2 isku xiris; isqabsasho, siiba ilkaha labada qal marka la isku keeno.

oncogene (‘aankaw,jiin) n. hidda-side (gene) awood u leh unug caadi ah in uu ka dhigo mid qaba kaankaro (cancerous).

chromatin (‘karawmatan) n. iskujir DNA, RNA, iyo proteins oo qaabeeya hidda-side laga helo gudaha unugyada dadka iyo noolayaasha kale. –chromatinic (ˌkarawma’tinik) adj.

euchromatin (,yuu’krawmatan) n. qayb ka mid ah iskujir DNA iyo proteins (chromatin) hiddo ahaanna firfircoon oo inta badan ka kooban hidda-sidayaal (genes). -euchromatic (ˌyuukraw’maadhik) adj.

histone (hi,stawn) n., pl. histones xayn kasta oo ka tirsan proteins  laga helo gudaha chromatin oo qaab-dhismeedka ka caawiya hidda-side (chromosome).

onychomycosis (,aanakawmaay’kawsis) n., pl. onychomycoses (,aanakawmaay’kaw,siiz) fangas (fungal) gala ciddiyaha.

open prostatectomy n. qalliin furan oo lagu saaro ama lagu jaro qanjirka (prostate gland) ayada oo dhinaca caloosha loo marayo.

optic nerve n. dareemaha isha ka qaada aragga oo geeya maskaxda.

oral glucose tolerance test n. baaris lagu eego sonkorow (diabetes).

oral mucosa n. cabeeb afeed.

orbital irradiation n. fallaaro shucaac (x-ray) ee lagu daweeyo il.

crucifer (ˈkuruusafar) n. 1 kaniisad qofkeeda qaada saliibka (isku tallaabta). 2 khudaarta bahda kaabajka (cabbage). -cruciferous (kuruu’sifaras) adj.

orthostatic hypotension n. diid; cadaadiska dhiigga oo dhaqso hoos ugu dhaca markii la istaago ama gogol laga soo kaco, keentana wareer.

osseointegration (,aasiyaw,inta’garayshan) n. lafta oo bir qoton looga sameeyo, siiba meel ilig ka banneeyay. -osseointergrated (,aasiyaw’intar,greydhid) adj.

osteoarthritis (,aastiyawaar’tharaaydhas) n. xibna-xanuun, siiba marka carjawda u dhaxaysa lafaha ay dhammaato. -osteoarthritic (ˌaastiyawaar’thiridhik) adj. Barbardhig rheumatoid arthritis.  

osseous (aasiyas) adj. xambaarsan, ku jirto ama ku qaab ah laf; lafeed: bony.

osteoclast (‘astiya,klasti) n. unug burburiya lafta duqowday si uu mid cusub oo caafimaad qabta ugu meel sameeyo. -osteoclastic (ˌaastiya’klaastik) adj.

osteocyte (‘aastiya,saayt) n. unug dayactira laf samaysmatay.

osteomyelitis (,aastiyaw,maaya’laaytas) n. laf bolol galay: bone infection.

osteon (‘aasti,yaan) n., pl. osteons dhiismasho laf, siiba adkaansho iyo isku malaasmad. -osteonal (ˌaasti’yaanal) adj.

osteopath (‘aastiya,paath) n., pl. osteopaths dhakatar ku takhasusay qalliin iyo daawa bixin: osteopathic medicine.

osteopathic medicine n. hab daawayn oo xoogga saara guud ahaan baxnaaninta bukaanka iyo qalfoofmuruqeedka (musculoskeletal) si looga baaqsado qalliin. Barbardhig allopathic medicine. kale loogu yeeraa osteopathy. eeg osteopathic medicine. -osteopathy (ˌaasti’yaapathii) n.

allopathic medicine n. hab daawayn oo xoogga saara ogaatin iyo ku daaweynta cuduro adeegsiga caadooyinkii iyo xaqiiq ku salayntood, sida daawooyinka iyo qalliinka. Barbardhig osteopathic medicine. kale loogu yeeraa allopathy.

musculoskeletal (,maskiyalaw’iskaletal) adj. la xariira muruqyada iyo qalfoofkaba: both muscles and the skeleton.

osteopenia (,aastiyaw’piiniya) n. khafiifid iyo tabaryarayn lafaha; xajmiga lafta oo ka yaraada caadiga walina aan gaarin jabis. -osteopenic (,aastiyaw’piinik) adj.

poll gland n. dhabi; ganjirka tawaadda awrka.

subcutaneous (,sabku’teyniiyas) adj. haragga ama maqaarka hoostiisa ah. e.g. Subcutaneous injections. -subcutaneously adv.

osteophyte (‘aastiya,faayt) n. laf ka sii dulbaxada xibin ama wareegga xibnaha lafdhabarta ama kalagoysyada. kale loogu yeeraa bone spur.

bone spur n. eeg osteophyte.

otic capsule n. laf ku dhexwareegsan dhagta gudaheeda.

dichotic(ˌdhaay,kawdhik) adj. la xariira dhagaha oo mid walba hesho dhawaq ka baddalan midda kale. e.g. dichotic listening tests. -dichotically (ˌdhaay’kawdhiklii) adj.

-otic adj. dibgale (suffix) la xariira ama caddeeya ficil, xaalad, ama hawl wali socota: symbiotic.

ijbol or IJBOL abbr. I just burst out laugh (qosol baan ka wareegay) = qbkw.

mutualism (‘miyuujawa,liizam) n. 1 kala faa’iidaysi. 2 dan ka wada dhexaysa ururro kala duwan ama dawlado. -mutualist (‘miyuujawaliisti) n.; -mutualistic (,miyuujawa’listik) adj.

wade (‘weeydh) v. waded; wading 1 dhexmaquurid biyo. e.g. We waded the river. 2 dhexjiirid dhib ama hawl. e.g. We waded through the big crowd. 3 [usu. with in or into] dhexgalid ama iskutuurid, siiba wax aan laga fiirsan. -wadable adj., or -wadeable (ˈweydhabal).

egret (‘iigrat) n. nooc ka mid ah shinbiraha luqunta iyo lugaha dheer.

heron (‘heran) n., pl. herons also heron shinbir sur iyo lugo dheer leh.

plumose (‘puluu,maws) adj. baallo leh: feathered.

commensalism (ka’mensa,liizam) n. wadanoolaansho; isku daynaysi; faa’iido ay isku qabaan laba noole oo midi cunto ama dan kale ku qabo, kan kale aan loo gaysan wax dhib ah, sida shinbir uga cunto sac shillinta, sacuna shillinta laga guro.

symbiotic (,simbi’yaadhik) adj. 1 dheef isku qaba ama isku danaysta. e.g. They have a symbiotic relationship. -symbiotically (ˌsimbi’yaadhiklii) adv.

otitis externa n. cun-cun dhagta kore ama duleelka ah. eeg swimmer’s ear.

otitis (aw’taaydhas) n. hurgun dhageed.

otosclerosis (,awdhawiskala’rawsis) n. laf aan caadi ahayn oo ku dhexwaynaata dhagta, taas oo keenta in maqalku dhumo.

outer ear n. dhagta dibaddeeda, duleelka ilaa durbaan-dhageedka (eardrum).

overactive bladder n. kaadis badan iyo kaadin rabisteed oo deg-deg ah.

overt proteinuria n. shaqada kallida oo hoos u dhacda, waana qayb ka mid ah cudur soo socda (waliba markii kallida jirani kaadida ku darto dheecaanka albumin).

oxidant (‘aaksadhanti) n. walax kasta oo awood u leh in ay ka hesho walax kale danab tabane (electron). -oxidant adj.

oxidizing agent n. chemistry walax kiimiko ahaan ku falgasha markay ogsijiin (oxygen) ku darsamikarto, siiba ayada oo ogolaata electrons.

hydrolyze (‘haaydra,laayz) v. hydrolyzed; hydrolyzing ku burburin biyo iskudhisyada falgal  kiimiko. -hydrolyzable (ˈhaaydra’laayzabal) adj.

nucleotide (‘nuukliya,taaydh) n. maalikiyuullo noole (organic) oo ka kooban organic nitrogenous base, pentose sugar iyo phosphate; aasaaska laga abuuro nucleic acids (RNA iyo DNA). Barbardhig nucleoside.

nucleoside (‘nuukliya,saaydh) n. asalka bu’da dhismaha (nucleic acids) unugyada noole oo dhan walxaha ay ka samaysanyihiin oo xukuma hiddaha (heredity-controlling), kana kooban maalikiyuullo sonkor ah kuna xiran nitrogen xambaarsan iskudhiska organic.

hydrolysis (haay’daraalasas) n. falgalbiyood; qaab caadi ah oo falgal kiimiko lagu daro biyo si iskudhiskooda kiimiko ee ka dhexjira walxaha loo burbursho. -hydrolytic (ˌhaaydra’lidhik) adj.; -hydrolytically (ˌhaaydra’lidhiklii) adv.

dehydrogenation (,dii’haay,daraaja’neyshan) n. ka saaris haydarjiin (hydrogen) iskudhis kiimiko. -dehydrogenate (ˌdii,haay’daraaja,neyt) v.

oxidize (‘aksadhayz) v. oxidized; oxidizing 1 ku darid kiimiko ahaan ogsajiin (oxygen). e.g. if you see a rusted car, that is the result of “oxidizing.” 2 ka saarid hal ama ka badan qurub tabane (atom, iron, ama molecule). 3 noqda oxidized, dufanka waxaa lagu darikaraa ogsijiin ama biyo si uu u qurmo. -oxidizable (ˌaaksa’dhaayzabal) adj.

rancid (‘raansad) adj. 1 qurmuun ah; ura, siiba isbaddal kiimiko ku dhacay ama qurmay. e.g. Rancid meat/milk. 2 aan fiicnayn; laga yaqyaqsado. e.g. It was a rancid political scandal. -rancidity (raan’sidhidhii) n.; -rancidness (ˈraansadhnis) n.

oxidation (,aaksa’dheyshan) n. 1 marka walax kiimiko ku baddalmato ku daris ogsijiin (oxidizing) darteed. 2 lagu daray ogsijiin (oxidized). -oxidative (ˈaaksa’dheydhiv) adj.; -oxidatively adv.

oxygenate (‘aaksija,nayt) v. oxygenated; oxygenating ku darid ogsijiin, sida dhiig. -oxygenation (ˌaaksija’neyshan) n.

oxygenated blood n. dhiig lagu daray ogsijiin.

exocrine (‘eksakaran) adj. la xariira wax la sameeyo, ama wax la tufo ama la sii daayo: exocrine glands and their secretions.

exocrine gland n. qanjir marinle; qanjir dibadda wax u soo tufa ama sii daaya, sida kan calyada (salivary gland).

dulla (‘dulla) n. doobbo, siiba tan awr (rati) qooqan.

pharynx (‘ferinkis) n., pl. pharynges (fa’rin,jiiz) also pharynxes dalqo; khaaxo; dalool iskugu xira sanka iyo afka kuna sii xirma hunguriga.

nasopharynx (,neysaw’feerinkis) n. dalqada qaybteeda sare ee sanka, qalka sarana xigta.

oropharynx (,oora’feerinkis) n. dalqada qybteeda hoose ee gadaasha carrabka iyo qalka hoose xigta.

immunolocalization n. xeel lagu ogaado meesha uu joogo maalikiyuul ama qaabdhis kale ee nud ama unug.  

peripheral artery disease n. abbr. PAD xaalad ay sababtay halbawlaha lugta oo xirmay.

pannus (ˈpaanas) n. 1 xuub cad oo isha daboola. 2 xuub jilbaha kala gooysyada ku dhasha.

papillary muscles n. muruqyo qotoma oo laga arko wadnaha qolqolkiisa hoose, kuna dhagaan gidaarkooda.  

parasomnia (paara’saamniya) n. hurdo-salal, sida dheelalaw, qaraw, ama riyo-baas.

parathyroid gland n. qanjir sii daaya dheecaanno xaddida heerka kaalsiyamka (calcium), saameeyana korista iyo ragaasidda lafta.

paroxysmal hemicrania n. madax-wareer dhif ah oo wata xanuun daran, wajiga barki ama indhaha gadaashooda ah.

pathogenic (,paatha’jenik) adj. keena ama keenikara cudur: pathogenic bacteria. -pathogenicity (ˌpaathaji’nisatii) n.

pathogenetic (,pathaje’nedhik) adj. ku xariira asalka cudur.

polycystic ovary syndrome n. abbr. PCOS xaalad aan caadi ahayn ee minku sameeyo tiro badan oo xawada ragga ah (androgens), taas oo ahayd in ay durmarka ku yaraato, raggana ku badato. kale loogu yeeraa polycystic ovarian syndrome.

PCOS n. abbr. polycystic ovary syndrome.

phosphodiesterase type 5 n. abbr. PDE5 daawo ragga kacsi siisa.

peak flow n. cabbir lagu eego sida ugu dhaqsa badan ee qof hawada uga soo buufinkaro sanbabka.

peak flow meter n. qalab lagu qiyaaso shaqada sanbabka, inta badanna waxaa lagu baaraa lagulana socdaa neefta (asthma).

niacin (‘naayasan) n. also vitamin B3 biyo-ku-milme faytamiin B oo laga helo cuntada, marka la cunana u baddala tamar.

pellagra n. cudur dhif ah oo ay keento ku yaraanta jirka niacin (vitamin B3), sababana shuban, xajiin, iyo xasuus-dhumin.

pepsin n. dheecaan kiimiko (enzyme) oo calooshu sii dayso si ay u burburiso nafaqada (protein).

percutaneous electrical nerve stimulation n. hab xanuunka lagu baabi’iyo, ayada oo la adeegto qodxo koronto dabyar leh, si maskaxda looga joojiyo xanuunka dareemayaashu u dirayaan.

percutaneous transluminal coronary angioplasty n. hab lagu furo halbawlayaasha waaweyn ee dhiigga u keena wadnaha (coronary arteries).

perfuse (,per’fiyus) v. perfused; perfusing 1 ku shubid; ku durid. e.g. The nurse perfused the new patient with blood. 2 ku fidid. e.g. The perfume perfused in the room. 3 ku shaacid. e.g. The white waves began to perfuse the Liida shores. 4 ku baahid. e.g. The bright moonlight started to perfuse the sea. -perfusion (ˌper’fiyuushan) n.

illegalize (i’liiga,laayze) v. illegalized; iligalizing; illegalizes ku dhawaaqid ama ka dhigid sharcidarro: to make illega. e.g. Somalia needs to illegalize chewing Qaad. -illegalization (ˌil,liigala’zeyshan) n.

pericarditis (,pera,kaar’dhaaydhas) n. barar xuubka wadnaha dahaara: pericarditis.

periodic limb movement disorder n., abbr. PLMD hurdoxumo markii la jiifo lugha ama cagaha ay dhaqdhaqaaqaan ama raftaan.

peripheral neuropathy n. dhaawac soo gaara dareemaha dheer ee taxan lafdhaabarta ilaa gacmaha iyo lugaha.

peripheral vascular disease n. cariiryawga xididdada dhiigga gaarsiiya lugaha, gacmaha, caloosha, iyo kalyaha.

pernicious anemia n. nooc dhiigyari ah oo unugyada dhiigga cas ay ballaartaan ayna dhuuqi waayaan vitamin B12.

personal emergency response system n. koor-gacmeed; koor luqunta la surto oo loogu qayladhaansado caawin.

fentanyl (‘fenta,nil) n. maandooriye gacankusamays ah oo loo adeegtoa xanuun baabi’iye ama suuxin: opioid narcotic painkiller. e.g. The misuse of fentanyl had caused the overdose death.

malposition (,maalpa’zishan) n. khalad ama meel khladan. e.g. Could dentist help correct teeth malposition?

pessary (‘pesari) n., pl. pessaries 1 siil-gale. e.g. Pessary can be inserted into the vagina safely. 2 qalab la galiyo xibinta daranka dumarka oo saxa fadhiga minka, kaadihaysta, iyo malawadka: therapeutic pessary.

pyronine’s disease n. haarmid gudaha gus oo ay keento qalloocsan asaga oo kacsan.

pH monitoring n. baaris aasidh ee hunguriyeed (esophageal acidity test); baaris lagu cabbiro inta stomach acid calooshu dib ugu soo laabto hunguriga.

premonitory (peri,maana’tori) adj. diginin bixiya: serving as a warning. e.g. Premonitorily symptoms. -premonitorily (piri,maan’tooralii) adv.

phacoemulsification (faakawi,malsafa’keyshan) n. also  phakoemulsification (ˌfaakawi,malsafa’keyshan) hab bu’da il lagu saaro ayada oo la adeegto gariir hirar cod sare leh (ultrasonic vibrations), loogana qaado xayaabada. -phacoemulsifier (,faakawi’malsa,faayar) n.

suction (‘sakshan) n. 1 dhuuqis, siiba dareere. 2 dhuuqe; qalab loo isticmaalo dhuuqis dareere ama hawo. e.g. The dentist bought a suction tool to suck out water and the excess saliva.                           -v. suctioned; suctioning; suctions dhuuqid; wax jirka laga dhuuqo, sida calyo, hawo, iwm.

phagocyte (‘faaga,sayat) n. unug dhunjiye; ceejiye; unugyo (macrophage or neutrophil) liqa unugyada kale, jeermiska, iyo walxaha jirka dibadda uga yimaada. -phagocytic (ˌfaaga’sidhik) adj.

phase shift disorder n. xilliga hurdada oo kala baddalma ama isdabamara.

phenothiazine (,fiinaw’thaaya,ziin) n. 1 cagaar hurdi ah ee iskudhika crystalline C12H9NS loona adeegto gooryaandile (anthelmintic) iyo cayayaan, siiba xannaanada xoolo (veterinary practice). 2 daawo aad u xoog badan oo la siiyo qof ay ka khaldantahay isku aadanaanta hadalka (schizophrenia).

phenylpropanolamine (,fenal,parawpa’noola,miin) n. daawo looqaato cabburka sanka.

pheochromocytoma (,fiiya,karawmasa’tawma) n., pl. pheochromocytomas also pheochromocytomata  (ˌfiiya,karawmasa’tawma) buro ka soo baxda qanjirka ku yaal kalida korkeeda (adrenal gland) oo soo daaya dheecaanno cariiriya xididdada dhiigga, kordhiyana dhiigkarka. kale loogu yeeraa pheo.

pheo (ˈfi,yaw) n., pl. pheos eeg pheochromocytoma.

phonophobia (,fawna’fawbiya) n. dhibsada codad, dhawaaq, qaylo, iyo shanqar. e.g. Phonophobia is a fear of loud sounds ama noises. -photophobic (ˌfawna’fawbik) adj.

photocoagulation (,fawdhakaw,agya’leshan) n. hab qalliin oo shucaac (laser) lagu awdo xididdo dhiig.

oncology (aan’kaalaji) n. laan ka mid ah caafimaadka oo gooni u eegta ka hortagga, baarista, daawaynta, iyo barashada kaankaro (cancer). -oncological (ˌaanka’laajikal) or oncologic (ˌaanka’laajik) adj.; -oncologist (aan’kaalajisti) n. (waa saddex qayb: medical oncologist, radiation oncologists, iyo surgical oncologists).

photopsia (faw’taapsiya) n. dhibto aragtida biriqda nalka ama walacda wax aad u ifa: perceived flashes of light.

photorefractive keratectomy (,fawdhaw,rifaraktiv,kera’tektami) n. qalliin shucaac (laser) lagu hagaajiyo il aragtideeda. Barbardhig radial keratotomy.

phytochemistry (,faydhaw’kemistari) n. laan ka mid ah kimistariga oo gooni u eegta dhirta kimistarigeeda, iyo iskudarka walaxa kiimiko ee dhirta laga sameeyo. -phytochemist (ˌfaaydhaw’kemisti) n.

phytoalexin (,faaydhaw-a’leksan) n. noocyo kiimiko kala duwan oo dhirtu samayso si ay ula dagaalanto cudurada ku dhasha, sida caabuq fangas (fungus).

phytogeography (,faaydhawji’yaagrafii) n. deegaan nololgeedeedyo; dhirtu deegaanada ay ku kala noolyihiin: geobotany. e.g. The phytogeography of the Gedo region. -phytogeographer (ˌfaaydhaw’ji’yaagrafar) n.; -phytogeographical (ˌfaaydhaw’jiiya’garaafikal) or -phytogeographic (ˌfaaydhaw,jiiya’graafik) adj.; -phytogeographically (ˌfaadhaw,jiiya’garaafiklii) adv.

lutein (‘luudhiyan) n. geed leh caleemo ballaaran oo lacuno.

bioremediation (ˌbaayawri,miidhi’yeyshan) n. kula tacaalid uurada iyo wasaqda ayada oo lagu adeegto jeersim noole ilma’aragto (microorganism bacteria).

phytosociology (,faaydhaw,sawsi’yaalajii) n. laan ka mid ah cilmiga barshada nafleyda oo gooni u eegta dhismaha, qaabka, iyo xariirka ka dhaxeeya bahwaynta dhirta iyo geedaha. -phytosociological (ˌfaaydhaw,sawsiiya’laajikal) adj.

-phagous adj. comb. form quuta; cuna: saprophagous.

prognosis (paraag’naw,sis) n., pl. prognoses (paraag’naw,siiz)1 sidii loo daawayn lahaa cudur, kadib markii la ogaaday. e.g. Her doctor said the prognosis is excellent. 2 saadaalin: forecast, prognostication.

prognostication (,paraag,naasta’keyshan) n. sii ogaansho; ka sii digis; sansaan: foretoken. 2 wax sii ogaadansho: forecast. 3 foreboding.

pineal gland (‘payniyel; ‘payniil) n. or pineal or pineal body or pineal organ qanjir yar oo bartamaha maskaxda ku jira, dirana dheecaanno ka jawaaba mugdiga iyo joogtaynta wareegga 24 saac. kale loogu yeeraa pineal, pineal body, pineal organ.

amyloid (‘aamaloydh) n. labeen oo kale ah oo si xad-dhaaf u fariista xibnaha iyo samayska (tissue) jirka xayawaanka, sida maskaxda dadka qaba cudurka Alzheimer’s.

prediabetes (,pirii dhaaya’piidhiiz) n. xaalad caafimaad oo khatar ah, markii heerka sonkorta dhiiggu ka sarrayso caadiga, laakiin aan wali gaarin in laqaado sonkorow (type 2). -prediabetic (ˌpirii’dhaaya’bedhik) adj. or n.

proteinuria (,parawdha,nuuriya) n. nafaqada (protein) oo soo raacda kaadida.

prehypertension (,pirii’haaypar,tanshan) n. dhiigkar ka sarreeya caadiga, laakiin aan gaarin heer dhiigkar buuxa, inta badana cadaadiska dhiigga sare (systolic) 120-139 mmHg, kan hoosana (diastolic) 80-89 mmHg. -prehypertensive (,pirii’haaypar,tensiv) adj.

millimeters of mercury n. abbr. mmHg lagu cabbiraa cadaadis dhiig, loona qoro: 120/70 mmHg.

premature atrial contraction n. wadne-daf; wadne-wa’. wadnaha oo aysan ku jirin dhiig badan oo uu saaro, hakad yar iyo garaac xoog ah ayaana israaca oo la moodo in uu garaac ka booday.

premature ejaculation n. abu-birriq; nin biyihiisu yimaadaan mark uu galiyaba.

presbycusis (,parezbi’kiyuusas) n., pl. presbycuses (,parezbi’kiyuu,siiz) dhagajig; maqalka oo da’da la dhuma, keentayna unugyada gudaha dhagta oo dhintay.

priapism (‘paraaya,pizam) n. gus iskiis u kacsan in ka badan saacado oo aan ahayn caadi, keentana xanuun.

sten- comb. form or steno- xiran; cariiri; yar; diiqo.

eurytherm (‘yuri’therm) n. noole ku noolaankara heer-kul kala duwan, sida dad, geel, daanyeer, ariga, iwm. -eurythermal or -eurythermic  -eurythermous adj.

ectotherm (ˈekta’,therm) n. xayawaan dhiig-qabaw (cold-blooded animal): poikilotherm. -ectothermic (ˌekta’tharmik) adj.

osmotic (aaz’maadhik) adj. u dareera xagga dhafaaga; la xariira osmosis. -osmotically (ˈaaz’maadhiklii) adv.

osmosis (aaz’mawsis) n. siimaw; milanka maalikiyuullada biyaha oo ka dhaqaaqa maalikiyuullada biyaha ribbanaanta hoose (lower concentration) aadana maalikiyuulada biyaha ribbanaanta sare.

prion (‘paraay,aan) n. prion protein nafaqo (protein) aan la aqoon shaqadeeda oo laga helo korka unugyada maskaxda.

probiotic (parawba’yaadhik) n. noole jeermis ilma’aragto ah oo faa’iido u leh jirka haddii lamariyo ama cunto uu raaco, sida caanaha garooray ama cuntada khamiirtay. Barbardhig prebiotic. -probiotic adj.

prebiotic (piriiba’yaadhik) n. 1 jiray horteed soo bixii nololeed. 2 jeermis ilma’aragto ah oo faa’iido wayn u leh marinnada dheefshiidka. Barbardhig probiotic.

sputter (‘ispadhar) v. sputtered; sputtering; sputters 1 tufid, siiba candhuuf. 2 hinqadtin. e.g. The old car sputtered and stopped. 3 taqtaqlayn, siiba hadal. 4 ka saarid qurubyo (atoms) dusha walax ayada oo lagu dhufanayo waxyaalo tamar sare leh. -sputterer n.

pulmonary edema n. sanbabka oo dareere buuxiyo, neefsashaduna adkeeto.

pulse pressure n. farqiga u dhexeeya dhiigga sare (systolic) oo laga jaray dhiigga hoose (diastolic). e.g. pulse pressure = dhiigga sare (120) – dhiigga hoose (80); pulse pressure = 40 mm Hg; wixii ka badan 40 waa halis.

allele (a’liyal) n. nooc kale oo ah hidda-side gaar ah (specific gene), taas oo midna ka yimid aabbaha, kan kalana hooyada; tusaale: laba wada dhashay baa mid leeyahay indho cagaaran, kan kalana leeyahay indho buluug ah (green allele iyo blue allele) -allelic (a’liilik) adj.; -allelism (a,’lii,lizam) n.

autosome (‘awdha,sawm) n. hidda-side (chromosome) aan ahayn sex chromosome.

incendiary (in’sendhi,yerii) adj. 1 gubaya; shidaya wax guba: arsenious. 2 la xariira hub qarxa ama wax guba. e.g. We defused incendiary bombs. 3 hadal kulul ama dhibaato shida. e.g. Incendiary issues. 4 aad u kulul, sida basbaas.                                                   -n. incendiaries 1 qof kiciya rabsho, muran, iyo buuq: inflammatory. 2 hub wax guba ama qarxiya. 3 dabshid; qof kas wax u guba: arson.

sigmoid (sig,moydh) adj. 1 sida xarafka C u qalloocan. 2 laba dhinac u qalloocada, sida S. 3 la xariira sigmoid colon (mindhicirka meesha uu uga xirmo malawadka oo ah sida S). -sigmoidally (sig’moydhalii) adv.

sleep apnea (‘isliip ‘apniya) n. neefsashada oo istaagta xilliga qofku hurdo oo haddana soo noqota.

sleep architecture n. qaab gundhigeedka hurdada caadiga ah, laba nooc ayaa jira: isha oo aan dhaqso u dhaqdhaqaaqin (non-rapid-eye-movement) iyo isha oo dhaqso u dhaqdhaqaaqda (rapid-eye-movement) = NREM/REM.

sleep paralysis n. marka aan la dhaqaaqikarin ama la hadlikarin ee qof hurdo ka toosayo ama sii gam’ayo.

spindle (‘ispindhal) n. 1 ul dun ama xarig lagu duubo. 2 birta dheer oo isku xirta lugaha gaari.               -v. spindled; spindling 1 yuuqmid; dheeraatin. 2 yuuqid; dhuubid, siiba ul ama bir. -spindler (ˈispindhlar) n.

bronze diabetes n. or bronzed diabetes eeg hemochromatosis.

renal diabetess n. eeg renal glycosuria.

diabetes mellitus (ˌdhaaya’biidhiiz ˈmelatas) n. cudur jirku uu san xukumin inta glucose (nooc sonkor) ku jirta dhiigga, kalyuhuna sameeyaan kaadi badan; noocyo badan ayaana jira: type 1, type 2, maturity-onset diabetes of the young (MODY), gestational diabetes, neonatal diabetes, and steroid-induced diabetes.

glucocorticoid (ˌguluukaw’koorti,koydh) n. noocyo kasta ee dhacaanno (steroid hormones) oo uu sameeyo qanjirka (adrenal cortex), qaybna ka qaadata dheefshiid kiimiko (metabolism) iyo ka hortagga barar (anti-inflammatory). Barbardhig mineralocorticoid.

steroid-induced diabetes n. isticmaalka steroids waxay sababi kartaa heerka sonkorta (glucose) oo dhiigga kor uga kacda.

maturity-onset diabetes of the young n. abbr. MODDY dhawr xaaladood oo aan caadi ahayn oo heerka sonkorta dhiiggu aad u kacsantahay.

MODDY n. abbr. maturity-onset diabetes of the young.

neonatal diabetes (ˌniyaw’neydhalˌdhaaya’biidhiiz) sonkorta oo aad u kacdsan (hyperglycemia) lana xariirta insulin oo aan jirka ku wareegayn ama ku yar.

renal glycosuria (ˈriinalˌgalaaykaw’shuriya) n. kaadida oo sonkor (glucose) soo raacdo.

type 2 diabetes n. cudur dabadheer oo jirku uusan samaysankarin sonkor (glucose) ku filan, laguna dadaalo cuntada oo layareeyo, jimicsi, culaabta oo la rido, iyo daawo afka laga qaato.

type 1 osteoporosis n. lafo dhammaad uu keeno caada-guurka.

type 2 osteoporosis n. lafo dhammaad uu keeno gabawga.

vacuum erection devices n. abbr. VED dhuun la gasho guska oo u soo dhuuqda dhiig u ku kacsado.

angina pectoris n. xabad-xanuun, inta badan dhiig xoog ugu soo butaaca halbawlaha.

vasculitis (,vaaski’laaydhas) n., pl. vasculitides (,vaaski’lidhadhiiz) hurgun xidid ama dhiig: inflammation of the wall of blood vessels. e.g. The cerebral arteries vasculitis caused inflammation.

lymph (‘limf) n. biyo ku laran dhigga cad.

lymph- comb. form or lympho- biyo: lymph.

lymphatic leukemia n. kale loogu yeeraa leukemia.

lymphogranuloma (‘limfaw,garaanya’lawma) n. eeg  lymphogranuloma venereum.

lymphogranuloma venereum (‘limfaw,garaanya’lawma va’niiriyam) n. cudurada galmada lagu kala qaado (venereal disease).

vasoconstrictor (,veyzawkan’istiriktar) n. daawo cariirisa duleelka xididdada: vasoconstriction.

vasoconstriction (,veysawkan’istirikshan) n. cariiryawga gudaha xididdada: narrowing of a blood vessel.

vasodilation (,veysawdhaay’leyshan) n. also vasodilatation (ˌveyzaw,dhila’teyshan) weynaynta daloolka gudaha xididdada: dilation.

vas (‘vaas) n., pl. vasa (‘veyza) xidid; dhuun; dalool. -vasal (ˈveyzal) adj.

vasomotor (,veyza’mawdhar) adj. la xariira dabaca iyo dhuqsanka duleelka xididka dhiigga: diameter of blood vessels.

vasovagal syncope n. suuxis, siiba marka jirku ka falceliyo, aragtida dhiig ama dareen. kale loogu yeeraa neurocardiogenic syncope or vasodepressor syncope.

vasodepressor syncope (ˌveyzawdi’paresar ˈsinka,pii) n. suuxdin ay keento caddaadiska dhiigga oo hoos u dhaca. eeg vasovagal syncope.

neurocardiogenic syncope (ˌnuuraw,kaardhi,yaw’jenik ˈsinka,pii) n. eeg vasovagal syncope.

vasovagal (,veyzaw’veygal) adj. la xariira xayn dareemayaal xididdo ah (vagus nerves) oo sababa tartiibinta garaaca wadnaha iyo ballaarinta xididdada.

vagus nerve (‘veygas ‘neerv) n. or vagal nerves waxay qabtaan shaqooyin gaar ah ee jirka, sida dheefshiidka, garaaca wadnaha oo ah ficil aan la xukumin.

vagal nerve n. eeg vagus nerve.

parasympathetic nervous system n. iskuxiran dareemayaal oo dajiya jirka xilliga walwalka ama khatarta, kale oo ay sahlaan dheefshiidka marka la nasaynayo.

vasodilator (,veysawdhaay’leydhar) n. daawooyin keena in marinnada xididdada dhiiggu weynaadaan si ay u yareeyaan cadaadiska dhiigga: vasodilation.

vasospasm (‘veysaw,ispaazam) n. xididdada oo joogto si dhaqsa ah isku xira, qulqulka dhiiguna hakad galiya. -vasospastic (ˌveyzaw’ispaastik) adj.

ventricular arrhythmia n. garaaca wadnaha oo aan caadi ahayn, kana dhaca qolqollada hoose (ventricles).

ventricular fibrillation n. abbr. VF, V-fib wadne-garaac aad ah oo aan caadi ahayn, kana dhaca qolqollada sare ee wadnaha, waana dhimasho ama nolol.

ventricular myocardium n. muruqyada wadnaha qolqolladiisa hoose.

ventricular rupture n. dillaac ku yimaada xuubka kala qaybsha qolqollada hoose ee wadnaha, taas oo keenta dhiig badan oo aada sanbabka.

dropsy (‘daraapsi) n. eeg edema.

ventricular septal defect n. abbr. VSD cillad wadnaha ah oo lagu dhasho, taas oo qolqollada hoose isku daloolaan. kale loogu yeeraa ventricular septum.

ventricular septum n. eeg ventricular septal defect.

venule (‘viin,yuul; ‘ven,yuul) n. xidid-yare.

vertebral artery n. halbawle mara lafdhabarta oo dhiigga geeya maskaxda.

vertebroplasty (‘vartabaraw,palaasti) n. hab daawayn oo xanuun looga yareeyo xibin lafdhabar oo jabtay ama dillaacday, laguna duro sibir (cement) gaar ah. Barbardhig kyphoplasty.

vestibular system n. hab cajiib ah oo ku dhexjira dhagta gudaheeda, qaabeeyana dheelitirka jirka iyo jihayntiisa. kale loogu yeeraa vestibular apparatus.

vestibular apparatus n. eeg vestibular system.

visual cortex n. maskaxda qaybteeda (occipital lobe) oo ay soo gaarto humaag-aragga indhuhu soo direen, iskuna habaysa.

efferent (‘efaranti; ‘iifaranti) adj. ka qaada (bar kulan sida maskaxda ama wadnaha) oo geeya meelo kale. e.g. The efferent signals from the brain. Barbardhig afferent. –efferent n.; -efferently adv.

efferent nerve n. dareen keene; dareeme maskaxda ka soo qaada dareen.

peripheral nervous system n. abbr. PNS dareemayaal ka soo faalala maskaxda iyo xangullaha, aadana jirka intiisa kale, una sii qaybsama (somatic nervous system iyo autonomic nervous system).

PNS n. abbr. peripheral nervous system.

somatic nervous system n. xayn dareemayaal ah oo ka sii farcama (peripheral nerve) xukumana dhaqdhaqaaqa muruqyada.

autonomic nervous system n. habdhiska dareen wadka; xayn dareemayaal ah oo ka sii farcama (peripheral nerve) oo iskood u dhaqaajiya garaaca wadnaha, cadaadiska dhiiga, neefsashada, dheefshiidka, iyo kacsiga.

visual field n. dhammaan il inta ay aragto, ayada oo aan la dhaqaajin madaxa. kale loogu yeeraa field of vision.

peripheral vision n. wixii laga arkikaro ilqooreedyada iyo kor-iyo-hoos ayada oo aan madaxa la dhaqaajin.

vitreous (‘vitriyas) adj. 1 quraarad u eg. 2 la xariira ama laga keenay quraarad. 3 la xariira dareere cad.

vitreous humor n. dareere aan lahayn midab oo ku jira isha.

VO2 max (‘viiaw’tuu‘maakis) n. inta ugu badan oxygen ee la qaadan karo inta lagu jiro jirdhis aad u daran.

volatile (‘vaaladhal) adj. 1 isbadali’og (angry or violent). e.g. She is a volatile person. 2 flying duulikara ama leh awood duulitaan. 3 price isbaddal (variable or erratic). 4 physics uumibaxa.                                                                -n. dhaqsa u uumibaxa. e.g. Volatile substances.

vulnerary (‘valna,reri) adj. loo adeegto bogsood nabar, siiba dhir ama daawo: for healing wounds. e.g. There are many vulnerary plants in my country.                                -n. daawo dhaawac: healing drug.

vulvar vestibulitis n. xanuun siilka afkiisa hore ah.

vulvodynia (‘valvaw,diiniya) n. xanuun siilka afkiisa hore ah, keenana cun-cun, gubasho, iyo xanuun mud-mud ah.

wall stress n. quwad ku dhacda wadnaha muriqiisa dibadda ah, oo ay keento cadaadiska gudaha dhigga fatahaya.

warfarin (‘woorfaran) n. daawo afka laga qaato oo dhiigga xinjiawga ka ilaalisa: anticoagulant medication.

prothrombin (,paraw’tharaamban) n. nafaqo (protein) beerku sameeyo oo dhiigga ka caawisa in uu si fiican u sameeyo xinjirawga.

anticoagulant (antiikaw’aagyalanti) n. lid xinjireeye; daawooyin ka kortaga xinjirawga dhiigga: blood thinner. –anticoagulant adj.

blood thinner n. dhiig-khafiifiye; daawo loo adeegto in ay dhiigga ka ilaaliso xinjirawga. -blood-thinning (ˈbaladh,thinin) adj.

water brash n. soo rogmasho calyo badan oo la liqay, inta badanna keenta laabjeex.

idiopathic (,idhiya’paathik) adj. 1 xaalad ama cudur iskiis iskaga yimaada, qarsoodi ama sabab aan la aqoon. e.g. Idiopathic epilepsy. 2 gaar ku ah qof. -idiopathically (ˌidhiya’paathiklii) adv.

hypersalivation (,haaypar,saala’veyshan) n. calyo aad u badan ama cay: sialorrhea.

ptyalism (‘taaya,lizam) n. eeg  hypersalivation, sialorrhea.

sialorrhea (,saayala,riiya) n. British sialorrhoea calyo aad u badan ama cay: hypersalivation. kale loogu yeeraa ptyalism.

Weber test n. or Weber’s test baaris lagu kala ogaado, in dhagta maqalku ka dhumay.

unilateral hearing loss n. dhumin maqalka hal dhag.

bilateral hearing loss n. dhumin maqalka labada dhagood.

Wernicke-Korsakoff syndrome n. cillad xagga dareemayaasha maskaxda ah, oo ay keento jirka oo ay ku yaraato faytamiin (vitamin B1).

Wernike’s area n. maskaxda qaybteeda fahamka hadalka.

olfactory lobe n. maskaxda qaybteeda qaabilsan urka.

gustation (‘ga,steyshan) n. dareen dhadhan: act of tasting. e.g. Gustation is sense of test.

gustatory (‘gasta,toori) adj. la xariira cuntayn ama dareen dhadhan. -gustatorily (ˌgasta’toralii) adv.

olfaction (aal’faakshan) n. 1 dareenka urka. 2 ur-dareemis. e.g. Olfaction can be effected by certain medications.

olfactometer (,aal,faak’taamadhar) n. qalab lagu cabbiro dareenka urka.

olfactory bulb n. maskaxda qaybteeda qaabilsan dareen ureed; nudo isku kuusan oo xambaarsan dhawr unugyo dareeme ureed, waana labo oo midi ku jiro maskaxda, kan kalana gadaasha dulka sanka.

olfactory (aal’faaktari) adj. la xariira dareen ureed. e.g. Olfactory sense organs. -olfactorily (aal’faaktaralii) adv.

piriform cortex (pira’foorm) n. abbr. PC maskaxda qaybteeda kala soocda ama kala garata urka.

white matter n. maskaxda qaybteeda hoose oo ay barkanyihiin dareemayaasha ku dahaaran xuubka cad (myelin).

myelin (‘maayalan) n. xuub cad oo daboola dareemayasha maskaxda iyo xangullaha lafdhabarta. -myelinic (ˌmaaya’linik) adj.

nociceptive (,nawsi’septive) adj. keena xanuun. e.g. Nociceptive pain. 2 xanuun keenay.

myelinated (‘maayala,neytidh) adj. ku dhexjira xuub: myelin. e.g. Nerve fibers are myelinated.

subcortical (,sab’koordhikal) adj. la xariira ama ku jira maskaxda qaybteeda hoose: subcortex.

subcortex (ˌsab’koor,tekis) n. qayb maskaxda ah oo ka hoosaysa cerebral cortex, kana kooban (brainstem, cerebellum, and corpus callosum)

cortical (‘koodhikal) adj. dusha sare oo daboosha korka xibnaha gudaha ku jira, sida kalli ama maskax.

cilium (‘silliiyam) n., pl. cilia (ˈsiliya) 1 gan; il-ma-argto tin le’eg oo ku dhex dulnool unugyada. 2 il baarkeed: eyelash.

white-coat hypertension n. xaal dhiiggu kaco marka qof looga cabbiro hosbitaal, marka uu guriga joogana caadi yahay, taas oo loo eedeeyo wal-wal iyo naxdin imaanshaha hosbitaalka ah.

yohimbine (yawhim’biin) n. dheecan sun ah oo laga dhiimiyo jirridda geedka yohimbe loona cuno kordhinta kacsi (aphrodisiac).

aphrodisiac (,afra’dhiiziyaak) n. daawo ama cunto loo isticmaalo keenidda kacsi. -aphrodisiac or -aphrodisiacal (ˌaafradhi’saayakal) adj.

zonule (‘zawn,yuwal) n. eeg zonule of zinn.

zonule of zinn n. duno yar-yar oo isha bu’deeda ku haya meesheeda. kale loo yaqaan ciliary zonule, zonula, zonula ciliaris.

suspensory (sa’spensarii) adj. 1 kor-u-haya ama tiiriya. e.g. She bought a suspensory new sports bra.   2 aan sii joogayn; laalaada.                                        -n. suspensory shay kor wax u haya.

thyroid-stimulating hormone n. abbr. TSH cillad hidda-raac oo saamaysa labada qanjir ee yar-yar (adrenal glands), kuwaas oo sii daaya dheecaan ka jawaaba cudurada jirka iyo walwalka. kale loogu yeeraa thyrotropic hormone, thyrotropin.

thyrotropic hormone n. eeg thyroid-stimulating hormone.

visceral fat n. xayr ku jirta caloosha, kuna wareegsan kalyaha; waana midda u daran caafimaad.

subcutaneous fat n. baruurta maqaarka ka hoosaysa.

telangiectasia (,te,lan,jiyek’teyshiya) n. or  telangiectasis (ˌte,laanji’yektasas) pl. elangiectasias or telangiectases (ˌte,laanje’yekta,siiz) xididdada yar-yar ee dhiigga oo casaada jirka cadna ka soo muuqda. -telangiectatic (ˌte,laanji,yek’taadhik) adj. kale loogu yeeraa spider vein.

spider vein n. eeg telangiectasia.

performance anxiety n. walaac xagga galmada.

poliosis (,pawli’yawsis) n., pl. polioses (,pawli’yaw,siiz) timaha oo midabku ka dhumo.

exegete (‘eksa,jiit) n. qof tarjuma qoraalladii hore.

exegesis (,eksa’jiisas) n., pl. exegeses (ˌeksa’jii,siiz) tarjumo iyo tafsiir; sharraxaad qoto dheer: exposition, explanation. e.g. I liked the teacher’s extensive exegesis of the Quran.

exegetical (,eksa’jedhikal) adj. also exegetic (ˌeksa’jedhik) la xariira tarjumo iyo tafsiir. e.g. The exegetical study of the Quran needs more knowledge.

phrenology (firi’naalaji) n. cilmiga barashada qalfoofka madaxa qaabkiisa iyo qiyaasticiisa, taas oo loo filayay sal ku haynta awood maskaxeedka iyo shaqsiga. -phrenological (ˌfarena’laajikal) adj.; -phrenologist (firi’naalajisti) n.

eugenics (yu’jenikis) n. fir-u-dayis dadka ayada oo la dhufaamo wixii fir-xun. e.g. Nanzi regime justified their eugenic program.

eugenic (yu’jenik) adj. 1 la xariira ama ku fiican fir/dir fiican. 2 la xariira eugenics. -eugenically (yu’jeniklii) adv.

mansplain (‘maan,ispaleyn) v. mansplained; mansplaining nin u sharraxa naag wax ay aad uga ogtahay. e.g. He was mansplaining to her about feminism. -mansplainer n.

cacophony (kaa’kaafani) n., pl. cacophonies buuq; sawaxan; wax badan oo isku qasan (incongruous): cacophony of colors/smells/sounds. e.g. A cacophony of monks sounds.

draconian (darey’kawniyan) adj. ciqaab ama sharci adag: severe, cruel.

limerence n. ka helis qof.

pareidolia (,per,aay’dawliya) n. ka dhex arkid hummaag ama sawir wax kale. e.g. I had experienced pareidolia when I had seen faces in clouds. Barbardhig apophenia.

apophenia (,aapa’fiiniya) n. ka dhex arkid wax sawirkood wax kale oo aan xariir la lahayn. Barbardhig pareidolia.

uncopyrightable (ˌan’kaapii,raaydhibal) n. aan la difaacikarin xaquuq daabacaad.

exonumia (,eksa’nuumiya) plural noun qaddaadiic; lacagaha birta ah wax la qaymi ah, sida tokens, medals or scrip.

anaplasma (,aana’palaazma) n., pl. anaplasmas or anaplasmata (ˌaana’palaazmadha) cudurada laga qaado bahda shillinta, qaniiyada diqsi, iyo unugyo dhiig oo qaaday cudurkaan ee dad ama duunyo.

systematics (,sista’maadhikis) n. 1 cilmiga wax kala soocidda. 2 nadaam kala soocan. 3 kala saaridda noolaha ayada oo loo eegayo xariirka caadiga ah oo ka dhexeeya: taxonomy.

protist (‘paraw,tisti) n. mid kasta oo ka mid ah beelo badan oo noolayaal hal-unugley ah oo u eg dhirta ama xoolaha ama labadaba. -protistan (paraw’tistan) adj. or n.

acanthamoeba (a,kaantha’miiba) n. dulin hal-unugle (jeermis) keenana hurgun isha ku dhasha, soona raaca biyo ama nabar isha ah.

nagana (na’gaana) n. cudur ku dhaca lo’, ugaar, iyo xoolaha kale oo la dhaqdo, waxaana gudbiya diqsi (tsetse fly).

tsetse fly (‘setsi ‘falaay; tii’tii falaay) n. diqsi dhiigyacab ah oo dad iyo duunyaba qaniina, gudbiyana muqlo (sleeping sickness).

amebiasis (,aami’baayasas) n. or amoebiasis pl. amebiases (ˌaami’baay,siiz) cudur uu keenay gooryaan ilma’aragtay ah, waxaana faafiya saxarada dadka.

ancylostomiasis (,aanki,lawsta’maayasas) n. or ankylostomiasis (ˌaanki,lawsta’maayasas) pl. ancylostomiases (ˌaanki,lawsta’maaya,siiz) also ankylostomiases (ˌaanki,lawsta’maaya,siiz) meel uu ku dhalay ama cudur uu keenyay dixiriga hookworm.

angiostomy (,aanji’yaastamii) n., pl. angiostomies qalliin xidid looga duleelsho meel dhuun yar laga gasho.

angiostatin (‘aanjiya,istaadhan) n. nafaqo (protein)  jirku caadi u samaysto oo ka hortagta abuuranka iyo waynaanta xididadda dhiigga: inhibits the growth of blood vessels.

anisakiasis (,aanasa’kaayasis) n. xanuun uu sababay dulan bahda nematode ee ku abuurma mindhicirka, lagana qaado hilibka ceeriin.

ascarid (‘aaskaradh) n. dulan (gooryaan) ku noolaada mindhicirka dadka.

ascariasis (,aaska’raayasas) n., pl. ascariases (ˌaaska’raaya,siiz) cudur uu keeno gooryaan mindicirka gala ee bahda ascarid.

Blastocystis hominis n. cudur uu keeno dulan hal-unugle ah oo ku noolaada marinada dheefshidka.

clonorchiasis (,kalawnoor’kaayasas) n. also clonorchiosis (,kalawnoorki’yawsas) pl. clonorchiases (,kalawnoor’kaaya,siiz)      also clonorchioses cudur dulan ku dhasho beerka oo uu keeno (liver fluke), lagana qaado kalluun yacyacood ah.

cryptosporidiosis (ˌkiriptaw’ispor,idhiyawsis) n., pl. cryptosporidioses (ˌkirptawispor,idhi’yaw,siiz) cudur gooryaan (cryptosporidia) uu keeno, watana shuban.

cysticercus (,sista’serkas) n., pl. systicerci (ˌsista’sar’saay) dulan wata kiish ukumo ugu jiraan oo gala muruqyada iyo maskaxda.

cysticercosis (ˌsista,sar’kawsas) n., pl. cysticercoses (ˌsista,sar’kaw,siiz) cudur uu keenay dulanka (tapeworm): cysticerci.

Dientamoeba (ˌdaay,enta’miiba) n. gooryan ku dhasha mindhicirka dadka iyo daanyeerka, keenana calool xanuun iyo doox.

dracunculiasis (dara,kankaya’laayasas) n. cudur uu keeno dixiri gala maqaarka. kale loo yeeraa Guinea Worm Disease (GWD).

dog tapeworm n. gooryaan (dulin) ku dhasha caloosha eeyaha iyo bisadaha.

echinococcus (i,kaayna’kaakas) n., pl. echinococci  (i,kaayna’kaak,saay) gooryaan mindhicirka ka jaqa dhiigga.

echinococcosis (i,kaaynakaa’kawsas) n., pl. echinococcoses (i,kaaynakaa’kaw,siiz) jirro uu keeno gooryaan ama dulin (echinococcus).

elephantiasis (elefan’taayasas) n., pl. elephantiases (elefan’taaya,siiz) lugabarar; xaalad lugaha ama meelo kale ee jirka ay bararaan, keenayna dulinka nematode oo jaqay.

nematode (‘nema,tawdh) n. dulin (gooryaan) dheer oo dhuuban, kuna dulnoolaada xoolaha, dhirta, ciidda ama biyaha. kale loogu yeeraa roundworm.

nonpathogenic (naan,paatha’jenik) adj. aan keenikarin cudur: not pathogenic. e.g. It considered to be nonpathogenic.

endolimax nana n. gooryaanka ugu yar oo ku noolaada mindhirka, inta badanna aan keenin cudur: intestine-dwelling amoebae.

histolysis (hi’staalasas) n., pl. histolyses milmid nudeed; dhaawac gaara samayska nuda jirkeedka (bodily tissues). -histolytic (ˌhista’lidhik) adj.

amok (a’maak) n. also amuck laayaan; dilaa, siiba qof kala sooc la’aan dad badan u laayay.                    -adv. 1 si xad dhaaf ah oo la xukumikarin. e.g. The children run amok. 2 laaya dad badan. -amok or -amuck adj.

entamoeba (,enta’miiba) n. noocyo badan oo dulin ama gooryaan, keenana shuban (dysentery).

fascioliasis (fa,siiya’laayasas) n., pl. fascioliases (fa,siiya’laaya,siiz) cudur uu keeno liver fluke.

fasciola (fa’siiyala) n., pl. fasciolae (fa’siiya,lii) or fasciolas cudur uu keeno fasciola hepatica.

liver fluke n. faraqle beer; dulin (trematode worms) gala dadka iyo xoolahaba, waxyeelleeyana beerka iyo marinada xammaytida.

fasciola hepatica n. eeg liver fluke.

fasciolopsiasis (fasiya,laap’saayasas) n., pl. fasciolopsiases (fasiya,laap’saaya,siiz) dulin gala mindhicirka, lagana qaado dhirbiyoodka aan aad loo karin oo la cuno.

filariasis (,fila’raayasas) n., pl. filariases (,fila’raaya,siiz) dulin ilma-aragto oo raaca dhiigga barariyana xibnaha, inta badanna dhilmaayo u kala qaaddo dadka.

foodborne (fuudh,born) n. or food-born cudur ay keentay cabbid ama cunid cunto quruntay oo uu ku dhashay jeerim, faayras, ama dulin ilma-aragto ah.

giardia (jii’yaardhiya) n. dulin aad u yar oo keena shuban, lagan qaado, ciidda, taabashad meel, cuntada, iyo biyo saxaro taabatay.

giardiasis (,jii,yaar’dhaayasas) n., pl. giardiases (,jii,yaar’dhaaya,siiz) cudur laga qaado dulanka giardia.

gnathostomiasis (na,thaasta’maayasas) n., pl. gnathostomiases (na,thaasta’maaya,siiz) cudur ama hurgun uu keenay nooc ah dulinka (nematode worm) ee bahda Gnathostoma, lagan qaado cunista kalluun ceeriin.

gnathostome (ney’thaastawm) n. dulin ku nool maqaarka iyo jirka, ka dibna u gudba gidaarada caloosha.

head lice infestation n. injir iyo qandhicil ku baxay timaha iyo dharka oo keena cun-cun: pediculosis.

heterophyes (,hedharaw’faaydhis) n. dulin ku noolaada mindhiciryaraha, siiba eeyaha, bisadah, iyo dadka (Egyptian mummy).

hydatid disease (haydhatidh) n. cudur aad khatar u ah loona dhinto, oo uu keeno dulin wata ukuntiisii.

hymenolepiasis (,haaymanawla’paayasas) n., pl. hymenolepiases (,haaymanawla’paaya,siiz) gooryaan-mindhicireed oo ah bahda Hymenolepis.

Iodamoeba buetschlii n. gooryaan aan dhibkeenin oo ku noolaada mindhicirweynaha dadka, doofaarka iyo xayawaanada kale: nonpathogenic parasitic ameba.

keratitis (,kera’taaydhas) n., pl. keratitides (ˌkera’tidha,dhiiz) hurgun ama barar isha guruxeeda ah: inflammation of the cornea. 

acanthamoeba keratitis infection n. hurgun isha u gaysta dhaawac wayn ama indha la’aan, oo uu keeno dulin ilma’aragtay hal-unugle ah. kale loogu yeero Acanthamoeba.

loaiasis (,lawa’aayasis) n. or loiasis n., pl. loaiases (,lawa’aaya,siiz) cudur uu keeno dixiri-indhood (eye worm) oo u gudba isha guruxeeda. Barbardhig Calabar swelling.

Calabar swelling n. eeg loaiasis.

lymphatic filariasis n. cudur barariya lugaha iyo meelo kale, loona yaqaan (elephantiasis), waxaana gudbiya kaneeco.

microsporidiosis (,maaykraw’ispiridhi’yawsas) n., pl. microsporidioses (,maaykraw’ispiridhi’yaw,siiz) cudur uu keeno dulinka Microsporidia: infection by microsporidians.

immunocompromised (imyanaw’kaampara,maayzti) adj. or immuno-compromised or immune-compromised wiiqmid habka isdifaaca jirka (immune system), oo uu sababay maandooriye ama cudur.

Microsporidia (,maaykrawispa’riidhiya) n. dulin aan dhaqsa u dhiman oo burburiya unugyada uu galo. -microsporidian (,maaykrawispa’riidhiyan) adj. or n.

myiasis (maay’aayasis) n. myiases (maay’aaya,siiz) hurgun ama barar uu keeno meel diqsi ku dhalay (fly maggots).

neurocysticercosis (,niiraw,sista,sar’kawsas) n., pl. neurocysticercoses (,niiraw,sista,sar’kaw,siiz) caabuq ku yimaada barta hoggaaminta dareemayaasha (central nervous system) oo uu keeno dixiri-doofaar (pork tapeworm).

hydrocephalus (,haaydaraw’sefalas) n. or hydrocephaly (ˌhaaydraw’sefalii) dagaanka fadhiga maskaxda oo dareere ku bato, keentana madaxweynaad: abnormal accumulation of fluid in the cerebral ventricles.

cranial cavity n. dagaan fadhiga maskaxda, kuna xiran oo uu difaaca dhawr xibno dareemayaal (supports several sense organs). 

Ocular Larva Migrans n. barar isha ah oo ay keento dulin ku dhasha, oo ka yimaada eeyaha iyo bisadaha.

eutherian (yu’thiiriyan) adj. la xariira naasleyda ay ku jirto kuwa ibida (mandheerta) leh. -eutherian n.

opisthorchiasis (a,pis,thor’kaayasis) n. dulan (flatworm) laga qaado cunista kalluun ceeriin.

paragonimiasis (paaragaana’maayasas) n., pl. paragonimiasis (paaragaana’maaya,siiz) cudur gala sanbabka (lung fluke) oo uu keeno dulinka bahda paragonimus, lagana qaado hilibka ceeriin.

paragonimus (,paara’gaanamas) n. dulin ballaaran oo gala sanbabka naasleeyda oo dadku ku jiro.

parasitic infection n. caabuq dulin; cudurada ay keenaan dulinka ku dulnool noole kale, sababana qandho, daal, xajiin, ama xanuun dareemayaasha.

pityriasis (,pidhi’raayasis) n. qob-dhac; xaalado kala duwan oo maqaarku qallalo, diir yaryarna ka kaco, siiba dadka iyo dabjoogta: shedding of flakes or scales.

phthiriasis (tha’raayasis) n., pl. phthiriases (tha’raaya,siiz) eeg pediculosis.

pinworm infection n. caabuq uu keeno dixiri ku dhasha dabada dulkeeda oo hurdo iyo hoyaad kuu diida, sababna u tahay ukumo uu ku dhalayo meeshaas.

uninucleate (,uni’nukliyat) n. hal bu’ le. e.g. The uninucleate sperm cell can fractalize the egg.

nucleate (‘nuuk,liyeyt) v. nucleated; nucleating 1 guntid ama abuurid bu’. e.g. The nucleate stage. 2 qaabayn bu’: to form a nucleus. -nucleation (ˌnuukli’yeyshan) n.; -nucleator (ˈnuukli’yeydhar) n.

amoeboid (a’miiboydh) adj. also ameboid qaab gooryaan leh (qaab amoeba leh); gooryaanka (amoeba) u ege, siiba xagga dhaqaaqa ama qaab-baddalka: resembling an amoeba.

plasmodium (palaaz’mawdhiyam) n., pl. plasmodia (palaaz’mawdhiya) nooc ka mid ah cudurka duumada oo keenta halis dhimasho.

syncytium (sin’sishiyam) n., pl. syncytia (sin’sishiya) 1 unug xambaarsan laba ama dhawr bu’ood. 2 coenocyte. -syncytial (sin’sishiyal)

coenocyte (ˈsiina,saayt) n. 1 unug leh dhawr bu’eed: a cell with multiple nuclei. 2 syncytium. -coenocytic (ˌsiina’sidhik) adj.

multinucleated (,moltii,’niyuukli,yaydhidh) adj. also multinucleate (ˌmaltii’nukliyat) qurub (atom) ama unug (cell) dhawr bu’ le ah: having multiple nuclei. e.g. Multinucleated cells are found in skeletal muscle. Barbardhig binucleate, uninucleate.

binucleate (ˌbaay’nuukliyat) n. or binucleated (ˌbaay’nukli’yeytidh) qurub (atom) ama unug (cell) laba bu’ le ah: having two nuclei.

pneumocystis carinii pneumonia (ˌnuma’sistas ka’raayni,yey nu’mawniya) n. abbr. PCP caabuq uu keenay fangas oo saameeya habka isdifaaca jirka, keenana qufac qalalan, neefgur, iyo xummad.

La Mano Dura n. Gacan Adag ama Gacan Bir ah (“Firm Hand” or “Iron Fist”).

fungal (‘fangal) adj. 1 la xariira ama leh calaamadaha fangas (fungus): pertaining to a fungus. e.g. It was a common fungal disease. 2 fangas ku dhashay.

sarcocystosis (,saarkawsis’tawsas) n. cudur uu keeno dulin noocyabadan oo ku dhaca dad iyo duunyo. kale loogu yeeraa sarcosporidiosis.

sarcosporidiosis (saarkawispa,ridhi’yawsas) n. eeg  sarcocystosis.

sleeping sickness n. muqlo; cudur uu gudbiyo diqsiga (tsetse fly) oo keena, qandho, dhaxan, xibna-xanuun, iyo muqlo.

soil-transmitted Helminths n. gooryaan mindhicireed, lagana qaado ciid wasakhaysan.

strongyloides (istaanja’loydhiiz) n. cudur uu keeno dulinka (nematode or roundworm) oo ku dhaca shinbiro, xamaarato, birri-biyood, dabjoog, iyo dadka.

strongyloidiasis (,istaanja,loy’dhaayasas) n. or  strongyloidosis (ˌistaraanja,loy’dhawsas) or strongyloidosis cudur uu keeno dulinka nematode ama roundworm oo nimdhicirka gala.

urticaria (,ardha’keriya) n. eeg hives. -urticarial (ˌardha’keriyal) adj.

swimmer’s itch n. xajiin daran oo laga qaado dulinka schistosome. kale loogu yeeraa cercarial dermatitis.

cercarial dermatitis n. xajiin uu keeno dulin ilama aragta ah oo ay soo qaadaan shinbiro iyo naasley, waxayna ka soo qaadeen xaaxeeyo (snail) biyo ku nool ah oo lagu dul dhalay dulinkaas.

schistosome (shista,sawm) n. dulin marka hore ku duldhala xaaxeeyo (snail) ku nool biyo macaan, marka uu waynaadana xididdada dhiigga shinbiro iyo naasleyda, dadkana u keena bilharzia. -schistosomal (ˌshista’sawmal) adj.; -schistosome adj.

toxocariasis (,taaksaka’raayasas) n., pl. toxocariasis (,taaksaka’raaya,siiz) cudur uu keeno dulinka nematode oo ah bahada Toxocara.

Toxocara (,taaksa’kaara) n. dulin (nematode worm) oo  caan ku ah eeyaha iyo bisadaha oo dadka u soo gudba.

toxoplasmosis (,taaksa,palaaz’mawsas) n., pl. toxoplasmosis (,taaksa,palaaz’maw,siiz) dulin dadku inta badan ka qaadaan hilib yacyacood ah ama xaarka bisadaha, ilmo uurjiif ahna wuu u gudbikaraa.

trichinosis (tirikanawsas) n., pl. trichinoses (tirikanaw,siiz) cudur laga qaado cunista hilibka ceeriin ama yacyacoodka ah ee qaaday dulinka trichinella.

trichinella (,tirika’nella) n., pl. trichinellae (,tirika’nelli) dulin inta badan ku dhexnoolaada duurjoogta iyo doofaar rabbaayad ah.

Trypanosoma (tiri,paana’sawma) n., pl. trypanosomas or trypanosomata  (tiri,paana’sawmadha) dulin ku noolaada dhiig dad, naasley, xamaarato, birribiyood, shimbiro, iyo kalluun; waxaana gudbiya qaniiyo cayayaan.

vector-borne diseases n. cudurro xayawaanku u soo gudbiyaan dadka, sida Lyme disease, tick-borne encephalitis, West Nile virus, Leishmaniosis and Crimean-Congo haemorrhagic fever.

visceral Larva Migrans n. cudur uu faafiyo  dulinka (roundworms) oo ay xooluhu u soo gudbiyaan dadka, inta badanna saamaysa ciyaalka.

whipworm (‘wip,worm) n. gooryaan (dulin) mindhicirka dadka ku noolaada dhibna u gaysta.

reverse zoonosis n., pl. reverse zoonoses 1 cudur dadku u gudbinkaro xayawaanka. 2 habka dadku ugu gudbiyo cudurka xayawaan.

anthroponosis (,antharapa’nawsas) n., pl. anthroponses (,antharapa’naw,siiz) 1 cudur dadku u gudbinkaro duunyada si caadi ah. 2 habka dadku cudur ugu gubinkaro xayawaan. 3 cudur dadku isku gudbinkaro. kale loogu yeeraa reverse zoonosis, zooanthroponosis. -anthroponotic (ˌaanthrapa’naadhik) adj.

zooanthroponosis (zawa,aantharapa’nawsis) n., pl. zooanthroponises (zawa,aantharapa’naw,siiz) eeg anthroponsis sense 1, reverse zoonosis. –zooanthroponotic (ˌzawa,aantharapa’naadhik) adj.

hymenolepis (,hayama’naalapas) n. dulinka loo badan yahay oo ah gooryaan-mindhicireedka dadka.

pillars of faith n. arkaan al-iimaan; lixda tiir ee Iimaanka.

primary dentition n. ilkaha caananuug.

deciduous teeth n. ilko caananuug; waa 20 ilig. 10 hoose iyo toban kore.

dentition (den’tishan) n. soo bixista iyo dhicista ilkaha.

dental prosthesis n. ilig gacan-ku-samays ah.

interim prosthesis n. ilko joogto ama ma-joogto noqonkara oo la adeegto waqti xaddidan.

removable prosthesis n. ilko la iska bixinkaro. kale loogu yeeraa dentures.

pulpectomy (,pal’pektamii) n., pl. pulpectomies laga saaro iligga dareemayaasha ku jira, lagana nadiifiyo jeermiska.

pulpotomy (,pal’paadhamii) n., pl. pulpotomies qalliin lagu saaro ilig qaarkiis: surgical removal portion of dental pulp.

radicular (ri’dhikilar) adj. 1 la xariira xidid ilig. e.g. Radicular pain. 2 la xariira xidid geed.

radicle (‘raadhikal) n. botany xidid hore ee abuuranka geed. 2 anatomy xididdada iyo dareemayaasha jirka.

hypocotyledonary adj. ka hoosaysa labada caleemood ee ugu horreaysa (cotyledons) ee mir soo baxaysa.

hypocotyl (‘haaypa,kaadhal) n. jirrida mir soo baxday caleenteeda laba-dhagoodka ah, iyo xididka inta u dhaxaysa (hypocotyledonous stem).

decalcification (ˌdhii,kaalsafa’keyshan) n. dhumiya ama saara kaalsiyam (calcium), siiba laf ama ciid. -decalcify (ˌdhii’kaalsafaay) transitive verb.

recalcification (,rii,kaalsafa’keyshan) n. dib-u soocilis isku darkii kaalsiyam (calcium) ka dhumay laf ama dhiig.

apexification n. hab ilig afka qotonkiisa hoose uu furanyahay oo lagu xirio kalshiyam (calcium): close an open tooth root.

apexogenesis n. iliga oo kor laga soo daloosho, si loo badbaadiyo dhuuxa ilig xididkiisu soo karayo.

reimplant (,rii’implaanti) v. reimplanted; reimplanting medical dib-ugu-celin ama dib-ugu-kabid, sida meel ama qayb jirka ka mid ah. e.g. The lost took was reimplanted into its socket.

reimplantation (,rii,im,palan’teyshan) n. qalliin ahaan dib-ugu-kabis ama dib-ugu-celis xibin ama ilig meeshoodii hore. e.g. The dentist recommended reimplantation of the tooth.

orthodontics (,oortha’daantikis) pl. n. [treated as singular] laan ka mid ah shaqada ilkayahannada oo gooni u eegta ilkaha caadiga ka baxsan, sida isku aadanaan la’aantooda (malocclusion). -orthodontic (ˌoortha’daantik) adj.; -orthodontically (ˌoortha’daantiklii) adv.; -orthodontist (ˌoorth’daantisti) n.

salivary gland n. qanjir yar oo calyo u sameeya afkaha.

sialodochoplasty (,saayalaw,dhawka’palaasti) n., pl. sialodochoplasties qalliin lagu hagaajiiyo qanjirka calyada dhala.

sialography (,saaya’laagrafi) n., pl. sialographies raajo lagu eego marinada calyada.

sialolithotomy (,saayalaw’lithaadhami) n., pl. sialolithotomie qalliin qanjirka weyn ee calyada dhagax looga soo saaro.

stomatitis (,istawma’taaydhas) n., pl. stomatitides (ˌistawma’tidhadhiiz) or stomatitises  (ˌistawma’daaydahsiiz)  nooc kasta oo ka mid ah cudurada ku dhaca afka.

astrolithology (,aastaraw’lithoolaji) n. cilimiga gooni u eega dhagaxda cirka ka soo dhacda: science of aerolites.

aerolite (ˈera,laayt) n. dhagaxda cirka ka soo dhacda: meteorite.

ornithotomy n. qalista iyo kala dhanbalka shinbiraha, baaritaan ahaan: dissection of birds.

lithotope (,litha’tawp) n. meelaha dhagaxda isku nooca ah ay ku abuuranyihiin.

morphotomy (moor’faadhimi) n. hab lagu kala qalo noole qaybihiisa, si wax looga ogaado xariirkooda, dhismahooda, fadhigooda, ama shaqadooda: anatomy.

lobotomy (law’baadhamii) n. qalliin maskaxda ah oo lagu sameeyo qof waalan oo qaba cudurka schizophrenia.

supernumerary (,supar’nuuma’rerii) adj. 1 dheeraad ah. e.g. A supernumerary finger. 2 tiro ka badan intii la rabay. e.g. We have supernumerary staff.

temporomandibular joint (‘temparawman’dhibyalar) adj. abbr. TMJ la xariira daanka hoose meesha uu uga xirmo qalka sare.

tomography (taw’maagrafii) n. qalab lagu soo bandhigo qayb ka mid ah jirka dadka oo adeegta fallaaro shucaac (x-rays) ama cod-sare (ultrasound). Barbardhig computed tomography. -tomographic (ˌtawma’garaafik) adj.

tracheotomy (tareyki’yaadhamii) n., pl. tracheotomies qalliin lagu sameeyo hunguriga cad si loofuro marin hawo.

xerostomia (,zira’stawmiya) n. af-qallayl; afka oo aan helin calyo ku filan: dryness of the mouth. kele loogu yeeraa dry mouth.

no-stop flight n. duulimaad aan joogsi lahayn oo toos u taga meeshii loo duulayay.

people mover n. dad-qaad; qalab iswada oo dad u fududeeya meelgayn, siiba gagooyin dayuuradeed iyo magaalada hoose; magayo badan ayuu leeyahay (moving walkway, autowalk, moving sidewalk, travolator, or travelator).

obturator (‘aabta,reydhar) n. qalab gala ama xira meel furan, sida duleelka lafta misig.

occlusal (a’kuluusal) adj. la xariira isku qabadka ilkaha. e.g. The occlusal X-ray analysis showed some discrepancies.

onlay (‘oon,leey) n. 1 dabool ilig dushi la saaro, siiba gaws. 2 dabool qurux ahaan shay loogu duldhajiyo.

orthognathic (,orthag’naathik) adj. la xariira qalliin daanka sare (maxilla) iyo daanka hoose (mandible) la iskula simo. e.g. My wife needs orthognathic surgery.

osteoid (‘aastiyoydh) adj. laf u eg ama aan laga aqoon.

pericoronal (,pera’koranal) adj. la xariira daboolka (crown) la saaray ilig. e.g. Pericoronal infection.

qubit (‘kiyubad) n., pl. qubits. eeg quantum.

rhotic (‘rawdhik) adj. phonetics af-guri ama lahjad af-Engish oo ku dhawaaqda /r/ haddii ay ka soo hormarto shibbane, sida (hard iyo cart) ama haddii ay eray u danbayso, sida (car iyo far). e.g. He speaks a rhotic dialect/accent. -rhoticity (raw’tisidhii) n.
